<!doctype lake><title>尚硅谷大模型技术之 Python（V1.8）</title><meta name="doc-version" content="1" /><meta name="viewport" content="fixed" /><meta name="typography" content="classic" /><meta name="paragraphSpacing" content="relax" /><meta name="defaultFontsize" content="16" /><meta name="autoSpacing" content="1" /><h1 data-lake-id="MP1mY" id="MP1mY"><span data-lake-id="u431ca272" id="u431ca272">第 1 章 必备基础知识</span></h1><h2 data-lake-id="f3OHN" id="f3OHN" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u7f9279a0" id="u7f9279a0">计算机组成</span></h2><h3 data-lake-id="U31iK" id="U31iK" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u94272a45" id="u94272a45">硬件</span></h3><p data-lake-id="u1debaee4" id="u1debaee4"><span data-lake-id="ue629f3ba" id="ue629f3ba"> 计算机硬件主要由五个部分组成，分别是：运算器、控制器、存储器、输入设备、输出设备。</span></p><blockquote data-lake-id="u346c0468" id="u346c0468" class="lake-alert lake-alert-tips"><p data-lake-id="u30d2641d" id="u30d2641d"><strong><span data-lake-id="u59550a80" id="u59550a80">📋</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="u3416c37f" id="u3416c37f">备注 </span></strong><span data-lake-id="u69f722a1" id="u69f722a1">:『运算器』和『控制器』一起组成了</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u5190d261" id="u5190d261" style="color: #AD1A2B">中央处理器（CPU）</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="uc21f2296" id="uc21f2296">。</span></strong></p></blockquote><p data-lake-id="u68af1efd" id="u68af1efd"><card type="inline" name="image" value="data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F35780599%2F1748393561986-f7bc28d7-d244-4777-8a38-03493153f17b.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u228bfcbc-6758-4aef-947b-7a31a5ca109%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u1fd6cc4f-fc18-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A960%2C%22height%22%3A349%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A235495%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1440%2C%22originHeight%22%3A524%2C%22ratio%22%3A1.5%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%83%BD%E5%90%8C%E6%97%B6%E5%BC%80%E5%87%A0%E4%B8%AA%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%2C%E5%8F%96%E5%86%B3%E4%BA%8E%E5%86%85%E5%AD%98%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8F%E8%83%BD%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%A4%9A%E5%B0%91%E4%B8%AA%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%2C%E5%8F%96%E5%86%B3%E4%BA%8E%E7%A1%AC%E7%9B%98%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8F.%22%2C%22x%22%3A70%2C%22y%22%3A458%2C%22width%22%3A859%2C%22height%22%3A30%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%228GB16GB32GB64GB512GB1TB%2C2TB%2C4TB%22%2C%22x%22%3A176%2C%22y%22%3A414%2C%22width%22%3A610%2C%22height%22%3A27%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22(%E7%94%A80%E5%92%8C1%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF)%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%BA%E5%99%A8%E6%8C%87%E4%BB%A4.%22%2C%22x%22%3A618%2C%22y%22%3A42%2C%22width%22%3A403%2C%22height%22%3A34%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22CPU%E5%8F%AA%E8%83%BD%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3%E5%B9%B6%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%8C%E5%88%B6(%22%2C%22x%22%3A272%2C%22y%22%3A41%2C%22width%22%3A376%2C%22height%22%3A33%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%9A%82%E6%97%B6%E6%80%A7%E5%AD%98%E5%82%A8%E6%8C%81%E4%B9%85%E5%8C%96%E5%AD%98%E5%82%A8%22%2C%22x%22%3A359%2C%22y%22%3A322%2C%22width%22%3A264%2C%22height%22%3A30%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%86%99%E9%80%9F%E5%BA%A6%E5%BF%AB%E5%AE%B9%E9%87%8F%E6%AF%94%E8%BE%83%22%2C%22x%22%3A382%2C%22y%22%3A367%2C%22width%22%3A235%2C%22height%22%3A30%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%BF%90%E7%AE%97%E5%99%A8%2B%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E5%99%A8%22%2C%22x%22%3A121%2C%22y%22%3A110%2C%22width%22%3A179%2C%22height%22%3A27%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E5%99%A8%22%2C%22x%22%3A136%2C%22y%22%3A199%2C%22width%22%3A147%2C%22height%22%3A28%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E7%A1%AC%E4%BB%B6%22%2C%22x%22%3A17%2C%22y%22%3A194%2C%22width%22%3A103%2C%22height%22%3A40%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E9%94%AE%E7%9B%98%E9%BC%A0%E6%A0%87%22%2C%22x%22%3A745%2C%22y%22%3A253%2C%22width%22%3A147%2C%22height%22%3A31%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E9%9F%B3%E7%AE%B1%22%2C%22x%22%3A992%2C%22y%22%3A252%2C%22width%22%3A66%2C%22height%22%3A32%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%22%2C%22x%22%3A757%2C%22y%22%3A111%2C%22width%22%3A94%2C%22height%22%3A28%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22CPU%22%2C%22x%22%3A178%2C%22y%22%3A250%2C%22width%22%3A74%2C%22height%22%3A30%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%BE%93%E5%87%BA%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%22%2C%22x%22%3A1085%2C%22y%22%3A110%2C%22width%22%3A103%2C%22height%22%3A30%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%AD%98%E5%82%A8%E5%99%A8%22%2C%22x%22%3A453%2C%22y%22%3A111%2C%22width%22%3A84%2C%22height%22%3A29%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E5%99%A8%22%2C%22x%22%3A1174%2C%22y%22%3A255%2C%22width%22%3A86%2C%22height%22%3A28%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%22%2C%22x%22%3A1148%2C%22y%22%3A208%2C%22width%22%3A120%2C%22height%22%3A19%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E7%A1%AC%E7%9B%98%22%2C%22x%22%3A545%2C%22y%22%3A255%2C%22width%22%3A68%2C%22height%22%3A28%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%86%85%E5%AD%98%22%2C%22x%22%3A358%2C%22y%22%3A254%2C%22width%22%3A64%2C%22height%22%3A30%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22R%22%2C%22x%22%3A1166%2C%22y%22%3A177%2C%22width%22%3A91%2C%22height%22%3A31%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22000%22%2C%22x%22%3A1354%2C%22y%22%3A211%2C%22width%22%3A65%2C%22height%22%3A23%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Atrue%2C%22title%22%3A%22%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E7%A1%AC%E4%BB%B6%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%2352514f%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Igm7T%22%7D"></card></p><blockquote data-lake-id="u42eae817" id="u42eae817" class="lake-alert lake-alert-color4"><p data-lake-id="u760e8f5e" id="u760e8f5e"><span data-lake-id="u90931ce1" id="u90931ce1">📢</span><strong><span data-lake-id="uce12b7fe" id="uce12b7fe" style="color: #AD1A2B">注意：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="ue3532a1b" id="ue3532a1b">计算机的 CPU 只能理解并执行</span><strong><span data-lake-id="uacfbdcc3" id="uacfbdcc3" style="color: #AD1A2B">二进制（用 0和1表示信息）</span></strong><span data-lake-id="ucf6ab7e7" id="ucf6ab7e7">的</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u4d70dbb8" id="u4d70dbb8" style="color: #AD1A2B">机器指令</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u9cdab026" id="u9cdab026">。</span></p></blockquote><blockquote data-lake-id="u5bce321e" id="u5bce321e" class="lake-alert lake-alert-info"><p data-lake-id="u65290f29" id="u65290f29"><strong><span data-lake-id="u4f4ec405" id="u4f4ec405">内存 </span></strong><span data-lake-id="uaa783838" id="uaa783838">VS</span><strong><span data-lake-id="uadd8dfcb" id="uadd8dfcb"> 硬盘：</span></strong></p><ul list="uda2ae7ef"><li fid="u1bc7b556" data-lake-id="u6858350c" id="u6858350c"><span data-lake-id="u6571bcde" id="u6571bcde">硬盘：持久化存储，读写速度不如内存快，但容量通常比较大（500GB、1TB、2TB 等）。</span></li><li fid="u1bc7b556" data-lake-id="ueadc1c8a" id="ueadc1c8a"><span data-lake-id="u39b04189" id="u39b04189">内存：暂时性存储，读写速度快，但容量通常不如硬盘大（8GB、16GB、32GB、64GB 等）。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id="u50ea1c05" id="u50ea1c05"><strong><span data-lake-id="u066bf6e9" id="u066bf6e9">通俗理解</span></strong><span data-lake-id="uf3889bea" id="uf3889bea">：能安装多少个游戏，取决于硬盘的大小；能同时开几个游戏，取决于内存的大小。</span></p></blockquote><table data-lake-id="lpJCS" id="lpJCS" margin="true" col-head="rgba(8,84,166,1);#FFFFFF" class="lake-table" style="width: 736px"><colgroup><col width="106"><col width="630"></colgroup><tbody><tr data-lake-id="u0eee259d" id="u0eee259d" style="height: 66px"><td data-lake-id="udcace294" id="udcace294" style="vertical-align: middle"><p data-lake-id="u0b2e6322" id="u0b2e6322" style="text-align: center"><span data-lake-id="u52ee3e5e" id="u52ee3e5e">运算器</span></p></td><td data-lake-id="u630b5fcc" id="u630b5fcc"><p data-lake-id="u732dbb49" id="u732dbb49" style="text-align: justify"><span data-lake-id="u81f09c22" id="u81f09c22">运算器（简称：ALU），专门负责执行各种『算术运算』和『逻辑运算』，它需要与控制单元、寄存器等紧密配合。</span></p></td></tr><tr data-lake-id="ud1e2e866" id="ud1e2e866"><td data-lake-id="u0e1053e9" id="u0e1053e9" style="vertical-align: middle"><p data-lake-id="u1f56b4b1" id="u1f56b4b1" style="text-align: center"><span data-lake-id="u0e50e351" id="u0e50e351">控制器</span></p></td><td data-lake-id="u747a2fdc" id="u747a2fdc"><p data-lake-id="uea3ed877" id="uea3ed877" style="text-align: justify"><span data-lake-id="ud3736cd1" id="ud3736cd1">计算机的控制中心，它指挥计算机各部分协调地工作，保证计算机按照预先规定的任务，有条不紊地进行操作及处理。</span></p></td></tr><tr data-lake-id="uc7875e4b" id="uc7875e4b" style="height: 66px"><td data-lake-id="uf6948ac3" id="uf6948ac3" style="vertical-align: middle"><p data-lake-id="u3ac02511" id="u3ac02511" style="text-align: center"><span data-lake-id="u1f4e99e6" id="u1f4e99e6">存储器</span></p></td><td data-lake-id="uce373ad1" id="uce373ad1"><p data-lake-id="u87ddf5af" id="u87ddf5af" style="text-align: justify"><span data-lake-id="ue8dd0bd3" id="ue8dd0bd3">计算机中的“资料库”，它既保存程序指令，又保存数据，各个硬件在需要访问或更新数据时，都会与它打交道，有了存储器，计算机才有“记忆”。</span></p></td></tr><tr data-lake-id="ue39076d0" id="ue39076d0"><td data-lake-id="u1f7c6191" id="u1f7c6191" style="vertical-align: middle"><p data-lake-id="u852c680c" id="u852c680c" style="text-align: center"><span data-lake-id="uf34682c2" id="uf34682c2">输入设备</span></p></td><td data-lake-id="uf3e51781" id="uf3e51781"><p data-lake-id="u984d4814" id="u984d4814" style="text-align: justify"><span data-lake-id="ub3c7e827" id="ub3c7e827">向计算机输入数据和信息的设备，是计算机与外界通信的桥梁。</span></p></td></tr><tr data-lake-id="u9384fde7" id="u9384fde7"><td data-lake-id="ud1fcc178" id="ud1fcc178" style="vertical-align: middle"><p data-lake-id="u0c737930" id="u0c737930" style="text-align: center"><span data-lake-id="uff6c56ef" id="uff6c56ef">输出设备</span></p></td><td data-lake-id="u4ae28ebb" id="u4ae28ebb"><p data-lake-id="uc3b5b01a" id="uc3b5b01a" style="text-align: justify"><span data-lake-id="ub4ba04e1" id="ub4ba04e1">用于输出计算机执行任务的结果，把各种结果数据或信息以：数字、字符、图像、声音等形式表示出来。</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><h3 data-lake-id="GwJMR" id="GwJMR" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u2b15068d" id="u2b15068d">软件</span></h3><p data-lake-id="uf6f3132b" id="uf6f3132b"><span data-lake-id="u0f7c6517" id="u0f7c6517">计算机软件主要分为：系统软件、应用软件。</span></p><p data-lake-id="ue703cd57" id="ue703cd57"><card type="inline" name="image" value="data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F35780599%2F1748308945147-646011dc-5d6d-4416-8fd4-d35e8dc4af2c.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ufd797de8-ede2-4f8a-9bfb-144f9801672%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u4b2e2bf4-3cf0-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A418.6500244140625%2C%22height%22%3A139%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A91719%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1164%2C%22originHeight%22%3A386%2C%22ratio%22%3A1.5%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6%22%2C%22x%22%3A198%2C%22y%22%3A246%2C%22width%22%3A177%2C%22height%22%3A45%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6%22%2C%22x%22%3A199%2C%22y%22%3A71%2C%22width%22%3A176%2C%22height%22%3A41%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22WINDOWS%22%2C%22x%22%3A414%2C%22y%22%3A123%2C%22width%22%3A113%2C%22height%22%3A22%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%B5%8F%E8%A7%88%E5%99%A8%22%2C%22x%22%3A892%2C%22y%22%3A313%2C%22width%22%3A74%2C%22height%22%3A28%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22ANDROID%22%2C%22x%22%3A724%2C%22y%22%3A123%2C%22width%22%3A95%2C%22height%22%3A22%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6%22%2C%22x%22%3A1%2C%22y%22%3A160%2C%22width%22%3A92%2C%22height%22%3A43%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22LINUX%22%2C%22x%22%3A586%2C%22y%22%3A124%2C%22width%22%3A67%2C%22height%22%3A21%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22STEAM%22%2C%22x%22%3A585%2C%22y%22%3A318%2C%22width%22%3A73%2C%22height%22%3A21%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22WORD%22%2C%22x%22%3A750%2C%22y%22%3A314%2C%22width%22%3A69%2C%22height%22%3A26%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%22%2C%22x%22%3A436%2C%22y%22%3A313%2C%22width%22%3A56%2C%22height%22%3A28%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22W%22%2C%22x%22%3A729%2C%22y%22%3A250%2C%22width%22%3A42%2C%22height%22%3A33%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22IOS%22%2C%22x%22%3A896%2C%22y%22%3A120%2C%22width%22%3A52%2C%22height%22%3A24%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Atrue%2C%22title%22%3A%22%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23535251%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22kJCUG%22%7D"></card></p><table data-lake-id="j7LvA" id="j7LvA" margin="true" width-mode="contain" col-head="rgba(8,84,166,1);#FFFFFF" class="lake-table" style="width: 721px"><colgroup><col width="100"><col width="621"></colgroup><tbody><tr data-lake-id="u2c7bf46d" id="u2c7bf46d" style="height: 66px"><td data-lake-id="u9d0599dc" id="u9d0599dc" style="vertical-align: middle"><p data-lake-id="uc9088829" id="uc9088829" style="text-align: center"><span data-lake-id="ud00fdaa6" id="ud00fdaa6">系统软件</span></p></td><td data-lake-id="ubff95424" id="ubff95424"><p data-lake-id="u6bfbc391" id="u6bfbc391" style="text-align: justify"><span data-lake-id="u2a1b7675" id="u2a1b7675" style="color: rgb(36, 41, 47)">直接管理和控制计算机硬件的软件，为应用软件提供运行平台，它负责协调硬件资源（如内存、处理器）并提供通用服务，例如：文件管理、设备控制、任务调度。</span></p></td></tr><tr data-lake-id="u9be1a079" id="u9be1a079" style="height: 66px"><td data-lake-id="uf1d40603" id="uf1d40603" style="vertical-align: middle"><p data-lake-id="ub884eff6" id="ub884eff6" style="text-align: center"><span data-lake-id="u1cd9e1e6" id="u1cd9e1e6">应用软件</span></p></td><td data-lake-id="ue5d559f4" id="ue5d559f4"><p data-lake-id="u3c15d70e" id="u3c15d70e" style="text-align: justify"><span data-lake-id="ued9b6949" id="ued9b6949" style="color: rgb(36, 41, 47)">用于执行特定任务的软件，满足用户的具体需求，如：文档编辑、数据分析、娱乐等，它依赖系统软件提供的资源和服务。</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><h2 data-lake-id="G4xMc" id="G4xMc" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u2601703e" id="u2601703e">计算机语言、代码、程序</span></h2><p data-lake-id="ue2b3ad63" id="ue2b3ad63"><card type="inline" name="image" value="data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F35780599%2F1749354580589-afaa798a-9e57-4d13-9162-4d73fcd80103.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u7873941c-1a28-456e-aacc-172787ea0d9%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u1699432d-af50-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A680.77502441406