5A">Pycharm 已经没有专业版了，现在的叫：完整版（也叫：统一版），完整版中包含：付费功能+ 免费功能，付费功能可以免费试用 30 天，到期不付费的话，软件依然可以打开，并且免费的功能也都能正常使用，所以此处推荐各位下载完整版。如果不想使用完整版，也可以下载社区版，具体下载方式，请参考视频教程。</span></p></blockquote><p data-lake-id="u0c66c6f4" id="u0c66c6f4"><span data-lake-id="uafc3be26" id="uafc3be26">2️⃣</span><span data-lake-id="u6d4c5998" id="u6d4c5998">以管理员身份运行安装包文件，点击下一步进行安装</span></p><p data-lake-id="u9c4c0b8e" id="u9c4c0b8e"><card type="inline" name="image" value="data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F35780599%2F1742542228520-a9798475-aa93-4062-af5e-d0436552a89f.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ueeb6f0a4-24aa-4cdb-82ef-ec77906c22d%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22ud90da455-653c-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A498.3333740234375%2C%22height%22%3A359%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A106744%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A749%2C%22originHeight%22%3A539%2C%22ratio%22%3A1.5%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22PYCHARM%20%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%20PYCHARM%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%20%E6%AC%A2%E8%BF%8E%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%20PC%20%E6%AD%A4%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E5%B0%86%E5%BC%95%E5%AF%BC%E4%BD%A0%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90PYCHARM%20%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85.%20%E5%9C%A8%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E4%B9%8B%E5%89%8D%2C%E8%AF%B7%E5%85%88%E5%85%B3%E9%97%AD%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F.%E8%BF%99%E5%B0%86%E7%A1%AE%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%89%20%E8%A3%85%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E8%83%BD%E5%A4%9F%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E6%89%80%E9%9C%80%E7%9A%84%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%2C%E4%BB%8E%E8%80%8C%E9%81%BF%E5%85%8D%E5%9C%A8%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%90%8E%E9%87%8D%20%E6%96%B0%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%9C%BA.%20%E7%82%B9%E5%87%BB%5B%E4%B8%8B%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5(N)%5D%E7%BB%A7%E7%BB%AD.%20%E4%B8%8B%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5(N)%20%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88(C)%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22x%22%3A33%2C%22y%22%3A8%2C%22width%22%3A115%2C%22height%22%3A21%2C%22text