d="ua80a48f8">概述 </span></h3><p data-lake-id="uf664bcf3" id="uf664bcf3"><span data-lake-id="uf4dd2e62" id="uf4dd2e62">来看这样一个场景：老师让学生把：姓名、年龄、体重写在纸上，纸上的文字，就是学生想要表达的内容，这些内容不需要计算、也不需要转换，就是字面上的含义，一看就能理解。</span></p><p data-lake-id="ub2bded6f" id="ub2bded6f"><card type="inline" name="image" value="data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F35780599%2F1746586662422-1232a3b9-69df-4fee-8f4b-5f28974bbfe9.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22uc0b3552f-4950-456e-b7ca-99059d44c41%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22uf29ec3d3-71d3-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A136%2C%22height%22%3A175%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A33459%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A400%2C%22originHeight%22%3A515%2C%22ratio%22%3A1.5%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22shadow%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%BC%A0%E4%BA%91%22%2C%22x%22%3A93%2C%22y%22%3A97%2C%22width%22%3A243%2C%22height%22%3A99%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%2265.2%22%2C%22x%22%3A100%2C%22y%22%3A324%2C%22width%22%3A125%2C%22height%22%3A72%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%228%22%2C%22x%22%3A103%2C%22y%22%3A201%2C%22width%22%3A57%2C%22height%22%3A137%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0.0597%2C0.0435%2C0.9361%2C0.9627%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23f4f4f4%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Xi1W3%22%7D"></card><span data-lake-id="uea83e5cb" id="uea83e5cb"> </span><card type="inline" name="image" value="data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F35780599%2F1747966924322-0759f53e-74c9-41e2-83d1-1d29a4885591.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u0e56a40b-fcec-4ba2-80fb-40c8b36413d%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u30f40c27-c0be-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A121%2C%22height%22%3A183%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A26838%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A301%2C%22originHeight%22%3A455%2C%22ratio%22%3A1.6500000953674316%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22shadow%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%9D%8E%E5%9B%9B%22%2C%22x%22%3A32%2C%22y%22%3A59%2C%22width%22%3A197%2C%22height%22%3A92%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%224.6%22%2C%22x%22%3A53%2C%22y%22%3A301%2C%22width%22%3A135%2C%22height%22%3A64%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%2222%22%2C%22x%22%3A52%2C%22y%22%3A190%2C%22width%22%3A80%2C%22height%22%3A60%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23f4f4f4%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22noG7h%22%7D"></card><span data-lake-id="ub5f3edb9" id="ub5f3edb9"> </span><card type="inline" name="image" value="data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F35780599%2F1747966935103-3e14aaeb-2f53-40b1-a9e6-ec7ace4c060d.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22uab939f5c-8c43-4fd4-b5ec-8e1142d5da8%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u30f40c27-c0be-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A121%2C%22height%22%3A175%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A28045%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A316%2C%22originHeight%22%3A458%2C%22ratio%22%3A1.6500000953674316%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22shadow%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E7%8E%8B%E4%BA%94%22%2C%22x%22%3A50%2C%22y%22%3A68%2C%22width%22%3A228%2C%22height%22%3A74%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%225%22%2C%22x%22%3A73%2C%22y%22%3A187%2C%22width%22%3A78%2C%22height%22%3A70%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%2280%22%2C%22x%22%3A66%2C%22y%22%3A283%2C%22width%22%3A75%2C%22height%22%3A69%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C0.9522%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23f7f7f7%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22EjKIx%22%7D"></card></p><p data-lake-id="u86ef5f61" id="u86ef5f61"><span data-lake-id="ua2b7d4ca" id="ua2b7d4ca">在程序中，也有上述这些“写出来就能被理解”的内容，这些内容在程序中叫做</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u3eae57f0" id="u3eae57f0" style="color: #AD1A2B">字面量</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u7f2521bf" id="u7f2521bf">，即：字面量就是直接写在代码中的“具体值”。</span></p><h3 data-lake-id="fuMxH" id="fuMxH" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u4fbdf2d6" id="u4fbdf2d6">写法</span></h3><p data-lake-id="u9be21d8d" id="u9be21d8d"><span data-lake-id="u529ae9af" id="u529ae9af">下面代码中的内容，都是字面量。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%E5%AD%97%E9%9D%A2%E9%87%8F%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22'%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89'%5Cn18%5Cn65.2%5Cn%5Cn'%E6%9D%8E%E5%9B%9B'%5Cn22%5Cn74.6%5Cn%5Cn'%E7%8E%8B%E4%BA%94'%5Cn25%5Cn80%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%E5%AD%97%E9%9D%A2%E9%87%8F%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22AkkdG%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><blockquote data-lake-id="ufb63ec0a" id="ufb63ec0a" class="lake-alert lake-alert-info"><p data-lake-id="u434926b1" id="u434926b1"><span data-lake-id="u09a8be72" id="u09a8be72">以上代码中的 </span><code data-lake-id="u14f1cfce" id="u14f1cfce"><span data-lake-id="ub15dc2fa" id="ub15dc2fa">'张三'</span></code><span data-lake-id="u6bb42192" id="u6bb42192">、</span><code data-lake-id="u7b289aa3" id="u7b289aa3"><span data-lake-id="u6a9939de" id="u6a9939de">'李四'</span></code><span data-lake-id="ud9fdd34a" id="ud9fdd34a">、</span><code data-lake-id="u5137c0b7" id="u5137c0b7"><span data-lake-id="ucac86124" id="ucac86124">'王五'</span></code><span data-lake-id="u4037ebe5" id="u4037ebe5"> 均为字符串。所谓字符串，就是由“字符”组成的“串”。例如，字符串 </span><code data-lake-id="u9a7a6a14" id="u9a7a6a14"><span data-lake-id="u30bcd47b" id="u30bcd47b">'张三'</span></code><span data-lake-id="u2a0a6aa1" id="u2a0a6aa1"> 由 </span><code data-lake-id="uba4be7ee" id="uba4be7ee"><span data-lake-id="uec03621a" id="uec03621a">'张</span></code><span data-lake-id="u30b8cd8c" id="u30b8cd8c">' 和 </span><code data-lake-id="u6f2d1362" id="u6f2d1362"><span data-lake-id="u3582f0f7" id="u3582f0f7">'三'</span></code><span data-lake-id="ua2ba745d" id="ua2ba745d"> 两个字符构成。</span></p><p data-lake-id="u8f5f4ca0" id="u8f5f4ca0"><span data-lake-id="ua9eb4afe" id="ua9eb4afe">从本质上看，字符串属于文本类型，可以由任意数量的字符组成——无论是中文、英文、数字，还是各种符号。此处我们只需对字符串的概念有初步认识，后续课程中将对其进行详细讲解。</span></p></blockquote><blockquote data-lake-id="uf9371ec0" id="uf9371ec0" class="lake-alert lake-alert-color4"><p data-lake-id="u77de2265" id="u77de2265"><span data-lake-id="u4268de18" id="u4268de18">📢</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u0bcbb220" id="u0bcbb220" style="color: #AD1A2B">注意：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="ue60ebcfc" id="ue60ebcfc">字符串必须要放到引号中，使用：单引号、双引号、三个单引号、三个双引号都可以，但必须是英文的引号。</span></p></blockquote><blockquote data-lake-id="u9a6ad340" id="u9a6ad340" class="lake-alert lake-alert-tips"><p data-lake-id="u182fd54f" id="u182fd54f"><strong><span data-lake-id="u4940b6b7" id="u4940b6b7">📋</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="u9ffcc5a7" id="u9ffcc5a7">备注：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="udb9e0c63" id="udb9e0c63">写在 Python 文件头部的字符串，会被自动识别成 docstring（文档字符串），文档字符串的主要作用是：对当前 Python 文件进行说明，且文档字符串必须用三个双引号。</span></p></blockquote><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%B2%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%5C%22%5C%22%5C%22%E8%BF%99%E6%98%AF%E6%88%91%E5%86%99%E7%9A%84%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AAPython%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%5C%22%5C%22%5C%22%5Cn%5Cn'%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89'%5Cn18%5Cn65.2%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%B2%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22iqOWk%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h2 data-lake-id="kQdl4" id="kQdl4" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u8a613a72" id="u8a613a72">变量与常量</span></h2><h3 data-lake-id="WFWqW" id="WFWqW" data-lake-index-type="2"><strong><span data-lake-id="u9587624d" id="u9587624d" class="lake-fontsize-14">变量</span></strong></h3><details data-lake-id="u2ffa688c" id="u2ffa688c" open="true" class="lake-collapse"><summary data-lake-id="uf8b5f87e" id="uf8b5f87e" class="lake-summary"><span data-lake-id="udf1d9fcd" id="udf1d9fcd">1️⃣</span><strong><span data-lake-id="ua4bec550" id="ua4bec550">前情回顾</span></strong></summary><p data-lake-id="ud6485664" id="ud6485664"><span data-lake-id="uf2d6fede" id="uf2d6fede">在上一节中，我们通过字面量的形式，记录了张三的体重，例如：</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%2265.2%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22cwYQE%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="ucbd2f2a2" id="ucbd2f2a2"><span data-lake-id="u9f9e2ece" id="u9f9e2ece">现在需要打印一些体重相关的内容，代码如下：</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22print('%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%93%E9%87%8D%E6%98%AF'%2C%2065.2)%5Cnprint('%E5%AF%B9%E4%BA%8E'%2C%2065.2%2C%20'%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%AA%E4%BD%93%E9%87%8D%EF%BC%8C%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89%E8%A7%89%E5%BE%97%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%A1%E6%84%8F')%5Cnprint('%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89%E5%86%B3%E5%AE%9A%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E5%87%8F%E8%82%A5%EF%BC%8C%E5%B8%8C%E6%9C%9B%E4%BD%93%E9%87%8D%E6%AF%94'%2C%2065.2%2C%20'%E8%BF%98%E8%A6%81%E5%B0%8F')%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22zQVsF%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><blockquote data-lake-id="u58a6afb4" id="u58a6afb4" class="lake-alert lake-alert-info"><p data-lake-id="ub2bbea8e" id="ub2bbea8e"><strong><span data-lake-id="uc7b905e9" id="uc7b905e9">📌</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="ue2bfae01" id="ue2bfae01">小贴士：</span></strong></p><ol list="ud2f49e87"><li fid="ua9674b23" data-lake-id="u9236dc1e" id="u9236dc1e"><span data-lake-id="u5afd0515" id="u5afd0515">使用</span><code data-lake-id="u151d00c5" id="u151d00c5"><span data-lake-id="udee0fcb8" id="udee0fcb8">print(内容)</span></code><span data-lake-id="u27e7c5ae" id="u27e7c5ae">可以输出内容（也叫：打印内容）这里说的“打印”不是打印在纸上，而是指：把内容呈现在控制台上。</span></li><li fid="ua9674b23" data-lake-id="ubd70ce30" id="ubd70ce30"><span data-lake-id="ud1eaff40" id="ud1eaff40">使用</span><code data-lake-id="u6b232765" id="u6b232765"><span data-lake-id="u26d219bb" id="u26d219bb">print(内容1, 内容2, 内容3)</span></code><span data-lake-id="u05f8b44b" id="u05f8b44b">可以输出多个内容，不同内容之间用逗号做分隔，输出的多个内容默认会在同一行，且输出的多个内容之间会有一个空格。</span></li></ol></blockquote><blockquote data-lake-id="u648531f9" id="u648531f9" class="lake-alert lake-alert-tips"><p data-lake-id="uaf38fabe" id="uaf38fabe"><span data-lake-id="uc62d641b" id="uc62d641b">📋</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u752296d1" id="u752296d1">备注：</span></strong><code data-lake-id="u73414cd6" id="u73414cd6"><span data-lake-id="u8ac6129f" id="u8ac6129f">print()</span></code><span data-lake-id="u5878f5c4" id="u5878f5c4">还有很多使用细节和技巧，后面会逐步介绍。</span></p></blockquote><p data-lake-id="u82c0b596" id="u82c0b596"><span data-lake-id="u8a795b2a" id="u8a795b2a">我们会发现，代码中的</span><code data-lake-id="uedfbd2f6" id="uedfbd2f6"><span data-lake-id="ubb3727ff" id="ubb3727ff">65.2</span></code><span data-lake-id="u50d0007b" id="u50d0007b">被使用了 3 次，当要修改张三的体重为</span><code data-lake-id="u08b05a70" id="u08b05a70"><span data-lake-id="u1bc4c0b0" id="u1bc4c0b0">64.2</span></code><span data-lake-id="u132a41bf" id="u132a41bf">时，就需要手动修改 3 个地方，修改起来会很麻烦，就像下面这样：</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22print('%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%93%E9%87%8D%E6%98%AF'%2C%2064.2)%5Cnprint('%E5%AF%B9%E4%BA%8E'%2C%2064.2%2C%20'%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%AA%E4%BD%93%E9%87%8D%EF%BC%8C%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89%E8%A7%89%E5%BE%97%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%A1%E6%84%8F')%5Cnprint('%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89%E5%86%B3%E5%AE%9A%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E5%87%8F%E8%82%A5%EF%BC%8C%E5%B8%8C%E6%9C%9B%E4%BD%93%E9%87%8D%E6%AF%94'%2C%2064.2%2C%20'%E8%BF%98%E8%A6%81%E5%B0%8F')%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22k5GmH%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card></details><details data-lake-id="uc9c08d53" id="uc9c08d53" open="true" class="lake-collapse"><summary data-lake-id="udbaa343f" id="udbaa343f" class="lake-summary"><strong><span data-lake-id="u93bcbd97" id="u93bcbd97">2️⃣</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="u3e3d5211" id="u3e3d5211">什么是变量？</span></strong></summary><p data-lake-id="u2769ee5a" id="u2769ee5a"><span data-lake-id="uf74ca470" id="uf74ca470">变量是数据的“代号”它可以和数据建立绑定关系，通过变量可以使用数据，或更新数据，之所以叫变量，是因为：它和某个值的绑定关系，可以随时改变。</span></p><p data-lake-id="u2a4cdd43" id="u2a4cdd43"><span data-lake-id="uf29e7445" id="uf29e7445">例如：在上述代码中，我们可以把体重值和某个『</span><strong><span data-lake-id="uef75f304" id="uef75f304" style="color: #AD1A2B">变量</span></strong><span data-lake-id="ueddde48a" id="ueddde48a">』建立一个『</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u687ab287" id="u687ab287" style="color: #AD1A2B">绑定关系</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="u72bd4729" id="u72bd4729">』</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u7b42c0a6" id="u7b42c0a6">，以后用到体重的时候，直接“呼唤”这个变量就可以了。</span></p></details><details data-lake-id="u1e7d4b7a" id="u1e7d4b7a" open="true" class="lake-collapse"><summary data-lake-id="u953a2d22" id="u953a2d22" class="lake-summary"><span data-lake-id="uc7b93065" id="uc7b93065">3️⃣</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u7aa7eb2a" id="u7aa7eb2a">具体语法</span></strong></summary><p data-lake-id="u23315327" id="u23315327"><span data-lake-id="ue264df25" id="ue264df25">语法为：</span><code data-lake-id="u3d29124c" id="u3d29124c"><span data-lake-id="u438bc5e8" id="u438bc5e8">变量名 = 值</span></code><span data-lake-id="u55f21a74" id="u55f21a74">，例如下面代码中的：</span><code data-lake-id="u9b87fb39" id="u9b87fb39"><span data-lake-id="u28e2ec4d" id="u28e2ec4d">name</span></code><span data-lake-id="u3973220d" id="u3973220d">、</span><code data-lake-id="u7c7b9c10" id="u7c7b9c10"><span data-lake-id="u756abb59" id="u756abb59">age</span></code><span data-lake-id="u5c1f57d0" id="u5c1f57d0">、</span><code data-lake-id="u671bc2aa" id="u671bc2aa"><span data-lake-id="ucdbbd140" id="ucdbbd140">weight</span></code><span data-lake-id="u15b76bb8" id="u15b76bb8">都是变量。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22name%20%3D%20'%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89'%5Cnage%20%3D%2018%5Cnweight%20%3D%2065.2%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22zS4o7%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><blockquote data-lake-id="uc8f85dd9" id="uc8f85dd9" class="lake-alert lake-alert-color4"><p data-lake-id="uf8817712" id="uf8817712"><span data-lake-id="ub9f79964" id="ub9f79964">📢</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u33cf835b" id="u33cf835b" style="color: #AD1A2B">注意：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u01d70ab4" id="u01d70ab4">变量名不需要加引号！</span></p></blockquote></details><details data-lake-id="uc162d952" id="uc162d952" open="true" class="lake-collapse"><summary data-lake-id="u375e440e" id="u375e440e" class="lake-summary"><span data-lake-id="u60d30503" id="u60d30503">4️⃣</span><strong><span data-lake-id="ued5603b6" id="ued5603b6">示例代码</span></strong></summary><p data-lake-id="uaf98c2dc" id="uaf98c2dc"><span data-lake-id="u05c77da6" id="u05c77da6">使用</span><code data-lake-id="ue7ebda88" id="ue7ebda88"><span data-lake-id="ue05ed65d" id="ue05ed65d">weight</span></code><span data-lake-id="u1abbacc1" id="u1abbacc1">变量存储体重值，并在后续代码中，多次使用</span><code data-lake-id="ud678cca1" id="ud678cca1"><span data-lake-id="u9969ea00" id="u9969ea00">weigth</span></code><span data-lake-id="u4d19e8c6" id="u4d19e8c6">变量。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22weight%20%3D%2065.2%5Cn%5Cnprint('%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%93%E9%87%8D%E6%98%AF'%2C%20weight)%5Cnprint('%E5%AF%B9%E4%BA%8E'%2C%20weight%2C%20'%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%AA%E4%BD%93%E9%87%8D%EF%BC%8C%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89%E8%A7%89%E5%BE%97%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%A1%E6%84%8F')%5Cnprint('%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89%E5%86%B3%E5%AE%9A%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E5%87%8F%E8%82%A5%EF%BC%8C%E5%B8%8C%E6%9C%9B%E4%BD%93%E9%87%8D%E6%AF%94'%2C%20weight%2C%20'%E8%BF%98%E8%A6%81%E5%B0%8F')%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22HIxGR%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="uc98495d9" id="uc98495d9"><span data-lake-id="u401dd5cd" id="u401dd5cd">需要修改体重时，通过</span><code data-lake-id="u1715394d" id="u1715394d"><span data-lake-id="u0ae686ca" id="u0ae686ca">weight</span></code><span data-lake-id="u5fe9d591" id="u5fe9d591">就可以修改，修改后再去使用</span><code data-lake-id="uc9b9a596" id="uc9b9a596"><span data-lake-id="ub0032406" id="ub0032406">weight</span></code><span data-lake-id="uf868cbf1" id="uf868cbf1">时，就是修改后的值了。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22weight%20%3D%2065.2%5Cnweight%20%3D%2064.2%5Cn%5Cnprint('%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%93%E9%87%8D%E6%98%AF'%2C%20weight)%5Cnprint('%E5%AF%B9%E4%BA%8E'%2C%20weight%2C%20'%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%AA%E4%BD%93%E9%87%8D%EF%BC%8C%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89%E8%A7%89%E5%BE%97%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%A1%E6%84%8F')%5Cnprint('%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89%E5%86%B3%E5%AE%9A%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E5%87%8F%E8%82%A5%EF%BC%8C%E5%B8%8C%E6%9C%9B%E4%BD%93%E9%87%8D%E6%AF%94'%2C%20weight%2C%20'%E8%BF%98%E8%A6%81%E5%B0%8F')%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22KjYR9%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card></details><details data-lake-id="ua1672292" id="ua1672292" open="true" class="lake-collapse"><summary data-lake-id="u41357e05" id="u41357e05" class="lake-summary"><span data-lake-id="ud6649f22" id="ud6649f22">5️⃣</span><strong><span data-lake-id="uc5bf62cc" id="uc5bf62cc">几个关键点</span></strong></summary><blockquote data-lake-id="u47a08d2a" id="u47a08d2a" class="lake-alert lake-alert-info"><ol list="u607f0b0e"><li fid="ua5b29c10" data-lake-id="u1a5c4ca6" id="u1a5c4ca6"><span data-lake-id="u77f41804" id="u77f41804">在数学中，像 </span><code data-lake-id="u319a6f63" id="u319a6f63"><span data-lake-id="u08a42289" id="u08a42289">1 + 1 = 2</span></code><span data-lake-id="u1afb2aae" id="u1afb2aae">这样的等式表示：等号左边的</span><code data-lake-id="ubf2d59aa" id="ubf2d59aa"><span data-lake-id="u26d416d2" id="u26d416d2">1 + 1</span></code><span data-lake-id="u7c3cf077" id="u7c3cf077">是具体的运算过程，等号右边的</span><code data-lake-id="u8ef31926" id="u8ef31926"><span data-lake-id="udf0132f1" id="udf0132f1">2</span></code><span data-lake-id="u9ef0db95" id="u9ef0db95">是该运算的结果。</span></li><li fid="ua5b29c10" data-lake-id="ubac9f55b" id="ubac9f55b"><span data-lake-id="u3e1f1b31" id="u3e1f1b31">在代码</span><code data-lake-id="u5754be0f" id="u5754be0f"><span data-lake-id="u56ec46f0" id="u56ec46f0">age = 18</span></code><span data-lake-id="u60aed128" id="u60aed128">中，等号表示：将等号</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u184d1dcd" id="u184d1dcd" style="color: #117CEE">右侧的值</span></strong><span data-lake-id="uca3faf7f" id="uca3faf7f">与</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u8948a04b" id="u8948a04b" style="color: #117CEE">左侧的变量</span></strong><span data-lake-id="ud902e816" id="ud902e816">建立</span><strong><span data-lake-id="uc04125a8" id="uc04125a8" style="color: #117CEE">绑定关系</span></strong><span data-lake-id="ud63c2b5d" id="ud63c2b5d">。因此，当程序中需要表示年龄 </span><code data-lake-id="u8f3c01f5" id="u8f3c01f5"><span data-lake-id="ube22b43e" id="ube22b43e">18</span></code><span data-lake-id="u702648e0" id="u702648e0">时，可以使用变量</span><code data-lake-id="ud0684be7" id="ud0684be7"><span data-lake-id="u9eaaada1" id="u9eaaada1">age</span></code><span data-lake-id="u1aff272e" id="u1aff272e">；同样，也可以通过</span><code data-lake-id="uf30e347d" id="uf30e347d"><span data-lake-id="ud248a660" id="ud248a660">age</span></code><span data-lake-id="u3f2b106d" id="u3f2b106d">来修改该数值。</span></li><li fid="ua5b29c10" data-lake-id="u22cebfb5" id="u22cebfb5"><code data-lake-id="u4619cc50" id="u4619cc50"><span data-lake-id="u8e952212" id="u8e952212">age = 18</span></code><span data-lake-id="uc03fe559" id="uc03fe559">这一行代码也被称为“赋值语句”，意思是将右侧的</span><code data-lake-id="u1ec3a6e9" id="u1ec3a6e9"><span data-lake-id="uadef50d8" id="uadef50d8">18</span></code><span data-lake-id="u7689e7b9" id="u7689e7b9">赋给变量</span><code data-lake-id="u3062c0bf" id="u3062c0bf"><span data-lake-id="u49579506" id="u49579506">age</span></code><span data-lake-id="ub5980a72" id="ub5980a72">。</span></li><li fid="ua5b29c10" data-lake-id="ua444b03a" id="ua444b03a"><span data-lake-id="u01092b98" id="u01092b98">在 Python 中，变量的创建与赋值是同时完成的。也就是说，当程序中出现一个变量时，它必须立即与某个值建立绑定关系。</span></li><li fid="ua5b29c10" data-lake-id="ud004dd35" id="ud004dd35"><span data-lake-id="u0afb70df" id="u0afb70df">变量名不应过于随意，命名时需要遵守一定的规则（具体命名规则将在下一小节讲解）。</span></li></ol></blockquote></details><h3 data-lake-id="FcEji" id="FcEji" data-lake-index-type="2"><strong><span data-lake-id="u4a20ad5e" id="u4a20ad5e" class="lake-fontsize-14">标识符命名规则</span></strong></h3><details data-lake-id="u2d210dac" id="u2d210dac" open="true" class="lake-collapse"><summary data-lake-id="ue686e2e1" id="ue686e2e1" class="lake-summary"><span data-lake-id="u642aa013" id="u642aa013">1️⃣</span><strong><span data-lake-id="ue474dfe4" id="ue474dfe4">什么是标识符？</span></strong></summary><p data-lake-id="u602551a7" id="u602551a7"><span data-lake-id="u77ad5e91" id="u77ad5e91">在程序中我们给： 变量、函数、类.....所起的</span><strong><span data-lake-id="uaea71dcd" id="uaea71dcd" style="color: #117CEE">名字</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u4927756b" id="u4927756b">，统称为</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u97797e56" id="u97797e56" style="color: #117CEE">标识符</span></strong><span data-lake-id="ud6e72c1f" id="ud6e72c1f">，即：在程序中所有我们可以自己起的名字，都是标识符。</span></p></details><details data-lake-id="ue48e1545" id="ue48e1545" open="true" class="lake-collapse"><summary data-lake-id="u2cb016cb" id="u2cb016cb" class="lake-summary"><strong><span data-lake-id="u8ed65a2b" id="u8ed65a2b">2️⃣</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="u3a6c6c51" id="u3a6c6c51">标识符命名规则如下：</span></strong></summary><blockquote data-lake-id="u2f96f5b8" id="u2f96f5b8" class="lake-alert lake-alert-info"><ol list="u88805499"><li fid="uc739b08f" data-lake-id="uc06150f2" id="uc06150f2"><span data-lake-id="u51e901d9" id="u51e901d9">只能包含：数字、字母、下划线，且</span><strong><span data-lake-id="ud740274d" id="ud740274d" style="color: #AD1A2B">不能</span></strong><span data-lake-id="ue174d633" id="ue174d633">以数字开头，</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u5bfcaf27" id="u5bfcaf27" style="color: #AD1A2B">不能</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u4310cd2a" id="u4310cd2a">包含空格。</span></li><li fid="uc739b08f" data-lake-id="u13e1d263" id="u13e1d263" style="text-align: justify"><span data-lake-id="udf389799" id="udf389799">区分大小写，即</span><code data-lake-id="uc9c8253a" id="uc9c8253a"><span data-lake-id="u24de5709" id="u24de5709">Name</span></code><span data-lake-id="u082bc387" id="u082bc387">和</span><code data-lake-id="u8c3296be" id="u8c3296be"><span data-lake-id="uc289cf3e" id="uc289cf3e">name</span></code><span data-lake-id="u48ec3412" id="u48ec3412">是两个不同的标识符。</span></li><li fid="uc739b08f" data-lake-id="u2fca3be8" id="u2fca3be8" style="text-align: justify"><strong><span data-lake-id="u747a4d3c" id="u747a4d3c" style="color: #AD1A2B">不能</span></strong><span data-lake-id="ub3d2147a" id="ub3d2147a">使用关键字（关键字的解释在下面</span><span data-lake-id="u000fb6c8" id="u000fb6c8">⬇️</span><span data-lake-id="u68a74625" id="u68a74625">）。</span></li><li fid="uc739b08f" data-lake-id="u52fedc9e" id="u52fedc9e" style="text-align: justify"><span data-lake-id="u9b05919e" id="u9b05919e">标识符尽量</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u97f80bab" id="u97f80bab" style="color: #AD1A2B">不要</span></strong><span data-lake-id="uc9ac4930" id="uc9ac4930">与内置函数同名。</span></li><li fid="uc739b08f" data-lake-id="u304cfb28" id="u304cfb28" style="text-align: justify"><span data-lake-id="u210ea794" id="u210ea794">标识符虽然没有长度限制，但应追求：简洁清晰，具有描述性。</span></li></ol></blockquote></details><details data-lake-id="ue3230de7" id="ue3230de7" open="true" class="lake-collapse"><summary data-lake-id="ud44f93f2" id="ud44f93f2" class="lake-summary"><strong><span data-lake-id="uc256c865" id="uc256c865">3️⃣</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="u0f8d2c47" id="u0f8d2c47">Python 中的关键字</span></strong></summary><p data-lake-id="uaf73d4ee" id="uaf73d4ee"><span data-lake-id="u0e89be4a" id="u0e89be4a">所谓“关键字”，是指那些：已被 Python 语言预先保留、具有特定含义和功能的标识符。这些关键字被系统征用，因而不能再作为变量名、函数名或其他标识符使用。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22Python%20%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E5%AD%97%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22False%20%20%20%20%20%5CtNone%20%20%20%20%20%20%5CtTrue%20%20%20%20%20%20%5Ctand%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%5Ctas%5Cnassert%20%20%20%20%5Ctasync%20%20%20%20%20%5Ctawait%20%20%20%20%20%5Ctbreak%20%20%20%20%20%5Ctclass%5Cncontinue%20%20%5Ctdef%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%5Ctdel%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%5Ctelif%20%20%20%20%20%20%5Ctelse%5Cnexcept%20%20%20%20%5Ctfinally%20%20%20%5Ctfor%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%5Ctfrom%20%20%20%20%20%20%5Ctglobal%5Cnif%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%5Ctimport%20%20%20%20%5Ctin%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%5Ctis%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%5Ctlambda%5Cnnonlocal%20%20%5Ctnot%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%5Ctor%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%5Ctpass%20%20%20%20%20%20%5Ctraise%5Cnreturn%20%20%20%20%5Cttry%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%5Ctwhile%20%20%20%20%20%5Ctwith%20%20%20%20%20%20%5Ctyield%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22Python%20%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E5%AD%97%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22V97s9%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><blockquote data-lake-id="ub12a769b" id="ub12a769b" class="lake-alert lake-alert-tips"><p data-lake-id="u866aa617" id="u866aa617"><span data-lake-id="u889e18e4" id="u889e18e4">📋</span><strong><span data-lake-id="udaba1ac1" id="udaba1ac1">备注：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u81e44e0b" id="u81e44e0b">上述关键字暂不作详细说明。随着课程的推进，我们会在实际讲解中逐步接触并使用这些关键字，届时再进行深入解释。初学者无需在此阶段强行记忆（这也并不现实），随着使用频率的增加，便会在后续学习中自然掌握。</span></p></blockquote></details><details data-lake-id="uf76cb9b2" id="uf76cb9b2" open="true" class="lake-collapse"><summary data-lake-id="u25d1a38a" id="u25d1a38a" class="lake-summary"><strong><span data-lake-id="u51dddbf9" id="u51dddbf9">4️⃣</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="u584ae20f" id="u584ae20f">常见的三种命名风格</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u8baf929c" id="u8baf929c">​</span></summary><blockquote data-lake-id="ufd67f160" id="ufd67f160" class="lake-alert lake-alert-info"><ol list="uef07274f"><li fid="u5eaeb94c" data-lake-id="uf709aa20" id="uf709aa20" style="text-align: justify"><strong><span data-lake-id="u5eaa6eaa" id="u5eaa6eaa" class="lake-fontsize-1515">大驼峰</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u60f408fb" id="u60f408fb" class="lake-fontsize-1515">（UpperCamelCase）: 每个单词的首字母大写，例如：</span><code data-lake-id="u3ade7364" id="u3ade7364"><span data-lake-id="u524d0639" id="u524d0639" class="lake-fontsize-1515">UserName</span></code></li><li fid="u5eaeb94c" data-lake-id="u512b7a5e" id="u512b7a5e" style="text-align: justify"><strong><span data-lake-id="u2040b766" id="u2040b766" class="lake-fontsize-1515">小驼峰</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u4624cfbe" id="u4624cfbe" class="lake-fontsize-1515">（lowerCamelCase）: 首词的首字母小写，后面单词首字母大写，例如：</span><code data-lake-id="u109dbdfc" id="u109dbdfc"><span data-lake-id="ub0288de7" id="ub0288de7" class="lake-fontsize-1515">userName</span></code></li><li fid="u5eaeb94c" data-lake-id="u829b6d94" id="u829b6d94" style="text-align: justify"><strong><span data-lake-id="u1dc65e6a" id="u1dc65e6a" class="lake-fontsize-1515">蛇形</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u2be922fd" id="u2be922fd" class="lake-fontsize-1515">（snake_case）：单词间用下划线连接，例如：</span><code data-lake-id="u4c3de441" id="u4c3de441"><span data-lake-id="u2c125fa2" id="u2c125fa2" class="lake-fontsize-1515">user_name</span></code></li></ol><p data-lake-id="ub1e87c46" id="ub1e87c46"><span data-lake-id="uece14955" id="uece14955">💡</span><span data-lake-id="u8cde3be4" id="u8cde3be4" class="lake-fontsize-1515">Python 中推荐使用『蛇形（snake_case）』写法。</span></p></blockquote><p data-lake-id="u9a4f372c" id="u9a4f372c"><span data-lake-id="ud6db8e77" id="ud6db8e77">举几个例子：</span></p><p data-lake-id="u0a33102a" id="u0a33102a"><card type="inline" name="image" value="data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F35780599%2F1747039497952-2b73656f-739b-4735-b758-db370ffecbc5.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u542a2a01-4169-473f-b2ee-eaf9df1eb2d%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u8753f935-e02d-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A614.7000122070312%2C%22height%22%3A204%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A61956%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1065%2C%22originHeight%22%3A354%2C%22ratio%22%3A1.5%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22FILEUPLOADPATH%22%2C%22x%22%3A787%2C%22y%22%3A252%2C%22width%22%3A217%2C%22height%22%3A24%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22USEREMAI1ADDRESS%22%2C%22x%22%3A224%2C%22y%22%3A193%2C%22width%22%3A221%2C%22height%22%3A24%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22FI1EUP1OADPATH%22%2C%22x%22%3A224%2C%22y%22%3A251%2C%22width%22%3A193%2C%22height%22%3A25%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22USEREMAI1ADDRESS%22%2C%22x%22%3A505%2C%22y%22%3A193%2C%22width%22%3A222%2C%22height%22%3A24%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22FI1EUP1OADPATH%22%2C%22x%22%3A507%2C%22y%22%3A251%2C%22width%22%3A190%2C%22height%22%3A24%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22ISIOGGEDIN%22%2C%22x%22%3A787%2C%22y%22%3A138%2C%22width%22%3A163%2C%22height%22%3A23%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22STUDENTSCORE%22%2C%22x%22%3A508%2C%22y%22%3A80%2C%22width%22%3A161%2C%22height%22%3A22%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22MAXRETRYCOUNT%22%2C%22x%22%3A784%2C%22y%22%3A311%2C%22width%22%3A209%2C%22height%22%3A22%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8D%E8%AF%95%E6%AC%A1%E6%95%B0%22%2C%22x%22%3A16%2C%22y%22%3A304%2C%22width%22%3A149%2C%22height%22%3A30%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22STUDENTSCORE%22%2C%22x%22%3A226%2C%22y%22%3A80%2C%22width%22%3A162%2C%22height%22%3A22%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22ISLOGGEDIN%22%2C%22x%22%3A226%2C%22y%22%3A139%2C%22width%22%3A135%2C%22height%22%3A23%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E9%82%AE%E7%AE%B1%E5%9C%B0%E5%9D%80%22%2C%22x%22%3A16%2C%22y%22%3A191%2C%22width%22%3A151%2C%22height%22%3A27%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22ISLOGGEDIN%22%2C%22x%22%3A506%2C%22y%22%3A138%2C%22width%22%3A136%2C%22height%22%3A23%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22MAXRETRYCOUNT%22%2C%22x%22%3A224%2C%22y%22%3A311%2C%22width%22%3A178%2C%22height%22%3A22%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E4%B8%8A%E4%BC%A0%E8%B7%AF%E5%BE%84%22%2C%22x%22%3A17%2C%22y%22%3A249%2C%22width%22%3A149%2C%22height%22%3A28%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22USEREMAI1ADDRESS%22%2C%22x%22%3A790%2C%22y%22%3A195%2C%22width%22%3A241%2C%22height%22%3A23%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22STUDENTSCORE%22%2C%22x%22%3A791%2C%22y%22%3A81%2C%22width%22%3A171%2C%22height%22%3A21%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22MAXRETRYCOUNT%22%2C%22x%22%3A506%2C%22y%22%3A310%2C%22width%22%3A174%2C%22height%22%3A23%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E7%99%BB%E5%BD%95%22%2C%22x%22%3A17%2C%22y%22%3A134%2C%22width%22%3A97%2C%22height%22%3A28%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%AD%A6%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E7%BB%A9%22%2C%22x%22%3A18%2C%22y%22%3A76%2C%22width%22%3A97%2C%22height%22%3A27%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87%E5%90%AB%E4%B9%89%22%2C%22x%22%3A52%2C%22y%22%3A18%2C%22width%22%3A97%2C%22height%22%3A29%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%A4%A7%E9%A9%BC%E5%B3%B0%22%2C%22x%22%3A303%2C%22y%22%3A17%2C%22width%22%3A78%2C%22height%22%3A28%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%B0%8F%E9%A9%BC%E5%B3%B0%22%2C%22x%22%3A583%2C%22y%22%3A18%2C%22width%22%3A79%2C%22height%22%3A28%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%9B%87%E5%BD%A2%22%2C%22x%22%3A886%2C%22y%22%3A18%2C%22width%22%3A49%2C%22height%22%3A27%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23efefef%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22c7HWd%22%7D"></card></p></details><h3 data-lake-id="FyPO8" id="FyPO8" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u755ed1b7" id="u755ed1b7">常量</span></h3><details data-lake-id="uc54834c6" id="uc54834c6" open="true" class="lake-collapse"><summary data-lake-id="ub0530e0d" id="ub0530e0d" class="lake-summary"><span data-lake-id="u2e0b9bc3" id="u2e0b9bc3">1️⃣</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u2feca017" id="u2feca017">什么是常量？</span></strong></summary><p data-lake-id="u3c6dba3b" id="u3c6dba3b"><span data-lake-id="uf20aca0f" id="uf20aca0f">在程序中一旦被赋值，就</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u87b1518c" id="u87b1518c" style="color: #ad1a2b">不希望</span></strong><span data-lake-id="uada6542b" id="uada6542b">被修改的量（区别于变量）。</span></p></details><details data-lake-id="u07aadccf" id="u07aadccf" open="true" class="lake-collapse"><summary data-lake-id="u57ad8e45" id="u57ad8e45" class="lake-summary"><span data-lake-id="ue4876345" id="ue4876345">2️⃣</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u33354285" id="u33354285">具体语法</span></strong></summary><p data-lake-id="uf5b8a08b" id="uf5b8a08b"><span data-lake-id="u02accad4" id="u02accad4">Python 中一般约定使用</span><strong><span data-lake-id="ua71d4415" id="ua71d4415" style="color: #ad1a2b">全大写</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u42eff022" id="u42eff022">变量名来表示常量，涉及到多个单词时，用下划线做分隔。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%E5%B8%B8%E9%87%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%86%99%E6%B3%95%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22ADULT_AGE%20%3D%2018%5CnMONTHS_IN_YEAR%20%3D%2012%5CnMAX_USERS%20%3D%201200%5CnPASSING_SCORE%20%3D%2060%5CnMAX_USERS%20%3D%201300%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%E5%B8%B8%E9%87%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%86%99%E6%B3%95%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22LWdRU%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card></details><details data-lake-id="ud5003974" id="ud5003974" open="true" class="lake-collapse"><summary data-lake-id="u83ca1765" id="u83ca1765" class="lake-summary"><strong><span data-lake-id="ua479abad" id="ua479abad">3️⃣</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="u04e6536f" id="u04e6536f">Python 中没有强制的常量机制</span></strong></summary><p data-lake-id="ubb33dd09" id="ubb33dd09"><span data-lake-id="ue0046aef" id="ue0046aef">当强制对常量进行修改时，最终也能改掉，但要自觉不改，这是 Python 程序员之间的约定。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%E5%B0%9D%E8%AF%95%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%E5%B8%B8%E9%87%8F%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22MONTHS_IN_YEAR%20%3D%2012%5Cnprint(MONTHS_IN_YEAR)%5Cn%5CnMONTHS_IN_YEAR%20%3D%2013%5Cnprint(MONTHS_IN_YEAR)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%E5%B0%9D%E8%AF%95%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%E5%B8%B8%E9%87%8F%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22hHRin%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card></details><h2 data-lake-id="UOLW8" id="UOLW8" data-lake-index-type="2" style="text-align: justify"><strong><span data-lake-id="ubb1e51d7" id="ubb1e51d7" class="lake-fontsize-14">注释</span></strong></h2><h3 data-lake-id="dPvRU" id="dPvRU" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u82437ba4" id="u82437ba4">概述</span></h3><p data-lake-id="u6ffdf808" id="u6ffdf808" style="text-indent: 2em"><span data-lake-id="uc12ef480" id="uc12ef480">注释是对代码的</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u30502b5d" id="u30502b5d" style="color: #AD1A2B">备注</span></strong><span data-lake-id="ua18e5db9" id="ua18e5db9">和</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u956769e6" id="u956769e6" style="color: #AD1A2B">解释</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u27f56dae" id="u27f56dae">，在代码执行的时，通常不起任何作用。</span></p><h3 data-lake-id="UKIno" id="UKIno" data-lake-index-type="2" style="text-align: justify"><strong><span data-lake-id="u71d6734e" id="u71d6734e" class="lake-fontsize-14">注释的作用</span></strong></h3><p data-lake-id="udcde9c23" id="udcde9c23" style="text-indent: 2em"><span data-lake-id="ueec0971b" id="ueec0971b">注释的核心作用如下：</span></p><blockquote data-lake-id="u22113bdc" id="u22113bdc" hindent="2em" class="lake-alert lake-alert-info"><ol list="ue26bdff3"><li fid="u6aeb2210" data-lake-id="uf168af1a" id="uf168af1a" style="text-align: justify"><span data-lake-id="u2855fd40" id="u2855fd40">提高代码的可读性，通常用来辅助程序员快速理解代码的逻辑。</span></li><li fid="u6aeb2210" data-lake-id="u9fcb5b75" id="u9fcb5b75" style="text-align: justify"><span data-lake-id="u9657c1ec" id="u9657c1ec">屏蔽掉暂时不需要的代码。</span></li></ol></blockquote><blockquote data-lake-id="u1a997786" id="u1a997786" hindent="2em" class="lake-alert lake-alert-color4"><p data-lake-id="u4aa7b555" id="u4aa7b555"><span data-lake-id="uc9248836" id="uc9248836">📢</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u1912a46e" id="u1912a46e" style="color: #AD1A2B">注意：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u52aca2f4" id="u52aca2f4">在代码中编写清晰易懂的注释，是程序员的基本素养之一！</span></p></blockquote><h3 data-lake-id="rAtUj" id="rAtUj" data-lake-index-type="2" style="text-align: justify"><strong><span data-lake-id="u114cf120" id="u114cf120" class="lake-fontsize-14">单行注释</span></strong></h3><p data-lake-id="u44f18b7e" id="u44f18b7e" style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em"><span data-lake-id="uf9a23f0e" id="uf9a23f0e">在 Python 中</span><code data-lake-id="uced2610b" id="uced2610b"><span data-lake-id="ua749e87a" id="ua749e87a">#</span></code><span data-lake-id="uba1dae36" id="uba1dae36">后的一行内内容，会被视为注释。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20name%20%E6%98%AF%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89%E7%9A%84%E5%90%8D%E5%AD%97%5Cnname%20%3D%20'%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89'%5Cn%23%20age%20%E6%98%AF%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89%E7%9A%84%E5%B9%B4%E9%BE%84%5Cnage%20%3D%2018%5Cn%23%20weight%20%E6%98%AF%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%93%E9%87%8D%EF%BC%88%E5%8D%95%E4%BD%8D%EF%BC%9Akg%EF%BC%89%5Cnweight%20%3D%2065.2%5Cn%5Cnprint(name%2C%20age%2C%20weight)%20%20%23%20%E8%BF%99%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E5%8F%A5%E6%89%93%E5%8D%B0%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22__widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22xoEtH%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%2C%22widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%7D" hindent="2em"></card><p data-lake-id="uecb154d4" id="uecb154d4" style="text-indent: 2em"><span data-lake-id="uea711c6b" id="uea711c6b">关于注释的书写格式：</span></p><blockquote data-lake-id="u3fa44eb9" id="u3fa44eb9" hindent="2em" class="lake-alert lake-alert-info"><ol list="ub48c806f"><li fid="u73fa8135" data-lake-id="u0c22acd4" id="u0c22acd4"><span data-lake-id="u0ea5df31" id="u0ea5df31">Python官方建议：在</span><code data-lake-id="ua6d046ff" id="ua6d046ff"><strong><span data-lake-id="u44a7a433" id="u44a7a433">#</span></strong></code><span data-lake-id="u3dd35f54" id="u3dd35f54">和注释的内容之间加一个空格，在代码和</span><code data-lake-id="u46a221c4" id="u46a221c4"><strong><span data-lake-id="u52cf2ff2" id="u52cf2ff2">#</span></strong></code><span data-lake-id="u92e36d69" id="u92e36d69">之间加两个空格。</span></li><li fid="u73fa8135" data-lake-id="ubca7ac82" id="ubca7ac82"><span data-lake-id="u09e9c034" id="u09e9c034">上述的规则属于 Python 编码规范，规范的具体内容，我们会在课程中逐渐给各位渗透。</span></li></ol></blockquote><h3 data-lake-id="CeXrf" id="CeXrf" data-lake-index-type="2" style="text-align: justify"><strong><span data-lake-id="u988ff100" id="u988ff100" class="lake-fontsize-14">多行注释</span></strong></h3><p data-lake-id="u4a51d7d7" id="u4a51d7d7" style="text-indent: 2em"><span data-lake-id="u06cc9378" id="u06cc9378">多行注释又称“块注释” ，Python 中的多行注释使用的是一组三引号（单引号，双引号都可以）</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u04a1d7a3" id="u04a1d7a3">。</span></strong></p><details data-lake-id="ucf3eb691" id="ucf3eb691" open="true" hindent="2em" class="lake-collapse"><summary data-lake-id="uf914a509" id="uf914a509" class="lake-summary"><span data-lake-id="u3dd5b30a" id="u3dd5b30a">1️⃣</span><span data-lake-id="uf4689f90" id="uf4689f90">多行注释可以换行，但不能嵌套。</span></summary><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%E5%A4%9A%E8%A1%8C%E6%B3%A8%E9%87%8A%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E6%8D%A2%E8%A1%8C%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%5C%22%5C%22%5C%22%5Cn%E6%88%91%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%9B%E6%B3%A8%E9%87%8A%5Cn%E6%88%91%E8%BF%98%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%9B%E6%B3%A8%E9%87%8A%5Cn%5C%22%5C%22%5C%22%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%E5%A4%9A%E8%A1%8C%E6%B3%A8%E9%87%8A%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E6%8D%A2%E8%A1%8C%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22__widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22JfTkw%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%2C%22widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%7D"></card></details><details data-lake-id="u6dcb84b9" id="u6dcb84b9" open="true" hindent="2em" class="lake-collapse"><summary data-lake-id="u4f524ffa" id="u4f524ffa" class="lake-summary"><span data-lake-id="u096eb26d" id="u096eb26d">2️⃣</span><span data-lake-id="u087ae822" id="u087ae822">多行注释本质是一个多行字符串。</span></summary><blockquote data-lake-id="u0c440a1b" id="u0c440a1b" class="lake-alert lake-alert-color4"><p data-lake-id="u84703909" id="u84703909"><strong><span data-lake-id="u31f943c9" id="u31f943c9" style="color: #AD1A2B">📢</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="u974e5bd5" id="u974e5bd5" style="color: #AD1A2B">注意：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="ud240194c" id="ud240194c">Python 中并没有真正的多行注释语法，所谓多行注释的本质其实还是字符串。</span></p></blockquote><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22print(%5Cn%20%20%20%20%5C%22%5C%22%5C%22%5Cn%20%20%20%20Hello%20World%5Cn%20%20%20%20Hello%20world%5Cn%20%20%20%20%5C%22%5C%22%5C%22%5Cn)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22__widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22zooRv%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%2C%22widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%7D"></card></details><h3 data-lake-id="S7fwU" id="S7fwU" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="ub210a42b" id="ub210a42b"> 文件编码注释</span></h3><p data-lake-id="u4aead69e" id="u4aead69e" style="text-indent: 2em"><span data-lake-id="u6536c457" id="u6536c457">文件编码又称“字符编码”，文件编码注释写在 Python 文件的首行，是一种特殊的注释。</span></p><p data-lake-id="ucd8be65d" id="ucd8be65d" style="text-indent: 2em"><span data-lake-id="u748e9ae8" id="u748e9ae8">它的作用是：指定当前文件的字符编码。  </span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20coding%3Dutf-8%5Cnprint('%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD%E5%95%8A%EF%BC%81')%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22__widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22N41Iv%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%2C%22widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%7D" hindent="2em"></card><h2 data-lake-id="gFfpA" id="gFfpA" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="uf75d6c93" id="uf75d6c93">字符编码</span></h2><h3 data-lake-id="zysvx" id="zysvx" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="ue36d8bcd" id="ue36d8bcd">概述</span></h3><p data-lake-id="ue2c9a960" id="ue2c9a960" style="text-indent: 2em"><span data-lake-id="uc71d91d7" id="uc71d91d7">计算机对数据会进行两个常见的操作，分别是：存储数据、读取数据。</span></p><ul list="u54dcae5f" data-lake-indent="1"><li fid="u488db8fc" data-lake-id="uaf841b83" id="uaf841b83"><span data-lake-id="u2c4995ce" id="u2c4995ce">存储数据时，计算机会进行</span><strong><span data-lake-id="ua220d920" id="ua220d920" style="color: #DF2A3F">编码</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u0a599bf3" id="u0a599bf3">。</span></li><li fid="u488db8fc" data-lake-id="u0458f779" id="u0458f779"><span data-lake-id="u19eceea6" id="u19eceea6">读取数据时，计算机会进行</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u9ebcfaa4" id="u9ebcfaa4" style="color: #DF2A3F">解码</span></strong><span data-lake-id="ub0204914" id="ub0204914">。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id="u993f3cfe" id="u993f3cfe" style="padding-left: 2em"><card type="inline" name="image" value="data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F35780599%2F1760676361078-7e14538b-66e1-4d50-a783-b89394156146.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22uae3f898c-defd-4353-9de8-6fdd90c05bd%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u9dc15b59-c913-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A503.7802734375%2C%22height%22%3A248%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A739941%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1904%2C%22originHeight%22%3A938%2C%22ratio%22%3A1.6500000953674316%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E7%BC%96%E7%A0%81%22%2C%22x%22%3A240%2C%22y%22%3A24%2C%22width%22%3A140%2C%22height%22%3A71%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%A7%A3%E7%A0%81%22%2C%22x%22%3A1517%2C%22y%22%3A23%2C%22width%22%3A144%2C%22height%22%3A72%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%22%2C%22x%22%3A1600%2C%22y%22%3A157%2C%22width%22%3A129%2C%22height%22%3A33%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E7%BC%96%E7%A0%81%22%2C%22x%22%3A227%2C%22y%22%3A569%2C%22width%22%3A127%2C%22height%22%3A66%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%22%2C%22x%22%3A190%2C%22y%22%3A146%2C%22width%22%3A133%2C%22height%22%3A38%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%A7%A3%E7%A0%81%22%2C%22x%22%3A1519%2C%22y%22%3A568%2C%22width%22%3A137%2C%22height%22%3A69%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%22%2C%22x%22%3A419%2C%22y%22%3A237%2C%22width%22%3A28%2C%22height%22%3A105%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E4%BA%8C%22%2C%22x%22%3A317%2C%22y%22%3A231%2C%22width%22%3A34%2C%22height%22%3A154%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD%E5%95%8A%22%2C%22x%22%3A1621%2C%22y%22%3A659%2C%22width%22%3A118%2C%22height%22%3A32%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%22%2C%22x%22%3A1426%2C%22y%22%3A227%2C%22width%22%3A30%2C%22height%22%3A133%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%220110%22%2C%22x%22%3A908%2C%22y%22%3A718%2C%22width%22%3A82%2C%22height%22%3A29%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%222%22%2C%22x%22%3A367%2C%22y%22%3A242%2C%22width%22%3A42%2C%22height%22%3A68%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E4%B8%800110%22%2C%22x%22%3A1429%2C%22y%22%3A697%2C%22width%22%3A138%2C%22height%22%3A29%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%AF%B9%E7%85%A7%E8%A1%A8A%22%2C%22x%22%3A329%2C%22y%22%3A395%2C%22width%22%3A118%2C%22height%22%3A26%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%AF%B9%E7%85%A7%E8%A1%A8A%22%2C%22x%22%3A1432%2C%22y%22%3A390%2C%22width%22%3A121%2C%22height%22%3A29%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%80%83%22%2C%22x%22%3A1521%2C%22y%22%3A228%2C%22width%22%3A36%2C%22height%22%3A60%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E9%9B%86%22%2C%22x%22%3A399%2C%22y%22%3A859%2C%22width%22%3A82%2C%22height%22%3A30%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD%E5%95%8A%22%2C%22x%22%3A140%2C%22y%22%3A680%2C%22width%22%3A111%2C%22height%22%3A29%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%221011%22%2C%22x%22%3A1503%2C%22y%22%3A776%2C%22width%22%3A61%2C%22height%22%3A31%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E7%AC%A6%E9%9B%86%22%2C%22x%22%3A1430%2C%22y%22%3A859%2C%22width%22%3A65%2C%22height%22%3A29%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%22%2C%22x%22%3A368%2C%22y%22%3A707%2C%22width%22%3A24%2C%22height%22%3A94%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%221011%22%2C%22x%22%3A487%2C%22y%22%3A780%2C%22width%22%3A59%2C%22height%22%3A27%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E4%B8%80%22%2C%22x%22%3A1532%2C%22y%22%3A261%2C%22width%22%3A23%2C%22height%22%3A84%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%220110%22%2C%22x%22%3A432%2C%22y%22%3A699%2C%22width%22%3A118%2C%22height%22%3A28%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22O00%22%2C%22x%22%3A558%2C%22y%22%3A306%2C%22width%22%3A102%2C%22height%22%3A28%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E4%B8%80%E9%94%99%22%2C%22x%22%3A371%2C%22y%22%3A357%2C%22width%22%3A82%2C%22height%22%3A33%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E4%B8%8D%E9%94%99%22%2C%22x%22%3A919%2C%22y%22%3A265%2C%22width%22%3A60%2C%22height%22%3A37%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%221010%22%2C%22x%22%3A486%2C%22y%22%3A740%2C%22width%22%3A61%2C%22height%22%3A24%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%82%A8%22%2C%22x%22%3A1372%2C%22y%22%3A699%2C%22width%22%3A38%2C%22height%22%3A55%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%221011%22%2C%22x%22%3A910%2C%22y%22%3A772%2C%22width%22%3A73%2C%22height%22%3A23%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%221010%22%2C%22x%22%3A911%2C%22y%22%3A745%2C%22width%22%3A79%2C%22height%22%3A23%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%221010%22%2C%22x%22%3A1497%2C%22y%22%3A739%2C%22width%22%3A63%2C%22height%22%3A24%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%220O0%22%2C%22x%22%3A612%2C%22y%22%3A751%2C%22width%22%3A102%2C%22height%22%3A28%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E9%94%80%22%2C%22x%22%3A1504%2C%22y%22%3A342%2C%22width%22%3A55%2C%22height%22%3A44%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%222%22%2C%22x%22%3A1452%2C%22y%22%3A234%2C%22width%22%3A80%2C%22height%22%3A33%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%22%2C%22x%22%3A1692%2C%22y%22%3A672%2C%22width%22%3A82%2C%22height%22%3A33%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E4%B8%80%22%2C%22x%22%3A364%2C%22y%22%3A300%2C%22width%22%3A33%2C%22height%22%3A58%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%95%8A%22%2C%22x%22%3A1376%2C%22y%22%3A757%2C%22width%22%3A34%2C%22height%22%3A61%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22VV%22%2C%22x%22%3A186%2C%22y%22%3A644%2C%22width%22%3A91%2C%22height%22%3A25%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22()%22%2C%22x%22%3A1444%2C%22y%22%3A819%2C%22width%22%3A49%2C%22height%22%3A24%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23454545%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22i4TXI%22%7D"></card></p><blockquote data-lake-id="u6d6a5f59" id="u6d6a5f59" hindent="2em" class="lake-alert lake-alert-tips"><p data-lake-id="u5e503bfe" id="u5e503bfe"><span data-lake-id="ub5b92eb7" id="ub5b92eb7">编码与解码，会遵循一定的规范，这个规范就是</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u8c256e8e" id="u8c256e8e" style="color: #AD1A2B">字符编码</span></strong><span data-lake-id="ued329633" id="ued329633">，并且编码与解码，必须遵循相同的编码规范，若所用的规范不一致，就会出现乱码。</span></p></blockquote><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%E9%94%99%E7%94%A8%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E7%BC%96%E7%A0%81%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%BC%E8%87%B4%E7%9A%84%E4%B9%B1%E7%A0%81%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20coding%3Diso-8859-1%5Cnprint('%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD%E5%95%8A%EF%BC%81')%20%20%23%20%C3%A4%C2%BD%20%C3%A5%C2%A5%C2%BD%C3%A5%C2%95%C2%8A%C3%AF%C2%BC%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%E9%94%99%E7%94%A8%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E7%BC%96%E7%A0%81%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%BC%E8%87%B4%E7%9A%84%E4%B9%B1%E7%A0%81%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22__widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22zWJ21%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%2C%22widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%7D" hindent="2em"></card><h3 data-lake-id="RmQGY" id="RmQGY" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u19aa27d1" id="u19aa27d1">常见编码方式</span></h3><blockquote data-lake-id="u3ee887d6" id="u3ee887d6" hindent="2em" class="lake-alert lake-alert-info"><p data-lake-id="u2b1090c1" id="u2b1090c1"><span data-lake-id="u318f320d" id="u318f320d">1. </span><code data-lake-id="ub30daae9" id="ub30daae9"><span data-lake-id="u0baf8b1e" id="u0baf8b1e">ASCII</span></code><span data-lake-id="u60363754" id="u60363754">：大写字母、小写字母、数字、一些符号，共计 28个字符。</span></p><p data-lake-id="u26e0e2d6" id="u26e0e2d6"><span data-lake-id="uf800ff5d" id="uf800ff5d">2. </span><code data-lake-id="ubbaf2cfa" id="ubbaf2cfa"><span data-lake-id="ufd3b8fad" id="ufd3b8fad">ISO 8859-1</span></code><span data-lake-id="uc28c0c0c" id="uc28c0c0c">：在</span><code data-lake-id="u35e8ae17" id="u35e8ae17"><span data-lake-id="u3cee66ca" id="u3cee66ca">ASCII</span></code><span data-lake-id="u12821a36" id="u12821a36">基础上扩展，支持西欧语言，共计 256 个字符。</span></p><p data-lake-id="u17cdfb10" id="u17cdfb10"><span data-lake-id="u53d7c7fc" id="u53d7c7fc">3. </span><code data-lake-id="uf39d2089" id="uf39d2089"><span data-lake-id="u309083d5" id="u309083d5">GB2312</span></code><span data-lake-id="u065788fb" id="u065788fb">：中国国家编码标准，收录约 6763 个简体中文常用汉字和符号。</span></p><p data-lake-id="ue44b0120" id="ue44b0120"><span data-lake-id="uf3e2ca9f" id="uf3e2ca9f">4. </span><code data-lake-id="u6b3f44fc" id="u6b3f44fc"><span data-lake-id="u3ef74702" id="u3ef74702">GBK</span></code><span data-lake-id="ua0e55eb0" id="ua0e55eb0">：兼容</span><code data-lake-id="u5dfb8763" id="u5dfb8763"><span data-lake-id="u0a7ce77d" id="u0a7ce77d">GB2312</span></code><span data-lake-id="ua7500961" id="ua7500961">，进一步扩展，支持简繁体中文和其他汉字，共收录 2 万多个字符。</span></p><p data-lake-id="u9d69221a" id="u9d69221a"><span data-lake-id="ub9aa0a73" id="ub9aa0a73">5. </span><code data-lake-id="u2cd21432" id="u2cd21432"><strong><span data-lake-id="u38883eed" id="u38883eed" style="color: #AD1A2B">UTF-8</span></strong></code><span data-lake-id="u6010d838" id="u6010d838">：国际通用的编码格式，也叫“</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u06442ba8" id="u06442ba8">万国码</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u530d3854" id="u530d3854">”，支持世界所有语言的字符，包括：中文、英文、阿拉伯文、日文、韩文等，向下兼容</span><code data-lake-id="u8be012cd" id="u8be012cd"><span data-lake-id="uf19d5b46" id="uf19d5b46">ASCII</span></code><span data-lake-id="u08261cc4" id="u08261cc4">，是现代互联网最常用的编码格式。</span></p></blockquote><blockquote data-lake-id="u9344ba04" id="u9344ba04" hindent="2em" class="lake-alert lake-alert-success"><p data-lake-id="u5040012f" id="u5040012f"><span data-lake-id="uf0ac1772" id="uf0ac1772">✅</span><strong><span data-lake-id="uca9c5c1f" id="uca9c5c1f">最佳实践：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="ua3c1a054" id="ua3c1a054">实际开发中，几乎都采用</span><code data-lake-id="u43dcf9a4" id="u43dcf9a4"><span data-lake-id="u1d893094" id="u1d893094">UTF-8</span></code><span data-lake-id="u4a2e62e7" id="u4a2e62e7">编码保存文件。</span></p></blockquote><blockquote data-lake-id="udc68c7c7" id="udc68c7c7" hindent="2em" class="lake-alert lake-alert-tips"><p data-lake-id="ue4f0d40d" id="ue4f0d40d"><strong><span data-lake-id="u89b7b6f1" id="u89b7b6f1">📋</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="u0eb2ac86" id="u0eb2ac86">备注</span></strong><span data-lake-id="ud8b1bc49" id="ud8b1bc49">：在 Python3 中，可以不写文件编码声明，因为 Python3 默认就使用</span><code data-lake-id="u9ccc2489" id="u9ccc2489"><span data-lake-id="ub777d567" id="ub777d567">UTF-8</span></code><span data-lake-id="u57991962" id="u57991962">编码。</span></p></blockquote><h2 data-lake-id="S2dLq" id="S2dLq" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u7d476fdc" id="u7d476fdc">数据类型</span></h2><h3 data-lake-id="ApqlD" id="ApqlD" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u0f6ecdb4" id="u0f6ecdb4">概述</span></h3><p data-lake-id="ueaa2aa26" id="ueaa2aa26" style="text-indent: 2em"><span data-lake-id="uc3734159" id="uc3734159">就像生活中的物品，都有自己所属的分类一样，数据也有自己所属的</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u19dcc916" id="u19dcc916">『数据类型』</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u2b1eec9b" id="u2b1eec9b">。</span></p><p data-lake-id="u9e1c1d30" id="u9e1c1d30" style="text-indent: 2em"><span data-lake-id="ua0089829" id="ua0089829">例如之前写过的这段代码：</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22'%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89'%5Cn18%5Cn65.2%5Cn%5Cn%5C%22%E6%9D%8E%E5%9B%9B%5C%22%5Cn22%5Cn74.6%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22__widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22OAvs1%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%2C%22widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%7D" hindent="2em"></card><p data-lake-id="u5758b4bd" id="u5758b4bd" style="text-indent: 2em"><span data-lake-id="u9ab7e06e" id="u9ab7e06e">在上述代码中：</span></p><blockquote data-lake-id="u5157dbe9" id="u5157dbe9" hindent="2em" class="lake-alert lake-alert-info"><p data-lake-id="u4f2b17e1" id="u4f2b17e1"><span data-lake-id="udd7ae62f" id="udd7ae62f">✅</span><code data-lake-id="uf0456de1" id="uf0456de1"><span data-lake-id="ueed1f659" id="ueed1f659">'张三'</span></code><span data-lake-id="u618bb167" id="u618bb167">、</span><code data-lake-id="ub1806dc4" id="ub1806dc4"><span data-lake-id="ud1f5d040" id="ud1f5d040">&quot;李四&quot;</span></code><span data-lake-id="u975fae8a" id="u975fae8a">这两个字面量，属于『</span><strong><span data-lake-id="uce7db101" id="uce7db101" style="color: #AD1A2B">字符串</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u11ea43c7" id="u11ea43c7">』类型。</span></p><p data-lake-id="u935ef59b" id="u935ef59b"><span data-lake-id="u051c2638" id="u051c2638">✅</span><code data-lake-id="u269e87c2" id="u269e87c2"><span data-lake-id="uf21e0183" id="uf21e0183">18</span></code><span data-lake-id="u17eaf56c" id="u17eaf56c">、</span><code data-lake-id="uded1691b" id="uded1691b"><span data-lake-id="u9a81ae8a" id="u9a81ae8a">22</span></code><span data-lake-id="u6ae65068" id="u6ae65068"> 这两个字面量，属于『</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u940e04cd" id="u940e04cd" style="color: #AD1A2B">整数</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="uef08101b" id="uef08101b">​</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u356960bc" id="u356960bc">』类型。</span></p><p data-lake-id="u782b03b9" id="u782b03b9"><span data-lake-id="u88774c8c" id="u88774c8c">✅</span><code data-lake-id="u4aab8520" id="u4aab8520"><span data-lake-id="u5d769c6b" id="u5d769c6b">65.2</span></code><span data-lake-id="ua1d00d6f" id="ua1d00d6f">、</span><code data-lake-id="u4d7f2298" id="u4d7f2298"><span data-lake-id="ue241fb42" id="ue241fb42">74.6</span></code><span data-lake-id="ua2e0fc6d" id="ua2e0fc6d">这两个字面量，属『</span><strong><span data-lake-id="uac76ea17" id="uac76ea17" style="color: #AD1A2B">浮点数</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="ue5497ef1" id="ue5497ef1">​</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u50b5fd68" id="u50b5fd68">』类型。</span></p></blockquote><p data-lake-id="u5a319d46" id="u5a319d46" style="text-indent: 2em"><span data-lake-id="ue89b0954" id="ue89b0954">三种最常见的数据类型：</span></p><table data-lake-id="acik0" id="acik0" margin="true" row-head="#074A92;#FFFFFF" hindent="2em" class="lake-table" style="width: 714px"><colgroup><col width="115"><col width="105"><col width="204"><col width="290"></colgroup><tbody><tr data-lake-id="u486d41ad" id="u486d41ad"><td data-lake-id="uf682c105" id="uf682c105"><p data-lake-id="u36a56af0" id="u36a56af0" style="text-align: center"><span data-lake-id="u4510b7e1" id="u4510b7e1">类型名称</span></p></td><td data-lake-id="uae5e9c01" id="uae5e9c01"><p data-lake-id="u163478e3" id="u163478e3" style="text-align: center"><span data-lake-id="u87a880e8" id="u87a880e8">英文名</span></p></td><td data-lake-id="u4676bdd3" id="u4676bdd3"><p data-lake-id="u79fd1eb9" id="u79fd1eb9" style="text-align: center"><span data-lake-id="u8201ede4" id="u8201ede4">举例</span></p></td><td data-lake-id="u94112698" id="u94112698"><p data-lake-id="uc6981bfd" id="uc6981bfd" style="text-align: center"><span data-lake-id="u6b4ad44d" id="u6b4ad44d">说明</span></p></td></tr><tr data-lake-id="u463912f1" id="u463912f1" style="height: 38px"><td data-lake-id="ua50d21a8" id="ua50d21a8"><p data-lake-id="ue1c2ddc7" id="ue1c2ddc7" style="text-align: center"><strong><span data-lake-id="udbd749dd" id="udbd749dd">整型</span></strong></p></td><td data-lake-id="udc493380" id="udc493380"><p data-lake-id="u9e737e9c" id="u9e737e9c" style="text-align: center"><code data-lake-id="u0fdb8d7a" id="u0fdb8d7a"><span data-lake-id="uafb7babc" id="uafb7babc">int</span></code></p></td><td data-lake-id="ue0dd97b3" id="ue0dd97b3"><p data-lake-id="u6182c477" id="u6182c477"><code data-lake-id="u2275a6d7" id="u2275a6d7"><span data-lake-id="ub04bcf4d" id="ub04bcf4d">5</span></code><span data-lake-id="u9da49537" id="u9da49537">, </span><code data-lake-id="ucf76d963" id="ucf76d963"><span data-lake-id="u3b629a78" id="u3b629a78">-3</span></code><span data-lake-id="u986eb7ab" id="u986eb7ab">, </span><code data-lake-id="u4ec03d08" id="u4ec03d08"><span data-lake-id="u9485d64b" id="u9485d64b">0</span></code><span data-lake-id="ue6f1488a" id="ue6f1488a">, </span><code data-lake-id="u8fa1fcf4" id="u8fa1fcf4"><span data-lake-id="u791f85c1" id="u791f85c1">2025</span></code></p></td><td data-lake-id="uad41151f" id="uad41151f"><p data-lake-id="u04a6b8a9" id="u04a6b8a9"><span data-lake-id="ub15f09f5" id="ub15f09f5">整数（不带小数点的数）</span></p></td></tr><tr data-lake-id="u3e7b8993" id="u3e7b8993"><td data-lake-id="u16bcadda" id="u16bcadda"><p data-lake-id="u94030d0d" id="u94030d0d" style="text-align: center"><strong><span data-lake-id="ud27c9548" id="ud27c9548">浮点型</span></strong></p></td><td data-lake-id="u3badeef6" id="u3badeef6"><p data-lake-id="u0b4e2d78" id="u0b4e2d78" style="text-align: center"><code data-lake-id="uf4429de0" id="uf4429de0"><span data-lake-id="ue37445cf" id="ue37445cf">float</span></code></p></td><td data-lake-id="ud0c99b9d" id="ud0c99b9d"><p data-lake-id="udde9a27f" id="udde9a27f"><code data-lake-id="u9c08af51" id="u9c08af51"><span data-lake-id="u6c463094" id="u6c463094">3.14</span></code><span data-lake-id="u5779b338" id="u5779b338">, </span><code data-lake-id="u88781c53" id="u88781c53"><span data-lake-id="u515bc756" id="u515bc756">-0.01</span></code></p></td><td data-lake-id="u8d7eb9d3" id="u8d7eb9d3"><p data-lake-id="uc2937263" id="uc2937263"><span data-lake-id="u12a1eec7" id="u12a1eec7">带小数点的数</span></p></td></tr><tr data-lake-id="u22b34852" id="u22b34852" style="height: 38px"><td data-lake-id="u84eea001" id="u84eea001"><p data-lake-id="u5f0f0542" id="u5f0f0542" style="text-align: center"><strong><span data-lake-id="u64d61ca9" id="u64d61ca9">字符串</span></strong></p></td><td data-lake-id="uf50cda3a" id="uf50cda3a"><p data-lake-id="u3d104b7f" id="u3d104b7f" style="text-align: center"><code data-lake-id="u4e649858" id="u4e649858"><strong><span data-lake-id="u12f5c0db" id="u12f5c0db" style="color: #DF2A3F">str</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u491047be" id="u491047be">ing</span></code></p></td><td data-lake-id="ub2580fca" id="ub2580fca"><p data-lake-id="u4c8716a3" id="u4c8716a3"><code data-lake-id="ufb148d02" id="ufb148d02"><span data-lake-id="u78753e3b" id="u78753e3b">&quot;Hello&quot;</span></code><span data-lake-id="ubb297326" id="ubb297326">, </span><code data-lake-id="uf7d45b79" id="uf7d45b79"><span data-lake-id="ue0b353d0" id="ue0b353d0">'Python'</span></code></p></td><td data-lake-id="u8419fef2" id="u8419fef2"><p data-lake-id="uf2083e63" id="uf2083e63"><span data-lake-id="ud725aff2" id="ud725aff2">文本，要用引号包起来</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><blockquote data-lake-id="ua8f311ac" id="ua8f311ac" hindent="2em" class="lake-alert lake-alert-tips"><p data-lake-id="uee11729b" id="uee11729b"><span data-lake-id="ucd012c7c" id="ucd012c7c">📋</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u150260c0" id="u150260c0">备注</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u1ee1eb36" id="u1ee1eb36">：数据类型不只上述的这三种，还有很多种，我们暂且先知道以上这三种即可，其他数据类型会在后续章节中逐步讲解。</span></p></blockquote><h3 data-lake-id="ejAJS" id="ejAJS" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u6e4d3b84" id="u6e4d3b84">查看数据类型</span></h3><p data-lake-id="u6dfea138" id="u6dfea138" style="text-indent: 2em"><span data-lake-id="u616d31f2" id="u616d31f2">通过</span><code data-lake-id="uab5eec1f" id="uab5eec1f"><span data-lake-id="uf3b53583" id="uf3b53583">type()</span></code><span data-lake-id="ubb6054e8" id="ubb6054e8">可以查看数据类型，</span><code data-lake-id="u14a6e85b" id="u14a6e85b"><span data-lake-id="uc379bd54" id="uc379bd54">type()</span></code><span data-lake-id="ud637f9eb" id="ud637f9eb">会返回当前数据的具体类型。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%20type(%20)%E6%9F%A5%E7%9C%8B%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%E6%8E%A5%E6%94%B6%20type()%20%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E%E7%9A%84%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%5Cnresult1%20%3D%20type('%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89')%5Cnresult2%20%3D%20type(18)%5Cnresult3%20%3D%20type(72.5)%5Cn%5Cnprint(result1)%20%23%20%3Cclass%20'str'%3E%20%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E6%AD%A4%E5%A4%84%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AFstring%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%20string%20%E7%9A%84%E7%AE%80%E5%86%99%EF%BC%9Astr%5Cnprint(result2)%20%23%20%3Cclass%20'int'%3E%5Cnprint(result3)%20%23%20%3Cclass%20'float'%3E%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%20type(%20)%E6%9F%A5%E7%9C%8B%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22__widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22xF6Sc%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%2C%22widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%7D" hindent="2em"></card><blockquote data-lake-id="u65834321" id="u65834321" hindent="2em" class="lake-alert lake-alert-color4"><p data-lake-id="ue9692caf" id="ue9692caf"><span data-lake-id="uaa6a6594" id="uaa6a6594">📢</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u10bc9629" id="u10bc9629" style="color: #AD1A2B">注意：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="uc714a891" id="uc714a891">在</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u71ae78b1" id="u71ae78b1" style="color: #DF2A3F"> </span></strong><span data-lake-id="u250b9355" id="u250b9355">Python 中：变量无类型，数据有类型。</span></p><p data-lake-id="u9585d9ab" id="u9585d9ab"><span data-lake-id="ubf5287eb" id="ubf5287eb">例如</span><code data-lake-id="u10415c61" id="u10415c61"><span data-lake-id="u535ef438" id="u535ef438">a = 10</span></code><span data-lake-id="ud998a3b8" id="ud998a3b8">，其中</span><code data-lake-id="u9be134e6" id="u9be134e6"><span data-lake-id="ue24477af" id="ue24477af">a</span></code><span data-lake-id="u31b5cbe8" id="u31b5cbe8">是没有类型的，但</span><code data-lake-id="u6cff568d" id="u6cff568d"><span data-lake-id="u75845c4d" id="u75845c4d">a</span></code><span data-lake-id="u27ac1b6c" id="u27ac1b6c">所关联的数据</span><code data-lake-id="ud809645f" id="ud809645f"><span data-lake-id="u039b4ad8" id="u039b4ad8">10</span></code><span data-lake-id="u14b72e20" id="u14b72e20">是有类型的，</span><code data-lake-id="u4d5896c6" id="u4d5896c6"><span data-lake-id="u37e4032f" id="u37e4032f">10</span></code><span data-lake-id="u36ebdd85" id="u36ebdd85">是整型，我们经常说</span><code data-lake-id="u49bc754b" id="u49bc754b"><span data-lake-id="u1e58bd32" id="u1e58bd32">a</span></code><span data-lake-id="u4b61f56f" id="u4b61f56f">是整型，其实是一种不太严谨的表述，严谨的表述应该是：</span><code data-lake-id="u58d0f321" id="u58d0f321"><span data-lake-id="u06206ea9" id="u06206ea9">a</span></code><span data-lake-id="u4ad3b2bf" id="u4ad3b2bf">所对应的数据</span><code data-lake-id="u8f85f7d5" id="u8f85f7d5"><span data-lake-id="u289f5fdf" id="u289f5fdf">10</span></code><span data-lake-id="u73072254" id="u73072254">是整型。</span></p></blockquote><p data-lake-id="u40752ae5" id="u40752ae5" style="text-indent: 2em"><span data-lake-id="ued2e95c6" id="ued2e95c6">也可以把变量交给</span><code data-lake-id="u004d5f53" id="u004d5f53"><span data-lake-id="udb162db1" id="udb162db1">type()</span></code><span data-lake-id="u8098eed4" id="u8098eed4">，最终返回的是：变量所对应的数据的类型。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%20type(%20)%20%E6%9F%A5%E7%9C%8B%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%E6%89%80%E5%AF%B9%E5%BA%94%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%9A%84%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22name%20%3D%20'%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89'%5Cnage%20%3D%2018%5Cnweight%20%3D%2072.5%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%E6%8E%A5%E6%94%B6type()%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E%E7%9A%84%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%5Cnresult1%20%3D%20type(name)%5Cnresult2%20%3D%20type(age)%5Cnresult3%20%3D%20type(weight)%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E6%89%93%E5%8D%B0%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%89%E4%B8%AA%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%5Cnprint(result1)%20%20%23%20%3Cclass%20'str'%3E%5Cnprint(result2)%20%20%23%20%3Cclass%20'str'%3E%5Cnprint(result3)%20%20%23%20%3Cclass%20'float'%3E%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%20type(%20)%20%E6%9F%A5%E7%9C%8B%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%E6%89%80%E5%AF%B9%E5%BA%94%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%9A%84%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22__widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22z4GXM%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%2C%22widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%7D" hindent="2em"></card><p data-lake-id="ua8a4c3cb" id="ua8a4c3cb" style="text-indent: 2em"><span data-lake-id="u2849b123" id="u2849b123">当然也可以不使用变量接收，直接打印</span><code data-lake-id="u8b3c2288" id="u8b3c2288"><span data-lake-id="u77e6aa23" id="u77e6aa23">type()</span></code><span data-lake-id="ue9673fbb" id="ue9673fbb">的结果</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22name%20%3D%20'%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89'%5Cnage%20%3D%2018%5Cnweight%20%3D%2072.5%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E6%89%93%E5%8D%B0%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%89%E4%B8%AA%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%5Cnprint(type(name))%20%20%23%20%3Cclass%20'str'%3E%5Cnprint(type(age))%20%20%23%20%3Cclass%20'str'%3E%5Cnprint(type(weight))%20%20%23%20%3Cclass%20'float'%3E%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22__widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22xTo4E%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%2C%22widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%7D" hindent="2em"></card><h3 data-lake-id="ikjtt" id="ikjtt" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="ud9f8927d" id="ud9f8927d">整型</span></h3><details data-lake-id="u020f03a4" id="u020f03a4" open="true" class="lake-collapse"><summary data-lake-id="u29e28f94" id="u29e28f94" class="lake-summary"><span data-lake-id="udc3aa8a5" id="udc3aa8a5">1️⃣</span><strong><span data-lake-id="ubca64691" id="ubca64691">什么是整型？</span></strong></summary><p data-lake-id="u67b2dde4" id="u67b2dde4"><span data-lake-id="u6e908fb9" id="u6e908fb9">所谓整型就是没有小数点的数字， Python 中的整型，可以是</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u5e6a75f2" id="u5e6a75f2" style="color: #AD1A2B">任意大小</span></strong><span data-lake-id="ub9895495" id="ub9895495">的整数，包括负整数。</span></p></details><details data-lake-id="u7829508b" id="u7829508b" open="true" class="lake-collapse"><summary data-lake-id="uea08bdd6" id="uea08bdd6" class="lake-summary"><span data-lake-id="ubdbcc61a" id="ubdbcc61a">2️⃣</span><strong><span data-lake-id="ub08f7492" id="ub08f7492">分隔符</span></strong></summary><p data-lake-id="u1d7e118f" id="u1d7e118f"><span data-lake-id="ufb8081f4" id="ufb8081f4">当书写很大的数时，可使用下划线将数字分组，使其更清晰易读；Python 自动忽略数字之间的下划线，并且这种写法也适用于浮点数，但要注意：此种写法只有 Python3.6 及以上版本才支持。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22num1%20%3D%2010_000_000%5Cnprint(num1)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22cEmft%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card></details><details data-lake-id="u85bee36d" id="u85bee36d" open="true" class="lake-collapse"><summary data-lake-id="u3cfc84b4" id="u3cfc84b4" class="lake-summary"><span data-lake-id="u655e58c0" id="u655e58c0">3️⃣</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u80d14bff" id="u80d14bff">整型上限值</span></strong></summary><p data-lake-id="u40f82dea" id="u40f82dea"><span data-lake-id="u0452b5f9" id="u0452b5f9">Python 中存储整数上限值的大小取决于：计算机的内存和处理能力，我们先来认识一下『幂运算符』，代码如下：</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22a%20%3D%203%20**%202%20%20%23%20%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA3%E7%9A%84%E5%B9%B3%E6%96%B9%5Cnb%20%3D%202%20**%203%20%20%23%20%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA2%E7%9A%843%E6%AC%A1%E6%96%B9%5Cn%5Cnprint(a)%20%20%23%209%5Cnprint(b)%20%20%23%208%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22pPdt5%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u555ec46f" id="u555ec46f"><span data-lake-id="ue8cfc6c2" id="ue8cfc6c2">通过幂运算，构建一个很大的数，随后打印它，我们会发现：代码报错了。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22a%20%3D%209%20**%209999%20%20%23%209%E7%9A%849999%E6%AC%A1%E6%96%B9%5Cnprint(a)%20%20%23%20%E6%89%93%E5%8D%B0x%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22lEaMc%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="ude34927c" id="ude34927c"><card type="inline" name="image" value="data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F35780599%2F1760848408483-b9e815b6-3bcf-4ae1-99d5-d7653b784433.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u203aec9e-5023-46c9-8b12-1eab9764134%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22uebac531c-c172-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A1189.6969009343406%2C%22height%22%3A126%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A59554%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1963%2C%22originHeight%22%3A208%2C%22ratio%22%3A1.6500000953674316%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22FLE%5C%22C%3AUSERSLTIANYUDESKTOPCHECK%5C%5C%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E7%AC%AC3%E7%AB%A019%E5%B8%83%E5%B0%94%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B-PY%2C1INE2%2CIN%3CN%22%2C%22x%22%3A28%2C%22y%22%3A44%2C%22width%22%3A1151%2C%22height%22%3A34%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22EDSTHELINIT(4300DIGITS)FORINTEGERSTRINGCONVERSION%3BUSESYS%22%2C%22x%22%3A232%2C%22y%22%3A164%2C%22width%22%3A1003%2C%22height%22%3A36%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22A1UEERROR%3AEXCEEDSTHELIMIT%22%2C%22x%22%3A16%2C%22y%22%3A169%2C%22width%22%3A425%2C%22height%22%3A28%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22TRACEBACKMOSTRECENTC%22%2C%22x%22%3A0%2C%22y%22%3A8%2C%22width%22%3A367%2C%22height%22%3A28%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22PRINT(A)%23%E6%89%93%E5%8D%B0X%22%2C%22x%22%3A53%2C%22y%22%3A87%2C%22width%22%3A268%2C%22height%22%3A28%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E4%BA%BA%E4%BA%BA%E4%BA%BA%22%2C%22x%22%3A57%2C%22y%22%3A126%2C%22width%22%3A156%2C%22height%22%3A18%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22111AST)%22%2C%22x%22%3A378%2C%22y%22%3A12%2C%22width%22%3A126%2C%22height%22%3A19%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%231e2025%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22z7m4V%22%7D"></card></p><p data-lake-id="u533d2353" id="u533d2353"><span data-lake-id="u262c1fc5" id="u262c1fc5">上面报错中提及了</span><code data-lake-id="u5ad890c4" id="u5ad890c4"><span data-lake-id="u2e525ea5" id="u2e525ea5" style="color: #DF2A3F">&quot;Exceeds the limit (4300 digits)&quot;</span></code><span data-lake-id="u9c5ce241" id="u9c5ce241">，但这并不代表 Python 最大只能表示</span><code data-lake-id="u0635faae" id="u0635faae"><span data-lake-id="u0c922164" id="u0c922164">4300</span></code><span data-lake-id="u9244f224" id="u9244f224">位的数，比如我们把</span><code data-lake-id="udf39848b" id="udf39848b"><span data-lake-id="uec96a6e0" id="uec96a6e0">print</span></code><span data-lake-id="uf5e31a58" id="uf5e31a58">删掉，会发现代码正常运行，并且此时的</span><code data-lake-id="u0ba3b467" id="u0ba3b467"><span data-lake-id="uada55d0a" id="uada55d0a">a</span></code><span data-lake-id="ubd7984b2" id="ubd7984b2">也是可以正常参与数学运算的。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22a%20%3D%209%20**%209999%20%20%23%209%E7%9A%849999%E6%AC%A1%E6%96%B9%5Cnb%20%3D%20a%20%2B%20100%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Xp8Ur%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u90c54e8e" id="u90c54e8e"><span data-lake-id="ub38211e4" id="ub38211e4">那加上了</span><code data-lake-id="uc80e2509" id="uc80e2509"><span data-lake-id="u0295893f" id="u0295893f">print(a)</span></code><span data-lake-id="ue03c4464" id="ue03c4464">为什么报错呢？原因如下：</span></p><blockquote data-lake-id="ubbd3e096" id="ubbd3e096" class="lake-alert lake-alert-info"><p data-lake-id="u2c7cd3f9" id="u2c7cd3f9"><span data-lake-id="udd6bb473" id="udd6bb473">调用</span><code data-lake-id="ua570b675" id="ua570b675"><span data-lake-id="u2d1106a4" id="u2d1106a4">print(a)</span></code><span data-lake-id="u33693f64" id="u33693f64">时，Python 底层会把</span><code data-lake-id="u97fbbed3" id="u97fbbed3"><span data-lake-id="u977edeca" id="u977edeca">a</span></code><span data-lake-id="uf9e3014d" id="uf9e3014d">的类型转换成『字符串类型』再输出，而从 Python3.11 起，Python 对超大整数转换字符串的长度进行了限制，默认位数是</span><code data-lake-id="u6affdc0a" id="u6affdc0a"><span data-lake-id="u99e7109e" id="u99e7109e">4300</span></code><span data-lake-id="u3c79d715" id="u3c79d715">位。</span></p></blockquote><p data-lake-id="u26b7c149" id="u26b7c149"><strong><span data-lake-id="ub15781f7" id="ub15781f7">💡</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="ua5614a2e" id="ua5614a2e">扩展知识（了解即可）</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u3de2d75d" id="u3de2d75d">：</span></p><p data-lake-id="u16d98930" id="u16d98930"><span data-lake-id="ue5977d10" id="ue5977d10">通过如下代码，可以解除字符串转换时的</span><code data-lake-id="uf988d4f4" id="uf988d4f4"><span data-lake-id="uc24574f9" id="uc24574f9">4300</span></code><span data-lake-id="u17e13fd4" id="u17e13fd4">位限制，如下代码中包含模块相关内容，我们还没有讲到，所以不必纠结下面代码的具体含义，只需要先知道：</span><code data-lake-id="u19f321d9" id="u19f321d9"><span data-lake-id="u94993b38" id="u94993b38">4300</span></code><span data-lake-id="u76df2e53" id="u76df2e53">位的限制可以修改即可。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22import%20sys%5Cnsys.set_int_max_str_digits(0)%20%23%20%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E4%B8%BA0%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E4%B8%8D%E4%BD%9C%E4%BB%BB%E4%BD%95%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%5Cn%5Cnx%20%3D%209%20**%209999%20%20%23%209%E7%9A%849999%E6%AC%A1%E6%96%B9%5Cnprint(x)%20%20%23%20%E6%89%93%E5%8D%B0x%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22wUMcD%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card></details><h3 data-lake-id="MHA5g" id="MHA5g" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u61f04628" id="u61f04628">浮点型 </span></h3><details data-lake-id="ud8fc05f3" id="ud8fc05f3" open="true" class="lake-collapse"><summary data-lake-id="ucb8cc8af" id="ucb8cc8af" class="lake-summary"><span data-lake-id="u34c8dc40" id="u34c8dc40">1️⃣</span><strong><span data-lake-id="ufd47da7b" id="ufd47da7b">什么是浮点型？</span></strong></summary><p data-lake-id="ub0adf038" id="ub0adf038"><span data-lake-id="ueb1795ad" id="ueb1795ad">所谓浮点型，就是带小数点的数字，比如：</span><code data-lake-id="uce8b158c" id="uce8b158c"><span data-lake-id="ub8c847f1" id="ub8c847f1">3.14</span></code><span data-lake-id="ubaf0b149" id="ubaf0b149">、</span><code data-lake-id="u42c57ecf" id="u42c57ecf"><span data-lake-id="u4d3f0d89" id="u4d3f0d89">-0.5</span></code><span data-lake-id="u879cfe40" id="u879cfe40">、</span><code data-lake-id="u66240e8a" id="u66240e8a"><span data-lake-id="u592a6c06" id="u592a6c06">2.0</span></code><span data-lake-id="u41d3cccd" id="u41d3cccd">都是浮点数。</span></p></details><details data-lake-id="uffe1b04d" id="uffe1b04d" open="true" class="lake-collapse"><summary data-lake-id="u6222721e" id="u6222721e" class="lake-summary"><span data-lake-id="u97f61d2d" id="u97f61d2d">2️⃣</span><strong><span data-lake-id="ub2ac7a0f" id="ub2ac7a0f">浮点型的表示方式</span></strong></summary><ol list="u44d81e6e"><li fid="u0c68d1e8" data-lake-id="u7c277a13" id="u7c277a13"><span data-lake-id="u6c2a7106" id="u6c2a7106">直接写</span></li></ol><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E6%B5%AE%E7%82%B9%E5%9E%8B%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E5%B8%A6%E6%9C%89%E5%B0%8F%E6%95%B0%E7%82%B9%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E3%80%82%5Cnweight%20%3D%2065.2%5Cnbalance%20%3D%201425.58%5Cnout_temp%20%3D%20-25.2%5Cnprice%20%3D%20120.0%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22__widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22tZEhv%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%2C%22widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%7D"></card><ol list="u44d81e6e" start="2"><li fid="u0c68d1e8" data-lake-id="ub4d2488b" id="ub4d2488b"><span data-lake-id="uaff2a7ba" id="uaff2a7ba">科学计数法</span></li></ol><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E6%B5%AE%E7%82%B9%E5%9E%8B%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E8%AE%A1%E6%95%B0%E6%B3%95%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E3%80%82%5Cnspeed_of_sound%20%3D%203.4e%2B2%20%20%23%203.4%E4%B9%98%E4%BB%A510%E7%9A%842%E6%AC%A1%E6%96%B9%E3%80%82%5Cnworld_population%20%3D%207.8e9%20%20%23%207.8%E4%B9%98%E4%BB%A510%E7%9A%849%E6%AC%A1%E6%96%B9%E3%80%82%5Cndistance_sun_earth%20%3D%201.496E8%20%20%23%201.496%E4%B9%98%E4%BB%A510%E7%9A%848%E6%AC%A1%E6%96%B9%E3%80%82%5Cnspeed_of_light%20%3D%202.998E%2B8%20%20%23%202.998%E4%B9%98%E4%BB%A510%E7%9A%848%E6%AC%A1%E6%96%B9%E3%80%82%5Cn%5Cnone_ml%20%3D%201e-3%20%20%23%201%E4%B9%98%E4%BB%A510%E7%9A%84-3%E6%AC%A1%E6%96%B9%E3%80%82%5Cnone_mg%20%3D%201E-3%20%20%23%201%E4%B9%98%E4%BB%A510%E7%9A%84-3%E6%AC%A1%E6%96%B9%E3%80%82%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22__widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Y1lYF%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%2C%22widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%7D"></card></details><h3 data-lake-id="FFrDN" id="FFrDN" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u39c1ab8b" id="u39c1ab8b">字符串</span></h3><h4 data-lake-id="S9PEB" id="S9PEB"><span data-lake-id="u456d77b4" id="u456d77b4">1️⃣</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u24b4349e" id="u24b4349e">字符的</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="u3a7720ec" id="u3a7720ec" style="color: #AD1A2B">四种</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="ue2facdc3" id="ue2facdc3">定义方式</span></strong></h4><table data-lake-id="JN3pB" id="JN3pB" margin="true" row-head="#074A92;#FFFFFF" class="lake-table" style="width: 709px"><colgroup><col width="116"><col width="201"><col width="392"></colgroup><tbody><tr data-lake-id="u11abf7b6" id="u11abf7b6"><td data-lake-id="uac729309" id="uac729309"><p data-lake-id="u5b1d34af" id="u5b1d34af" style="text-align: center"><span data-lake-id="u0302fa08" id="u0302fa08">写法</span></p></td><td data-lake-id="u865b093c" id="u865b093c"><p data-lake-id="ua62ee922" id="ua62ee922" style="text-align: center"><span data-lake-id="u917973a8" id="u917973a8">示例</span></p></td><td data-lake-id="u68aa54df" id="u68aa54df"><p data-lake-id="ub80e2057" id="ub80e2057" style="text-align: center"><span data-lake-id="ud5ca6129" id="ud5ca6129">适用场景</span></p></td></tr><tr data-lake-id="ubdc43ece" id="ubdc43ece"><td data-lake-id="u40d97b3b" id="u40d97b3b"><p data-lake-id="u98a3d409" id="u98a3d409"><span data-lake-id="ueebc46bd" id="ueebc46bd">单引号</span></p></td><td data-lake-id="u4ab7898c" id="u4ab7898c"><p data-lake-id="ua558b9ef" id="ua558b9ef"><code data-lake-id="u7cd9ad2e" id="u7cd9ad2e"><span data-lake-id="uc16612db" id="uc16612db">'你好，尚硅谷'</span></code></p></td><td data-lake-id="ub166a262" id="ub166a262" rowSpan="2" style="vertical-align: middle"><p data-lake-id="u23f7e956" id="u23f7e956" style="text-align: center"><span data-lake-id="ubd74a150" id="ubd74a150">单行字符串（不能直接换行，换行需要使用圆括号）</span></p></td></tr><tr data-lake-id="u2756d7df" id="u2756d7df"><td data-lake-id="u2d353d6e" id="u2d353d6e"><p data-lake-id="u2b73ea0f" id="u2b73ea0f"><span data-lake-id="u59606f6b" id="u59606f6b">双引号</span></p></td><td data-lake-id="uf8e9ad9d" id="uf8e9ad9d"><p data-lake-id="u44ac58d0" id="u44ac58d0"><code data-lake-id="u4f3fa224" id="u4f3fa224"><span data-lake-id="u09f51b61" id="u09f51b61">&quot;你好，尚硅谷&quot;</span></code></p></td></tr><tr data-lake-id="ua1ae533c" id="ua1ae533c"><td data-lake-id="u860fbdc8" id="u860fbdc8"><p data-lake-id="uccccf478" id="uccccf478"><span data-lake-id="u58d2ac1b" id="u58d2ac1b">三个单引号</span></p></td><td data-lake-id="uf836401d" id="uf836401d"><p data-lake-id="ub2115941" id="ub2115941"><code data-lake-id="uabe28d21" id="uabe28d21"><span data-lake-id="u7a840ca4" id="u7a840ca4">'''你好，尚硅谷'''</span></code></p></td><td data-lake-id="u4ca07bc2" id="u4ca07bc2" rowSpan="2" style="vertical-align: middle"><p data-lake-id="ub4dd7065" id="ub4dd7065"><span data-lake-id="u157f2566" id="u157f2566">多行字符串（可以直接换行）</span></p></td></tr><tr data-lake-id="u3f53c265" id="u3f53c265"><td data-lake-id="uf768ffe3" id="uf768ffe3"><p data-lake-id="u62f7ca33" id="u62f7ca33"><span data-lake-id="uf0003b40" id="uf0003b40">三个双引号</span></p></td><td data-lake-id="u9d162e00" id="u9d162e00"><p data-lake-id="ueaa502b5" id="ueaa502b5"><code data-lake-id="ucdf47b72" id="ucdf47b72"><span data-lake-id="uc41c38c6" id="uc41c38c6">&quot;&quot;&quot;你好，尚硅谷&quot;&quot;&quot;&quot;</span></code></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p data-lake-id="u55e514e6" id="u55e514e6"><span data-lake-id="uf46e9eee" id="uf46e9eee">下面代码所表示的都是字符串：</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E5%8D%95%E5%BC%95%E5%8F%B7%E5%92%8C%E5%8F%8C%E5%BC%95%E5%8F%B7%E7%9A%84%E5%86%99%E6%B3%95%E6%98%AF%E7%AD%89%E4%BB%B7%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E4%BA%8C%E8%80%85%E9%83%BD%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E6%8D%A2%E8%A1%8C%EF%BC%88%E8%A6%81%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%86%E6%8B%AC%E5%8F%B7%E6%89%8D%E8%83%BD%E6%8D%A2%E8%A1%8C%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%95%E5%BC%95%E5%8F%B7%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%9A%E3%80%82%5Cnmessage1%20%3D%20'%E5%B0%9A%E7%A1%85%E8%B0%B7%EF%BC%8C%E8%AE%A9%E5%A4%A9%E4%B8%8B%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E9%9A%BE%E5%AD%A6%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF!'%5Cnmessage2%20%3D%20%5C%22%E5%B0%9A%E7%A1%85%E8%B0%B7%EF%BC%8C%E8%AE%A9%E5%A4%A9%E4%B8%8B%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E9%9A%BE%E5%AD%A6%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF!%5C%22%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E4%B8%89%E4%B8%AA%E5%8D%95%E5%BC%95%E5%8F%B7%E7%9A%84%E5%86%99%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E6%8D%A2%E8%A1%8C%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E4%B8%94%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%E5%A4%9A%E8%A1%8C%E6%B3%A8%E9%87%8A%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E3%80%82%5Cnmessage3%20%3D%20'''%E5%B0%9A%E7%A1%85%E8%B0%B7%EF%BC%8C%E8%AE%A9%E5%A4%A9%E4%B8%8B%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E9%9A%BE%E5%AD%A6%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF!'''%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E4%B8%89%E4%B8%AA%E5%8F%8C%E5%BC%95%E5%8F%B7%E7%9A%84%E5%86%99%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E6%8D%A2%E8%A1%8C%EF%BC%8C%E4%B9%9F%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%E5%A4%9A%E8%A1%8C%E6%B3%A8%E9%87%8A%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%98%E8%83%BD%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%B2%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E3%80%82%5Cnmessage4%20%3D%20%5C%22%5C%22%5C%22%E5%B0%9A%E7%A1%85%E8%B0%B7%EF%BC%8C%E8%AE%A9%E5%A4%A9%E4%B8%8B%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E9%9A%BE%E5%AD%A6%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF!%5C%22%5C%22%5C%22%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22__widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ezgZB%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%2C%22widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%7D"></card><h4 data-lake-id="qIuUR" id="qIuUR"><strong><span data-lake-id="ubcd31b97" id="ubcd31b97">2️⃣</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="u17a91fc3" id="u17a91fc3">字符串的格式化输出</span></strong></h4><details data-lake-id="ud050abac" id="ud050abac" open="true" class="lake-collapse"><summary data-lake-id="u7ff11608" id="u7ff11608" class="lake-summary"><strong><span data-lake-id="uc65723dd" id="uc65723dd">写法 1</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u702374d5" id="u702374d5">：直接用加号进行拼接，写起来很麻烦，而且只能是字符串之间拼接。</span></summary><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22name%20%3D%20'%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89'%5Cngender%20%3D%20'%E7%94%B7'%5Cnweight%20%3D%2065.2%5Cnage%20%3D%2012%5Cn%5Cninfo1%20%3D%20'%E6%88%91%E5%8F%AB'%20%2B%20name%20%2B%20'%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%91%E6%98%AF'%20%2B%20gender%20%2B%20'%E7%94%9F'%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22uwtCk%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card></details><details data-lake-id="ub5ac7ce8" id="ub5ac7ce8" open="true" class="lake-collapse"><summary data-lake-id="u24e35aca" id="u24e35aca" class="lake-summary"><strong><span data-lake-id="u59587292" id="u59587292">写法 2</span></strong><span data-lake-id="ud085ed27" id="ud085ed27">：使用占位符。</span></summary><p data-lake-id="u4eeed75b" id="u4eeed75b"><span data-lake-id="u8c272a22" id="u8c272a22">具体规则：</span></p><ul list="u0d706fab"><li fid="u27de1ff8" data-lake-id="u55a6cf70" id="u55a6cf70"><code data-lake-id="u992d8c26" id="u992d8c26"><span data-lake-id="u2f389440" id="u2f389440">%s</span></code><span data-lake-id="udd7b6480" id="udd7b6480">占位字符串</span></li><li fid="u27de1ff8" data-lake-id="u79f6bc34" id="u79f6bc34"><code data-lake-id="u46ad0968" id="u46ad0968"><span data-lake-id="ubd87aa24" id="ubd87aa24">%f</span></code><span data-lake-id="udd0d1daf" id="udd0d1daf">占位浮点数</span></li><li fid="u27de1ff8" data-lake-id="u5a6c8265" id="u5a6c8265"><code data-lake-id="u8e1a488b" id="u8e1a488b"><span data-lake-id="u8296b0ab" id="u8296b0ab">%i</span></code><span data-lake-id="u25dfe094" id="u25dfe094">占位整数</span></li><li fid="u27de1ff8" data-lake-id="u6f29446d" id="u6f29446d"><code data-lake-id="u835cabf7" id="u835cabf7"><span data-lake-id="u7e14bb36" id="u7e14bb36">%d</span></code><span data-lake-id="u24a19ecc" id="u24a19ecc">占位十进制的整数</span></li><li fid="u27de1ff8" data-lake-id="u02eddff6" id="u02eddff6"><code data-lake-id="u23d3334c" id="u23d3334c"><span data-lake-id="u9c778f57" id="u9c778f57">%s</span></code><span data-lake-id="u6eec1441" id="u6eec1441">是万能的（如果我们提供的数据不是字符串，那 Python 就会把数据转成字符串）。</span></li></ul><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22name%20%3D%20'%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89'%5Cngender%20%3D%20'%E7%94%B7'%5Cnweight%20%3D%2065.2%5Cnage%20%3D%2012%5Cn%5Cninfo2%20%3D%20'%E6%88%91%E5%8F%AB%25s%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%91%E6%98%AF%25s%E7%94%9F%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%91%E4%BD%93%E9%87%8D%E6%98%AF%25f%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B4%E9%BE%84%E6%98%AF%25d'%20%25%20(name%2C%20gender%2C%20weight%2C%20age)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22GvI4H%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card></details><details data-lake-id="u42be720f" id="u42be720f" open="true" class="lake-collapse"><summary data-lake-id="u87bf979d" id="u87bf979d" class="lake-summary"><strong><span data-lake-id="u62e794a1" id="u62e794a1">写法 3</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u26d4fd11" id="u26d4fd11">：使用 f-string，这是目前 Python 最推荐的方式。</span></summary><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22name%20%3D%20'%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89'%5Cngender%20%3D%20'%E7%94%B7'%5Cnweight%20%3D%2065.2%5Cnage%20%3D%2012%5Cn%5Cninfo3%20%3D%20f'%E6%88%91%E5%8F%AB%7Bname%7D%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%91%E6%98%AF%7Bgender%7D%E7%94%9F%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%91%E4%BD%93%E9%87%8D%E6%98%AF%7Bweight%7D%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B4%E9%BE%84%E6%98%AF%7Bage%7D'%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22I4SRG%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card></details><h4 data-lake-id="EuzSl" id="EuzSl"><span data-lake-id="u8364bbaa" id="u8364bbaa">3️⃣</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u8801cf25" id="u8801cf25">占位符精度控</span></strong></h4><p data-lake-id="u831c7c96" id="u831c7c96"><span data-lake-id="u8e5b3d86" id="u8e5b3d86">在占位符前方，可以使用</span><code data-lake-id="u8e7d7354" id="u8e7d7354"><span data-lake-id="u2d1973df" id="u2d1973df">m.n</span></code><span data-lake-id="u22ae884f" id="u22ae884f">的形式来指定精度，具体规则见下图：</span></p><p data-lake-id="ud9e7a768" id="ud9e7a768"><card type="inline" name="image" value="data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F35780599%2F1760683740087-1061a968-bbf5-4cb2-8f29-4371145a7656.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22uf6582e3a-7e4d-41c0-84b6-5d5ef45db6a%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u9dc15b59-c913-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A613.7802734375%2C%22height%22%3A208%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A204281%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1355%2C%22originHeight%22%3A460%2C%22ratio%22%3A1.6500000953674316%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%221%2C%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%B2%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%80%E5%B0%8F%E5%AE%BD%E5%BA%A6%2C%E4%BD%8D%E6%95%B0%E4%B8%8D%E5%A4%9F%E4%BC%9A%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E7%A9%BA%E6%A0%BC%E8%A1%A5%E5%85%A8%2C%E4%BD%8D%E6%95%B0%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%8E%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%B2%E9%95%BF%E5%BA%A6%E5%88%99%E4%B8%8D%E8%B5%B7%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%22%2C%22x%22%3A31%2C%22y%22%3A336%2C%22width%22%3A1077%2C%22height%22%3A35%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E7%B2%BE%E5%BA%A6%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%2C%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%9A%E8%BE%93%E5%87%BAN%E4%B8%AA%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6(%E8%8B%A5N%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%8E%E5%AE%9E%E9%99%85%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%B2%E9%95%BF%E5%BA%A6%2C%E5%88%99%E4%B8%8D%E8%B5%B7%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8)%22%2C%22x%22%3A453%2C%22y%22%3A250%2C%22width%22%3A859%2C%22height%22%3A34%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%222.%E6%AD%A3%E6%95%B0%E6%98%AF%E5%8F%B3%E5%AF%B9%E9%BD%90%2C%E8%B4%9F%E6%95%B0%E6%98%AF%E5%B7%A6%E5%AF%B9%E9%BD%90%22%2C%22x%22%3A27%2C%22y%22%3A376%2C%22width%22%3A401%2C%22height%22%3A35%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%25OM.NS%22%2C%22x%22%3A524%2C%22y%22%3A61%2C%22width%22%3A176%2C%22height%22%3