%E8%B4%9F%E6%95%B0%E6%98%AF%E5%B7%A6%E5%AF%B9%E9%BD%90%22%2C%22x%22%3A30%2C%22y%22%3A414%2C%22width%22%3A408%2C%22height%22%3A30%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%25OM.ND%22%2C%22x%22%3A525%2C%22y%22%3A56%2C%22width%22%3A195%2C%22height%22%3A52%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%234a4843%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22eqPPZ%22%7D"></card></p><p data-lake-id="u2eb344d6" id="u2eb344d6"><span data-lake-id="u713e24bf" id="u713e24bf">示例代码：</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22info%20%3D%20'%E6%88%91%E5%8F%AB%25-4.1s%EF%BC%8C%E6%80%A7%E5%88%AB%E6%98%AF%253.2s%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%93%E9%87%8D%E6%98%AF%25-9.3f%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B4%E9%BE%84%E6%98%AF%25-6.4d'%20%25%20(name%2C%20gender%2C%20weight%2C%20age)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22__widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22RZAax%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%2C%22widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%7D"></card><h4 data-lake-id="yLLmJ" id="yLLmJ"><span data-lake-id="u5652f838" id="u5652f838">4️⃣</span><strong><span data-lake-id="ufb825ee7" id="ufb825ee7">转义字符</span></strong></h4><p data-lake-id="u9a7da4ec" id="u9a7da4ec"><span data-lake-id="uf2467f72" id="uf2467f72">在字符串中，有些字符不能直接写（换行、制表符、引号等）这时就要使用转义字符。</span></p><p data-lake-id="ua6a62798" id="ua6a62798"><span data-lake-id="u6c16ffa4" id="u6c16ffa4">例如下面的</span><code data-lake-id="u41c29acf" id="u41c29acf"><span data-lake-id="u6e86ce49" id="u6e86ce49">message</span></code><span data-lake-id="u6a5f9e3d" id="u6a5f9e3d">字符串中包含了一个单引号，但如果就这样直接写，就会报错</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22print('%E5%9C%A8Python%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8'%E5%8C%85%E8%A3%B9%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%B2')%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22__widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22S98bm%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%2C%22widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u6e74e497" id="u6e74e497"><span data-lake-id="u268b42f1" id="u268b42f1">使用转义字符后，即可正常输出：</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22print('%E5%9C%A8Python%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%5C%5C'%E5%8C%85%E8%A3%B9%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%B2')%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22__widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22fZaRr%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%2C%22widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u2028e2ad" id="u2028e2ad"><span data-lake-id="u7a2e5e05" id="u7a2e5e05">常见的转义字符梳理：</span></p><table data-lake-id="TtJKg" id="TtJKg" margin="true" row-head="#074A92;#FFFFFF" class="lake-table" style="width: 501px"><colgroup><col width="136"><col width="365"></colgroup><tbody><tr data-lake-id="u86f96dbc" id="u86f96dbc"><td data-lake-id="uaeb755f7" id="uaeb755f7"><p data-lake-id="u1a5d0bf6" id="u1a5d0bf6" style="text-align: center"><span data-lake-id="uf658eb15" id="uf658eb15">转义字符</span></p></td><td data-lake-id="u6d3db2b7" id="u6d3db2b7"><p data-lake-id="u9c9ab10f" id="u9c9ab10f" style="text-align: center"><span data-lake-id="uf36e6b11" id="uf36e6b11">表示的含义</span></p></td></tr><tr data-lake-id="u2dccf536" id="u2dccf536"><td data-lake-id="u45b9b5f2" id="u45b9b5f2"><p data-lake-id="uae89975b" id="uae89975b"><code data-lake-id="ua253da1e" id="ua253da1e"><span data-lake-id="ufddd29d0" id="ufddd29d0">\'</span></code></p></td><td data-lake-id="ucbcde5bd" id="ucbcde5bd"><p data-lake-id="ucbc837d7" id="ucbc837d7"><code data-lake-id="udb70dbc6" id="udb70dbc6"><span data-lake-id="u1f8e4f3f" id="u1f8e4f3f">'</span></code></p></td></tr><tr data-lake-id="uc2680bf7" id="uc2680bf7"><td data-lake-id="u3c9e1166" id="u3c9e1166"><p data-lake-id="u9d0124f8" id="u9d0124f8"><code data-lake-id="ud9751a46" id="ud9751a46"><span data-lake-id="u1b076565" id="u1b076565">\&quot;</span></code></p></td><td data-lake-id="uc7eb4f95" id="uc7eb4f95"><p data-lake-id="u3f339641" id="u3f339641"><code data-lake-id="u964011ac" id="u964011ac"><span data-lake-id="u1caa3875" id="u1caa3875">&quot;</span></code></p></td></tr><tr data-lake-id="u90c17dca" id="u90c17dca"><td data-lake-id="ue68b97d6" id="ue68b97d6"><p data-lake-id="u18203124" id="u18203124"><code data-lake-id="u7c17fe50" id="u7c17fe50"><span data-lake-id="u36ef9adf" id="u36ef9adf">\n</span></code></p></td><td data-lake-id="uce7fd3d7" id="uce7fd3d7"><p data-lake-id="u099faaac" id="u099faaac"><span data-lake-id="ue2a4575e" id="ue2a4575e">换行</span></p></td></tr><tr data-lake-id="ua7cba9c3" id="ua7cba9c3"><td data-lake-id="u4ed09060" id="u4ed09060"><p data-lake-id="u570f7b55" id="u570f7b55"><code data-lake-id="u578f7dfe" id="u578f7dfe"><span data-lake-id="u1dd48e32" id="u1dd48e32">\\</span></code></p></td><td data-lake-id="uc7b13453" id="uc7b13453"><p data-lake-id="ub80d8676" id="ub80d8676"><code data-lake-id="u14142ab0" id="u14142ab0"><span data-lake-id="ue023ad7b" id="ue023ad7b">\</span></code></p></td></tr><tr data-lake-id="u7a399c19" id="u7a399c19"><td data-lake-id="uace60c31" id="uace60c31"><p data-lake-id="ua11ba275" id="ua11ba275"><code data-lake-id="u29e9e8d6" id="u29e9e8d6"><span data-lake-id="u918d2d32" id="u918d2d32">\b</span></code></p></td><td data-lake-id="u71a4386c" id="u71a4386c"><p data-lake-id="u3e807fd1" id="u3e807fd1"><span data-lake-id="u33bdca7a" id="u33bdca7a">删除前一个字符</span></p></td></tr><tr data-lake-id="u3c5a0cf7" id="u3c5a0cf7"><td data-lake-id="u3bcbccb8" id="u3bcbccb8"><p data-lake-id="u0364bc7e" id="u0364bc7e"><code data-lake-id="u28f16b00" id="u28f16b00"><span data-lake-id="u0c3c4fe8" id="u0c3c4fe8">\r</span></code></p></td><td data-lake-id="u0e517ed6" id="u0e517ed6"><p data-lake-id="ucad4e2fb" id="ucad4e2fb"><span data-lake-id="ud5c1d611" id="ud5c1d611">使光标回到本行开头，覆盖输出</span></p></td></tr><tr data-lake-id="ubc0949eb" id="ubc0949eb"><td data-lake-id="u010c88c5" id="u010c88c5"><p data-lake-id="ud85142b6" id="ud85142b6"><code data-lake-id="ubd7dbb43" id="ubd7dbb43"><span data-lake-id="ua327f743" id="ua327f743">\t</span></code></p></td><td data-lake-id="u9f69fdcb" id="u9f69fdcb"><p data-lake-id="uf219ed09" id="uf219ed09"><span data-lake-id="u57af504f" id="u57af504f">表示水平制表符（让光标跳转到下一个制表位）</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p data-lake-id="u7dec562d" id="u7dec562d"><span data-lake-id="u25e5cc73" id="u25e5cc73">测试代码：</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%20%5C%5C'%20%E8%BE%93%E5%87%BA%20'%5Cnprint('%E5%9C%A8Python%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%5C%5C'%E5%8C%85%E8%A3%B9%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%B2')%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%20%5C%5C%5C%22%20%E8%BE%93%E5%87%BA%20%5C%22%5Cnprint(%5C%22%E5%9C%A8Python%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%5C%5C%5C%22%E5%8C%85%E8%A3%B9%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%B2%5C%22)%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%20%5C%5Cn%20%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E6%8D%A2%E8%A1%8C%5Cnprint('%E6%B3%A8%E5%86%8C%E4%BC%9A%E5%91%98%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF%EF%BC%9A%5C%5Cn%E5%A7%93%E5%90%8D%5C%5Cn%E5%B9%B4%E9%BE%84%5C%5Cn%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E5%8F%B7')%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%20%5C%5C%5C%5C%20%E8%BE%93%E5%87%BA%20%5C%5C%5Cnprint('D%3A%5C%5C%5C%5Cnice')%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%20%5C%5Cb%20%E5%88%A0%E9%99%A4%E5%89%8D%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%5Cnprint('helloo%5C%5Cb')%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%20%5C%5Cr%20%E4%BD%BF%E5%85%89%E6%A0%87%E5%9B%9E%E5%88%B0%E6%9C%AC%E8%A1%8C%E5%BC%80%E5%A4%B4%EF%BC%8C%E8%A6%86%E7%9B%96%E8%BE%93%E5%87%BA%5Cnprint('67%25%5C%5Cr68%25')%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%20%5C%5Ct%20%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3%E5%88%B6%E8%A1%A8%E7%AC%A6%EF%BC%88%E8%AE%A9%E5%85%89%E6%A0%87%E8%B7%B3%E8%BD%AC%E5%88%B0%E4%B8%8B%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%88%B6%E8%A1%A8%E4%BD%8D%EF%BC%89%5Cn%23%20%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%88%B6%E8%A1%A8%E4%BD%8D%E5%88%B0%E5%BA%95%E6%98%AF%E5%87%A0%E4%BD%8D%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%8D%E7%A1%AE%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E5%9C%A8%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%B2%E5%90%8E%E9%9D%A2%E5%8A%A0.expandtabs()%E6%9D%A5%E6%8C%87%E5%AE%9A%E4%BD%8D%E6%95%B0%E3%80%82%5Cnprint('1234123412341234')%5Cnprint('ab%5C%5Ctcd.expandtabs(4)')%5Cnprint('abc%5C%5Ctd.expandtabs(4)')%5Cnprint('abcd%5C%5Cta.expandtabs(4)')%5Cnprint('%E6%88%91%E6%98%AF%5C%5Ct%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87.expandtabs(4)')%5Cn%5Cnprint('12341234123412341234')%5Cnprint('%E5%A7%93%E5%90%8D%5C%5Ct%E6%80%A7%E5%88%AB%5C%5Ct%E5%B9%B4%E9%BE%84')%5Cnprint('%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89%5C%5Ct%E7%94%B7%5C%5Ct%5C%5Ct18')%5Cnprint('%E6%9D%8E%E5%9B%9B%5C%5Ct%E5%A5%B3%5C%5Ct%5C%5Ct25')%5Cnprint('%E7%8E%8B%E4%BA%94%5C%5Ct%E7%94%B7%5C%5Ct%5C%5Ct32')%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22__widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22gVjAC%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%2C%22widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%7D"></card><h2 data-lake-id="uBSYd" id="uBSYd" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u2b47a5e3" id="u2b47a5e3">数据类型转换</span></h2><h3 data-lake-id="Af12S" id="Af12S" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u054554d4" id="u054554d4">概述</span></h3><p data-lake-id="u4ea76cb6" id="u4ea76cb6"><span data-lake-id="ud5f07329" id="ud5f07329">何为数据类型转换？—— 把一种类型的数据，变成另一种类型。</span></p><h3 data-lake-id="YAoOZ" id="YAoOZ" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u292d8539" id="u292d8539">为什么要数据类型转换</span></h3><p data-lake-id="u86cc56f7" id="u86cc56f7"><span data-lake-id="uf019bd47" id="uf019bd47">例如下面这些场景中，我们得到的数据类型，和最终要用的数据类型是不一致的，那就需要类型转换：</span></p><blockquote data-lake-id="uf94255cb" id="uf94255cb" class="lake-alert lake-alert-info"><ol list="ubc691dfb"><li fid="u67def022" data-lake-id="u47687d48" id="u47687d48"><span data-lake-id="u0c04fee9" id="u0c04fee9">用户输入的内容是都是字符串，若需要进行数学运算，就必须进行数据类型转换。</span></li><li fid="u67def022" data-lake-id="u159f7542" id="u159f7542"><span data-lake-id="u34390d78" id="u34390d78">对文件进行写入操作时，要将其他类型的数据转为字符串。</span></li><li fid="u67def022" data-lake-id="ub6139ee3" id="ub6139ee3"><span data-lake-id="ubc891ab4" id="ubc891ab4">从数据库中读取出的内容都是字符串若需要进行数学运算，也需要数据类型转换</span></li></ol><p data-lake-id="ua93a1e9f" id="ua93a1e9f" style="text-indent: 2em"><span data-lake-id="u2e4bbcbb" id="u2e4bbcbb">......</span></p></blockquote><h3 data-lake-id="ReqFQ" id="ReqFQ" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u7e04fd7a" id="u7e04fd7a">具体转换方式</span></h3><p data-lake-id="uc0e86d82" id="uc0e86d82"><span data-lake-id="uf38092dc" id="uf38092dc">通过以下函数，可以对数据类型进行转换</span></p><table data-lake-id="uBNnA" id="uBNnA" margin="true" row-head="#074A92;#FFFFFF" class="lake-table" style="width: 607px"><colgroup><col width="87"><col width="206"><col width="314"></colgroup><tbody><tr data-lake-id="u18b60224" id="u18b60224"><td data-lake-id="u72a200fb" id="u72a200fb"><p data-lake-id="u4aefe1c5" id="u4aefe1c5" style="text-align: center"><strong><span data-lake-id="u002a60a6" id="u002a60a6">函数</span></strong></p></td><td data-lake-id="u0764b8f6" id="u0764b8f6"><p data-lake-id="ue73f3df4" id="ue73f3df4" style="text-align: center"><strong><span data-lake-id="u53d7d7bc" id="u53d7d7bc">说明</span></strong></p></td><td data-lake-id="ucfa504bb" id="ucfa504bb"><p data-lake-id="uee513866" id="uee513866" style="text-align: center"><strong><span data-lake-id="ud1e0dfdd" id="ud1e0dfdd">示例</span></strong></p></td></tr><tr data-lake-id="u8687761c" id="u8687761c"><td data-lake-id="u6d5e87a8" id="u6d5e87a8" style="background-color: #f2f2f2; vertical-align: middle"><p data-lake-id="udda33917" id="udda33917"><strong><span data-lake-id="u99e154a1" id="u99e154a1" style="color: black">int(x)</span></strong></p></td><td data-lake-id="ua533290d" id="ua533290d" style="background-color: #f2f2f2; vertical-align: middle"><p data-lake-id="u3e1fdfd0" id="u3e1fdfd0"><span data-lake-id="ud5bda125" id="ud5bda125" style="color: black">将x转换为一个整数</span></p></td><td data-lake-id="u7d5cd9c8" id="u7d5cd9c8" style="background-color: #f2f2f2"><p data-lake-id="u3283583d" id="u3283583d"><card type="inline" name="image" value="data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F35780599%2F1760685873454-38c2d74a-8af0-414a-b15d-22bbe4340282.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22uf4242ce9-6504-4f3b-8f1f-2eb991a4b11%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u9dc15b59-c913-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%