%22TpeyU%22%7D"></card></p><blockquote data-lake-id="u55c43aec" id="u55c43aec" class="lake-alert lake-alert-tips"><p data-lake-id="u9054adc9" id="u9054adc9"><span data-lake-id="u79add097" id="u79add097">📋</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u15589961" id="u15589961">备注</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u78df3a2c" id="u78df3a2c">：True 和 False 是布尔类型，会在下一小节讲，暂且先知道：True 表示真，False 表示假。</span></p></blockquote><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%E6%AF%94%E8%BE%83%E8%BF%90%E7%AE%97%E7%AC%A6%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%3D%3D%E5%88%A4%E6%96%AD%E5%B7%A6%E5%8F%B3%E4%B8%A4%E4%BE%A7%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E7%9B%B8%E7%AD%89%5Cna%20%3D%205%5Cnb%20%3D%207%5Cnc%20%3D%20'5'%5Cnresult%20%3D%20a%20%3D%3D%20c%5Cnprint(result)%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8!%3D%E5%88%A4%E6%96%AD%E5%B7%A6%E5%8F%B3%E4%B8%A4%E4%BE%A7%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E4%B8%8D%E7%AD%89%5Cna%20%3D%205%5Cnb%20%3D%207%5Cnc%20%3D%20'5'%5Cnresult%20%3D%20a%20!%3D%20c%5Cnprint(result)%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%3E%E5%88%A4%E6%96%AD%E5%B7%A6%E4%BE%A7%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%8E%E5%8F%B3%E4%BE%A7%5Cna%20%3D%209%5Cnb%20%3D%207%5Cnc%20%3D%20'5'%5Cnresult%20%3D%20a%20%3E%20b%5Cnprint(result)%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%3C%E5%88%A4%E6%96%AD%E5%B7%A6%E4%BE%A7%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%8E%E5%8F%B3%E4%BE%A7%5Cna%20%3D%203%5Cnb%20%3D%207%5Cnc%20%3D%20'5'%5Cnresult%20%3D%20a%20%3C%20b%5Cnprint(result)%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%3E%3D%E5%88%A4%E6%96%AD%E5%B7%A6%E4%BE%A7%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%8E%E7%AD%89%E4%BA%8E%E5%8F%B3%E4%BE%A7%5Cna%20%3D%206%5Cnb%20%3D%207%5Cnc%20%3D%20'5'%5Cnresult%20%3D%20a%20%3E%3D%20b%5Cnprint(result)%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%3C%3D%E5%88%A4%E6%96%AD%E5%B7%A6%E4%BE%A7%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%8E%E7%AD%89%E4%BA%8E%E5%8F%B3%E4%BE%A7%5Cna%20%3D%209%5Cnb%20%3D%207%5Cnc%20%3D%20'5'%5Cnresult%20%3D%20a%20%3C%3D%20b%5Cnprint(result)%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A%E8%BF%99%E4%BA%9B%E6%AF%94%E8%BE%83%E8%BF%90%E7%AE%97%E7%AC%A6%EF%BC%8C%E5%90%8C%E6%A0%B7%E9%80%82%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8E%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%B2%5Cnmsg1%20%3D%20'abc'%5Cnmsg2%20%3D%20'abc666'%5Cnprint(msg1%20%3D%3D%20msg2)%5Cn%5Cnmsg1%20%3D%20'abc'%5Cnmsg2%20%3D%20'abc'%5Cnprint(msg1%20!%3D%20msg2)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%E6%AF%94%E8%BE%83%E8%BF%90%E7%AE%97%E7%AC%A6%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22KG02Z%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><blockquote data-lake-id="u4c534fb5" id="u4c534fb5" class="lake-alert lake-alert-info"><p data-lake-id="u0f612c3c" id="u0f612c3c"><span data-lake-id="ufe0891b5" id="ufe0891b5">​</span><strong><span data-lake-id="ue055660a" id="ue055660a">📌</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="u4b54a69e" id="u4b54a69e">小贴士：</span></strong></p><ul list="uc9579ccb"><li fid="u6246e379" data-lake-id="ub6c35ed3" id="ub6c35ed3"><span data-lake-id="u9e247475" id="u9e247475">字符串进行比较时，是依次比较每个字符的 Unicode 编码。</span></li><li fid="u6246e379" data-lake-id="ufe160383" id="ufe160383"><span data-lake-id="u4eaa0b41" id="u4eaa0b41">Unicode 编码是一种全球通用的字符编码标准，它会给每个字符都分配一个“身份证号”。  </span></li></ul></blockquote><p data-lake-id="u5e18f1f7" id="u5e18f1f7"><span data-lake-id="ud69206ad" id="ud69206ad">具体比较规则是：</span></p><blockquote data-lake-id="ubbd33fc4" id="ubbd33fc4" class="lake-alert lake-alert-info"><ol list="u87639242"><li fid="ud70046e4" data-lake-id="u76f13316" id="u76f13316"><span data-lake-id="uc19fb3eb" id="uc19fb3eb">从左到右，依次比较两个字符串中的字符。</span></li><li fid="ud70046e4" data-lake-id="u6e6808a2" id="u6e6808a2"><span data-lake-id="u8c020b73" id="u8c020b73">先比较第一个字符：</span></li></ol><ul list="u28aa95b6" data-lake-indent="1"><li fid="ud70046e4" data-lake-id="u0a675278" id="u0a675278"><span data-lake-id="u81a58248" id="u81a58248">如果两个字符不相等，就直接根据它们的 Unicode 码值比较大小。</span></li><li fid="ud70046e4" data-lake-id="uc191a25f" id="uc191a25f"><span data-lake-id="u2916ed6b" id="u2916ed6b">如果相等，则继续下一步。</span></li></ul><ol list="u87639242" start="3"><li fid="ud70046e4" data-lake-id="ucd8a48d9" id="ucd8a48d9"><span data-lake-id="ua20f3db4" id="ua20f3db4">继续比较下一个字符，依次往后进行，直到遇到不相等的字符为止。</span></li><li fid="ud70046e4" data-lake-id="ua533d167" id="ua533d167"><span data-lake-id="uedb06011" id="uedb06011">当出现不相等的字符时，比较它们的 Unicode 码大小，后续的字符将不再参与比较。</span></li></ol><p data-lake-id="ufbbf049f" id="ufbbf049f" style="text-indent: 2em"><card type="inline" name="image" value="data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F35780599%2F1760688683540-8b0ab28b-5d77-4128-805b-535f25a816d9.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u81739ba7-a320-4844-b9ae-4d16cd315ed%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u9dc15b59-c913-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A530%2C%22height%22%3A264%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A575921%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1694%2C%22originHeight%22%3A845%2C%22ratio%22%3A1.6500000953674316%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22PYTHON%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%B2%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E6%AF%94%E8%BE%83%E6%97%B6%2C%E6%98%AF%E4%BE%9D%E6%AC%A1%E6%AF%94%E8%BE%83%E6%AF%8F%E4%B8%AA%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E7%9A%84UNICODE%E7%BC%96%E7%A0%81.%22%2C%22x%22%3A92%2C%22y%22%3A12%2C%22width%22%3A1475%2C%22height%22%3A57%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%3AUNICODE%E7%BC%96%E7%A0%81%E6%98%AFPYTHON%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%89%E7%9A%84%2C%E8%80%8C%E6%98%AF%E5%85%A8%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E9%80%9A%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86.%22%2C%22x%22%3A113%2C%22y%22%3A109%2C%22width%22%3A1473%2C%22height%22%3A51%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22PYTHON%E4%B8%AD%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E4