ndex-type="2"><span data-lake-id="uacbdad7a" id="uacbdad7a">循环</span></h2><p data-lake-id="udd87e878" id="udd87e878"><span data-lake-id="uf373d26a" id="uf373d26a">循环是一种让代码“重复执行”的机制，当某个条件成立时，程序会反复执行一些语句，直到条件不再满足时，再停止运行。</span></p><h3 data-lake-id="cH3ib" id="cH3ib" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="ua6ef40b3" id="ua6ef40b3">while 循环</span></h3><p data-lake-id="u1c82058f" id="u1c82058f"><strong><span data-lake-id="u09353dc7" id="u09353dc7">1️⃣</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="u0072c5ec" id="u0072c5ec">语法格式：</span></strong></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22while%20%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8B%E6%97%B6%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C1%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8B%E6%97%B6%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C2%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ZD2w6%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u948488f2" id="u948488f2"><strong><span data-lake-id="uea0353f2" id="uea0353f2">2️⃣</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="ua1f13c11" id="ua1f13c11">循环逻辑：</span></strong></p><blockquote data-lake-id="ua5428754" id="ua5428754" class="lake-alert lake-alert-tips"><ol list="ue28d87e7"><li fid="u8e35b714" data-lake-id="u82d8f852" id="u82d8f852" style="text-align: justify"><span data-lake-id="u2107d4ea" id="u2107d4ea">先判断循环条件是否成立（是否为 </span><code data-lake-id="u1df5f8b9" id="u1df5f8b9"><span data-lake-id="u8f6140cd" id="u8f6140cd">True</span></code><span data-lake-id="u9988b01a" id="u9988b01a">）</span></li><li fid="u8e35b714" data-lake-id="u8d3015ab" id="u8d3015ab" style="text-align: justify"><span data-lake-id="ub2b1998c" id="ub2b1998c">如果成立 → 执行循环中的代码</span></li><li fid="u8e35b714" data-lake-id="u000941af" id="u000941af" style="text-align: justify"><span data-lake-id="ucb599f63" id="ucb599f63">执行完循环体 → 再次判断循环条件</span></li><li fid="u8e35b714" data-lake-id="udedb9714" id="udedb9714" style="text-align: justify"><span data-lake-id="u36631444" id="u36631444">若仍成立 → 继续执行循环中的代码</span></li><li fid="u8e35b714" data-lake-id="u63b9fa11" id="u63b9fa11" style="text-align: justify"><span data-lake-id="ud16d203e" id="ud16d203e">若不成立 → 循环结束  </span></li></ol></blockquote><p data-lake-id="u7eb4caff" id="u7eb4caff"><strong><span data-lake-id="u1175e313" id="u1175e313">3️⃣</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="u9239a6d1" id="u9239a6d1">代码示例：</span></strong></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22n%20%3D%201%5Cnwhile%20n%20%3C%3D%2010%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(f'%E7%AC%AC%7Bn%7D%E6%AC%A1%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD%E5%95%8A')%5Cn%20%20%20%20n%20%2B%3D%201%5Cnprint(f'%E6%88%91%E6%98%AFwhile%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%A4%96%E7%9A%84%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%EF%BC%8C%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E5%88%B0%E8%BF%99%E9%87%8C%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E5%B7%B2%E7%BB%8F%E7%BB%93%E6%9D%9F%E4%BA%86%EF%BC%8C%E6%AD%A4%E6%97%B6%E7%9A%84n%E6%98%AF%EF%BC%9A%7Bn%7D')%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22OId9Z%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><blockquote data-lake-id="u94d67610" id="u94d67610" class="lake-alert lake-alert-color4"><p data-lake-id="ue5453ea5" id="ue5453ea5"><span data-lake-id="u99d9a66c" id="u99d9a66c">📢</span><strong><span data-lake-id="ua910abee" id="ua910abee" style="color: #AD1A2B">注意：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="uaa5393bd" id="uaa5393bd">如果条件一直成立，就是无限循环（死循环）。例如上述代码中，如果忘记编写</span><code data-lake-id="u6c7a01af" id="u6c7a01af"><span data-lake-id="u4754b982" id="u4754b982">n += 1</span></code><span data-lake-id="u97fa7c6b" id="u97fa7c6b">就会产生死循环。</span></p></blockquote><p data-lake-id="u710b228c" id="u710b228c"><strong><span data-lake-id="u48c243ea" id="u48c243ea">4️⃣</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="ubcb4f585" id="ubcb4f585">案例：</span></strong></p><p data-lake-id="u578c8e8d" id="u578c8e8d"><card type="inline" name="image" value="data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F35780599%2F1760705999116-d5b56e8b-872e-427a-be86-6bc8f94af8fb.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ubd5bb7b8-e12d-4635-9f18-f610bc9db6d%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u9dc15b59-c913-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A398.14959716796875%2C%22height%22%3A161%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A222766%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1081%2C%22originHeight%22%3A438%2C%22ratio%22%3A1.6500000953674316%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8B%A5%E5%9B%9E%E7%AD%94%E7%B2%BE%2C%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%B0%B1%E4%BC%9A%E4%B8%8D%E6%96%AD%E7%8E%AF%E6%8F%90%E7%9A%84%2C%E7%9B%B4%E5%88%B0%E7%AD%94%E5%AF%B9%E4%B8%BA%E6%AD%A2.%22%2C%22x%22%3A79%2C%22y%22%3A269%2C%22width%22%3A960%2C%22height%22%3A50%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%8B%A5%E5%9B%9E%E7%AD%94%E6%AD%A3%E7%A1%AE%2C%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E5%8F%B0%E6%89%93%E5%8D%B0%E9%80%83%E8%84%B1%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%2C%E5%B9%B6%E7%BB%93%E6%9D%9F%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF.%22%2C%22x%22%3A95%2C%22y%22%3A356%2C%22width%22%3A864%2C%22height%22%3A48%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%A8%A1%E6%8B%9F%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%AF%86%E5%AE%A4%E9%80%83%E8%84%B1%E5%9C%BA%E6%99%AF%22%2C%22x%22%3A171%2C%22y%22%3A13%2C%22width%22%3A566%2C%22height%22%3A63%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E5%BF%85%E9%A1%BB%E6%AD%A3%E7%A1%AE%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%9E%E7%AD%94%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%2C%E6%89%8D%E8%83%BD%5C%22%E9%80%83%E5%87%BA%E5%AF%86%E5%AE%A4%5C%22%22%2C%22x%22%3A98%2C%22y%22%3A188%2C%22width%22%3A777%2C%22height%22%3A46%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%222%E8%8B%A5%E5%9B%9E%E7%AD%94%E9%93%B2%22%2C%22x%22%3A54%2C%22y%22%3A271%2C%22width%22%3A200%2C%22height%22%3A48%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23504d4a%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22y05HI%22%7D"></card></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22print('%F0%9F%98%A6%E6%82%A8%E7%8E%B0%E5%9C%A8%E8%BA%AB%E5%A4%84%E5%AF%86%E5%AE%A4%EF%BC%8C%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E6%AD%A3%E7%A1%AE%E5%9B%9E%E7%AD%94%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E4%B9%8B%E5%90%8E%EF%BC%8C%E6%89%8D%E8%83%BD%E9%80%83%E5%87%BA%E5%AF%86%E5%AE%A4%EF%BC%81')%5Cnriddle%20%3D%20'%E4%BD%A0%E6%98%AF%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%9F'%5Cnanswer%20%3D%20'%E4%BD%A0%E7%9A%84%E5%BF%83%E4%B8%8A%E4%BA%BA'%5Cnguess%20%3D%20''%5Cn%5Cnwhile%20guess%20!%3D%20answer%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(f'%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%EF%BC%9A%7Briddle%7D')%5Cn%20%20%20%20guess%20%3D%20input('%E8%AF%B7%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88%EF%BC%9A')%5Cn%20%20%20%20if%20guess%20%3D%3D%20answer%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20print('%E2%9C%85%EF%B8%8F%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88%E6%AD%A3%E7%A1%AE%EF%BC%8C%E9%80%83%E8%84%B1%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%EF%BC%81')%5Cn%20%20%20%20else%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20print('%E2%9D%8C%EF%B8%8F%E5%9B%9E%E7%AD%94%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF%EF%BC%8C%E8%AF%B7%E5%86%8D%E6%83%B3%E6%83%B3%EF%BC%81')%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22l8sCO%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h3 data-lake-id="c35Mg" id="c35Mg" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u068535b7" id="u068535b7">for 循环</span></h3><p data-lake-id="uc3a3e7f3" id="uc3a3e7f3"><strong><span data-lake-id="u6af672da" id="u6af672da">1️⃣</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="u1fa6cec3" id="u1fa6cec3">语法格式：</span></strong></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22for%20%E4%B8%B4%E6%97%B6%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%20in%20%E5%8F%AF%E8%BF%AD%E4%BB%A3%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%EF%BC%9A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E8%A6%81%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C1%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E8%A6%81%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E7%9A%84%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C2%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22MqRlj%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><blockquote data-lake-id="uf3f6555a" id="uf3f6555a" class="lake-alert lake-alert-info"><p data-lake-id="u9c50b2aa" id="u9c50b2aa"><strong><span data-lake-id="u0bb8d237" id="u0bb8d237">💡</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="ubd081721" id="ubd081721">什么叫『可迭代对象』？</span></strong></p><p data-lake-id="u7e15a2fc" id="u7e15a2fc"><span data-lake-id="u93fa4292" id="u93fa4292">比如我们有一个盒子，里面装着：苹果、香蕉、橙子。我们可以一个接一个地把水果取出来，那这个盒子，就相当于 Python 中的可迭代对象。每次 for 循环执行时，其实就是在“取出一个水果”，目前我们还没学到“类”和“对象”，先记住一句话： 能一个个取出来的，就是可迭代的。</span></p></blockquote><p data-lake-id="u1a09a30f" id="u1a09a30f"><strong><span data-lake-id="u680f1d77" id="u680f1d77">2️⃣</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="u941f18fd" id="u941f18fd">循环逻辑：</span></strong></p><blockquote data-lake-id="u5708f46b" id="u5708f46b" class="lake-alert lake-alert-tips"><ol list="u69a7666c"><li fid="uc496432d" data-lake-id="u82e23047" id="u82e23047" style="text-align: justify"><span data-lake-id="u96254ea4" id="u96254ea4">从可迭代对象中取出第一个元素 → 赋值给临时变量</span></li><li fid="uc496432d" data-lake-id="u49ef39a7" id="u49ef39a7" style="text-align: justify"><span data-lake-id="u30fcad01" id="u30fcad01">执行循环中的代码</span></li><li fid="uc496432d" data-lake-id="u757ff2e2" id="u757ff2e2" style="text-align: justify"><span data-lake-id="uf5601282" id="uf5601282">取出下一个元素 → 重复执行</span></li><li fid="uc496432d" data-lake-id="ucefe07c7" id="ucefe07c7" style="text-align: justify"><span data-lake-id="udd355ea8" id="udd355ea8">当所有元素取完后 → 循环结束  </span></li></ol></blockquote><p data-lake-id="u1571f0b8" id="u1571f0b8"><strong><span data-lake-id="uab1b1d5b" id="uab1b1d5b">3️⃣</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="u70f3a5e0" id="u70f3a5e0">代码示例：</span></strong></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8for%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E9%81%8D%E5%8E%86range()%E6%89%80%E6%8C%87%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%5Cnn%20%3D%200%5Cnfor%20n%20in%20range(1%2C%2011)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(f'%E7%AC%AC%7Bn%7D%E6%AC%A1%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD%E5%95%8A')%5Cnprint(f'%E6%88%91%E6%98%AFfor%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%A4%96%E7%9A%84%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%EF%BC%8C%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E5%88%B0%E8%BF%99%E9%87%8C%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E5%B7%B2%E7%BB%8F%E7%BB%93%E6%9D%9F%E4%BA%86%EF%BC%8C%E6%AD%A4%E6%97%B6%E7%9A%84n%E6%98%AF%EF%BC%9A%7Bn%7D')%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8for%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E9%81%8D%E5%8E%86%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%B2%5Cnfor%20m%20in%20'abcdef'%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(m)%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E6%BC%94%E7%A4%BA%E7%94%B1%E4%BA%8E%E8%AF%AF%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E9%80%A0%E6%88%90%E7%9A%84%E6%AD%BB%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%8B%E9%9D%A2%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%A8%E5%88%B0%E4%BA%86%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E5%90%8E%E9%9D%A2%E4%BC%9A%E8%AE%B2%E8%A7%A3%EF%BC%89%5Cn%23%20%E5%A4%87%E6%B3%A8%EF%BC%9Afor%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E8%BF%98%E8%83%BD%E9%81%8D%E5%8E%86%E5%BE%88%E5%A4%9A%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E8%AE%B2%E5%88%B0%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%9C%E8%A5%BF%EF%BC%8C%E6%AF%94%E5%A6%82%EF%BC%9A%E5%85%83%E7%BB%84%E3%80%81%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8%E3%80%81%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1......%5Cnnums%20%3D%20%5B1%2C2%2C3%5D%5Cnfor%20i%20in%20nums%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%23%20nums.append(4)%20%23%20%E6%AD%A4%E8%A1%8C%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E4%BC%9A%E9%80%A0%E6%88%90%E6%AD%BB%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(i)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22dCpd2%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><blockquote data-lake-id="u4ccbc907" id="u4ccbc907" class="lake-alert lake-alert-info"><p data-lake-id="u688cda60" id="u688cda60"><span data-lake-id="u8f93578e" id="u8f93578e">以上代码中的：</span><code data-lake-id="uf1927c38" id="uf1927c38"><span data-lake-id="u6cdfec91" id="u6cdfec91">range(1, 11)</span></code><span data-lake-id="u3a6ed3b2" id="u3a6ed3b2">、</span><code data-lake-id="uf6a1e57d" id="uf6a1e57d"><span data-lake-id="u321992dc" id="u321992dc">'abcdef'</span></code><span data-lake-id="u7bcfe6d3" id="u7bcfe6d3">、</span><code data-lake-id="ua7dc948b" id="ua7dc948b"><span data-lake-id="u190659ee" id="u190659ee">[1,2,3