C%22width%22%3A1078%2C%22height%22%3A272%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23505050%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22VX3pO%22%7D"></card></p><h3 data-lake-id="jpIDC" id="jpIDC" data-lake-index-type="2"><strong><span data-lake-id="u98b38d18" id="u98b38d18">Python 中函数的分类</span></strong></h3><p data-lake-id="ua1c514df" id="ua1c514df"><span data-lake-id="u1bdefaf5" id="u1bdefaf5">Python 中函数分为三类：①内置函数、②模块提供的函数、③自定义函数。</span></p><p data-lake-id="ub987106e" id="ub987106e"><card type="inline" name="image" value="data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F35780599%2F1760747758646-c3c53f81-b645-4452-9249-4dbc9d4bbb16.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u5457f103-62c5-4be0-bd33-77e741f2823%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u647eed17-9a7a-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A621.7783813476562%2C%22height%22%3A135%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A151024%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1795%2C%22originHeight%22%3A391%2C%22ratio%22%3A1.6500000953674316%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E5%91%98%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E7%9A%84%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0(%E5%85%88%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E5%86%8D%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8).%22%2C%22x%22%3A392%2C%22y%22%3A312%2C%22width%22%3A698%2C%22height%22%3A52%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E5%AF%BC%E5%85%A5%E6%8C%87%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%E6%A8%A1%E5%9D%97%E5%90%8E%2C%E6%89%8D%E8%83%BD%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8.%22%2C%22x%22%3A393%2C%22y%22%3A217%2C%22width%22%3A626%2C%22height%22%3A48%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22PRINT()TYPE()%2CRANGE()%22%2C%22x%22%3A1114%2C%22y%22%3A122%2C%22width%22%3A542%2C%22height%22%3A40%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%97%A0%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E4%BB%BB%E4%BD%95%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%2C%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E5%B0%B1%E8%83%BD%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8.%22%2C%22x%22%3A399%2C%22y%22%3A116%2C%22width%22%3A569%2C%22height%22%3A46%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%85%B7%E4%BD%93%E5%86%99%E6%B3%95%2C%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%8B%E4%B8%80%E5%B0%8F%E8%8A%82%E8%AE%B2%E8%A7%A3.%22%2C%22x%22%3A1096%2C%22y%22%3A319%2C%22width%22%3A520%2C%22height%22%3A49%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22MATH.SGRT()MATH.F1OOR().%22%2C%22x%22%3A1104%2C%22y%22%3A226%2C%22width%22%3A603%2C%22height%22%3A39%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%A8%A1%E5%9D%97%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E7%9A%84%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%22%2C%22x%22%3A45%2C%22y%22%3A216%2C%22width%22%3A287%2C%22height%22%3A47%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%86%85%E7%BD%AE%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%22%2C%22x%22%3A120%2C%22y%22%3A117%2C%22width%22%3A155%2C%22height%22%3A43%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%22%2C%22x%22%3A96%2C%22y%22%3A315%2C%22width%22%3A202%2C%22height%22%3A46%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E4%B8%BE%E4%BE%8B%22%2C%22x%22%3A1387%2C%22y%22%3A15%2C%22width%22%3A102%2C%22height%22%3A53%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E%22%2C%22x%22%3A688%2C%22y%22%3A17%2C%22width%22%3A99%2C%22height%22%3A51%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%22%2C%22x%22%3A134%2C%22y%22%3A19%2C%22width%22%3A94%2C%22height%22%3A46%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%2354534e%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22xuqvq%22%7D"></card></p><blockquote data-lake-id="u49019a5b" id="u49019a5b"><p data-lake-id="ucd04d0f4" id="ucd04d0f4"><strong><span data-lake-id="uf5c0bdf7" id="uf5c0bdf7">相关官方文档：</span></strong></p><p data-lake-id="ucec4a9ec" id="ucec4a9ec"><span data-lake-id="ud3257446" id="ud3257446">内置函数：</span><a href="https://docs.python.org/zh-cn/3.13/library/functions.html" target="_blank" data-lake-id="uf3ccd6d4" id="uf3ccd6d4"><span data-lake-id="u12e413b7" id="u12e413b7">https://docs.python.org/zh-cn/3.13/library/functions.html</span></a></p><p data-lake-id="u56152ae4" id="u56152ae4"><span data-lake-id="u5e271be0" id="u5e271be0">模块提供的函数：</span><a href="https://docs.python.org/zh-cn/3.13/py-modindex.html" target="_blank" data-lake-id="ud0fbb225" id="ud0fbb225"><span data-lake-id="u55c8dde3" id="u55c8dde3">https://docs.python.org/zh-cn/3.13/py-modindex.html</span></a></p></blockquote><blockquote data-lake-id="u6f3fe998" id="u6f3fe998" class="lake-alert lake-alert-tips"><p data-lake-id="u6e49ec2b" id="u6e49ec2b"><strong><span data-lake-id="ue2b3029f" id="ue2b3029f">📋</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="u6352f929" id="u6352f929">备注：</span></strong></p><ol list="ud9e747b7"><li fid="ue2d687fb" data-lake-id="u968a0157" id="u968a0157"><span data-lake-id="u6f518ade" id="u6f518ade">内置函数与模块提供的函数， Python 都已经提前定义完毕，我们只管调用即可。</span></li><li fid="ue2d687fb" data-lake-id="ub8e320b9" id="ub8e320b9"><span data-lake-id="u8744db4e" id="u8744db4e">本章主要讲解自定义函数，对于内置函数和模块提供的函数，后面用到哪个讲哪个。</span></li></ol></blockquote><h2 data-lake-id="aNrqB" id="aNrqB" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="ucbd85c84" id="ucbd85c84">基本使用</span></h2><h3 data-lake-id="hm64C" id="hm64C" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="ufd12ea25" id="ufd12ea25">定义函数</span></h3><p data-lake-id="u58037bbf" id="u58037bbf"><strong><span data-lake-id="u87bd1d36" id="u87bd1d36">1️⃣</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="u9d4d806f" id="u9d4d806f">语法格式：</span></strong></p><blockquote data-lake-id="ue80039d2" id="ue80039d2"><p data-lake-id="u1e4212bf" id="u1e4212bf"><span data-lake-id="u4e6f9734" id="u4e6f9734">如下语法格式是函数的基本定义，不涉及：接收参数和返回值。</span></p></blockquote><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22def%20%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E5%90%8D()%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E4%BD%93%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E4%BD%93%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22nLr1S%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u261d5f98" id="u261d5f98"><strong><span data-lake-id="u167a8da4" id="u167a8da4">2️⃣</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="u2c2a6f48" id="u2c2a6f48">语法图解：</span></strong></p><p data-lake-id="u6c06dfb9" id="u6c06dfb9"><card type="inline" name="image" value="data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F35780599%2F1760748625874-41db5b9a-0272-40ff-9a1d-c9a7f393f0b0.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u6f5ef916-1141-44ea-9737-2a6460ff72d%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u06fb607d-ba8d-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A548.7783813476562%2C%22height%22%3A177%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A76696%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1499%2C%22originHeight%22%3A483%2C%22ratio%22%3A1.6500000953674316%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22PRINT(%E5%B0%9A%E7%A1%85%E8%B0%B7%2C%E8%AE%A9%E5%A4%A9%E4%B8%8B%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E9%9A%BE%E5%AD%A6%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF!%22%2C%22x%22%3A425%2C%22y%22%3A276%2C%22width%22%3A961%2C%22height%22%3A53%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22PRINT(%E6%AC%A2%E8%BF%8E%E6%9D%A5%E5%88%B0%E5%B0%9A%E7%A1%85%E8%B0%B7%E8%AF%BE%E5%A0%82!)%22%2C%22x%22%3A492%2C%22y%22%3A220%2C%22width%22%3A733%2C%22height%22%3A49%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%9B%BA%E5%AE%9A%E6%A0%BC%E5%BC%8F(%E4%BB%A5%E5%90%8E%E9%87%8C%E9%9D%A2%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%86%99%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0)%22%2C%22x%22%3A822%2C%22y%22%3A80%2C%22width%22%3A581%2C%22height%22%3A49%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22EFWEICOME%22%2C%22x%22%3A406%2C%22y%22%3A172%2C%22width%22%3A327%2C%22height%22%3A39%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E5%AD%97%22%2C%22x%22%3A5%2C%22y%22%3A84%2C%22width%22%3A322%2C%22height%22%3A45%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%8C%BA%E6%95%B0%E5%90%8D%22%2C%22x%22%3A520%2C%22y%22%3A14%2C%22width%22%3A135%2C%22height%22%3A48%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22DEFINE%22%2C%22x%22%3A109%2C%22y%22%3A138%2C%22width%22%3A131%2C%22height%22%3A38%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E4%BD%93%22%2C%22x%22%3A867%2C%22y%22%3A427%2C%22width%22%3A125%2C%22height%22%3A42%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%2341403f%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22L44eT%22%7D"></card></p><p data-lake-id="u77a96885" id="u77a96885"><span data-lake-id="u89b5062b" id="u89b5062b">3️⃣</span><strong><span data-lake-id="uab241150" id="uab241150">说明：</span></strong></p><blockquote data-lake-id="u76f40d5b" id="u76f40d5b" class="lake-alert lake-alert-info"><ul list="u0dcd8dfa"><li fid="uff0f8da1" data-lake-id="ud8c876f1" id="ud8c876f1"><span data-lake-id="u1266ad16" id="u1266ad16">定义函数的关键字是</span><code data-lake-id="u5d934751" id="u5d934751"><span data-lake-id="u2bc98cc1" id="u2bc98cc1">def</span></code><span data-lake-id="ucad1fddd" id="ucad1fddd">，需要将</span><code data-lake-id="ufb19a1bb" id="ufb19a1bb"><span data-lake-id="ud5b7b4d0" id="ud5b7b4d0">def</span></code><span data-lake-id="u2a0ceb09" id="u2a0ceb09">与函数名用空格隔开，随后紧跟</span><code data-lake-id="ufaf77f58" id="ufaf77f58"><span data-lake-id="u4c37b3ab" id="u4c37b3ab">():</span></code><span data-lake-id="u0f55cd1f" id="u0f55cd1f">。</span></li><li fid="uff0f8da1" data-lake-id="u38a44cf7" id="u38a44cf7"><span data-lake-id="uaffdc561" id="uaffdc561">函数的命名遵循我们之前讲过的</span><span data-lake-id="ueffd22fc" id="ueffd22fc" style="color: rgb(38, 38, 38)">『</span><span data-lake-id="u83e4865f" id="u83e4865f">标识符命名规范</span><span data-lake-id="u423dd688" id="u423dd688" style="color: rgb(38, 38, 38)">』</span><span data-lake-id="u08f97fa7" id="u08f97fa7">。</span></li><li fid="uff0f8da1" data-lake-id="u734ed0f3" id="u734ed0f3"><span data-lake-id="u63a13b5f" id="u63a13b5f">函数定义完毕后，只是告诉 Python 我们定义了一个函数，可以完成某些功能，但此时函数体还没有执行，需要调用函数后，函数体才会执行！</span></li></ul></blockquote><p data-lake-id="ua7cb2333" id="ua7cb2333"><span data-lake-id="u16e7c44f" id="u16e7c44f">4️⃣</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u94d353c6" id="u94d353c6">示例代码：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u23a9d384" id="u23a9d384">定义一个名为 </span><code data-lake-id="uecde0ebe" id="uecde0ebe"><span data-lake-id="ud3195bc1" id="ud3195bc1">welcome</span></code><span data-lake-id="ua352712c" id="ua352712c"> 的函数，函数体中打印两句欢迎语。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%5Cndef%20welcome()%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20print('%E6%AC%A2%E8%BF%8E%E6%9D%A5%E5%88%B0%E5%B0%9A%E7%A1%85%E8%B0%B7%E8%AF%BE%E5%A0%82%EF%BC%81')%5Cn%20%20%20%20print('%E5%B0%9A%E7%A1%85%E8%B0%B7%EF%BC%8C%E8%AE%A9%E5%A4%A9%E4%B8%8B%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E9%9A%BE%E5%AD%A6%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%EF%BC%81')%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22C0ScH%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h3 data-lake-id="Tfb9V" id="Tfb9V" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u410d8ca8" id="u410d8ca8">调用函数</span></h3><p data-lake-id="uec58ee4d" id="uec58ee4d"><strong><span data-lake-id="ud20d6c2d" id="ud20d6c2d">1️⃣</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="ucbe82725" id="ucbe82725">语法格式：</span></strong></p><blockquote data-lake-id="u6235f8ef" id="u6235f8ef"><p data-lake-id="u881734ac" id="u881734ac"><span data-lake-id="u0457c1d5" id="u0457c1d5">如下语法格式是基本调用形式，不涉及：传递参数。</span></p></blockquote><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E5%90%8D()%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22PkVZM%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u54082eea" id="u54082eea"><strong><span data-lake-id="u40e92153" id="u40e92153">2️⃣</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="uade28d0a" id="uade28d0a">语法图解：</span></strong></p><p data-lake-id="ud1c0eeec" id="ud1c0eeec"><card type="inline" name="image" value="data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F35780599%2F1760779202564-04a27d4a-45c6-4d64-aaf6-e8cbbf6f9b7c.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ub2f05d57-7309-4377-926a-053b3a24cf7%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u06fb607d-ba8d-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A173.10226440429688%2C%22height%22%3A144%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A38952%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A548%2C%22originHeight%22%3A455%2C%22ratio%22%3A1.6500000953674316%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22(%E5%9B%BA%E5%AE%9A%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84)%22%2C%22x%22%3A280%2C%22y%22%3A383%2C%22width%22%3A227%2C%22height%22%3A50%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22XXXXX%22%2C%22x%22%3A47%2C%22y%22%3A184%2C%22width%22%3A214%2C%22height%22%3A47%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E5%90%8D%22%2C%22x%22%3A82%2C%22y%22%3A19%2C%22width%22%3A173%2C%22height%22%3A56%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%9C%86%E6%B4%BB%E5%8F%B7%22%2C%22x%22%3A112%2C%22y%22%3A381%2C%22width%22%3A146%2C%22height%22%3A52%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23494949%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22xk9k6%22%7D"></card></p><p data-lake-id="u798f73f1" id="u798f73f1"><strong><span data-lake-id="u8b67de57" id="u8b67de57">3️⃣</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="ud2d67837" id="ud2d67837">示例代码</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u13a243dc" id="u13a243dc">：编写代码，调用我们刚才定义的</span><code data-lake-id="u48d8b157" id="u48d8b157"><span data-lake-id="uc2a14cec" id="uc2a14cec">welcome</span></code><span data-lake-id="u7c01ae14" id="u7c01ae14">函数。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%5Cndef%20welcome()%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20print('%E6%AC%A2%E8%BF%8E%E6%9D%A5%E5%88%B0%E5%B0%9A%E7%A1%85%E8%B0%B7%E8%AF%BE%E5%A0%82%EF%BC%81')%5Cn%20%20%20%20print('%E5%B0%9A%E7%A1%85%E8%B0%B7%EF%BC%8C%E8%AE%A9%E5%A4%A9%E4%B8%8B%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E9%9A%BE%E5%AD%A6%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%EF%BC%81')%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E8%B0%83%E7%94%A8%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%88%E8%AE%A9%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E8%B5%B7%E6%9D%A5%EF%BC%89%5Cnwelcome()%5Cnwelcome()%5Cnwelcome()%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22__widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22lhSwk%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%2C%22widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%7D"></card><blockquote data-lake-id="u7515e099" id="u7515e099" class="lake-alert lake-alert-color4"><p data-lake-id="ub188d0c5" id="ub188d0c5"><strong><span data-lake-id="ue09b4af5" id="ue09b4af5" style="color: #DF2A3F">⚠️</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="u643c6b00" id="u643c6b00" style="color: #DF2A3F">注意：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u700ef7df" id="u700ef7df">函数必须先定义再调用。</span></p></blockquote><h2 data-lake-id="LSQtG" id="LSQtG" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="uba328c1d" id="uba328c1d">参数</span></h2><h3 data-lake-id="KQ9s9" id="KQ9s9" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u76ef7f2e" id="u76ef7f2e">参数的作用</span></h3><p data-lake-id="u3611d7b8" id="u3611d7b8"><span data-lake-id="ude54f510" id="ude54f510">参数可以让函数接收外部传入的数据，能让函数更具通用性和灵活性，比如下面的这个需求：</span></p><blockquote data-lake-id="uce77c80a" id="uce77c80a" class="lake-alert lake-alert-info"><p data-lake-id="u85c83976" id="u85c83976"><strong><span data-lake-id="u8ac9e126" id="u8ac9e126">📒</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="ue6c4b32e" id="ue6c4b32e">需求：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="ua0b92998" id="ua0b92998">定义一个名为</span><code data-lake-id="u43c67531" id="u43c67531"><span data-lake-id="u88251d5b" id="u88251d5b">order</span></code><span data-lake-id="u24470b56" id="u24470b56">的函数，在函数体中打印用户的点餐信息。</span></p></blockquote><p data-lake-id="ub53371e1" id="ub53371e1"><span data-lake-id="uee27bfb4" id="uee27bfb4">用如下代码实现，就会面临两个问题：</span><strong><span data-lake-id="ub6d7c2af" id="ub6d7c2af">① </span></strong><span data-lake-id="u742aa9b7" id="u742aa9b7">每次的点餐数量只能是一份。</span><strong><span data-lake-id="uba897503" id="uba897503">②</span></strong><span data-lake-id="ub2994c50" id="ub2994c50"> 每次点的菜品只能是辣椒炒肉。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%E4%B8%8D%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%20order%20%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%5Cndef%20order()%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20num%20%3D%201%5Cn%20%20%20%20dish%20%3D%20'%E8%BE%A3%E6%A4%92%E7%82%92%E8%82%89'%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(f'%E6%82%A8%E7%82%B9%E7%9A%84%E6%98%AF%EF%BC%9A%7Bnum%7D%E4%BB%BD%20%7Bdish%7D')%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E8%B0%83%E7%94%A8%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%5Cnorder()%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%E4%B8%8D%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%20order%20%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Pz8qO%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="ub9a58f26" id="ub9a58f26"><span data-lake-id="u88ed4d98" id="u88ed4d98">但如果在上述代码的基础上，使用参数，就可以灵活修改点餐数量和菜品，写法如下：</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%20order%20%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%88%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E7%9A%84%E5%90%8C%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%9A%E5%A3%B0%E6%98%8E%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E4%B8%A4%E4%B8%AA%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%86%E5%88%AB%E6%98%AF%EF%BC%9A%E8%8F%9C%E5%93%81%E6%95%B0%E9%87%8F%20num%EF%BC%8C%E5%92%8C%E8%8F%9C%E5%93%81%E5%90%8D%E7%A7%B0%20dish%EF%BC%89%5Cndef%20order(num%2C%20dish)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(f'%E6%82%A8%E7%82%B9%E7%9A%84%E6%98%AF%EF%BC%9A%7Bnum%7D%E4%BB%BD%20%7Bdish%7D')%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(f'%7Bdish%7D%E5%8F%AF%E6%98%AF%E5%BE%88%E5%A5%BD%E5%90%83%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%81')%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(f'%E4%BD%A0%E5%8F%AA%E7%82%B9%E4%BA%86%7Bnum%7D%E4%BB%BD%EF%BC%8C%E5%A4%9F%E5%90%83%E5%90%97%EF%BC%9F%5C%5Cn')%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E8%B0%83%E7%94%A8%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%88%E8%B0%83%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%90%8C%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%9A%E4%BC%A0%E9%80%92%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%A4%E4%B8%AA%E5%80%BC%EF%BC%89%5Cnorder(1%2C%20'%E8%BE%A3%E6%A4%92%E7%82%92%E8%82%89')%5Cnorder(2%2C%20'%E8%BE%A3%E5%AD%90%E9%B8%A1')%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%20order%20%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ZIBiy%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h3 data-lake-id="PAjZy" id="PAjZy" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="ue05a62f1" id="ue05a62f1">实参与形参</span></h3><p data-lake-id="u93bf2074" id="u93bf2074"><span data-lake-id="u450e4129" id="u450e4129" style="color: rgb(38, 38, 38)">在使用函数时，要注意区分『形参』与『实参』。</span></p><ul list="uc0ec017e"><li fid="u00fbf3b3" data-lake-id="u401a3ff1" id="u401a3ff1"><strong><span data-lake-id="u94862ebe" id="u94862ebe" style="color: rgb(38, 38, 38)">形参（形式参数）</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u38bd919b" id="u38bd919b" style="color: rgb(38, 38, 38)">：在定义函数时，用来接收数据的变量叫形参，形参是函数定义者设置的。</span></li><li fid="u00fbf3b3" data-lake-id="u7a216c76" id="u7a216c76"><strong><span data-lake-id="u67bb103d" id="u67bb103d" style="color: rgb(38, 38, 38)">实参（实际参数）</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u3c4c6377" id="u3c4c6377" style="color: rgb(38, 38, 38)">：在调用函数时，给函数传递的具体值叫实参，实参是函数调用者提供的。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id="ue4ca20ee" id="ue4ca20ee"><card type="inline" name="image" value="data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F35780599%2F1760782644014-3b537df6-3df7-4bde-ba57-c53c8cab4ce2.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u3a6d8a92-6ecd-44b2-9047-fa69c0968b7%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u06fb607d-ba8d-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A395.6250305175781%2C%22height%22%3A227%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A57009%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1029%2C%22originHeight%22%3A591%2C%22ratio%22%3A1.6500000953674316%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22PRINT(F%E6%82%A8%E7%82%B9%E7%9A%84%E6%98%AF%3A%7BNUM%7D%E4%BB%BD%7BDISH%7D)%22%2C%22x%22%3A156%2C%22y%22%3A247%2C%22width%22%3A833%2C%22height%22%3A47%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22ORDENNUM%2CDISH%3A%22%2C%22x%22%3A161%2C%22y%22%3A192%2C%22width%22%3A434%2C%22height%22%3A42%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22DEN2%2C%E8%BE%A3%E5%AD%90%22%2C%22x%22%3A117%2C%22y%22%3A374%2C%22width%22%3A319%2C%22height%22%3A44%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%BE%A3%E6%B7%91%E7%82%92%E6%B2%99%E8%82%89)%22%2C%22x%22%3A260%2C%22y%22%3A306%2C%22width%22%3A283%2C%22height%22%3A45%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22ORDEN1%22%2C%22x%22%3A73%2C%22y%22%3A312%2C%22width%22%3A179%2C%22height%22%3A35%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%AE%9E%E5%8F%82%22%2C%22x%22%3A275%2C%22y%22%3A540%2C%22width%22%3A79%2C%22height%22%3A40%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%BD%A2%E5%8F%82%22%2C%22x%22%3A397%2C%22y%22%3A20%2C%22width%22%3A78%2C%22height%22%3A41%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22DEF%22%2C%22x%22%3A77%2C%22y%22%3A196%2C%22width%22%3A79%2C%22height%22%3A34%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%233a3837%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22WB98G%22%7D"></card></p><blockquote data-lake-id="u0fa5c260" id="u0fa5c260" class="lake-alert lake-alert-tips"><p data-lake-id="u6a06fad7" id="u6a06fad7"><strong><span data-lake-id="ub3fcb8e9" id="ub3fcb8e9">📋</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="u56782072" id="u56782072">备注</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u60c608a5" id="u60c608a5">：形参存储的到底是什么数据，</span><span data-lake-id="u9a4ea266" id="u9a4ea266" style="color: rgb(38, 38, 38)">要看调用者传递的实参具体是什么。</span></p></blockquote><blockquote data-lake-id="u0a2c190e" id="u0a2c190e" class="lake-alert lake-alert-color4"><p data-lake-id="uf1970f1c" id="uf1970f1c"><span data-lake-id="u718bf51a" id="u718bf51a">📢</span><strong><span data-lake-id="ub1067b70" id="ub1067b70" style="color: #AD1A2B">注意</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u18e8ae29" id="u18e8ae29" style="color: #AD1A2B">：</span><span data-lake-id="u46fbea7c" id="u46fbea7c">形参的使用范围仅限函数体内。</span></p></blockquote><h3 data-lake-id="U8u51" id="U8u51" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u2fb8d7b6" id="u2fb8d7b6">位置参数</span></h3><p data-lake-id="u4da36655" id="u4da36655"><strong><span data-lake-id="u8a7d118d" id="u8a7d118d">位置参数：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u81da8b42" id="u81da8b42">调用函数时，根据参数在函数定义时出现的顺序，把实参的值，依次传递给对应的形参。</span></p><blockquote data-lake-id="u5c1c04b4" id="u5c1c04b4" class="lake-alert lake-alert-info"><p data-lake-id="u591261dc" id="u591261dc"><span data-lake-id="u587d1346" id="u587d1346">例如在上一小节所写的</span><code data-lake-id="ufb58fc6d" id="ufb58fc6d"><span data-lake-id="uffba41e6" id="uffba41e6">order</span></code><span data-lake-id="u3125131c" id="u3125131c">函数，就是在使用位置参数，其中形参与实参的对应关系如下图：</span></p><p data-lake-id="ucdd0ac36" id="ucdd0ac36"><card type="inline" name="image" value="data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F35780599%2F1760789258131-558d642c-692e-476c-b338-a366e905025d.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u0f493749-8fc7-4cd0-b1a3-b993ffa1e55%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u06fb607d-ba8d-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A396.76513671875%2C%22height%22%3A87%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A47007%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1275%2C%22originHeight%22%3A280%2C%22ratio%22%3A1.6500000953674316%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E8%BE%A3%E6%B7%91%E5%A6%99%E8%82%89%22%2C%22x%22%3A324%2C%22y%22%3A185%2C%22width%22%3A318%2C%22height%22%3A64%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22FDISH)%22%2C%22x%22%3A982%2C%22y%22%3A99%2C%22width%22%3A293%2C%22height%22%3A65%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22NUM%E5%88%86%22%2C%22x%22%3A735%2C%22y%22%3A100%2C%22width%22%3A246%2C%22height%22%3A64%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22DISH%22%2C%22x%22%3A504%2C%22y%22%3A14%2C%22width%22%3A190%2C%22height%22%3A66%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22ORDER%22%2C%22x%22%3A148%2C%22y%22%3A24%2C%22width%22%3A182%2C%22height%22%3A43%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22ONDEN%22%2C%22x%22%3A9%2C%22y%22%3A195%2C%22width%22%3A187%2C%22height%22%3A48%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22NUM%22%2C%22x%22%3A353%2C%22y%22%3A21%2C%22width%22%3A139%2C%22height%22%3A51%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22DEF%22%2C%22x%22%3A9%2C%22y%22%3A21%2C%22width%22%3A122%2C%22height%22%3A44%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22NN%E5%8D%81E%22%2C%22x%22%3A159%2C%22y%22%3A108%2C%22width%22%3A219%2C%22height%22%3A33%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%231a180f%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22zEjht%22%7D"></card></p></blockquote><blockquote data-lake-id="u6231db6d" id="u6231db6d" class="lake-alert lake-alert-color4"><p data-lake-id="u778e2e9c" id="u778e2e9c"><span data-lake-id="u43c9de3c" id="u43c9de3c">📢</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u3339bdeb" id="u3339bdeb" style="color: #AD1A2B">注意：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u9f6bdbb0" id="u9f6bdbb0">在使用</span><span data-lake-id="u44618eeb" id="u44618eeb" style="color: rgb(38, 38, 38)">『位置参数』</span><span data-lake-id="ua80903e9" id="ua80903e9">时，实参的个数与顺序，必须和形参保持一致！</span></p></blockquote><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%E6%97%B6%E7%9A%84%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF%E7%A4%BA%E8%8C%83%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22def%20order(num%2C%20dish)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(f'%E6%82%A8%E7%82%B9%E7%9A%84%E6%98%AF%EF%BC%9A%7Bnum%7D%E4%BB%BD%20%7Bdish%7D')%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(f'%7Bdish%7D%E5%8F%AF%E6%98%AF%E5%BE%88%E5%A5%BD%E5%90%83%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%81')%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(f'%E4%BD%A0%E5%8F%AA%E7%82%B9%E4%BA%86%7Bnum%7D%E4%BB%BD%EF%BC%8C%E5%A4%9F%E5%90%83%E5%90%97%EF%BC%9F%5C%5Cn')%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%E6%98%AF%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF%E7%A4%BA%E8%8C%83%5Cnorder(3)%20%20%23%20%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%E5%B0%91%E4%BA%86%5Cnorder(4%2C%20'%E5%AE%AB%E4%BF%9D%E9%B8%A1%E4%B8%81'%2C%207)%20%20%23%20%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%86%5Cnorder('%E5%AE%AB%E4%BF%9D%E9%B8%A1%E4%B8%81'%2C%204)%20%20%23%20%E5%AE%9E%E5%8F%82%E9%A1%BA%E5%BA%8F%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E5%92%8C%E5%BD%A2%E5%8F%82%E4%BF%9D%E6%8C%81%E4%B8%80%E8%87%B4%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%9A%E6%8A%A5%E9%94%99%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86%E4%BC%9A%E9%80%A0%E6%88%90%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E9%94%99%E4%B9%B1%E3%80%82%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%E6%97%B6%E7%9A%84%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF%E7%A4%BA%E8%8C%83%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22kylNe%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h3 data-lake-id="AOZxB" id="AOZxB" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="ud95a0216" id="ud95a0216">关键字参数</span></h3><p data-lake-id="u60532675" id="u60532675"><strong><span data-lake-id="udcaca5ee" id="udcaca5ee">关键字参数：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u24f31391" id="u24f31391">函数调用时通过</span><code data-lake-id="uc4a75dda" id="uc4a75dda"><strong><span data-lake-id="ua6c0b0ac" id="ua6c0b0ac">形参名 = 值</span></strong></code><span data-lake-id="u743a7454" id="u743a7454">的形式传递的参数，就是关键字参数。</span></p><p data-lake-id="uc978561f" id="uc978561f"><span data-lake-id="u2c7acbea" id="u2c7acbea">关键字参数的优势是：不受顺序限制。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E5%AD%97%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%5Cndef%20greet(name%2C%20gender%2C%20age%2C%20height)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(f'%E6%88%91%E5%8F%AB%7Bname%7D%EF%BC%8C%E6%80%A7%E5%88%AB%7Bgender%7D%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B4%E9%BE%84%E6%98%AF%7Bage%7D%EF%BC%8C%E8%BA%AB%E9%AB%98%E6%98%AF%7Bheight%7Dcm')%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E8%B0%83%E7%94%A8%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%88%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E5%AD%97%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%89%5Cngreet(name%3D'%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89'%2C%20gender%3D'%E7%94%B7'%2C%20age%3D18%2C%20height%3D172)%5Cngreet(height%3D172%2C%20age%20%3D%2018%2C%20gender%3D'%E7%94%B7'%2C%20name%3D'%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89')%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E5%AD%97%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22QCvKI%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><blockquote data-lake-id="ua10e9af8" id="ua10e9af8" class="lake-alert lake-alert-color4"><p data-lake-id="ube62df21" id="ube62df21"><span data-lake-id="u605b9064" id="u605b9064" style="color: #AD1A2B">📢</span><strong><span data-lake-id="ucf02f9e1" id="ucf02f9e1" style="color: #AD1A2B">注意：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u35fb61d4" id="u35fb61d4">『位置参数』和『关键字参数』可以混用，但『位置参数』必须写在『关键字参数』之前！</span></p></blockquote><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%E3%80%8E%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%E3%80%8F%E5%92%8C%E3%80%8E%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E5%AD%97%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%E3%80%8F%20%E6%B7%B7%E7%94%A8%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E6%AD%A3%E7%A1%AE%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%5Cngreet('%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89'%2C%20'%E7%94%B7'%2C%20height%3D172%2C%20age%3D18)%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B%5Cngreet(height%3D172%2C%20age%3D18%2C%20'%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89'%2C%20'%E7%94%B7')%5Cngreet(name%3D'%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89'%2C%20'%E7%94%B7'%2C%2018%2C%20172)%5Cngreet(name%3D'%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89'%2C%20'%E7%94%B7'%2C%20age%3D18%2C%20172)%5Cngreet(height%3D172%2C%20age%3D18%2C%20gender%3D'%E7%94%B7'%2C%20name%3D'%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89'%2C%20age%3D19)%5Cngreet(height%3D172%2C%20age%3D18%2C%20gender%3D'%E7%94%B7'%2C%20name%3D'%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89'%2C%20school%3D'%E5%B0%9A%E7%A1%85%E8%B0%B7')%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%E3%80%8E%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%E3%80%8F%E5%92%8C%E3%80%8E%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E5%AD%97%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%E3%80%8F%20%E6%B7%B7%E7%94%A8%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22txPwq%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h3 data-lake-id="PmPKL" id="PmPKL" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u9cb6c330" id="u9cb6c330">限制传参方式</span></h3><p data-lake-id="ua2e50289" id="ua2e50289"><strong><span data-lake-id="ue39eb685" id="ue39eb685">具体限制方式：</span></strong><code data-lake-id="uc046bb76" id="uc046bb76"><span data-lake-id="ub2db81bf" id="ub2db81bf">/</span></code><span data-lake-id="u1d70c8db" id="u1d70c8db">前面只能用『位置参数』，</span><code data-lake-id="uaa55505d" id="uaa55505d"><span data-lake-id="ua2e6e897" id="ua2e6e897">*</span></code><span data-lake-id="u00d11b06" id="u00d11b06">后面只能用『关键字参数』</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u1cde575b" id="u1cde575b">。</span></strong></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%E4%BC%A0%E5%8F%82%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%88%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%2F%E5%92%8C*%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%E4%BC%A0%E5%8F%82%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%EF%BC%89%5Cndef%20greet(name%2C%20%2F%2C%20gender%2C%20*%2C%20age%2C%20height)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(f'%E6%88%91%E5%8F%AB%7Bname%7D%EF%BC%8C%E6%80%A7%E5%88%AB%7Bgender%7D%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B4%E9%BE%84%E6%98%AF%7Bage%7D%EF%BC%8C%E8%BA%AB%E9%AB%98%E6%98%AF%7Bheight%7Dcm')%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E6%AD%A3%E7%A1%AE%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B%5Cngreet('%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89'%2C%20'%E7%94%B7'%2C%20age%3D18%2C%20height%3D172)%5Cngreet('%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89'%2C%20gender%3D'%E7%94%B7'%2C%20age%3D18%2C%20height%3D172)%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B%5Cngreet(name%3D'%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89'%2C%20gender%3D'%E7%94%B7'%2C%20age%3D18%2C%20height%3D172)%5Cngreet('%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89'%2C%20'%E7%94%B7'%2C%2018%2C%20height%3D172)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%E4%BC%A0%E5%8F%82%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Al1fu%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h3 data-lake-id="IpXgi" id="IpXgi" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u370a46c0" id="u370a46c0">参数默认值</span></h3><p data-lake-id="u270420c2" id="u270420c2"><span data-lake-id="uc286cdf5" id="uc286cdf5">在定义函数时，可以</span><span data-lake-id="ue1df5bf1" id="ue1df5bf1" style="color: rgb(38, 38, 38)">通过</span><code data-lake-id="u5b144907" id="u5b144907"><strong><span data-lake-id="u61e50522" id="u61e50522" style="color: rgb(38, 38, 38)">形参名 = 值</span></strong></code><span data-lake-id="ue2d0f171" id="ue2d0f171" style="color: rgb(38, 38, 38)">的形式，</span><span data-lake-id="u5941e351" id="u5941e351">为形参设置一个默认值，这样就可以实现：</span></p><ul list="uc7c98f31"><li fid="u563c0c70" data-lake-id="uece10f91" id="uece10f91"><span data-lake-id="u941ecd16" id="u941ecd16">若调用函数时</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u3b512bdd" id="u3b512bdd" style="color: #AD1A2B">没有传入</span></strong><span data-lake-id="ued60f035" id="ued60f035">该参数的值，就使用默认值。</span></li><li fid="u563c0c70" data-lake-id="u0bb2721b" id="u0bb2721b"><span data-lake-id="u04ba0ef5" id="u04ba0ef5">若调用函数时</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u50f0429e" id="u50f0429e" style="color: #5C8D07">传入了</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u393ab8e0" id="u393ab8e0">该参数的值，就使用传入的值。</span></li></ul><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%88%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%E9%BB%98%E8%AE%A4%E5%80%BC%EF%BC%89%5Cndef%20greet(name%2C%20gender%2C%20age%2C%20height%2C%20msg%3D'%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD')%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(f'%E6%88%91%E5%8F%AB%7Bname%7D%EF%BC%8C%E6%80%A7%E5%88%AB%7Bgender%7D%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B4%E9%BE%84%E6%98%AF%7Bage%7D%EF%BC%8C%E8%BA%AB%E9%AB%98%E6%98%AF%7Bheight%7Dcm')%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(f'%E6%88%91%E6%83%B3%E8%AF%B4%EF%BC%9A%7Bmsg%7D')%5Cn%20%20%20%20%5Cn%23%20%E8%B0%83%E7%94%A8%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%5Cngreet('%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89'%2C%20'%E7%94%B7'%2C%2018%2C%20172)%5Cngreet('%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89'%2C%20'%E7%94%B7'%2C%2018%2C%20172%2C%20'hello')%5Cngreet('%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89'%2C%20'%E7%94%B7'%2C%2018%2C%20172%2C%20msg%3D'hello')%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22sg9rK%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><blockquote data-lake-id="u140d8d66" id="u140d8d66" class="lake-alert lake-alert-color4"><p data-lake-id="ua359aab7" id="ua359aab7"><span data-lake-id="u3ba89937" id="u3ba89937">📢</span><strong><span data-lake-id="ufd247427" id="ufd247427" style="color: #AD1A2B">注意：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u2f49a42f" id="u2f49a42f">定义函数时，『默认参数』必须放在『必选参数』的后面，或者换一种说法就是：某个形参，一旦设置了默认值，那它后面的所有形参，也必须要写默认值！</span></p></blockquote><p data-lake-id="u1c4df7d1" id="u1c4df7d1"><span data-lake-id="u21cd951c" id="u21cd951c">例如：下面的代码中，</span><code data-lake-id="u21730bb4" id="u21730bb4"><span data-lake-id="u985cee22" id="u985cee22">msg='你好'</span></code><span data-lake-id="u681d4b93" id="u681d4b93">这个默认参数，居然写在了位置参数</span><code data-lake-id="u84c79da5" id="u84c79da5"><span data-lake-id="u36d7115c" id="u36d7115c">height</span></code><span data-lake-id="u60344c04" id="u60344c04">前面，所以就会报错。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%E9%BB%98%E8%AE%A4%E5%80%BC%E7%9A%84%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%88%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%E9%BB%98%E8%AE%A4%E5%80%BC%E7%9A%84%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B%EF%BC%89%5Cndef%20greet(name%2C%20gender%2C%20age%2C%20%20msg%3D'%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD'%2C%20height)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(f'%E6%88%91%E5%8F%AB%7Bname%7D%EF%BC%8C%E6%80%A7%E5%88%AB%7Bgender%7D%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B4%E9%BE%84%E6%98%AF%7Bage%7D%EF%BC%8C%E8%BA%AB%E9%AB%98%E6%98%AF%7Bheight%7Dcm')%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(f'%E6%88%91%E6%83%B3%E8%AF%B4%EF%BC%9A%7Bmsg%7D')%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%E9%BB%98%E8%AE%A4%E5%80%BC%E7%9A%84%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22W7cdB%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h3 data-lake-id="cm9DM" id="cm9DM" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u0ece500e" id="u0ece500e">可变参数</span></h3><p data-lake-id="ua9e099b8" id="ua9e099b8"><span data-lake-id="uf51664ed" id="uf51664ed">在定义函数时，如果不确定会传入多少个参数，那就可以使用可变参数，具体写法有两种：</span></p><ul list="u0d83a3e4"><li fid="ue0a161c8" data-lake-id="u76f4ae03" id="u76f4ae03"><span data-lake-id="u284bd7d2" id="u284bd7d2">使用</span><code data-lake-id="u96ccca5e" id="u96ccca5e"><span data-lake-id="u7fbfcb12" id="u7fbfcb12">*形参名</span></code><span data-lake-id="u932b5dea" id="u932b5dea">来接收任意数量的『位置参数』，多个位置参数最终会被打包成一个</span><span data-lake-id="ucb341110" id="ucb341110" style="color: rgb(38, 38, 38)">『</span><span data-lake-id="ud08fc5c7" id="ud08fc5c7">元组</span><span data-lake-id="udc0ec7a4" id="udc0ec7a4" style="color: rgb(38, 38, 38)">』。</span></li><li fid="ue0a161c8" data-lake-id="ucd7a6bd5" id="ucd7a6bd5"><span data-lake-id="uf7c7c88c" id="uf7c7c88c">使用</span><code data-lake-id="uc78833b9" id="uc78833b9"><span data-lake-id="u8bbaba43" id="u8bbaba43">**形参名</span></code><span data-lake-id="u1a016a40" id="u1a016a40">来接收任意数量的『关键字参数』，多个关键字参数最终会被打包成一个</span><span data-lake-id="u889a4d60" id="u889a4d60" style="color: rgb(38, 38, 38)">『</span><span data-lake-id="u1efe5cc7" id="u1efe5cc7">字典</span><span data-lake-id="u8e49c377" id="u8e49c377" style="color: rgb(38, 38, 38)">』。</span></li></ul><blockquote data-lake-id="u2fcf60bb" id="u2fcf60bb" class="lake-alert lake-alert-tips"><p data-lake-id="uabc0839d" id="uabc0839d"><strong><span data-lake-id="u3e5d5a8b" id="u3e5d5a8b">📋</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="uaa86b92e" id="uaa86b92e">备注：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u66c06dde" id="u66c06dde">元组和字典都是新的数据类型，后面才会讲，但没关系，这不耽误大家理解本小节的内容。</span></p></blockquote><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%E5%8F%AF%E5%8F%98%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%9A*args%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%88%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8*args%E5%8E%BB%E6%8E%A5%E6%94%B6%EF%BC%9A%E5%8F%AF%E5%8F%98%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%8Cargs%E5%8F%AA%E6%98%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%B6%E4%B9%A0%E6%83%AF%E8%BF%99%E4%B9%88%E5%86%99%EF%BC%8C%E5%BD%93%E7%84%B6%E4%B9%9F%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E6%8D%A2%E6%88%90%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%EF%BC%89%5Cndef%20test1(*args)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%23%20%E6%AD%A4%E5%A4%84args%E7%9A%84%E5%80%BC%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E7%A7%8D%E6%96%B0%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AB%EF%BC%9A%E5%85%83%E7%BB%84%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E4%B8%8B%E4%B8%80%E7%AB%A0%E5%B0%B1%E5%8E%BB%E8%AE%B2%E5%85%83%E7%BB%84%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(args)%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E8%B0%83%E7%94%A8%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%5Cntest1('%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89'%2C%20'%E7%94%B7'%2C%2018%2C%20172)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%E5%8F%AF%E5%8F%98%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%9A*args%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22m2ekL%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%E5%8F%AF%E5%8F%98%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E5%AD%97%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%9A**kwargs%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%88%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8**kwargs%E5%8E%BB%E6%8E%A5%E6%94%B6%EF%BC%9A%E5%8F%AF%E5%8F%98%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E5%AD%97%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%8Ckwargs%E5%8F%AA%E6%98%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%B6%E4%B9%A0%E6%83%AF%E8%BF%99%E4%B9%88%E5%86%99%EF%BC%8C%E5%BD%93%E7%84%B6%E4%B9%9F%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E6%8D%A2%E6%88%90%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%EF%BC%89%5Cndef%20test2(**kwargs)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%23%20%E6%AD%A4%E5%A4%84kwargs%E7%9A%84%E5%80%BC%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E7%A7%8D%E6%96%B0%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AB%EF%BC%9A%E5%AD%97%E5%85%B8%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E4%B8%8B%E4%B8%80%E7%AB%A0%E5%B0%B1%E5%8E%BB%E8%AE%B2%E5%AD%97%E5%85%B8%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(kwargs)%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E8%B0%83%E7%94%A8%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%5Cntest2(name%3D'%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89'%2C%20gender%3D'%E7%94%B7'%2C%20age%3D18%2C%20height%3D172)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%E5%8F%AF%E5%8F%98%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E5%AD%97%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%9A**kwargs%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22swwGs%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u1d708b45" id="u1d708b45"><span data-lake-id="ub36c23fc" id="ub36c23fc">💡</span><span data-lake-id="u4bde97fe" id="u4bde97fe">『可变位置参数』和『可变关键字参数』，可以同时使用，但必须要</span><strong><span data-lake-id="uad62515f" id="uad62515f" style="color: #AD1A2B">先写</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="u8c7fcdaf" id="u8c7fcdaf">『</span></strong><span data-lake-id="ubefaf52d" id="ubefaf52d">可变位置参数</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u266fc6ca" id="u266fc6ca">』</span></strong><span data-lake-id="ue161fd48" id="ue161fd48">。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%E5%90%8C%E6%97%B6%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%9A%E5%8F%AF%E5%8F%98%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%E3%80%81%E5%8F%AF%E5%8F%98%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E5%AD%97%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%88%E5%90%8C%E6%97%B6%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%9A%E5%8F%AF%E5%8F%98%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%E3%80%81%E5%8F%AF%E5%8F%98%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E5%AD%97%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%89%5Cndef%20test3(a%2C%20b%2C%20*args%2C%20c%3D'%E5%B0%9A%E7%A1%85%E8%B0%B7'%2C%20**kwargs)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(a)%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(b)%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(c)%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(args)%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(kwargs)%5Cn%23%20%E8%B0%83%E7%94%A8%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%5Cntest3('%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89'%2C%20'%E7%94%B7'%2C%20'%E6%8A%BD%E7%83%9F'%2C%20'%E5%96%9D%E9%85%92'%2C%20age%3D18%2C%20height%3D172)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%E5%90%8C%E6%97%B6%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%9A%E5%8F%AF%E5%8F%98%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%E3%80%81%E5%8F%AF%E5%8F%98%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E5%AD%97%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22UiMOa%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h3 data-lake-id="raP25" id="raP25" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="uc192c793" id="uc192c793">特殊的字面量 None</span></h3><p data-lake-id="u5efb80e7" id="u5efb80e7"><span data-lake-id="u9feb8b37" id="u9feb8b37">None 是一个特殊的字面量，用来表示：空值、无值、无意义。</span></p><p data-lake-id="u0596b760" id="u0596b760"><span data-lake-id="u76c746dd" id="u76c746dd">例如：</span><code data-lake-id="ub8b8ef66" id="ub8b8ef66"><span data-lake-id="udbd64179" id="udbd64179">msg = None</span></code><span data-lake-id="u6b8ba169" id="u6b8ba169"> 的含义是 —— 我先定义一个变量 </span><code data-lake-id="ua11ead4f" id="ua11ead4f"><span data-lake-id="ub24b40e4" id="ub24b40e4">msg</span></code><span data-lake-id="u1454f163" id="u1454f163">，但目前还不知道它会存储什么类型的值，那能不能写成 </span><code data-lake-id="u39454072" id="u39454072"><span data-lake-id="u9d034128" id="u9d034128">msg = 0</span></code><span data-lake-id="u6e56b896" id="u6e56b896"> 呢？这要看具体情况：</span></p><blockquote data-lake-id="u00941eed" id="u00941eed" class="lake-alert lake-alert-info"><ul list="uf177f9ba"><li fid="u6d096ae0" data-lake-id="ud2ea597a" id="ud2ea597a"><span data-lake-id="u7e95c287" id="u7e95c287">如果确定 </span><code data-lake-id="u9fac6ada" id="u9fac6ada"><span data-lake-id="u092e3d4f" id="u092e3d4f">msg</span></code><span data-lake-id="u17495033" id="u17495033"> 之后会存放数值类型的数据，那这样写是可以的。</span></li><li fid="u6d096ae0" data-lake-id="u805c5fe7" id="u805c5fe7"><span data-lake-id="u9996df52" id="u9996df52">但如果还不确定 </span><code data-lake-id="u404c88cf" id="u404c88cf"><span data-lake-id="u672b8b67" id="u672b8b67">msg</span></code><span data-lake-id="u89da49a9" id="u89da49a9"> 将来会存放什么类型的数据，最好不要写成 </span><code data-lake-id="u81058f40" id="u81058f40"><span data-lake-id="u4338a651" id="u4338a651">msg = 0</span></code><span data-lake-id="u4822f3eb" id="u4822f3eb">，否则可能会误导别人以为它一定是数值类型。</span></li></ul></blockquote><p data-lake-id="ue2d83698" id="ue2d83698"><span data-lake-id="u066cd972" id="u066cd972">所以使用 None 更加中立、开放，因为它不暗示变量的类型。</span></p><blockquote data-lake-id="ub57addd0" id="ub57addd0"><p data-lake-id="u4f87cf05" id="u4f87cf05"><span data-lake-id="uf33a2cbf" id="uf33a2cbf">None 的官方文档：</span><a href="https://docs.python.org/zh-cn/3.13/library/constants.html#None" target="_blank" data-lake-id="uaf144d40" id="uaf144d40"><span data-lake-id="u6615ebc1" id="u6615ebc1">https://docs.python.org/zh-cn/3.13/library/constants.html#None</span></a></p></blockquote><blockquote data-lake-id="u6a2a5f99" id="u6a2a5f99" class="lake-alert lake-alert-info"><p data-lake-id="ub637ccfe" id="ub637ccfe"><strong><span data-lake-id="u952525d0" id="u952525d0">💡</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="u9268970f" id="u9268970f">几个关键点：</span></strong></p><ol list="ude7b8de1"><li fid="uf26fe553" data-lake-id="u276508c6" id="u276508c6"><code data-lake-id="u388c0607" id="u388c0607"><span data-lake-id="u316fb5a7" id="u316fb5a7">None</span></code><span data-lake-id="u873a882e" id="u873a882e">的类型是</span><code data-lake-id="u15b6bc7c" id="u15b6bc7c"><span data-lake-id="u9d2435aa" id="u9d2435aa">NoneType</span></code><span data-lake-id="u1eb1a069" id="u1eb1a069">。</span></li><li fid="uf26fe553" data-lake-id="ud6a1c556" id="ud6a1c556"><code data-lake-id="u48824dd3" id="u48824dd3"><span data-lake-id="u4a014a06" id="u4a014a06" style="color: rgb(38, 38, 38)">None</span></code><span data-lake-id="u27afb0d6" id="u27afb0d6" style="color: rgb(38, 38, 38)">出现在布尔判断中(</span><code data-lake-id="u276ffc83" id="u276ffc83"><span data-lake-id="u7c7ca219" id="u7c7ca219" style="color: rgb(38, 38, 38)">if</span></code><span data-lake-id="u6ed77d68" id="u6ed77d68" style="color: rgb(38, 38, 38)">判断条件、</span><code data-lake-id="uba63b66e" id="uba63b66e"><span data-lake-id="ue4136a4d" id="ue4136a4d" style="color: rgb(38, 38, 38)">while</span></code><span data-lake-id="u737b836e" id="u737b836e" style="color: rgb(38, 38, 38)">循环条件)，会被当作</span><code data-lake-id="ud6bae3ff" id="ud6bae3ff"><span data-lake-id="ucad18c43" id="ucad18c43" style="color: rgb(38, 38, 38)">False</span></code><span data-lake-id="uee5300ff" id="uee5300ff" style="color: rgb(38, 38, 38)">来处理。</span></li><li fid="uf26fe553" data-lake-id="u6be602b7" id="u6be602b7"><code data-lake-id="u80ee6d1c" id="u80ee6d1c"><span data-lake-id="u6b48bbfa" id="u6b48bbfa">None</span></code><span data-lake-id="u56b46b8b" id="u56b46b8b">不能参与任何数学运算，也不能与字符串拼接。</span></li><li fid="uf26fe553" data-lake-id="uc5b55f42" id="uc5b55f42"><span data-lake-id="uf9e4ee9f" id="uf9e4ee9f">不给函数设置返回值，那函数默认就会返回</span><code data-lake-id="uc4ba01e1" id="uc4ba01e1"><span data-lake-id="u4df6e3e8" id="u4df6e3e8">None</span></code></li></ol></blockquote><p data-lake-id="uec04fc47" id="uec04fc47"><code data-lake-id="uaf776062" id="uaf776062"><span data-lake-id="u08f4e70d" id="u08f4e70d">None</span></code><span data-lake-id="ud6070cbc" id="ud6070cbc">出现最多的两个场景：</span></p><blockquote data-lake-id="u61e139ae" id="u61e139ae" class="lake-alert lake-alert-info"><p data-lake-id="u85818244" id="u85818244"><span data-lake-id="u8ed65f2b" id="u8ed65f2b">1️⃣</span><span data-lake-id="u4a105bad" id="u4a105bad">函数中没有写</span><code data-lake-id="u540b0810" id="u540b0810"><span data-lake-id="u477d7ff7" id="u477d7ff7">return</span></code><span data-lake-id="u17df83c4" id="u17df83c4">，或写了</span><code data-lake-id="u24a6cc8e" id="u24a6cc8e"><span data-lake-id="ueb775dbf" id="ueb775dbf">return</span></code><span data-lake-id="u36882416" id="u36882416">但没有返回任何内容  。</span></p><p data-lake-id="ueb894beb" id="ueb894beb"><span data-lake-id="u0268c210" id="u0268c210">2️⃣</span><span data-lake-id="ub681a416" id="ub681a416">变量定义时，暂时还不知道要存放什么，可以先赋值为</span><code data-lake-id="u85139063" id="u85139063"><span data-lake-id="ufe70f4d6" id="ufe70f4d6">None</span></code><span data-lake-id="ud51ac678" id="ud51ac678">。</span></p></blockquote><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20None%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%89%B9%E6%AE%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%AD%97%E9%9D%A2%E9%87%8F%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%83%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%EF%BC%9A%E7%A9%BA%E5%80%BC%20%2F%20%E6%97%A0%E5%80%BC%20%2F%20%E6%97%A0%E6%84%8F%E4%B9%89%E3%80%82%5Cnmsg%20%3D%20None%5Cn%5Cn%23%20None%20%E7%9A%84%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%E6%98%AF%20NoneType%E3%80%82%5Cnprint(type(msg))%5Cn%5Cn%23%20None%20%E8%BD%AC%E4%B8%BA%E5%B8%83%E5%B0%94%E5%80%BC%E6%98%AF%20False%E3%80%82%5Cnprint(bool(msg))%5Cnif%20not%20msg%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20print('%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD')%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E5%8F%82%E4%B8%8E%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%A6%E8%BF%90%E7%AE%97%EF%BC%8C%E4%B9%9F%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%8E%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%B2%E6%8B%BC%E6%8E%A5%E3%80%82%5Cn%23%20result1%20%3D%20msg%20%2B%201%5Cn%23%20result1%20%3D%20msg%20%2B%20'hello'%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22H9X2g%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h2 data-lake-id="Bzkww" id="Bzkww" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u7948edb9" id="u7948edb9">返回值</span></h2><h3 data-lake-id="zCvct" id="zCvct" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="udf7e6fb4" id="udf7e6fb4">什么是返回值</span></h3><p data-lake-id="u387b6f87" id="u387b6f87"><strong><span data-lake-id="u81a0e6f2" id="u81a0e6f2">函数返回值：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u091b9104" id="u091b9104">函数执行完毕后，会把执行结果交给调用者，这个执行结果就是函数的返回值。</span></p><p data-lake-id="uec492cb1" id="uec492cb1"><span data-lake-id="u07cc9ef1" id="u07cc9ef1">我们之前用过的这些内置函数，都有返回值：</span></p><p data-lake-id="u34ae18fd" id="u34ae18fd"><card type="inline" name="image" value="data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F35780599%2F1760795152024-a8cbd774-0893-44bc-9041-c6779ec9e16c.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22uef819830-96ed-49e5-a0ae-939095e17a0%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u06fb607d-ba8d-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A382.57501220703125%2C%22height%22%3A134%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A47860%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A953%2C%22originHeight%22%3A333%2C%22ratio%22%3A1.6500000953674316%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%227EEOAE)%22%2C%22x%22%3A204%2C%22y%22%3A148%2C%22width%22%3A558%2C%22height%22%3A78%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E4%B8%80RES2-IT(15.6)%22%2C%22x%22%3A234%2C%22y%22%3A88%2C%22width%22%3A545%2C%22height%22%3A65%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%3E%E4%B8%80RES1%3DTYPE(%5C%22%E5%B0%94%E5%A5%BD%E5%95%8A%22%2C%22x%22%3A206%2C%22y%22%3A32%2C%22width%22%3A685%2C%22height%22%3A42%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E4%B8%80RES4%3DCHR(97%22%2C%22x%22%3A257%2C%22y%22%3A204%2C%22width%22%3A479%2C%22height%22%3A42%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22-RES5%3DB001(300%22%2C%22x%22%3A286%2C%22y%22%3A261%2C%22width%22%3A487%2C%22height%22%3A40%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%3CCLASS%22%2C%22x%22%3A1%2C%22y%22%3A35%2C%22width%22%3A158%2C%22height%22%3A35%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22TRUE%22%2C%22x%22%3A164%2C%22y%22%3A266%2C%22width%22%3A99%2C%22height%22%3A35%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%2215%22%2C%22x%22%3A203%2C%22y%22%3A89%2C%22width%22%3A65%2C%22height%22%3A44%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%2297%22%2C%22x%22%3A202%2C%22y%22%3A140%2C%22width%22%3A81%2C%22height%22%3A50%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23343434%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22GRVZQ%22%7D"></card></p><p data-lake-id="ude402a27" id="ude402a27"><span data-lake-id="ud51530a5" id="ud51530a5">对于自定义的函数，即便我们不去设置返回值，函数也会默认返回</span><code data-lake-id="u31f1bc0c" id="u31f1bc0c"><span data-lake-id="u40cb7f5d" id="u40cb7f5d">None</span></code><span data-lake-id="uad40e74d" id="uad40e74d">，由于</span><code data-lake-id="u58e32aec" id="u58e32aec"><span data-lake-id="u287fa8ed" id="u287fa8ed">None</span></code><span data-lake-id="uc2de6a1e" id="uc2de6a1e">表示空，所以如果一个函数的返回值是</span><code data-lake-id="u4916a125" id="u4916a125"><span data-lake-id="u595e3a77" id="u595e3a77">None</span></code><span data-lake-id="u86383d83" id="u86383d83">的话，就也可以说：这个函数“没有”返回值。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%5Cndef%20add(n1%2C%20n2)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(f'%E6%88%91%E6%94%B6%E5%88%B0%E4%BA%86%EF%BC%9A%7Bn1%7D%E3%80%81%7Bn2%7D%EF%BC%8C%E4%BA%8C%E8%80%85%E7%9B%B8%E5%8A%A0%E6%98%AF%EF%BC%9A%7Bn1%20%2B%20n2%7D')%5Cn%20%20%20%20print('add%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E5%AE%8C%E6%AF%95%E4%BA%86')%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E8%B0%83%E7%94%A8%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%5Cnresult%20%3D%20add(100%2C%20200)%5Cnprint(result)%20%20%23%20None%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22gWbqD%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h3 data-lake-id="Hdwp5" id="Hdwp5" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="ub8aaa267" id="ub8aaa267">如何设置返回值</span></h3><p data-lake-id="uac2d0cf8" id="uac2d0cf8"><span data-lake-id="u51f524b2" id="u51f524b2">使用</span><code data-lake-id="u07c99c68" id="u07c99c68"><span data-lake-id="u2c18781b" id="u2c18781b">return</span></code><span data-lake-id="u707337a3" id="u707337a3">关键字可以设置函数的返回值，</span><code data-lake-id="ud695c242" id="ud695c242"><span data-lake-id="u2c657954" id="u2c657954">return</span></code><span data-lake-id="ud364eca2" id="ud364eca2">的作用有两个，分别是：</span></p><ol list="u20534690"><li fid="ua139cbe2" data-lake-id="u56163ea4" id="u56163ea4"><span data-lake-id="u9b12e63a" id="u9b12e63a">结束函数的运行。</span></li><li fid="ua139cbe2" data-lake-id="u35a316a0" id="u35a316a0"><span data-lake-id="u499a6476" id="u499a6476">把</span><code data-lake-id="u68186897" id="u68186897"><span data-lake-id="u7ec8f151" id="u7ec8f151">return</span></code><span data-lake-id="uf4358307" id="uf4358307">后面的值，作为函数的返回值。</span></li></ol><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E%E5%80%BC%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%5Cndef%20add(n1%2C%20n2)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(f'%E6%88%91%E6%94%B6%E5%88%B0%E4%BA%86%EF%BC%9A%7Bn1%7D%E3%80%81%7Bn2%7D%EF%BC%8C%E4%BA%8C%E8%80%85%E7%9B%B8%E5%8A%A0%E6%98%AF%EF%BC%9A%7Bn1%20%2B%20n2%7D')%5Cn%20%20%20%20print('add%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E5%AE%8C%E6%AF%95%E4%BA%86')%5Cn%20%20%20%20return%20n1%20%2B%20n2%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E8%B0%83%E7%94%A8%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%5Cnresult%20%3D%20add(100%2C%20200)%5Cnprint(result)%5Cn%5Cn%23%20print%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E6%98%AF%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E%E5%80%BC%E7%9A%84%5Cnres%20%3D%20print('hello')%5Cnprint(res)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E%E5%80%BC%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22hXFre%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h2 data-lake-id="aPAvb" id="aPAvb" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u848ccecd" id="u848ccecd">全局作用域 VS 局部作用域</span></h2><h3 data-lake-id="uKIKb" id="uKIKb" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u3e1f332c" id="u3e1f332c">什么是作用域？</span></h3><p data-lake-id="u46fb7632" id="u46fb7632"><span data-lake-id="uac9aa81c" id="uac9aa81c">作用域就是变量能</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u0f6aa30d" id="u0f6aa30d" style="color: #ED740C">起作用的范围</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u2e4cb70d" id="u2e4cb70d">（变量在哪里能用，在哪里不能用），Python 中有多种作用域，我们先来学习：全局作用域、局部作用域。</span></p><h3 data-lake-id="O25fK" id="O25fK" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u236abbc5" id="u236abbc5">全局作用域 _ 全局变量</span></h3><ol list="u7adb6a33"><li fid="ue4ecdd58" data-lake-id="u0b461af2" id="u0b461af2"><strong><span data-lake-id="u7c55d810" id="u7c55d810">全局作用域：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="uc67a0b05" id="uc67a0b05">整个</span><code data-lake-id="ua640e834" id="ua640e834"><span data-lake-id="u3a4c84b1" id="u3a4c84b1">.py</span></code><span data-lake-id="uc980feea" id="uc980feea">文件最外层的范围，就是全局作用域。</span></li><li fid="ue4ecdd58" data-lake-id="u3462bde5" id="u3462bde5"><strong><span data-lake-id="udd45e7e4" id="udd45e7e4">全局变量：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u498cfc83" id="u498cfc83">写在全局作用域中的变量，就叫：全局变量，全局变量在整个程序中都可以访问。</span></li></ol><p data-lake-id="u28de6cad" id="u28de6cad" style="text-indent: 2em"><card type="inline" name="image" value="data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F35780599%2F1760798762045-98ef22ad-db01-48a3-a0c2-ff48148cd9c5.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u3df4514b-fe88-4d8e-aaac-d692c0c694c%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u06fb607d-ba8d-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A455.7802734375%2C%22height%22%3A239%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A59857%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1286%2C%22originHeight%22%3A675%2C%22ratio%22%3A1.6500000953674316%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%85%A8%E5%B1%80%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%E5%9F%9F%3A%E6%95%B4%E4%B8%AAPY%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%96%E5%B1%82%E7%9A%84%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%2C%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E5%85%A8%E5%B1%80%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%E5%9F%9F.%22%2C%22x%22%3A35%2C%22y%22%3A29%2C%22width%22%3A1209%2C%22height%22%3A54%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%B1%80%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F(%E5%9C%A8%E5%BD%93%E5%89%8D%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E7%9A%84%E4%BB%BB%E6%84%8F%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E9%83%BD%E8%83%BD%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%22%2C%22x%22%3A508%2C%22y%22%3A152%2C%22width%22%3A726%2C%22height%22%3A46%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22DEMO.PY%22%2C%22x%22%3A167%2C%22y%22%3A633%2C%22width%22%3A146%2C%22height%22%3A34%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22100%22%2C%22x%22%3A125%2C%22y%22%3A135%2C%22width%22%3A90%2C%22height%22%3A32%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22200%22%2C%22x%22%3A117%2C%22y%22%3A181%2C%22width%22%3A97%2C%22height%22%3A34%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22B%22%2C%22x%22%3A42%2C%22y%22%3A182%2C%22width%22%3A40%2C%22height%22%3A32%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E4%B8%80%22%2C%22x%22%3A80%2C%22y%22%3A185%2C%22width%22%3A53%2C%22height%22%3A28%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22A%22%2C%22x%22%3A44%2C%22y%22%3A137%2C%22width%22%3A35%2C%22height%22%3A39%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E4%B8%89%22%2C%22x%22%3A67%2C%22y%22%3A140%2C%22width%22%3A73%2C%22height%22%3A28%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23e3e309%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22lW5Ih%22%7D"></card></p><h3 data-lake-id="bIynk" id="bIynk" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u1127317d" id="u1127317d">局部作用域 _ 局部变量</span></h3><ol list="u59b2a6e5"><li fid="u7acfbd34" data-lake-id="u281165e6" id="u281165e6"><strong><span data-lake-id="u8270a30b" id="u8270a30b">局部作用域：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u58db311c" id="u58db311c">函数的内部范围，就是局部作用域。 </span></li><li fid="u7acfbd34" data-lake-id="ucacba537" id="ucacba537"><strong><span data-lake-id="u06035dfa" id="u06035dfa">局部变量：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u004856c2" id="u004856c2">写在局部作用域中（函数内部）的变量，叫：局部变量，它只能在当前函数中使用。</span></li></ol><p data-lake-id="u1731a0b6" id="u1731a0b6" style="text-indent: 2em"><card type="inline" name="image" value="data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F35780599%2F1760799330564-af9b0894-e963-4735-a59a-b46954d68cad.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22uc5739bd2-ccd9-4205-8f45-6a0aab2ff15%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u06fb607d-ba8d-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A437.84844970703125%2C%22height%22%3A264%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A65233%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1135%2C%22originHeight%22%3A685%2C%22ratio%22%3A1.6500000953674316%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22stroke%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%86%85%E9