20975028">新增</span></h4><p data-lake-id="u98be149d" id="u98be149d"><span data-lake-id="ud420a34f" id="ud420a34f">列表的新增指的是：向列表中添加元素，主要有如下三种添加方式：</span></p><p data-lake-id="u18f08ef6" id="u18f08ef6"><strong><span data-lake-id="u629a7a1e" id="u629a7a1e">方式1</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u9f5c90d4" id="u9f5c90d4">：使用：</span><code data-lake-id="u8b5f682b" id="u8b5f682b"><span data-lake-id="u4f977108" id="u4f977108">列表.append(元素)</span></code><span data-lake-id="u7fb1bd65" id="u7fb1bd65">，在列表尾部追加一个元素。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%9A%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8%E7%9A%84append%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8%E5%B0%BE%E9%83%A8%E8%BF%BD%E5%8A%A0%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%5Cnnums%20%3D%20%5B10%2C%2020%2C%2030%2C%2040%5D%5Cnnums.append(50)%5Cnprint(nums)%20%20%23%20%5B10%2C%2020%2C%2030%2C%2040%2C%2050%5D%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22LGiu0%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="ue842d3ed" id="ue842d3ed"><strong><span data-lake-id="u38552853" id="u38552853">方式2</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u418dc570" id="u418dc570">：使用：</span><code data-lake-id="u2ee094ed" id="u2ee094ed"><span data-lake-id="u3bc9bd28" id="u3bc9bd28">列表.insert(元素)</span></code><span data-lake-id="uce45ee6a" id="uce45ee6a">，在指定下标处添加一个元素。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%9A%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8%E7%9A%84insert%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%8C%E5%9C%A8%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8%E7%9A%84%E6%8C%87%E5%AE%9A%E4%B8%8B%E6%A0%87%E5%A4%84%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%5Cnnums%20%3D%20%5B10%2C%2020%2C%2030%2C%2040%5D%5Cnnums.insert(2%2C%20666)%5Cnprint(nums)%20%20%23%20%5B10%2C%2020%2C%20666%2C%2030%2C%2040%5D%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22XpIRf%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u572bfa51" id="u572bfa51"><strong><span data-lake-id="uff416b5e" id="uff416b5e">方式3</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u896e2923" id="u896e2923">：使用：</span><code data-lake-id="u45412844" id="u45412844"><span data-lake-id="u7ea63fce" id="u7ea63fce">列表.extend(可迭代对象)</span></code><span data-lake-id="u6dd8caa0" id="u6dd8caa0">，将可迭代对象中的内容依次取出，追加到列表尾部。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E4%B8%89%EF%BC%9A%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8%E7%9A%84extend%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%86%E5%8F%AF%E8%BF%AD%E4%BB%A3%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E4%BE%9D%E6%AC%A1%E5%8F%96%E5%87%BA%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%BD%E5%8A%A0%E5%88%B0%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8%E5%B0%BE%E9%83%A8%5Cnnums%20%3D%20%5B10%2C%2020%2C%2030%2C%2040%5D%5Cnnums.extend('%E5%B0%9A%E7%A1%85%E8%B0%B7')%5Cnnums.extend(range(1%2C%204))%5Cnnums.extend(%5B70%2C%2080%2C%2090%5D)%5Cnprint(nums)%20%20%23%20%5B10%2C%2020%2C%2030%2C%2040%2C%20'%E5%B0%9A'%2C%20'%E7%A1%85'%2C%20'%E8%B0%B7'%2C%201%2C%202%2C%203%2C%2070%2C%2080%2C%2090%5D%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22qkq1Q%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h4 data-lake-id="HJI36" id="HJI36"><span data-lake-id="u3866aeb3" id="u3866aeb3">2️⃣</span><span data-lake-id="u25f14ac9" id="u25f14ac9">删除</span></h4><p data-lake-id="u586b9c39" id="u586b9c39"><span data-lake-id="u06b3040a" id="u06b3040a">主要有如下四种删除方式：</span></p><p data-lake-id="u9780e2b7" id="u9780e2b7"><strong><span data-lake-id="ua198ff91" id="ua198ff91">方式1：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="ue1e39b33" id="ue1e39b33">使用：</span><code data-lake-id="ue192a36b" id="ue192a36b"><span data-lake-id="u5771680b" id="u5771680b">列表.pop(下标)</span></code><span data-lake-id="u46306de9" id="u46306de9">，删除指定位置的元素，并将删除的元素返回。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%9A%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8%E7%9A%84pop%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%A0%E9%99%A4%E6%8C%87%E5%AE%9A%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%9A%84%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E%E8%AF%A5%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%5Cnnums%20%3D%20%5B10%2C%2020%2C%2010%2C%2040%2C%2050%5D%5Cnresult%20%3D%20nums.pop(1)%5Cnprint(nums)%20%20%20%23%20%5B10%2C%2010%2C%2040%2C%2050%5D%5Cnprint(result)%20%23%2020%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22wBKDj%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u795ec229" id="u795ec229"><strong><span data-lake-id="ue17d8023" id="ue17d8023">方式2：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="uc8d6aadb" id="uc8d6aadb">使用：</span><code data-lake-id="u7fe95e93" id="u7fe95e93"><span data-lake-id="u26e4709f" id="u26e4709f">列表.remove(值)</span></code><span data-lake-id="u6db39745" id="u6db39745">，删除列表中第一次出现的指定值。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%9A%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8%E7%9A%84remove%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%A0%E9%99%A4%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8%E4%B8%AD%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%E5%87%BA%E7%8E%B0%E7%9A%84%E6%8C%87%E5%AE%9A%E5%80%BC%5Cnnums%20%3D%20%5B10%2C%2020%2C%2010%2C%2040%2C%2050%5D%5Cnnums.remove(10)%5Cnprint(nums)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22KPxy5%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u17845134" id="u17845134"><strong><span data-lake-id="u4110d065" id="u4110d065">方式3：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u80150a0b" id="u80150a0b">使用：</span><code data-lake-id="uc54b626a" id="uc54b626a"><span data-lake-id="u3e990bd9" id="u3e990bd9">列表.clear()</span></code><span data-lake-id="u398eda98" id="u398eda98">，删除列表中所有的元素（变成一个空列表）。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E4%B8%89%EF%BC%9A%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%8