7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%204.%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%86%85%E7%BD%AE%E7%9A%84%20min%20%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%8C%E8%8E%B7%E5%8F%96%E5%AE%B9%E5%99%A8%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%80%E5%B0%8F%E5%80%BC%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E%E5%80%BC%E6%98%AF%EF%BC%9A%E6%9C%80%E5%B0%8F%E5%80%BC%E3%80%82%5Cn%23%20%E5%A4%87%E6%B3%A8%EF%BC%9Amin%20%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E4%B8%8E%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E7%82%B9%E4%B8%8E%20max%20%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E4%B8%80%E6%A0%B7%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AA%E4%B8%8D%E8%BF%87%20min%20%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E%E7%9A%84%E6%98%AF%E6%9C%80%E5%B0%8F%E5%80%BC%5Cnnums%20%3D%20%5B23%2C%2011%2C%2032%2C%2030%2C%2017%5D%5Cnresult%20%3D%20min(nums)%5Cnprint(result)%20%23%2011%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22usZ77%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="uda370a93" id="uda370a93"><span data-lake-id="uf5af30c5" id="uf5af30c5">5️⃣</span><code data-lake-id="uc0370835" id="uc0370835"><span data-lake-id="u86070422" id="u86070422">sum(数据容器)</span></code><span data-lake-id="ucabcd127" id="ucabcd127">，对容器中所有元素求和（只能是数值类型），返回值：所有元素的和。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%205.%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%86%85%E7%BD%AE%E7%9A%84%20sum%20%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%B9%E5%AE%B9%E5%99%A8%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E6%B1%82%E5%92%8C%EF%BC%88%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%E5%8F%AA%E8%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E6%95%B0%E5%80%BC%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82%5Cnnums%20%3D%20%5B10%2C%2020%2C%2030%2C%2040%2C%2050%5D%5Cnresult%20%3D%20sum(nums)%5Cnprint(result)%20%23%20150%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22xuO1Q%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h3 data-lake-id="xCzZh" id="xCzZh" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u68348842" id="u68348842">列表的循环遍历</span></h3><p data-lake-id="ueb787b77" id="ueb787b77"><span data-lake-id="u0fabfcd3" id="u0fabfcd3">所谓遍历，就是将列表的每个元素依次取出进行处理，代码如下：</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%20while%20%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E9%81%8D%E5%8E%86%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E6%88%90%E7%BB%A9%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8%5Cnscore_list%20%3D%20%5B62%2C%2050%2C%2060%2C%2048%2C%2080%2C%2020%2C%2095%5D%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8while%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E9%81%8D%E5%8E%86%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8%5Cnindex%20%3D%200%5Cnwhile%20index%20%3C%20len(score_list)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(score_list%5Bindex%5D)%5Cn%20%20%20%20index%20%2B%3D%201%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%20while%20%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E9%81%8D%E5%8E%86%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22__widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22DBQj5%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%2C%22widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%7D"></card><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%20for%20%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E9%81%8D%E5%8E%86%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8for%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E9%81%8D%E5%8E%86%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8%5Cnfor%20item%20in%20score_list%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(item)%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8for%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E9%81%8D%E5%8E%86%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8%EF%BC%88%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87range%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%20%E5%92%8C%20len%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E6%8C%89%E7%85%A7%E7%B4%A2%E5%BC%95%E9%81%8D%E5%8E%86%EF%BC%89%5Cnfor%20index%20in%20range(len(score_list))%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(score_list%5Bindex%5D)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%20for%20%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E9%81%8D%E5%8E%86%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22__widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22vP3at%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%2C%22widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%7D"></card><blockquote data-lake-id="ue9985c72" id="ue9985c72" class="lake-alert lake-alert-info"><ol list="u751826c1"><li fid="ua48fac82" data-lake-id="ub96400ea" id="ub96400ea"><span data-lake-id="uc3e44e39" id="uc3e44e39">在上述遍历中，</span><code data-lake-id="u774ca7b7" id="u774ca7b7"><span data-lake-id="u0bfb0ce5" id="u0bfb0ce5">while</span></code><span data-lake-id="u6737618e" id="u6737618e">循环需要结束条件，所以我们定义了</span><code data-lake-id="u72478ebe" id="u72478ebe"><span data-lake-id="u98ffdd56" id="u98ffdd56">index</span></code><span data-lake-id="uced5368d" id="uced5368d">变量，所以打印时，就可以方便的借助</span><code data-lake-id="ued2162cb" id="ued2162cb"><span data-lake-id="ue75022ba" id="ue75022ba">index</span></code><span data-lake-id="u0b3fde9f" id="u0b3fde9f">输出当前元素是第几个。</span></li><li fid="ua48fac82" data-lake-id="u136725f3" id="u136725f3"><span data-lake-id="uce5cc673" id="uce5cc673">而</span><code data-lake-id="u301c9f96" id="u301c9f96"><span data-lake-id="u55965419" id="u55965419">for</span></code><span data-lake-id="u96ab3b7b" id="u96ab3b7b">循环的遍历，不需要</span><code data-lake-id="u255f5f79" id="u255f5f79"><span data-lake-id="ucf37b40f" id="ucf37b40f">index</span></code><span data-lake-id="uecc10f19" id="uecc10f19">，那如果也想打印元素是第几个，但又不想去定义</span><code data-lake-id="u26ef8cb4" id="u26ef8cb4"><span data-lake-id="u04b9f5c8" id="u04b9f5c8">index</span></code><span data-lake-id="u66546e12" id="u66546e12">的话，可以借助</span><code data-lake-id="u8067e8c6" id="u8067e8c6"><strong><span data-lake-id="ud5333fa8" id="ud5333fa8">enumerate</span></strong></code><span data-lake-id="u3f4ad0b5" id="u3f4ad0b5">这个内置函数，它可以在遍历时</span><strong><span data-lake-id="ueb625973" id="ueb625973">获取索引和值</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u21c09c01" id="u21c09c01">，代码如下：</span></li></ol></blockquote><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%20for%20%E7%BB%93%E5%90%88%20enumerate%20%E9%81%8D%E5%8E%86%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8for%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E9%81%8D%E5%8E%86%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8%EF%BC%88%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87enumerate%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%90%8C%E6%97%B6%E8%8E%B7%E5%8F%96%E4%B8%8B%E6%A0%87%EF%BC%88%E7%B4%A2%E5%BC%95%E5%80%BC%EF%BC%89%E5%92%8C%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%EF%BC%89%5Cn%23%20enumerate%20%E7%9A%84%20start%20%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E8%AE%A9%E8%AE%A1%E6%95%B0%E4%BB%8E%E6%8C%87%E5%AE%9A%E5%80%BC%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%EF%BC%88%E6%94%B9%E5%8F%98%E7%9A%84%E6%98%AF%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E6%97%B6%E7%9A%84%E2%80%9C%E7%BC%96%E5%8F%B7%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E7%9C%9F%E6%AD%A3%E7%9A%84%E7%B4%A2%E5%BC%95%E5%80%BC%EF%BC%89%5Cnfor%20index%2C%20item%20in%20enumerate(score_list%2C%20start%3D5)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(index%2C%20item%2C%20score_list%5B0%5D)%5Cnprint('%E6%9C%80%E5%90%8E%E7%9A%84%E6%89%93%E5%8D%B0'%2C%20score_list%5B0%5D)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%20for%20%E7%BB%93%E5%90%88%20enumerate%20%E9%81%8D%E5%8E%86%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22__widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Ueyx1%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%2C%22widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%7D"></card><h3 data-lake-id="zo2Jq" id="zo2Jq" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="ufcfa4a38" id="ufcfa4a38">列表特点总结</span></h3><ol list="ub37b06ea"><li fid="u018367ed" data-lake-id="u85617472" id="u85617472"><span data-lake-id="u5eeabd53" id="u5eeabd53">可存放不同类型的元素。</span></li><li fid="u018367ed" data-lake-id="u53d7987f" id="u53d7987f"><span data-lake-id="uc816aec3" id="uc816aec3">元素是有序存储的（正索引、负索引）。</span></li><li fid="u018367ed" data-lake-id="u8fba05af" id="u8fba05af"><span data-lake-id="u6d6c62b1" id="u6d6c62b1">列表中的元素允许重复。</span></li><li fid="u018367ed" data-lake-id="u3c34d760" id="u3c34d760"><span data-lake-id="u984f0fbf" id="u984f0fbf">元素是允许修改的（增、删、改、查、其他操作）。</span></li><li fid="u018367ed" data-lake-id="u1eaf2e5e" id="u1eaf2e5e"><span data-lake-id="u6b5fab76" id="u6b5fab76">长度不固定，可以随着操作自动调整大小。</span></li></ol><blockquote data-lake-id="u45dfd6fd" id="u45dfd6fd" class="lake-alert lake-alert-info"><p data-lake-id="u6ff821bb" id="u6ff821bb"><strong><span data-lake-id="uf7d0e720" id="uf7d0e720">📍</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="u099a245b" id="u099a245b">一句话总结</span></strong><span data-lake-id="udfcf0ea9" id="udfcf0ea9">：列表是最常用的数据容器，当遇到要“存储一批数据”的场景时，首选列表。</span></p></blockquote><h3 data-lake-id="TOryX" id="TOryX" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u7c3bffc2" id="u7c3bffc2">列表小练习</span></h3><p data-lake-id="u9fa4c99f" id="u9fa4c99f"><strong><span data-lake-id="u98c00548" id="u98c00548">需求：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="uf7a503a7" id="uf7a503a7">实现一个成绩统计程序，可以对多名学生的成绩，进行统计和分析。具体统计的项目如下图：</span></p><p data-lake-id="ufdff3f78" id="ufdff3f78"><card type="inline" name="image" value="data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F35780599%2F1760879477478-e6b7935d-236a-4138-96f1-d5625e96e354.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u5152b0ff-c261-4897-a2bf-f2e39a589ca%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22uebac531c-c172-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A230.7783966064453%2C%22height%22%3A222%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A75446%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A724%2C%22originHeight%22%3A696%2C%22ratio%22%3A1.6500000953674316%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%88%86%E6%95%B0%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%8E%E7%AD%89%E4%BA%8E90%22%2C%22x%22%3A329%2C%22y%22%3A452%2C%22width%22%3A367%2C%22height%22%3A51%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%88%86%E6%95%B0%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%8E%E7%AD%89%E4%BA%8E60%22%2C%22x%22%3A329%2C%22y%22%3A282%2C%22width%22%3A366%2C%22height%22%3A48%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%87%E5%88%86%E6%95%B0%22%2C%22x%22%3A92%2C%22y%22%3A629%2C%22width%22%3A199%2C%22height%22%3A54%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E4%BC%98%E7%A7%80%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B0%22%2C%22x%22%3A89%2C%22y%22%3A453%2C%22width%22%3A203%2C%22height%22%3A54%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%90%88%E6%A0%BC%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B0%22%2C%22x%22%3A84%2C%22y%22%3A282%2C%22width%22%3A198%2C%22height%22%3A52%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%90%88%E6%A0%BC%E7%8E%87%22%2C%22x%22%3A92%2C%22y%22%3A368%2C%22width%22%3A152%2C%22height%22%3A53%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E6%80%BB%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B0%22%2C%22x%22%3A77%2C%22y%22%3A19%2C%22width%22%