ake-id="ub2bf8355" id="ub2bf8355">，从集合中移除指定元素（若元素不存在，不会报错），无返回值。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20discard%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%9A%E4%BB%8E%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88%E4%B8%AD%E7%A7%BB%E9%99%A4%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%EF%BC%88%E7%A7%BB%E9%99%A4%E4%B8%8D%E5%AD%98%E5%9C%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%9A%E6%8A%A5%E9%94%99%EF%BC%89%5Cns1%20%3D%20%7B10%2C%2020%2C%2030%2C%2040%2C%2050%7D%5Cns1.discard(80)%5Cnprint(s1)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22vf6lq%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u18598a69" id="u18598a69"><strong><span data-lake-id="u9152a09e" id="u9152a09e">方式3：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="ufea49c43" id="ufea49c43">使用</span><code data-lake-id="uac4b6de6" id="uac4b6de6"><span data-lake-id="u8cfe10d5" id="u8cfe10d5">集合.pop()</span></code><span data-lake-id="u8c5d6929" id="u8c5d6929">，从集合中移除一个任意元素，返回值：移除的那个元素。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20pop%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%9A%E4%BB%8E%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88%E4%B8%AD%E7%A7%BB%E9%99%A4%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E4%BB%BB%E6%84%8F%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E%E5%80%BC%E6%98%AF%E7%A7%BB%E9%99%A4%E7%9A%84%E9%82%A3%E4%B8%AA%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%5Cns1%20%3D%20%7B10%2C%2020%2C%2030%2C%2040%2C%2050%7D%5Cns2%20%3D%20%7B'%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD'%2C%20'%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC'%2C%20'%E5%B0%9A%E7%A1%85%E8%B0%B7'%2C%20'hello'%7D%5Cnresult%20%3D%20s1.pop()%5Cnprint(s1)%5Cnprint(result)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22pIiNL%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u6090d73d" id="u6090d73d"><strong><span data-lake-id="uc763929f" id="uc763929f">方式4：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u90d8c529" id="u90d8c529">使用</span><code data-lake-id="u0e66b29c" id="u0e66b29c"><span data-lake-id="ubba3dfa1" id="ubba3dfa1">集合.clear()</span></code><span data-lake-id="u16096832" id="u16096832">，清空集合，无返回值。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20clear%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%9A%E6%B8%85%E7%A9%BA%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88%5Cns1%20%3D%20%7B10%2C%2020%2C%2030%2C%2040%2C%2050%7D%5Cns1.clear()%5Cnprint(s1)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22PS9YT%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="uec35808b" id="uec35808b"><span data-lake-id="ufc6c6ebb" id="ufc6c6ebb">3️⃣</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u2f38ed6b" id="u2f38ed6b">修改</span></strong></p><blockquote data-lake-id="u852ab3f4" id="u852ab3f4" class="lake-alert lake-alert-color4"><p data-lake-id="uc55af920" id="uc55af920"><strong><span data-lake-id="u7ff8ed8b" id="u7ff8ed8b" style="color: #AD1A2B">📢</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="ub59f7c80" id="ub59f7c80" style="color: #AD1A2B">注意：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u1c0a8b3c" id="u1c0a8b3c">集合没有下标，也不支持</span><code data-lake-id="u1ebffe15" id="u1ebffe15"><span data-lake-id="u35a75677" id="u35a75677">replace</span></code><span data-lake-id="udc9e49d8" id="udc9e49d8">方法，所以集合没有专门用于“改”的方法，但可以使用：</span><code data-lake-id="u6d6a181d" id="u6d6a181d"><span data-lake-id="u0b2f6614" id="u0b2f6614">remove</span></code><span data-lake-id="u349beebc" id="u349beebc">+</span><code data-lake-id="uf2ed55c1" id="uf2ed55c1"><span data-lake-id="u03547250" id="u03547250">add</span></code><span data-lake-id="u9f5366e3" id="u9f5366e3">的组合，来达到“修改”的效果。</span></p></blockquote><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E6%94%B9%5Cn%23%20%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%20add%20%2B%20remove%20%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%84%E5%90%88%EF%BC%8C%E6%9D%A5%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%E7%9A%84%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C%5Cns1%20%3D%20%7B10%2C%2020%2C%2030%2C%2040%2C%2050%7D%5Cns1.remove(20)%5Cns1.add(66)%5Cnprint(s1)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22FDBjo%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u3c838464" id="u3c838464"><span data-lake-id="u01c0b9b7" id="u01c0b9b7">4️⃣</span><strong><span data-lake-id="uda8a78d3" id="uda8a78d3">查询</span></strong></p><blockquote data-lake-id="u3ad2be02" id="u3ad2be02" class="lake-alert lake-alert-color4"><p data-lake-id="u58688f1e" id="u58688f1e"><strong><span data-lake-id="ub9f0f28c" id="ub9f0f28c" style="color: #AD1A2B">📢</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="u92aa5637" id="u92aa5637" style="color: #AD1A2B">注意：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u1cc2c868" id="u1cc2c868">由于集合没有下标，也不支持切片操作，所以集合不具备按位置访问的能力。虽然不能通过下标读取元素，但可以使用【成员运算符】来判断：某个元素是否在集合中，成员运算符我们会放在后面讲，不过大家可以提前感受一下：</span></p></blockquote><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E6%9F%A5%EF%BC%9A%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E4%B8%8B%E6%A0%87%E5%8E%BB%E8%AF%BB%E5%8F%96%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86%E8%83%BD%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%20%E3%80%90%E6%88%90%E5%91%98%E8%BF%90%E7%AE%97%E7%AC%A6%E3%80%91%E5%8E%BB%E6%9F%A5%E7%9C%8B%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88%E4%B8%AD%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E5%8C%85%E5%90%AB%E6%8C%87%E5%AE%9A%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%5Cn%23%20%E7%94%B1%E4%BA%8E%E6%88%90%E5%91%98%E8%BF%90%E7%AE%97%E7%AC%A6%E9%80%82%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8E%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%AE%B9%E5%99%A8%EF%BC%8C%E6%89%80%E4%BB%A5%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E4%BC%9A%E7%AD%89%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%AE%B9%E5%99%A8%E9%83%BD%E8%AE%B2%E5%AE%8C%E4%BB%A5%E5%90%8E%EF%BC%8C%E5%86%8D%E8%AF%B4%E6%88%90%E5%91%98%E8%BF%90%E7%AE%97%E7%AC%A6%5Cns1%20%3D%20%7B10%2C%2020%2C%2030%2C%2040%2C%2050%7D%5Cn%23%20s1%5B0%5D%20%23%20%E6%AD%A4%E8%A1%8C%E6%8A%A5%E9%94%99%EF%BC%8C%E5%9B%A0%E4%B8%BA%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E4%B8%8B%E6%A0%87%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E5%85%88%E6%8F%90%E5%89%8D%E6%84%9F%E5%8F%97%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%8B%E6%88%90%E5%91%98%E8%BF%90%E7%AE%97%E7%AC%A6%5Cnresult%20%3D%2020%20not%20in%20s1%5Cnprint(result)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22jyAyF%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h3 data-lake-id="bDVxY" id="bDVxY" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u9a55b9fc" id="u9a55b9fc">常用方法</span></h3><p data-lake-id="u7903dc2f" id="u7903dc2f"><span data-lake-id="uccb31d5e" id="uccb31d5e">集合常用的方法有如下几个：</span></p><p data-lake-id="u4eade5ae" id="u4eade5ae"><span data-lake-id="ud462ed82" id="ud462ed82">1️⃣</span><span data-lake-id="u7278349f" id="u7278349f">使用</span><code data-lake-id="u5355e376" id="u5355e376"><span data-lake-id="ufbb81f7e" id="ufbb81f7e">集合A.difference(集合B)</span></code><span data-lake-id="u3a40c020" id="u3a40c020">，找出集合A中，不同于集合B的元素。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88A.difference(%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88B)%EF%BC%9A%5Cn%23%20%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%9A%E6%89%BE%E5%87%BA%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88A%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E4%BA%8E%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88B%E7%9A%84%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%EF%BC%88%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88A%20%E4%B8%8E%20%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88B%20%E9%83%BD%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%98%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E%E7%9A%84%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E6%96%B0%E7%9A%84%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88%EF%BC%89%5Cns1%20%3D%20%7B10%2C%2020%2C%2030%2C%2040%2C%2050%7D%5Cns2%20%3D%20%7B30%2C%2040%2C%2050%2C%2060%2C%2070%7D%5Cnresult%20%3D%20s1.difference(s2)%5Cnprint(s1)%5Cnprint(s2)%5Cnprint(result)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22vVX0l%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="ua4c94b6f" id="ua4c94b6f"><span data-lake-id="u452e214a" id="u452e214a">2️⃣</span><span data-lake-id="u64c9c7d5" id="u64c9c7d5">使用</span><code data-lake-id="u085662d9" id="u085662d9"><span data-lake-id="u714c7af3" id="u714c7af3">集合A.difference_update(集合B)</span></code><span data-lake-id="u7c815dd5" id="u7c815dd5">，从集合A中，删除集合B中存在的元素。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88A.difference_update(%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88B)%EF%BC%9A%5Cn%23%20%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%9A%E4%BB%8E%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88A%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%A0%E9%99%A4%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88B%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%98%E5%9C%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%EF%BC%88%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88A%E4%BC%9A%E8%A2%AB%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%EF%BC%8C%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88B%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%9A%EF%BC%89%5Cns1%20%3D%20%7B10%2C%2020%2C%2030%2C%2040%2C%2050%7D%5Cns2%20%3D%20%7B30%2C%2040%2C%2050%2C%2060%2C%2070%7D%5Cns1.difference_update(s2)%5Cnprint(s1)%5Cnprint(s2)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22dwnYY%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u36dcb539" id="u36dcb539"><span data-lake-id="u0f117e23" id="u0f117e23">3️⃣</span><span data-lake-id="u66eeb79b" id="u66eeb79b">使用</span><code data-lake-id="u0c38ef33" id="u0c38ef33"><span data-lake-id="uf4f077fd" id="uf4f077fd">集合A.union(集合B)</span></code><span data-lake-id="u6fa3e058" id="u6fa3e058">，合并两个集合，集合A 和 集合B 都不变，返回的是一个新的集合。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88A.union(%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88B)%EF%BC%9A%5Cn%23%20%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%9A%E5%90%88%E5%B9%B6%E4%B8%A4%E4%B8%AA%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88%EF%BC%8C%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88A%20%E5%92%8C%20%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88B%20%E9%83%BD%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%98%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E%E7%9A%84%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E6%96%B0%E7%9A%84%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88%5Cns1%20%3D%20%7B10%2C%2020%2C%2030%2C%2040%2C%2050%7D%5Cns2%20%3D%20%7B30%2C%2040%2C%2050%2C%2060%2C%2070%7D%5Cnresult%20%3D%20s2.union(s1)%5Cnprint(s1)%5Cnprint(s2)%5Cnprint(result)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22qzX0c%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u19f1e1d1" id="u19f1e1d1"><span data-lake-id="ubcf0feb4" id="ubcf0feb4">4️⃣</span><span data-lake-id="udb4a5cd0" id="udb4a5cd0">使用</span><code data-lake-id="uec22630a" id="uec22630a"><span data-lake-id="u6a8b8f00" id="u6a8b8f00">集合A.issubset(集合B)</span></code><span data-lake-id="ue93b36f4" id="ue93b36f4">，判断集合A是否为集合B的子集，返回值为布尔值。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88A.issubset(%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88B)%EF%BC%9A%5Cn%23%20%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%9A%E5%88%A4%E6%96%AD%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88A%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E4%B8%BA%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88B%E7%9A%84%E5%AD%90%E9%9B%86%5Cn%23%20%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%20%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88A%E7%9A%84%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%E9%83%BD%E5%9C%A8%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88B%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E9%82%A3%E5%B0%B1%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9ETrue%EF%BC%8C%E5%90%A6%E5%88%99%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9EFalse%5Cns1%20%3D%20%7B10%2C%2020%2C%2030%2C%2040%2C%2050%7D%5Cns2%20%3D%20%7B30%2C%2040%2C%2050%2C%2060%2C%2070%7D%5Cns3%20%3D%20%7B30%2C%2040%2C%2050%7D%5Cnresult%20%3D%20s3.issubset(s1)%5Cnprint(result)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22T2aXe%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u1cedcde8" id="u1cedcde8"><span data-lake-id="uc0f99b2c" id="uc0f99b2c">5️⃣</span><span data-lake-id="uf67a2751" id="uf67a2751">使用</span><code data-lake-id="u84b777cd" id="u84b777cd"><span data-lake-id="u9ec02233" id="u9ec02233">集合A.issuperset(集合B)</span></code><span data-lake-id="u0e6a3ec7" id="u0e6a3ec7">，判断集合A是否是集合B的超集，返回值为布尔值。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88A.issuperset(%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88B)%EF%BC%9A%5Cn%23%20%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%9A%E5%88%A4%E6%96%AD%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88A%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E6%98%AF%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88B%E7%9A%84%E8%B6%85%E9%9B%86%5Cn%23%20%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88A%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%85%E5%90%AB%E4%BA%86%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88B%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%EF%BC%8C%E9%82%A3%E5%B0%B1%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9ETrue%EF%BC%8C%E5%90%A6%E5%88%99%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9EFalse%5Cns1%20%3D%20%7B10%2C%2020%2C%2030%2C%2040%2C%2050%7D%5Cns2%20%3D%20%7B30%2C%2040%2C%2050%2C%2060%2C%2070%7D%5Cns3%20%3D%20%7B30%2C%2040%2C%2050%7D%5Cnresult%20%3D%20s1.issuperset(s3)%5Cnprint(result)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22uSkjD%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="uddce296c" id="uddce296c"><span data-lake-id="u3dca2090" id="u3dca2090">6️⃣</span><span data-lake-id="u796641c1" id="u796641c1">使用</span><code data-lake-id="u8625b22e" id="u8625b22e"><span data-lake-id="u9a012ae5" id="u9a012ae5">集合A.isdisjoint(集合B)</span></code><span data-lake-id="ub65a1f92" id="ub65a1f92">，判断集合A和集合B是否没有交集，返回值为布尔值。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88A.isdisjoint(%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88B)%EF%BC%9A%5Cn%23%20%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%9A%5Cn%23%20%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%A4%E9%9B%86%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9ETrue%EF%BC%9B%E5%8F%AA%E8%A6%81%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%85%AC%E5%85%B1%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%B1%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9EFalse%5Cns1%20%3D%20%7B10%2C%2020%2C%2030%2C%2040%2C%2050%7D%5Cns2%20%3D%20%7B30%2C%2040%2C%2050%2C%2060%2C%2070%7D%5Cns3%20%3D%20%7B80%2C%2090%7D%5Cnresult%20%3D%20s1.isdisjoint(s2)%5Cnprint(result)%5Cn%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22FrnMP%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h3 data-lake-id="d6blP" id="d6blP" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u24ac7619" id="u24ac7619">集合的数学运算</span></h3><p data-lake-id="ue8337899" id="ue8337899"><span data-lake-id="u46891968" id="u46891968">集合的数学运算如下：</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22s1%20%3D%20%7B10%2C%2020%2C%2030%2C%2040%2C%2050%2C%2060%7D%5Cns2%20%3D%20%7B40%2C%2050%2C%2060%2C%2070%2C%2080%2C%2090%7D%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E5%B9%B6%E9%9B%86%5Cnresult%20%3D%20s1%20%7C%20s2%5Cnprint(result)%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E4%BA%A4%E9%9B%86%5Cnresult%20%3D%20s1%20%26%20s2%5Cnprint(result)%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E5%B7%AE%E9%9B%86%5Cnresult%20%3D%20s1%20-%20s2%5Cnprint(result)%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E5%AF%B9%E7%A7%B0%E5%B7%AE%E9%9B%86%5Cnresult%20%3D%20s1%20%5E%20s2%5Cnprint(result)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22FlvU5%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h3 data-lake-id="lzQY3" id="lzQY3" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u1bca6c5f" id="u1bca6c5f">集合的循环遍历</span></h3><p data-lake-id="u1b4ecbfa" id="u1b4ecbfa"><span data-lake-id="ue7b76b76" id="ue7b76b76">由于集合不支持下标，所以集合不能使用 while 循环遍历。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22s1%20%3D%20%7B10%2C%2020%2C%2030%2C%2040%2C%2050%2C%2060%7D%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8while%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E9%81%8D%E5%8E%86%EF%BC%88%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%E6%98%AF%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B%EF%BC%89%5Cn%23%20index%20%3D%200%5Cn%23%20while%20index%20%3C%20len(s1)%3A%5Cn%23%20%20%20%20%20print(s1%5Bindex%5D)%5Cn%23%20%20%20%20%20index%20%2B%3D%201%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8for%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E9%81%8D%E5%8E%86%5Cnfor%20item%20in%20s1%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(item)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22fqKT9%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h3 data-lake-id="gaiPa" id="gaiPa" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="ubdae826d" id="ubdae826d">集合特点总结</span></h3><ol list="uc4e39b73"><li fid="u93dcdae1" data-lake-id="u556f02f4" id="u556f02f4"><span data-lake-id="u19c8469a" id="u19c8469a">无序：集合中的元素没有固定顺序，无法通过下标访问。</span></li><li fid="u93dcdae1" data-lake-id="u99b8374a" id="u99b8374a"><span data-lake-id="u35df81d8" id="u35df81d8">不重复：集合会自动去重，同一个元素只会保留一份。</span></li><li fid="u93dcdae1" data-lake-id="ue282d652" id="ue282d652"><span data-lake-id="u774242b7" id="u774242b7">分为两种：可变集合合（set）和不可变集合（forzenset）。</span></li><li fid="u93dcdae1" data-lake-id="u988c609c" id="u988c609c"><span data-lake-id="u6caf108d" id="u6caf108d">集合中的元素必须是不可变类型（如：数字、字符串、元组）。</span></li><li fid="u93dcdae1" data-lake-id="uf19b389e" id="uf19b389e"><span data-lake-id="uce4e4dea" id="uce4e4dea">集合支持：并集、交集、差集、对称差集等数学操作。</span></li></ol><blockquote data-lake-id="uc8eadef1" id="uc8eadef1" class="lake-alert lake-alert-info"><p data-lake-id="u96d9a46c" id="u96d9a46c"><strong><span data-lake-id="u43badfb9" id="u43badfb9">📍</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="ud8e6a403" id="ud8e6a403">一句话总结：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u0ff83ccc" id="u0ff83ccc">集合是可以去重的数据容器，当只关心元素是否存在，而不在乎顺序的时，首选集合。</span></p></blockquote><h2 data-lake-id="Crbw2" id="Crbw2" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u7e9c9758" id="u7e9c9758">字典</span></h2><h3 data-lake-id="tqmYf" id="tqmYf" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="ub56a137b" id="ub56a137b">概述</span></h3><p data-lake-id="ua08cfbb8" id="ua08cfbb8"><strong><span data-lake-id="u088fbb4c" id="u088fbb4c">字典：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u2ec14521" id="u2ec14521">用来存放一组『键值对』数据，可通过『键(key)』对『值(value)』进行：增、删、改、查操作。</span></p><blockquote data-lake-id="u76d76f34" id="u76d76f34"><p data-lake-id="u4c3cf8d7" id="u4c3cf8d7"><span data-lake-id="ubf210d99" id="ubf210d99">字典就像一个带标签的收纳盒，你贴上标签（键），然后放进东西（值） 。</span></p></blockquote><h3 data-lake-id="br6SI" id="br6SI" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u66d50c91" id="u66d50c91">定义字典</span></h3><p data-lake-id="uba82eacf" id="uba82eacf"><span data-lake-id="u46dafe2b" id="u46dafe2b">用大括号</span><code data-lake-id="u846130ac" id="u846130ac"><span data-lake-id="udf505d8b" id="udf505d8b">{}</span></code><span data-lake-id="u5e021421" id="u5e021421">包裹，每个元素之间用逗号</span><code data-lake-id="u6d5abef3" id="u6d5abef3"><span data-lake-id="u92771086" id="u92771086">,</span></code><span data-lake-id="uef6cffb5" id="uef6cffb5">分隔，每个元素的格式为</span><code data-lake-id="u84f6b352" id="u84f6b352"><span data-lake-id="uc380baaa" id="uc380baaa">key:value</span></code></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E6%9C%89%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%E7%9A%84%E5%AD%97%E5%85%B8%5Cnd1%20%3D%20%7B'%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89'%3A%2072%2C%20'%E6%9D%8E%E5%9B%9B'%3A%2060%2C%20'%E7%8E%8B%E4%BA%94'%3A%2085%7D%5Cnprint(type(d1)%2C%20d1)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22YSXAB%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="uf3d24fe6" id="uf3d24fe6"><span data-lake-id="ude135eff" id="ude135eff">字典中的 key 不能重复，若出现重复，则后写的会覆盖之前写的。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%2