r(welcome)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E4%B9%9F%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22GFDxT%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card></details><details data-lake-id="ua56c3671" id="ua56c3671" open="true" class="lake-collapse"><summary data-lake-id="ubb1995f3" id="ubb1995f3" class="lake-summary"><span data-lake-id="ua60c7dc3" id="ua60c7dc3">6️⃣</span><span data-lake-id="ud6c9cbdf" id="ud6c9cbdf">函数也可以作为返回值</span></summary><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22def%20welcome()%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20print('%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD%E5%95%8A')%5Cn%20%20%20%20def%20show_msg(msg)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20print(msg)%5Cn%20%20%20%20return%20show_msg%5Cn%5Cn%23%20result%20%3D%20welcome()%5Cn%23%20result('%E5%B0%9A%E7%A1%85%E8%B0%B7')%5Cnwelcome()('%E5%B0%9A%E7%A1%85%E8%B0%B7')%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22VKUCm%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card></details><h2 data-lake-id="b8myz" id="b8myz" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u056ad8da" id="u056ad8da">函数的多返回值</span></h2><p data-lake-id="ubfa8643a" id="ubfa8643a"><span data-lake-id="uc055b8e0" id="uc055b8e0">在</span><code data-lake-id="u0152e85d" id="u0152e85d"><span data-lake-id="u140e87f4" id="u140e87f4">return</span></code><span data-lake-id="ud922fb6e" id="ud922fb6e">关键字后面写多个值，并且多个值之间用逗号隔开，Python 会自动把多个值打包成元组。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22def%20calculate(x%2C%20y)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20res1%20%3D%20x%20%2B%20y%5Cn%20%20%20%20res2%20%3D%20x%20-%20y%5Cn%20%20%20%20return%20res1%2C%20res2%20%23%20%E5%AE%9E%E9%99%85%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E%E7%9A%84%E6%98%AF%EF%BC%9A(res1%2C%20res2)%5Cn%5Cnresult%20%3D%20calculate(10%2C%2020)%5Cnr1%2C%20r2%20%3D%20calculate(10%2C%2020)%5Cn%5Cnprint(result)%20%20%23%20(30%2C%20-10)%5Cnprint(r1)%20%20%20%20%20%20%23%2030%5Cnprint(r2)%20%20%20%20%20%20%23%20-10%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22KG6b8%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h2 data-lake-id="HH13G" id="HH13G" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u2805a786" id="u2805a786">参数的打包与解包</span></h2><p data-lake-id="udc984aa3" id="udc984aa3"><span data-lake-id="u53b9eb66" id="u53b9eb66">定义函数时，打包接收参数：</span></p><ul list="ube6202ae"><li fid="u20a543bf" data-lake-id="ua4901bb5" id="ua4901bb5"><code data-lake-id="u526267be" id="u526267be"><span data-lake-id="u531c8c6e" id="u531c8c6e">*形参名</span></code><span data-lake-id="u91ed45d2" id="u91ed45d2">：打包所有的位置参数（会形成一个元组）。</span></li><li fid="u20a543bf" data-lake-id="u962ca1a8" id="u962ca1a8"><code data-lake-id="u6eb0998f" id="u6eb0998f"><span data-lake-id="u919afc96" id="u919afc96">**形参名</span></code><span data-lake-id="u06e68d5d" id="u06e68d5d"> ：打包所有的关键字参数（会形成一个字典）。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id="uba12158a" id="uba12158a"><span data-lake-id="ue9498838" id="ue9498838">调用函数时，解包传递参数：</span></p><ul list="u9292efbf"><li fid="u7f962768" data-lake-id="uf1ab43b1" id="uf1ab43b1"><code data-lake-id="uf1d831de" id="uf1d831de"><span data-lake-id="uc5064f62" id="uc5064f62">*变量名</span></code><span data-lake-id="ub571e069" id="ub571e069">：将元组拆解成一个一个独立的位置参数。</span></li><li fid="u7f962768" data-lake-id="u19cba7f7" id="u19cba7f7"><code data-lake-id="ubfa478f3" id="ubfa478f3"><span data-lake-id="u68f15c53" id="u68f15c53">**变量名</span></code><span data-lake-id="ue079d616" id="ue079d616">：将字典拆解一个一个</span><code data-lake-id="uc8d42b35" id="uc8d42b35"><span data-lake-id="uc5d91d78" id="uc5d91d78">key=value</span></code><span data-lake-id="ua2072b74" id="ua2072b74">形式的关键字参数。</span></li></ul><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E6%89%93%E5%8C%85%E6%8E%A5%E6%94%B6%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%9A%5Cn%23%20*args%20%20%20%20%EF%BC%9A%E6%89%93%E5%8C%85%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%88%E4%BC%9A%E5%BD%A2%E6%88%90%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%85%83%E7%BB%84%EF%BC%89%5Cn%23%20**kwargs%20%EF%BC%9A%E6%89%93%E5%8C%85%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E5%AD%97%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%88%E4%BC%9A%E5%BD%A2%E6%88%90%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%AD%97%E5%85%B8%EF%BC%89%5Cndef%20show_info(*args%2C%20**kwargs)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(args)%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(kwargs)%5Cn%5Cnnums%20%3D%20(10%2C%2020%2C%2030)%5Cnperson%20%3D%20%7B'name'%3A%20'%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89'%2C%20'age'%3A%2018%7D%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E8%A7%A3%E5%8C%85%E4%BC%A0%E9%80%92%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%9A%5Cn%23%20*nums%20%20%20%20%EF%BC%9A%E5%B0%86%E5%85%83%E7%BB%84%E6%8B%86%E8%A7%A3%E6%88%90%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%8B%AC%E7%AB%8B%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%5Cn%23%20**person%20%EF%BC%9A%E5%B0%86%E5%AD%97%E5%85%B8%E6%8B%86%E8%A7%A3%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%20key%3Dvalue%20%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E5%AD%97%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%5Cnshow_info(*nums%2C%20**person)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22PxBey%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h2 data-lake-id="cniqL" id="cniqL" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u1c84427a" id="u1c84427a">高阶函数</span></h2><p data-lake-id="u02ad9053" id="u02ad9053"><span data-lake-id="ud9756704" id="ud9756704"> 当一个函数的『参数是函数』或者『返回值是函数』那该函数就是『高阶函数』。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%E9%AB%98%E9%98%B6%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22def%20welcome()%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20print('%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD%E5%95%8A%EF%BC%81')%5Cn%20%20%20%20%5Cn%23%20caller%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%E6%98%AF%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%8C%E6%89%80%E4%BB%A5caller%E6%98%AF%E9%AB%98%E9%98%B6%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%5Cndef%20caller(f)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20print('call%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E8%B0%83%E7%94%A8')%5Cn%20%20%20%20f()%5Cn%20%20%20%20%5Cncaller(welcome)%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%23%20outer%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E7%9A%84%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E%E5%80%BC%E6%98%AF%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%8C%E6%89%80%E4%BB%A5outer%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E6%98%AF%E9%AB%98%E9%98%B6%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%5Cndef%20outer()%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20print('%E6%88%91%E6%98%AFouter')%5Cn%20%20%20%20def%20inner()%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20print('%E6%88%91%E6%98%AFinner')%5Cn%20%20%20%20return%20inner%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%E9%AB%98%E9%98%B6%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22bGJMc%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u1734bc34" id="u1734bc34"><span data-lake-id="u1d00e69b" id="u1d00e69b">高阶函数的意义：</span></p><blockquote data-lake-id="u52fa6caf" id="u52fa6caf" class="lake-alert lake-alert-info"><ol list="ufd23233e"><li fid="u56ba0344" data-lake-id="u8ab09990" id="u8ab09990"><span data-lake-id="ua2a4f21e" id="ua2a4f21e">代码复用性高：可以把行为“独立出去”，传入不同函数实现不同逻辑。</span></li><li fid="u56ba0344" data-lake-id="u9f7163ec" id="u9f7163ec"><span data-lake-id="uddb3aba5" id="uddb3aba5">能让函数更灵活，更通用。</span></li><li fid="u56ba0344" data-lake-id="u2da205b6" id="u2da205b6"><span data-lake-id="u1b52982d" id="u1b52982d">高阶函数是：装饰器、闭包的基础。（后面会讲）</span></li></ol></blockquote><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%E9%AB%98%E9%98%B6%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E5%B0%8F%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22def%20info(msg)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20return%20'%5B%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BA%5D'%20%2B%20msg%5Cndef%20warn(msg)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20return%20'%5B%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%5D'%20%2B%20msg%5Cndef%20error(msg)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20return%20'%5B%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF%5D'%20%2B%20msg%5Cn%5Cndef%20log(fun%2C%20text)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(fun(text))%5Cn%5Cnlog(info%2C%20'%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E4%BF%9D%E5%AD%98%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%EF%BC%81')%5Cnlog(warn%2C%20'%E7%A3%81%E7%9B%98%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E4%B8%8D%E8%B6%B3%EF%BC%81')%5Cnlog(error%2C%20'%E8%AF%A5%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E4%B8%8D%E5%AD%98%E5%9C%A8%EF%BC%81')%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%E9%AB%98%E9%98%B6%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E5%B0%8F%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22lyVa9%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h2 data-lake-id="aRtnR" id="aRtnR" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="uc33f6bd8" id="uc33f6bd8">条件表达式</span></h2><details data-lake-id="u4798dac7" id="u4798dac7" open="true" class="lake-collapse"><summary data-lake-id="ud7372829" id="ud7372829" class="lake-summary"><strong><span data-lake-id="u3458cd55" id="u3458cd55">表达式：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u29298845" id="u29298845">执行后最终能得到一个值的代码，就是表达式，例如这些都是表达式：</span></summary><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%E8%A1%A8%E8%BE%BE%E5%BC%8F%E4%B8%BE%E4%BE%8B%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%223%20%2B%205%5Cn'abc'%20*%203%5Cn5%20%3E%203%5Cn'y'%20in%20'Python'%5Cnlen('hello')%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%E8%A1%A8%E8%BE%BE%E5%BC%8F%E4%B8%BE%E4%BE%8B%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22__widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22p7T30%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%2C%22widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%7D"></card><blockquote data-lake-id="uf099f062" id="uf099f062"><p data-lake-id="uddcc3e7a" id="uddcc3e7a"><span data-lake-id="u90214d7c" id="u90214d7c">表达式最终会形成一个值，可以写在任何一个需要值的地方。</span></p></blockquote></details><details data-lake-id="u33d537e2" id="u33d537e2" open="true" class="lake-collapse"><summary data-lake-id="u2a83c18a" id="u2a83c18a" class="lake-summary"><strong><span data-lake-id="u0121662c" id="u0121662c">条件表达式： </span></strong><span data-lake-id="u1a89de72" id="u1a89de72">根据不同的条件，得到不同的值，又称：三元表达式，也叫：三目运算符。</span></summary><p data-lake-id="u7d52ba11" id="u7d52ba11"><span data-lake-id="u563ba677" id="u563ba677">1️⃣</span><span data-lake-id="uaf6ec207" id="uaf6ec207">语法格式为：</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C1%20if%20%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%20else%20%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C2%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ySRu1%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><blockquote data-lake-id="u2acff97a" id="u2acff97a"><p data-lake-id="uc8c3e8a1" id="uc8c3e8a1"><span data-lake-id="u5d55425c" id="u5d55425c">具体规则： 如果条件为真，整个表达式的结果就是“结果1”，否则就是“结果2”。  </span></p></blockquote><p data-lake-id="ubb36194e" id="ubb36194e"><span data-lake-id="u7c2d5d3b" id="u7c2d5d3b">2️⃣</span><span data-lake-id="u23e7ece6" id="u23e7ece6">代码示例：</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22age%20%3D%2020%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E4%BC%A0%E7%BB%9Fif-else%E5%86%99%E6%B3%95%5Cnif%20age%20%3E%3D%2018%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20text%20%3D%20'%E6%88%90%E5%B9%B4'%5Cnelse%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20text%20%3D%20'%E6%9C%AA%E6%88%90%E5%B9%B4'%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E8%A1%A8%E8%BE%BE%E5%BC%8F%E5%86%99%E6%B3%95%5Cntext%20%3D%20'%E6%88%90%E5%B9%B4'%20if%20age%20%3E%3D%2018%20else%20'%E6%9C%AA%E6%88%90%E5%B9%B4%C2%B7'%5Cnprint(text)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22dCoeP%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u79b9294d" id="u79b9294d"><span data-lake-id="ucaaf32d6" id="ucaaf32d6">3️⃣</span><span data-lake-id="u2f434bb8" id="u2f434bb8"> 什么时候适合用条件表达式？ ——  简单的二选一场景，可以让代码更紧凑。  </span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22rain%20%3D%20True%5Cnfood%20%3D%20'%E5%A4%96%E5%8D%96'%20if%20rain%20else%20'%E5%87%BA%E5%8E%BB%E5%90%83'%5Cn%5Cnis_vip%20%3D%20True%5Cndisscount%20%3D%200.8%20if%20is_vip%20else%201.0%5Cn%5Cnis_login%20%3D%20True%5Cnmsg%20%3D%20'%E6%AC%A2%E8%BF%8E%E5%9B%9E%E6%9D%A5%EF%BC%81'%20if%20is_login%20else%20'%E8%AF%B7%E5%85%88%E7%99%BB%E5%BD%95%EF%BC%81'%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22mdPq0%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card></details><h2 data-lake-id="phgbg" id="phgbg" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="ud5e45901" id="ud5e45901">匿名函数</span></h2><ul list="u1e7411bd"><li fid="u08813a0a" data-lake-id="uf9dbd2ea" id="uf9dbd2ea"><strong><span data-lake-id="u7fbf2612" id="u7fbf2612">概念：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u989baa39" id="u989baa39">所谓『匿名函数』，就是没有名字的函数，它无需使用</span><code data-lake-id="ucc6083e9" id="ucc6083e9"><span data-lake-id="u3668de00" id="u3668de00">def</span></code><span data-lake-id="u768c81bf" id="u768c81bf">关键字去定义。</span></li><li fid="u08813a0a" data-lake-id="uf717411c" id="uf717411c"><strong><span data-lake-id="ubff352ef" id="ubff352ef">语法：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="ufb01a4b5" id="ufb01a4b5">Python 中使用</span><code data-lake-id="u8d20e081" id="u8d20e081"><span data-lake-id="u87b865a9" id="u87b865a9">lambda</span></code><span data-lake-id="u40ef909c" id="u40ef909c">关键字来定义『匿名函数』，格式为：</span><code data-lake-id="uaeac374c" id="uaeac374c"><strong><span data-lake-id="u89d24dd2" id="u89d24dd2">lambda 参数: 表达式</span></strong></code></li><li fid="u08813a0a" data-lake-id="uc71d96ab" id="uc71d96ab"><strong><span data-lake-id="u010eaa06" id="u010eaa06">使用场景：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u58a47d72" id="u58a47d72"> 当一个函数只用一次、只做一点点小事，使用匿名函数会更简洁。  </span></li></ul><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%E6%99%AE%E9%80%9A%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%99%AE%E9%80%9A%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C%5Cndef%20add(x%2C%20y)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20return%20x%20%2B%20y%5Cn%5Cndef%20sub(x%2C%20y)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20return%20x%20-%20y%5Cn%5Cndef%20calculate(func%2C%20a%2C%20b)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(f'%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C%E4%B8%BA%EF%BC%9A%7Bfunc(a%2C%20b)%7D')%5Cn%5Cncalculate(add%2C%2030%2C%2010)%5Cncalculate(sub%2C%2030%2C%2010)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%E6%99%AE%E9%80%9A%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22__widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22PWLkz%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%2C%22widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%7D" hindent="2em"></card><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%E5%8C%BF%E5%90%8D%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%8C%BF%E5%90%8D%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C%5Cndef%20calculate(func%2C%20a%2C%20b)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(f'%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C%E4%B8%BA%EF%BC%9A%7Bfunc(a%2C%20b)%7D')%5Cn%5Cncalculate(lambda%20x%2C%20y%3A%20x%20%2B%20y%2C%2030%2C%2010)%5Cncalculate(lambda%20x%2C%20y%3A%20x%20-%20y%2C%2030%2C%2010)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%E5%8C%BF%E5%90%8D%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22__widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22aCY8P%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%2C%22widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%7D" hindent="2em"></card><ul list="u912d1c1a"><li fid="u47d86cdb" data-lake-id="u348cffe7" id="u348cffe7"><strong><span data-lake-id="u3f919879" id="u3f919879">特点：</span></strong></li></ul><blockquote data-lake-id="u0535692f" id="u0535692f" hindent="2em" class="lake-alert lake-alert-info"><ol list="ua87a8486"><li fid="u2b17b86f" data-lake-id="ub027b957" id="ub027b957"><span data-lake-id="u78e191c5" id="u78e191c5">只能写一行，不能写多行代码。</span></li><li fid="u2b17b86f" data-lake-id="u66fbc9c7" id="u66fbc9c7"><span data-lake-id="ued84cb11" id="ued84cb11">不能写代码块（if、for、while）</span></li><li fid="u2b17b86f" data-lake-id="u73c0e996" id="u73c0e996"><span data-lake-id="ub4ddeb57" id="ub4ddeb57">冒号右边必须是表达式，且只能写一个表达式。</span></li><li fid="u2b17b86f" data-lake-id="u6ba277b0" id="u6ba277b0"><span data-lake-id="u857ba7a7" id="u857ba7a7">执行结果自动作为返回值。</span></li></ol></blockquote><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%E5%8C%BF%E5%90%8D%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%20%2B%20%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E8%A1%A8%E8%BE%BE%E5%BC%8F%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22is_adult%20%3D%20lambda%20age%3A%20'%E6%88%90%E5%B9%B4'%20if%20age%20%3E%3D%2018%20else%20'%E6%9C%AA%E6%88%90%E5%B9%B4'%5Cnprint(is_adult(18))%5Cnprint(is_adult(13))%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%E5%8C%BF%E5%90%8D%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%20%2B%20%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E8%A1%A8%E8%BE%BE%E5%BC%8F%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22__widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22rimF7%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%2C%22widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%7D" hindent="2em"></card><h2 data-lake-id="MEq6j" id="MEq6j" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u22db5155" id="u22db5155">几个数据处理函数</span></h2><h3 data-lake-id="NDq0Y" id="NDq0Y" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u103667eb" id="u103667eb">map 函数</span></h3><ul list="u6b22ef64"><li fid="u9d2f9c9b" data-lake-id="uda2b3903" id="uda2b3903"><code data-lake-id="u98fe07d0" id="u98fe07d0"><span data-lake-id="u8d4e5a1e" id="u8d4e5a1e">map</span></code><span data-lake-id="uef6da2d0" id="uef6da2d0">函数：对一组数据中的每一个元素，统一执行某种操作（加工），并生成一组新数据。</span></li><li fid="u9d2f9c9b" data-lake-id="ud60b08e9" id="ud60b08e9"><span data-lake-id="ufb610b68" id="ufb610b68">语法格式：</span><code data-lake-id="u416c036f" id="u416c036f"><span data-lake-id="u1d5eb7cc" id="u1d5eb7cc">map(操作函数, 可迭代对象)</span></code></li></ul><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22s