"><span data-lake-id="u8b210818" id="u8b210818">概念：用一条简洁语句，从可迭代对象中，生成新列表的语法结构。</span></li><li fid="u8da99768" data-lake-id="u4bcc71c0" id="u4bcc71c0"><span data-lake-id="u73b4b21d" id="u73b4b21d">语法格式：</span><code data-lake-id="u85946e9f" id="u85946e9f"><span data-lake-id="udd44d226" id="udd44d226">[ 表达式 for 变量 in 可迭代对象 ]</span></code></li></ul><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82%EF%BC%9A%E8%AE%A9nums%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8%E4%B8%AD%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E7%9A%84%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%EF%BC%8C%E9%83%BD%E5%8F%98%E4%B8%BA%E5%8E%9F%E6%9D%A5%E7%9A%842%E5%80%8D%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%9A%E7%94%A8map%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%5Cnnums%20%3D%20%5B10%2C%2020%2C%2030%2C%2040%5D%5Cnresult%20%3D%20list(map(lambda%20n%3A%20n%20*%202%2C%20nums))%5Cnprint(result)%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%9A%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8for%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E7%BB%93%E5%90%88append%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%5Cnnums%20%3D%20%5B10%2C%2020%2C%2030%2C%2040%5D%5Cnresult%20%3D%20%5B%5D%5Cnfor%20n%20in%20nums%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20result.append(n%20*%202)%5Cnprint(result)%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E4%B8%89%EF%BC%9A%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8%E6%8E%A8%E5%AF%BC%E5%BC%8F(%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8%E6%8E%A8%E5%AF%BC%E5%BC%8F%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%8A%E9%9D%A2%20for%20%2B%20append%20%E7%9A%84%E7%AE%80%E5%86%99%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F)%5Cnnums%20%3D%20%5B10%2C%2020%2C%2030%2C%2040%5D%5Cnresult%20%3D%20%5Bn%20*%202%20for%20n%20in%20nums%5D%5Cnprint(result)%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E5%B8%A6%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%E7%9A%84%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8%E6%8E%A8%E5%AF%BC%E5%BC%8F%5Cnnums%20%3D%20%5B10%2C%2020%2C%2030%2C%2040%5D%5Cnresult%20%3D%20%5Bn%20*%202%20for%20n%20in%20nums%20if%20n%20%3E%2020%5D%5Cnprint(result)%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E5%AD%97%E5%85%B8%E6%8E%A8%E5%AF%BC%E5%BC%8F%5Cnnames%20%3D%20%5B'%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89'%2C%20'%E6%9D%8E%E5%9B%9B'%2C%20'%E7%8E%8B%E4%BA%94'%5D%5Cnscores%20%3D%20%5B60%2C%2070%2C%2080%5D%5Cnresult%20%3D%20%7Bnames%5Bi%5D%3A%20scores%5Bi%5D%20for%20i%20in%20range(len(names))%7D%5Cnprint(result)%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88%E6%8E%A8%E5%AF%BC%E5%BC%8F%5Cnnames%20%3D%20%5B'%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89'%2C%20'%E6%9D%8E%E5%9B%9B'%2C%20'%E7%8E%8B%E4%BA%94'%5D%5Cnresult%20%3D%20%7Bn%20%2B%20'%EF%BC%81'%20for%20n%20in%20names%7D%5Cnprint(result)%5Cn%5Cnnames%20%3D%20%5B'%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89'%2C%20'%E6%9D%8E%E5%9B%9B'%2C%20'%E7%8E%8B%E4%BA%94'%5D%5Cn%23%20%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%EF%BC%9APython%E4%B8%AD%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E5%85%83%E7%BB%84%E6%8E%A8%E5%AF%BC%E5%BC%8F%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8B%E9%9D%A2%E8%BF%99%E7%A7%8D%E5%86%99%E6%B3%95%E5%8F%AB%EF%BC%9A%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E5%99%A8%EF%BC%88%E5%90%8E%E9%9D%A2%E4%BC%9A%E4%BB%94%E7%BB%86%E8%AE%B2%EF%BC%89%5Cnresult%20%3D%20(n%20%2B%20'%EF%BC%81'%20for%20n%20in%20names)%5Cnprint(result)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22__widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22r7GMK%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%2C%22widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%7D" hindent="2em"></card><h2 data-lake-id="EQGCn" id="EQGCn" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u255987c5" id="u255987c5">常用内置函数梳理</span></h2><p data-lake-id="u745e0930" id="u745e0930"><span data-lake-id="u1a917e3a" id="u1a917e3a">以下函数是截至目前，我们需要掌握的一些常用函数，注意：下面这些并不是所有，我们后面还会学习到更多的常用内置函数。（详细讲解请参考视频教程）</span></p><h3 data-lake-id="UxVJY" id="UxVJY" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="uf6282713" id="uf6282713">输入与输出</span></h3><table data-lake-id="l6cEm" id="l6cEm" margin="true" row-head="rgba(8,84,166,1);#FFFFFF" class="lake-table" style="width: 378px"><colgroup><col width="154"><col width="224"></colgroup><tbody><tr data-lake-id="uc52dd69e" id="uc52dd69e"><td data-lake-id="u86a5b7b3" id="u86a5b7b3"><p data-lake-id="u5d03cbba" id="u5d03cbba" style="text-align: center"><span data-lake-id="ua0740070" id="ua0740070">函数 / 参数</span></p></td><td data-lake-id="uddeb6ae3" id="uddeb6ae3"><p data-lake-id="u8fd2b47a" id="u8fd2b47a" style="text-align: center"><span data-lake-id="udb740ff1" id="udb740ff1">功能说明</span></p></td></tr><tr data-lake-id="uf0c55e63" id="uf0c55e63"><td data-lake-id="u8469ca1a" id="u8469ca1a"><p data-lake-id="u57bad117" id="u57bad117"><code data-lake-id="u8993aea6" id="u8993aea6"><span data-lake-id="u2edded24" id="u2edded24">print</span></code></p></td><td data-lake-id="ud1111272" id="ud1111272"><p data-lake-id="u9a053cf7" id="u9a053cf7"><span data-lake-id="uea3c9b64" id="uea3c9b64">输出指定内容</span></p></td></tr><tr data-lake-id="u9616314a" id="u9616314a"><td data-lake-id="u8dd54ea9" id="u8dd54ea9"><p data-lake-id="u033551fa" id="u033551fa"><code data-lake-id="u5353647d" id="u5353647d"><span data-lake-id="ufd72144f" id="ufd72144f">objects</span></code></p></td><td data-lake-id="u43033e13" id="u43033e13"><p data-lake-id="u1c85b45a" id="u1c85b45a"><span data-lake-id="u4c1e0e7d" id="u4c1e0e7d">要输出的内容</span></p></td></tr><tr data-lake-id="u5112fa91" id="u5112fa91"><td data-lake-id="u3866f925" id="u3866f925"><p data-lake-id="u1421ca00" id="u1421ca00"><code data-lake-id="u49fb8616" id="u49fb8616"><span data-lake-id="u736c1bbc" id="u736c1bbc">sep</span></code></p></td><td data-lake-id="u7a519b31" id="u7a519b31"><p data-lake-id="ufd07e1a9" id="ufd07e1a9"><span data-lake-id="u8a3926ff" id="u8a3926ff">输出多个内容时的分隔符</span></p></td></tr><tr data-lake-id="u0fee7dcb" id="u0fee7dcb"><td data-lake-id="uf4c99109" id="uf4c99109"><p data-lake-id="u69dd977e" id="u69dd977e"><code data-lake-id="u8526c1c0" id="u8526c1c0"><span data-lake-id="u8059c748" id="u8059c748">end</span></code></p></td><td data-lake-id="u1498c2bd" id="u1498c2bd"><p data-lake-id="u898f1337" id="u898f1337"><span data-lake-id="uc37a9a39" id="uc37a9a39">结尾追加的内容</span></p></td></tr><tr data-lake-id="ue9de06dc" id="ue9de06dc"><td data-lake-id="u5e867265" id="u5e867265"><p data-lake-id="u2be3007e" id="u2be3007e"><code data-lake-id="u46406e0d" id="u46406e0d"><span data-lake-id="u2ca576a4" id="u2ca576a4">file</span></code></p></td><td data-lake-id="uac5d816b" id="uac5d816b"><p data-lake-id="u41da4cb7" id="u41da4cb7"><span data-lake-id="uf2ff2e0e" id="uf2ff2e0e">输出位置（默认控制台）</span></p></td></tr><tr data-lake-id="u6a43c28b" id="u6a43c28b"><td data-lake-id="u44cc02f3" id="u44cc02f3"><p data-lake-id="u39d3315c" id="u39d3315c"><code data-lake-id="u8dd773e5" id="u8dd773e5"><span data-lake-id="ud860f196" id="ud860f196">flush</span></code></p></td><td data-lake-id="uceba3606" id="uceba3606"><p data-lake-id="u8b588b70" id="u8b588b70"><span data-lake-id="ubd59865c" id="ubd59865c">是否立即刷新输出</span></p></td></tr><tr data-lake-id="ufa0939b3" id="ufa0939b3"><td data-lake-id="u62e3e277" id="u62e3e277"><p data-lake-id="u54288395" id="u54288395"><code data-lake-id="u9def3c8a" id="u9def3c8a"><span data-lake-id="u4cde9fc0" id="u4cde9fc0">input()</span></code></p></td><td data-lake-id="uf799f6a6" id="uf799f6a6"><p data-lake-id="u22f465e1" id="u22f465e1"><span data-lake-id="uaf25ca97" id="uaf25ca97">获取用户输入</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><h3 data-lake-id="Qi9mM" id="Qi9mM" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u20045637" id="u20045637">类型转换</span></h3><table data-lake-id="TLtM9" id="TLtM9" margin="true" row-head="rgba(8,84,166,1);#FFFFFF" class="lake-table" style="width: 382px"><colgroup><col width="155"><col width="227"></colgroup><tbody><tr data-lake-id="u35cf766d" id="u35cf766d"><td data-lake-id="uffcf2c43" id="uffcf2c43"><p data-lake-id="uae05410c" id="uae05410c" style="text-align: center"><span data-lake-id="uce36f987" id="uce36f987">函数</span></p></td><td data-lake-id="ue5581710" id="ue5581710"><p data-lake-id="u096ce6bb" id="u096ce6bb" style="text-align: center"><span data-lake-id="u83774deb" id="u83774deb">功能说明</span></p></td></tr><tr data-lake-id="ua55ba064" id="ua55ba064"><td data-lake-id="ucf362532" id="ucf362532"><p data-lake-id="uefc20fea" id="uefc20fea"><code data-lake-id="ua53d0b72" id="ua53d0b72"><span data-lake-id="u720fac6e" id="u720fac6e">int()</span></code></p></td><td data-lake-id="ucea17731" id="ucea17731"><p data-lake-id="u0e6111ce" id="u0e6111ce"><span data-lake-id="u6942edc2" id="u6942edc2">转为整数</span></p></td></tr><tr data-lake-id="ub50bb4ab" id="ub50bb4ab"><td data-lake-id="u9e4e048f" id="u9e4e048f"><p data-lake-id="u7744cc3e" id="u7744cc3e"><code data-lake-id="u0fbafa63" id="u0fbafa63"><span data-lake-id="ub003fe31" id="ub003fe31">float()</span></code></p></td><td data-lake-id="u8f08c34d" id="u8f08c34d"><p data-lake-id="u0e2509ff" id="u0e2509ff"><span data-lake-id="ud4d0b507" id="ud4d0b507">转为浮点数</span></p></td></tr><tr data-lake-id="ue7bc3291" id="ue7bc3291"><td data-lake-id="ubfdc19ec" id="ubfdc19ec"><p data-lake-id="uf1c7ff8c" id="uf1c7ff8c"><code data-lake-id="u75d6d87d" id="u75d6d87d"><span data-lake-id="u870bd636" id="u870bd636">str()</span></code></p></td><td data-lake-id="ud3868603" id="ud3868603"><p data-lake-id="u586dfefd" id="u586dfefd"><span data-lake-id="u422ec57d" id="u422ec57d">转为字符串</span></p></td></tr><tr data-lake-id="ua5dd51ca" id="ua5dd51ca"><td data-lake-id="u24887c59" id="u24887c59"><p data-lake-id="u26fce8f4" id="u26fce8f4"><code data-lake-id="uce30316d" id="uce30316d"><span data-lake-id="u3156bd4a" id="u3156bd4a">bool()</span></code></p></td><td data-lake-id="udea53b8d" id="udea53b8d"><p data-lake-id="u5a1b4f2d" id="u5a1b4f2d"><span data-lake-id="u41969e8b" id="u41969e8b">转为布尔值</span></p></td></tr><tr data-lake-id="ua128aea4" id="ua128aea4"><td data-lake-id="u711d76e6" id="u711d76e6"><p data-lake-id="u45ae9066" id="u45ae9066"><code data-lake-id="u09c2c007" id="u09c2c007"><span data-lake-id="u6dd008b6" id="u6dd008b6">list()</span></code></p></td><td data-lake-id="u6d5179fd" id="u6d5179fd"><p data-lake-id="u00f507d3" id="u00f507d3"><span data-lake-id="ub1ed3cb6" id="ub1ed3cb6">转为列表</span></p></td></tr><tr data-lake-id="udfdab836" id="udfdab836"><td data-lake-id="ue6a5fff4" id="ue6a5fff4"><p data-lake-id="u1b3afc5f" id="u1b3afc5f"><code data-lake-id="ue0f1c29a" id="ue0f1c29a"><span data-lake-id="ufb14985e" id="ufb14985e">tuple()</span></code></p></td><td data-lake-id="ub8b237d6" id="ub8b237d6"><p data-lake-id="u727a77b0" id="u727a77b0"><span data-lake-id="uce95c2b3" id="uce95c2b3">转为元组</span></p></td></tr><tr data-lake-id="u8e382d04" id="u8e382d04"><td data-lake-id="u0cd0113a" id="u0cd0113a"><p data-lake-id="u325ac302" id="u325ac302"><code data-lake-id="u6d4a56af" id="u6d4a56af"><span data-lake-id="u7c6a2f2e" id="u7c6a2f2e">set()</span></code></p></td><td data-lake-id="u663f0caf" id="u663f0caf"><p data-lake-id="u089882fa" id="u089882fa"><span data-lake-id="ue79b6ba6" id="ue79b6ba6">转为集合</span></p></td></tr><tr data-lake-id="uc599ec3a" id="uc599ec3a"><td data-lake-id="u9f44224a" id="u9f44224a"><p data-lake-id="u1acda4ed" id="u1acda4ed"><code data-lake-id="u900428d1" id="u900428d1"><span data-lake-id="u3d6de8c8" id="u3d6de8c8">dict()</span></code></p></td><td data-lake-id="u9e076a49" id="u9e076a49"><p data-lake-id="u6e5d0c00" id="u6e5d0c00"><span data-lake-id="u33bf830a" id="u33bf830a">转为字典</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><h3 data-lake-id="JyNzl" id="JyNzl" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u04d33e17" id="u04d33e17">数学相关</span></h3><table data-lake-id="Oaaul" id="Oaaul" margin="true" row-head="rgba(8,84,166,1);#FFFFFF" class="lake-table" style="width: 655px"><colgroup><col width="160"><col width="495"></colgroup><tbody><tr data-lake-id="ud423b295" id="ud423b295"><td data-lake-id="u9098a54f" id="u9098a54f"><p data-lake-id="udbd1c506" id="udbd1c506"><span data-lake-id="ue7df2d6f" id="ue7df2d6f">函数</span></p></td><td data-lake-id="ue58d2d9a" id="ue58d2d9a"><p data-lake-id="ud7701a04" id="ud7701a04"><span data-lake-id="u0830dc89" id="u0830dc89">功能说明</span></p></td></tr><tr data-lake-id="ufcc1a138" id="ufcc1a138"><td data-lake-id="uf28d4d3f" id="uf28d4d3f"><p data-lake-id="ucfff9d8a" id="ucfff9d8a"><code data-lake-id="u4e70c8e2" id="u4e70c8e2"><span data-lake-id="ucc48fef2" id="ucc48fef2">abs()</span></code></p></td><td data-lake-id="u4f73051e" id="u4f73051e"><p data-lake-id="u3da1b6ff" id="u3da1b6ff"><span data-lake-id="u64126c15" id="u64126c15">取绝对值</span></p></td></tr><tr data-lake-id="u29cfaed1" id="u29cfaed1"><td data-lake-id="u3aca170f" id="u3aca170f"><p data-lake-id="u0f7de23a" id="u0f7de23a"><code data-lake-id="ud3cf77b1" id="ud3cf77b1"><span data-lake-id="ue98fefd4" id="ue98fefd4">round()</span></code></p></td><td data-lake-id="udd094b90" id="udd094b90"><p data-lake-id="ua04dee67" id="ua04dee67"><span data-lake-id="ufa9bac9f" id="ufa9bac9f">银行家舍入法：小于5舍，大于5入，等于5看奇偶（奇入偶舍）</span></p></td></tr><tr data-lake-id="u9236dbe9" id="u9236dbe9"><td data-lake-id="u1ec29569" id="u1ec29569"><p data-lake-id="uf0927a8f" id="uf0927a8f"><code data-lake-id="ud764e2a6" id="ud764e2a6"><span data-lake-id="u7ada579b" id="u7ada579b">pow(a, b)</span></code></p></td><td data-lake-id="ufa08ef1c" id="ufa08ef1c"><p data-lake-id="udf13d66f" id="udf13d66f"><span data-lake-id="u70e7faff" id="u70e7faff">计算 a 的 b 次方</span></p></td></tr><tr data-lake-id="ueed5414c" id="ueed5414c"><td data-lake-id="ub9d3039e" id="ub9d3039e"><p data-lake-id="u87136daf" id="u87136daf"><code data-lake-id="u1f9af607" id="u1f9af607"><span data-lake-id="ue2104b64" id="ue2104b64">pow(a, b, c)</span></code></p></td><td data-lake-id="u0a0e03a5" id="u0a0e03a5"><p data-lake-id="ua1a437d0" id="ua1a437d0"><span data-lake-id="u75446406" id="u75446406">计算 a 的 b 次方后，再对 c 取模</span></p></td></tr><tr data-lake-id="uc507ad96" id="uc507ad96"><td data-lake-id="u8cdfab5d" id="u8cdfab5d"><p data-lake-id="u4722643a" id="u4722643a"><code data-lake-id="ud5183825" id="ud5183825"><span data-lake-id="u730d3125" id="u730d3125">divmod(a, b)</span></code></p></td><td data-lake-id="u40ce1a8b" id="u40ce1a8b"><p data-lake-id="u11ee7af3" id="u11ee7af3"><span data-lake-id="ud8bcbcf4" id="ud8bcbcf4">返回 </span><code data-lake-id="uad63031d" id="uad63031d"><span data-lake-id="u1d8b457b" id="u1d8b457b">(商, 余数)</span></code></p></td></tr><tr data-lake-id="udd3f6170" id="udd3f6170"><td data-lake-id="ub144d179" id="ub144d179"><p data-lake-id="u3af2bfda" id="u3af2bfda"><code data-lake-id="u6e2fbc5b" id="u6e2fbc5b"><span data-lake-id="u3b242fb6" id="u3b242fb6">max()</span></code></p></td><td data-lake-id="u04922b07" id="u04922b07"><p data-lake-id="u9c558c64" id="u9c558c64"><span data-lake-id="u6b69f623" id="u6b69f623">最大值（支持 </span><code data-lake-id="uddbfefb9" id="uddbfefb9"><span data-lake-id="ub95d47ac" id="ub95d47ac">key</span></code><span data-lake-id="uf2f1827b" id="uf2f1827b">）</span></p></td></tr><tr data-lake-id="u66e6abf9" id="u66e6abf9"><td data-lake-id="u2c808831" id="u2c808831"><p data-lake-id="uf7b5d597" id="uf7b5d597"><code data-lake-id="u0e4f46c9" id="u0e4f46c9"><span data-lake-id="uecae7188" id="uecae7188">min()</span></code></p></td><td data-lake-id="u481f9555" id="u481f9555"><p data-lake-id="u4fdf2632" id="u4fdf2632"><span data-lake-id="u7e1448e4" id="u7e1448e4">最小值（支持 </span><code data-lake-id="ue02fbe09" id="ue02fbe09"><span data-lake-id="u101e0415" id="u101e0415">key</span></code><span data-lake-id="uef48415e" id="uef48415e">）</span></p></td></tr><tr data-lake-id="u55e6e4ae" id="u55e6e4ae"><td data-lake-id="u856d66a4" id="u856d66a4"><p data-lake-id="u6c2f4e33" id="u6c2f4e33"><code data-lake-id="u8f9480f0" id="u8f9480f0"><span data-lake-id="u54cbc6b6" id="u54cbc6b6">sum()</span></code></p></td><td data-lake-id="u511ede55" id="u511ede55"><p data-lake-id="u3b80862f" id="u3b80862f"><span data-lake-id="u75ac7a1c" id="u75ac7a1c">求和</span></p></td></tr><tr data-lake-id="uad90dc24" id="uad90dc24"><td data-lake-id="ua97d99be" id="ua97d99be"><p data-lake-id="u3080c9a8" id="u3080c9a8"><code data-lake-id="u22d6a99c" id="u22d6a99c"><span data-lake-id="u7ffdb965" id="u7ffdb965">map()</s