span data-lake-id="uf4ac99d6" id="uf4ac99d6">深拷贝只复制可变对象，不可变对象会直接引用。</span></li><li fid="u163503c2" data-lake-id="u0cb68972" id="u0cb68972"><span data-lake-id="ufb0e7419" id="ufb0e7419">元组中如果只包含不可变对象，则深拷贝没有效果。</span></li></ol></blockquote><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22import%20copy%5Cna%20%3D%20666%5Cn%23%20a%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E5%8F%98%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%B3%E4%BE%BF%E8%B0%83%E7%94%A8deepcopy%E4%B9%9F%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%9A%E6%B7%B1%E6%8B%B7%E8%B4%9D%EF%BC%8C%E4%BC%9A%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E5%BC%95%E7%94%A8%5Cnb%20%3D%20copy.deepcopy(a)%5Cn%5Cnprint(id(a))%5Cnprint(id(b))%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22gWNwz%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22import%20copy%5Cnnums1%20%3D%20(10%2C%2020%2C%2030%2C%20%5B40%2C%2050%5D)%5Cn%23%20nums1%E5%85%83%E7%BB%84%E4%B8%AD%E5%8F%AA%E5%8C%85%E5%90%AB%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E5%8F%98%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%B3%E4%BE%BF%E8%B0%83%E7%94%A8deepcopy%E4%B9%9F%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%9A%E6%B7%B1%E6%8B%B7%E8%B4%9D%5Cnnums2%20%3D%20copy.deepcopy(nums1)%5Cn%5Cnprint(id(nums1))%5Cnprint(id(nums2))%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22T5YN5%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h2 data-lake-id="VDwIt" id="VDwIt" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u01c106a7" id="u01c106a7">四种作用域</span></h2><p data-lake-id="ub81e63ad" id="ub81e63ad"><span data-lake-id="u9f0e7606" id="u9f0e7606">Python 中有四种作用域，分别是：</span></p><blockquote data-lake-id="ua1e91bb7" id="ua1e91bb7" class="lake-alert lake-alert-info"><ol list="ub5143359"><li fid="u32216652" data-lake-id="ud3b186a1" id="ud3b186a1"><strong><span data-lake-id="uc1c0b798" id="uc1c0b798" style="color: #AD1A2B">L</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u5f6ed712" id="u5f6ed712">ocal（局部作用域）</span></li><li fid="u32216652" data-lake-id="u294d0e68" id="u294d0e68"><strong><span data-lake-id="ub5adf0cf" id="ub5adf0cf" style="color: #AD1A2B">E</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u5f13afd9" id="u5f13afd9">nclosing（外层作用域）</span></li><li fid="u32216652" data-lake-id="u7dde90c6" id="u7dde90c6"><strong><span data-lake-id="u4ffab95e" id="u4ffab95e" style="color: #AD1A2B">G</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u775eca9c" id="u775eca9c">lobal（全局作用域）</span></li><li fid="u32216652" data-lake-id="u3cda52f6" id="u3cda52f6"><strong><span data-lake-id="u60c97af8" id="u60c97af8" style="color: #AD1A2B">B</span></strong><span data-lake-id="ub826af1d" id="ub826af1d">uilt-in（内建作用域）</span></li></ol></blockquote><p data-lake-id="u8ed323a2" id="u8ed323a2"><span data-lake-id="uc2744740" id="uc2744740">当访问一个变量时，Python 会按以下顺序查找：  </span><strong><span data-lake-id="u186a6fbb" id="u186a6fbb" style="color: #AD1A2B">L</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u3c744260" id="u3c744260">ocal   =&gt;  </span><strong><span data-lake-id="u043d3b85" id="u043d3b85" style="color: #AD1A2B">E</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u6f1b7df5" id="u6f1b7df5">nclosing   =&gt; </span><strong><span data-lake-id="udf7e2f42" id="udf7e2f42" style="color: #AD1A2B">G</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u236e66f1" id="u236e66f1">lobal   =&gt; </span><strong><span data-lake-id="ua17a0e19" id="ua17a0e19" style="color: #AD1A2B">B</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u6ccff586" id="u6ccff586">uilt-in</span></p><p data-lake-id="u51b7d9cc" id="u51b7d9cc"><card type="inline" name="image" value="data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fpng%2F35780599%2F1765149103254-8ff8aa0b-2ffd-498f-acbe-9e9537156e47.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ub1df5712-17df-4d8a-903a-318301b7dba%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22uad1178d8-2b8b-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A1077.3333333333333%2C%22height%22%3A715%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A206070%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1616%2C%22originHeight%22%3A1073%2C%22ratio%22%3A1.25%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22shadow%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22text%22%3A%22PRINT(TEST%E6%94%B6%E5%88%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0B%E6%98%AF%2CB)%2366%22%2C%22x%22%3A182%2C%22y%22%3A371%2C%22width%22%3A639%2C%22height%22%3A37%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22PRINT(TEST%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84C%E5%92%8CD%E5%88%86%E5%88%AB%E6%98%AF'%2CC%2CD)%232O0%22%2C%22x%22%3A172%2C%22y%22%3A512%2C%22width%22%3A746%2C%22height%22%3A38%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22RINT(TEST%E4%B8%AD%E6%89%93%E5%8D%B0%E7%9A%84A%E6%98%AF%5C%22%2CA)%231OO%22%2C%22x%22%3A186%2C%22y%22%3A324%2C%22width%22%3A627%2C%22height%22%3A34%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22PRINT(%E5%85%A8%E5%90%8C%E6%89%93%E5%8D%B0%E7%9A%84A%E6%98%AF%2CA)%2310O%22%2C%22x%22%3A100%2C%22y%22%3A907%2C%22width%22%3A581%2C%22height%22%3A38%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%A4%96%E5%B1%82%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%E5%9F%9F(ENCLOSFNG)%22%2C%22x%22%3A839%2C%22y%22%3A278%2C%22width%22%3A589%2C%22height%22%3A44%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%86%85%E5%BB%BA%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%E5%9F%9F(BUT-N)%22%2C%22x%22%3A1137%2C%22y%22%3A42%2C%22width%22%3A452%2C%22height%22%3A44%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%85%A8%E5%B1%80%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%E5%9F%9F(GOBA)%22%2C%22x%22%3A1079%2C%22y%22%3A134%2C%22width%22%3A421%2C%22height%22%3A48%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22PRINT(%E6%88%91%E6%98%AFTEST%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0)%22%2C%22x%22%3A180%2C%22y%22%3A279%2C%22width%22%3A416%2C%22height%22%3A36%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22RINT(INNER%E4%B8%AD%E6%89%93%E7%9A%84C%E6%98%AF%5C%22%2CC)%22%2C%22x%22%3A263%2C%22y%22%3A799%2C%22width%22%3A546%2C%22height%22%3A32%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E5%B1%80%E9%83%A8%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%E5%9F%9F(LOCAL)%22%2C%22x%22%3A963%2C%22y%22%3A612%2C%22width%22%3A377%2C%22height%22%3A44%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22PRINTINNER%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84E%E6%98%AF%2CE)%22%2C%22x%22%3A255%2C%22y%22%3A753%2C%22width%22%3A494%2C%22height%22%3A33%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22DEFINNER%22%2C%22x%22%3A174%2C%22y%22%3A567%2C%22width%22%3A214%2C%22height%22%3A28%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22DEMO.PY%22%2C%22x%22%3A717%2C%22y%22%3A60%2C%22width%22%3A155%2C%22height%22%3A36%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%23200300%22%2C%22x%22%3A789%2C%22y%22%3A513%2C%22width%22%3A203%2C%22height%22%3A31%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22INNER%22%2C%22x%22%3A171%2C%22y%22%3A860%2C%22width%22%3A202%2C%22height%22%3A31%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22TEST(66%22%2C%22x%22%3A99%2C%22y%22%3A954%2C%22width%22%3A155%2C%22height%22%3A35%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22C-999%22%2C%22x%22%3A258%2C%22y%22%3A705%2C%22width%22%3A155%2C%22height%22%3A31%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%2CC%E4%BA%95999%22%2C%22x%22%3A690%2C%22y%22%3A803%2C%22width%22%3A205%2C%22height%22%3A29%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22E%3D400%22%2C%22x%22%3A252%2C%22y%22%3A614%2C%22width%22%3A147%2C%22height%22%3A30%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22NONLOCAL%22%2C%22x%22%3A258%2C%22y%22%3A664%2C%22width%22%3A182%2C%22height%22%3A27%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22E%23400%22%2C%22x%22%3A664%2C%22y%22%3A755%2C%22width%22%3A165%2C%22height%22%3A28%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22FTEST(B)%3A%22%2C%22x%22%3A149%2C%22y%22%3A230%2C%22width%22%3A188%2C%22height%22%3A29%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%3D300%22%2C%22x%22%3A192%2C%22y%22%3A474%2C%22width%22%3A131%2C%22height%22%3A26%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22DEF%22%2C%22x%22%3A98%2C%22y%22%3A228%2C%22width%22%3A93%2C%22height%22%3A31%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E4%BA%8C100%22%2C%22x%22%3A130%2C%22y%22%3A146%2C%22width%22%3A111%2C%22height%22%3A30%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22%E4%B8%80999%22%2C%22x%22%3A322%2C%22y%22%3A428%2C%22width%22%3A138%2C%22height%22%3A30%7D%2C%7B%22text%22%3A%22200%22%2C%22x%22%3A238%2C%22y%22%3A425%2C%22width%22%3A95%2C%22height%22%3A33%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%233c5b44%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u6b5793e1%22%7D"></card></p><blockquote data-lake-id="u782af6bf" id="u782af6bf" class="lake-alert lake-alert-color4"><p data-lake-id="u6887b050" id="u6887b050"><span data-lake-id="ueb31a313" id="ueb31a313">上述图示的详细分析，请参考视频教程。</span></p></blockquote><h3 data-lake-id="F0d2z" id="F0d2z" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u8cd822a6" id="u8cd822a6">局部作用域（Local）</span></h3><p data-lake-id="u16227c04" id="u16227c04"><strong><span data-lake-id="u36189f3a" id="u36189f3a">定义：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u076fa28a" id="u076fa28a">函数的内部就是局部作用域，局部作用域中的变量，只在该函数内部可见。</span></p><p data-lake-id="u6e85356c" id="u6e85356c"><strong><span data-lake-id="u6e2fec63" id="u6e2fec63">特点：</span></strong></p><ul list="ue7951f55"><li fid="u2ed2dcde" data-lake-id="uc831c905" id="uc831c905"><span data-lake-id="u9eafa620" id="u9eafa620">每次调用函数都会创建一个新的局部作用域。</span></li><li fid="u2ed2dcde" data-lake-id="u0e97119c" id="u0e97119c"><span data-lake-id="u4a9a38d8" id="u4a9a38d8">函数运行结束后，局部作用域会随之销毁。</span></li><li fid="u2ed2dcde" data-lake-id="u104a773b" id="u104a773b"><span data-lake-id="u6b853d85" id="u6b853d85">局部作用域优先级最高，即：查找一个变量时，Python 会首先在局部作用域中查找。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id="ue5f8e0ae" id="ue5f8e0ae"><strong><span data-lake-id="u0435f596" id="u0435f596">举例：</span></strong></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22def%20test()%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20x%20%3D%2010%20%20%23%20x%20%E5%9C%A8%E5%B1%80%E9%83%A8%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%E5%9F%9F%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(x)%20%20%23%20%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%5Cn%5Cnprint(x)%20%20%23%20%E2%9D%8C%20%E6%8A%A5%E9%94%99%EF%BC%9Ax%20%E5%9C%A8%E5%B1%80%E9%83%A8%E4%B9%8B%E5%A4%96%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E8%A7%81%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22AJ7Rt%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h3 data-lake-id="vNxWh" id="vNxWh" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u11377b14" id="u11377b14">外层作用域（Enclosing）</span></h3><p data-lake-id="u7eef6cc2" id="u7eef6cc2"><strong><span data-lake-id="uc3232267" id="uc3232267">定义：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u577482db" id="u577482db">如果函数中又定义了函数，那么外层函数的作用域，就是内层函数的 Enclosing 作用域。</span></p><p data-lake-id="u6e7f0f55" id="u6e7f0f55"><strong><span data-lake-id="u0da067c5" id="u0da067c5">特点：</span></strong></p><ul list="u30ecc303"><li fid="u6c0da5d4" data-lake-id="u980d8ae3" id="u980d8ae3"><span data-lake-id="ub31f4f7c" id="ub31f4f7c">只有当函数“嵌套定义”时才会出现。</span></li><li fid="u6c0da5d4" data-lake-id="u30fc31aa" id="u30fc31aa"><span data-lake-id="u347a688b" id="u347a688b">内层函数可以读取外层函数变量。</span></li><li fid="u6c0da5d4" data-lake-id="ue9c21b75" id="ue9c21b75"><span data-lake-id="ubd1bb4b5" id="ubd1bb4b5">想修改外层变量必须使用</span><code data-lake-id="u47a5d910" id="u47a5d910"><span data-lake-id="ucf239a38" id="ucf239a38">nonlocal</span></code><span data-lake-id="u897c645a" id="u897c645a">。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id="uf5509c4c" id="uf5509c4c"><strong><span data-lake-id="u0d38936e" id="u0d38936e">举例：</span></strong></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22def%20outer()%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20y%20%3D%2020%20%20%23%20outer%20%E7%9A%84%E5%B1%80%E9%83%A8%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%20%E2%86%92%20inner%20%E7%9A%84%20Enclosing%20%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%5Cn%5Cn%20%20%20%20def%20inner()%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20print(y)%20%20%23%20%E5%86%85%E5%B1%82%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E8%AF%BB%E5%8F%96%E5%A4%96%E5%B1%82%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%5Cn%5Cn%20%20%20%20inner()%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22pJY2U%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u3798e9a3" id="u3798e9a3"><strong><span data-lake-id="ub65107e3" id="ub65107e3">修改外层变量：</span></strong></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22def%20outer()%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20y%20%3D%2020%5Cn%20%20%20%20def%20inner()%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20nonlocal%20y%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20y%20%3D%2099%20%20%23%20%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%E5%A4%96%E5%B1%82%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E4%BD%9C%E7%94%A8%E5%9F%9F%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Ci0HS%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h3 data-lake-id="sPtep" id="sPtep" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u222b7419" id="u222b7419">全局作用域（Global）</span></h3><p data-lake-id="u675082af" id="u675082af"><strong><span data-lake-id="u49c9501c" id="u49c9501c">定义：</span></strong><code data-lake-id="ua470c638" id="ua470c638"><span data-lake-id="u4ee23345" id="u4ee23345">.py</span></code><span data-lake-id="u1c49cf85" id="u1c49cf85">文件就是全局作用域，全局作用域中的变量，在当前</span><code data-lake-id="ufbf0e3a2" id="ufbf0e3a2"><span data-lake-id="ub5ea2bde" id="ub5ea2bde">.py</span></code><span data-lake-id="u440e1f7b" id="u440e1f7b">文件的任何位置都可以访问。</span></p><p data-lake-id="ua254074d" id="ua254074d"><strong><span data-lake-id="u368392a0" id="u368392a0">特点：</span></strong></p><ul list="u63a76724"><li fid="ub9cab8f6" data-lake-id="uce4086fb" id="uce4086fb"><span data-lake-id="u0d72dbdb" id="u0d72dbdb">全局变量只在当前</span><code data-lake-id="uf55904a1" id="uf55904a1"><span data-lake-id="uf84ffdff" id="uf84ffdff">.py</span></code><span data-lake-id="ufe6e92ec" id="ufe6e92ec">文件中可见。</span></li><li fid="ub9cab8f6" data-lake-id="uafc8291d" id="uafc8291d"><span data-lake-id="u90ea93dd" id="u90ea93dd">函数内部可以使用</span><code data-lake-id="u6936d609" id="u6936d609"><span data-lake-id="uc69d57a4" id="uc69d57a4">global</span></code><span data-lake-id="uf05bda9f" id="uf05bda9f">关键字修改全局变量。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id="u3de9d2ff" id="u3de9d2ff"><strong><span data-lake-id="ua8339be8" id="ua8339be8">例子：</span></strong></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22a%20%3D%20100%20%20%23%20%E5%85%A8%E5%B1%80%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%5Cn%5Cndef%20test()%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(a)%20%20%23%20%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E8%AF%BB%E5%8F%96%5Cn%5Cntest()%5Cnprint(a)%20%20%23%20%E5%9C%A8%E6%9C%AC%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E4%BB%BB%E4%BD%95%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E9%83%BD%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22M3TsR%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u362e1e4f" id="u362e1e4f"><strong><span data-lake-id="u43a91ed4" id="u43a91ed4">如果要修改：</span></strong></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22a%20%3D%20100%5Cn%5Cndef%20test()%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20global%20a%5Cn%20%20%20%20a%20%3D%20200%20%20%23%20%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%E5%85%A8%E5%B1%80%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22TEQa1%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h3 data-lake-id="jOPap" id="jOPap" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u133050a2" id="u133050a2">内建作用域（Built-in）</span></h3><p data-lake-id="uc0ff6f28" id="uc0ff6f28"><strong><span data-lake-id="uae7d03fc" id="uae7d03fc">定义：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u0b0b0a21" id="u0b0b0a21">Python 预先定义好的东西，会放在内建作用域中，所有</span><code data-lake-id="uc855887b" id="uc855887b"><span data-lake-id="uf117e939" id="uf117e939">.py</span></code><span data-lake-id="u757118ad" id="u757118ad">文件都可以直接使用。</span></p><p data-lake-id="uaa242de5" id="uaa242de5"><strong><span data-lake-id="u92669275" id="u92669275">特点：</span></strong></p><ul list="uf60f2935"><li fid="u3feb63f2" data-lake-id="uf48a21f1" id="uf48a21f1"><span data-lake-id="u29ac020c" id="u29ac020c">所有</span><code data-lake-id="u47416d8c" id="u47416d8c"><span data-lake-id="u3eeaeb17" id="u3eeaeb17">.py</span></code><span data-lake-id="ua15ec747" id="ua15ec747">文件都能直接使用其中的名称。</span></li><li fid="u3feb63f2" data-lake-id="ue39d6a03" id="ue39d6a03"><span data-lake-id="ufc264927" id="ufc264927">例如：</span><code data-lake-id="u73a8f844" id="u73a8f844"><span data-lake-id="uc813f585" id="uc813f585">print</span></code><span data-lake-id="u5c3f2ce8" id="u5c3f2ce8">、</span><code data-lake-id="uac0d07de" id="uac0d07de"><span data-lake-id="u2cbdb2a7" id="u2cbdb2a7">len</span></code><span data-lake-id="u2c8d069a" id="u2c8d069a">、</span><code data-lake-id="uf9f230d1" id="uf9f230d1"><span data-lake-id="u6d09482e" id="u6d09482e">range</span></code><span data-lake-id="u37754042" id="u37754042">、</span><code data-lake-id="ua0d8f991" id="ua0d8f991"><span data-lake-id="u2bffee68" id="u2bffee68">sum</span></code><span data-lake-id="u59b4554d" id="u59b4554d">、</span><code data-lake-id="u47510332" id="u47510332"><span data-lake-id="u740d777d" id="u740d777d">max</span></code><span data-lake-id="ub03c18e7" id="ub03c18e7"> 等。</span></li><li fid="u3feb63f2" data-lake-id="u522e827c" id="u522e827c"><span data-lake-id="u3dbfd1c3" id="u3dbfd1c3">查找优先级最低，即：查找一个变量时，内建作用域是“最后一道防线”。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id="ucb8f71ed" id="ucb8f71ed"><strong><span data-lake-id="u33e546d9" id="u33e546d9">例子：</span></strong></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22print('hello')%20%5Cnlen(%5B1%2C%202%2C%203%5D)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22a8yjw%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h2 data-lake-id="fNldr" id="fNldr" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="ubbec2b7e" id="ubbec2b7e">闭包</span></h2><h3 data-lake-id="kU7h2" id="kU7h2" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="ue7b94787" id="ue7b94787">前置知识</span></h3><p data-lake-id="u6d8bb37a" id="u6d8bb37a"><strong><span data-lake-id="uec3094ea" id="uec3094ea">前置知识 1： 局部作用域的生命周期。</span></strong></p><ul list="u934b1f9e"><li fid="ufe7e79ab" data-lake-id="ue4389c1a" id="ue4389c1a"><span data-lake-id="ud8ec413a" id="ud8ec413a">每次调用函数时，都会创建一个新的局部作用域。</span></li><li fid="ufe7e79ab" data-lake-id="u13627031" id="u13627031"><span data-lake-id="uc5807752" id="uc5807752">函数执行完毕后，该作用域就会被销毁，其中的局部变量，也会随之释放。</span></li></ul><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22def%20outer()%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20num%20%3D%2010%5Cn%20%20%20%20num%20%2B%3D%201%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(num)%5Cn%5Cnouter()%20%2311%5Cnouter()%20%2311%5Cnouter()%20%2311%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22jSYgD%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><blockquote data-lake-id="ufb871ab7" id="ufb871ab7"><p data-lake-id="u31dc6bf6" id="u31dc6bf6"><span data-lake-id="u83d45ddf" id="u83d45ddf"> 在上述代码中：每次调用 </span><code data-lake-id="u0d7b27da" id="u0d7b27da"><span data-lake-id="u81bdbaff" id="u81bdbaff">outer()</span></code><span data-lake-id="ud9dc327a" id="ud9dc327a">，</span><code data-lake-id="ufde0ca2a" id="ufde0ca2a"><span data-lake-id="u06ad19f5" id="u06ad19f5">num</span></code><span data-lake-id="uf9107d04" id="uf9107d04"> 都会重新生成，不会保存上一次的值。  </span></p></blockquote><p data-lake-id="u41152766" id="u41152766"><strong><span data-lake-id="u25c64fbc" id="u25c64fbc">前置知识 2：内层函数访问外层变量。</span></strong></p><ul list="u704caeea"><li fid="u3bb42740" data-lake-id="u44a877c1" id="u44a877c1"><span data-lake-id="uc68e4b85" id="uc68e4b85">【内层函数】可以访问到【外层函数】作用域中的变量。</span></li><li fid="u3bb42740" data-lake-id="u675dfcae" id="u675dfcae"><span data-lake-id="uf8d45378" id="uf8d45378">访问外层变量不用</span><code data-lake-id="u00889c11" id="u00889c11"><span data-lake-id="u969ed759" id="u969ed759">nonlocal</span></code><span data-lake-id="u2b222ed9" id="u2b222ed9">，修改外层变量时要使用</span><code data-lake-id="uce43b736" id="uce43b736"><span data-lake-id="u0fcec05d" id="u0fcec05d">nonlocal</span></code><span data-lake-id="u1edf0670" id="u1edf0670">。</span></li></ul><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22def%20outer()%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20num%20%3D%2010%5Cn%5Cn%20%20%20%20def%20inner()%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20print(num)%5Cn%20%20%20%20inner()%5Cn%5Cnouter()%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22gHsNR%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u59d16de5" id="u59d16de5"><span data-lake-id="u272fdfd5" id="u272fdfd5">如下代码验证了：理论上</span><code data-lake-id="uf13b3a1f" id="uf13b3a1f"><span data-lake-id="u91f134a4" id="u91f134a4">num</span></code><span data-lake-id="uea672948" id="uea672948">变量应该在</span><code data-lake-id="u8ccb4747" id="u8ccb4747"><span data-lake-id="u04f19b4c" id="u04f19b4c">outer</span></code><span data-lake-id="u64c56e5b" id="u64c56e5b">函数调用完销毁，但实际并没有。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22def%20outer()%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20num%20%3D%2010%5Cn%5Cn%20%20%20%20def%20inner()%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20print(num)%5Cn%5Cn%20%20%20%20return%20inner%5Cn%5Cnf%20%3D%20outer()%5Cnf()%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Ui8p3%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h3 data-lake-id="RHDiv" id="RHDiv" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u54fbbbb0" id="u54fbbbb0">什么是闭包</span></h3><ul list="udcd843f4"><li fid="u92def489" data-lake-id="ue405c5eb" id="ue405c5eb"><strong><span data-lake-id="ue5212d9a" id="ue5212d9a">闭包 = 内层函数 + 被内层函数引用的外层变量。</span></strong></li><li fid="u92def489" data-lake-id="ue4a2abdb" id="ue4a2abdb"><strong><span data-lake-id="ufecd1827" id="ufecd1827">产生闭包的三个条件如下：</span></strong></li></ul><blockquote data-lake-id="u144e56b5" id="u144e56b5" hindent="2em" class="lake-alert lake-alert-info"><ol list="u10605e7b"><li fid="ubdd9cf49" data-lake-id="uef4238cd" id="uef4238cd"><span data-lake-id="u41bccaa8" id="u41bccaa8">必须有函数嵌套</span></li><li fid="ubdd9cf49" data-lake-id="ufbec8f70" id="ufbec8f70"><span data-lake-id="u07a1ceb1" id="u07a1ceb1">内层函数使用了外层函数的变量</span></li><li fid="ubdd9cf49" data-lake-id="u39830dfb" id="u39830dfb"><span data-lake-id="u84ae61db" id="u84ae61db">外层函数返回内层函数</span></li></ol></blockquote><h3 data-lake-id="u7xgb" id="u7xgb" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u9ac92d20" id="u9ac92d20">闭包的基本形式</span></h3><p data-lake-id="u21a52763" id="u21a52763"><span data-lake-id="udcca8419" id="udcca8419">在上述代码的基础上，我们在</span><code data-lake-id="u89dd3e26" id="u89dd3e26"><span data-lake-id="ua0700c4b" id="ua0700c4b">inner</span></code><span data-lake-id="u432ec8b1" id="u432ec8b1">函数中不仅要打印</span><code data-lake-id="ufbbba41f" id="ufbbba41f"><span data-lake-id="uae09a22e" id="uae09a22e">num</span></code><span data-lake-id="u88217581" id="u88217581">，还要去修改</span><code data-lake-id="uc8a1935a" id="uc8a1935a"><span data-lake-id="u93d974e0" id="u93d974e0">num</span></code><span data-lake-id="u538a6dae" id="u538a6dae">（修改时记得加上</span><code data-lake-id="u42e1da09" id="u42e1da09"><span data-lake-id="u4d965e91" id="u4d965e91">nonlocal num</span></code><span data-lake-id="u1abeadcc" id="u1abeadcc">）。最终发现：</span><code data-lake-id="u61af5010" id="u61af5010"><span data-lake-id="u050c51ba" id="u050c51ba">num</span></code><span data-lake-id="u60b30f2b" id="u60b30f2b">的值居然还可以一直增加，所以截至目前，证明了一件事：本应该随着</span><code data-lake-id="u6589e60f" id="u6589e60f"><span data-lake-id="u385cf2ef" id="u385cf2ef">outer</span></code><span data-lake-id="ue19fd23d" id="ue19fd23d">函数调用结束而死去的</span><code data-lake-id="u431b7846" id="u431b7846"><span data-lake-id="u42f2bada" id="u42f2bada">num</span></code><span data-lake-id="u482cee0f" id="u482cee0f">，并没有死去，并且</span><code data-lake-id="ub94e26fa" id="ub94e26fa"><span data-lake-id="u1af62073" id="u1af62073">inner</span></code><span data-lake-id="u26df2906" id="u26df2906">函数依然可以对</span><code data-lake-id="u0e4549d8" id="u0e4549d8"><span data-lake-id="u8dfc56f2" id="u8dfc56f2">num</span></code><span data-lake-id="u3ef7203d" id="u3ef7203d">进行读取和修改。所以我们观察如下的代码形式，完全符合上述的闭包产生条件，所以此时就出现了</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u3cf2ea7d" id="u3cf2ea7d" style="color: #DF2A3F">闭包</span></strong><span data-lake-id="ua268a1a9" id="ua268a1a9">。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22def%20outer()%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20num%20%3D%2010%5Cn%5Cn%20%20%20%20def%20inner()%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20nonlocal%20num%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20num%20%2B%3D%201%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20print(num)%5Cn%5Cn%20%20%20%20return%20inner%5Cn%5Cnf%20%3D%20outer()%5Cnf()%20%23%2011%5Cnf()%20%23%2012%5Cnf()%20%23%2013%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22qSOeL%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h3 data-lake-id="Ri83u" id="Ri83u" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u702452e8" id="u702452e8">闭包是如何保存外层变量的？</span></h3><p data-lake-id="u2cb2265a" id="u2cb2265a"><span data-lake-id="u71b672ad" id="u71b672ad">外层变量会被保存到 </span><strong><span data-lake-id="u7824d5ee" id="u7824d5ee" style="color: #DF2A3F">闭包单元（cell）</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u5b231fd5" id="u5b231fd5">中，例如下面代码中，那些被</span><code data-lake-id="u5280825e" id="u5280825e"><span data-lake-id="ue8c33cb6" id="ue8c33cb6"> inner</span></code><span data-lake-id="u20d4a7d4" id="u20d4a7d4">函数所使用到的</span><code data-lake-id="ued5548de" id="ued5548de"><span data-lake-id="u89cad16c" id="u89cad16c">outer</span></code><span data-lake-id="ud35da1d5" id="ud35da1d5">函数中的局部变量，会被封存在</span><strong><span data-lake-id="ud9b8d8ec" id="ud9b8d8ec" style="color: #DF2A3F">闭包单元（cell）</span></strong><span data-lake-id="uaa83ad6a" id="uaa83ad6a"> 中，这些</span><code data-lake-id="u365a1b22" id="u365a1b22"><span data-lake-id="u76f1c8b5" id="u76f1c8b5">cell</span></code><span data-lake-id="u9411d698" id="u9411d698">组成一个 </span><code data-lake-id="ue48447e8" id="ue48447e8"><span data-lake-id="uc2feb7e8" id="uc2feb7e8">__closure__</span></code><span data-lake-id="ub13b95e7" id="ub13b95e7"> 元组，保存在了</span><code data-lake-id="u1c1309db" id="u1c1309db"><span data-lake-id="u1a8b33b4" id="u1a8b33b4">inner</span></code><span data-lake-id="ucbea5f28" id="ucbea5f28">函数上。  </span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22def%20outer()%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20num%20%3D%2010%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(id(num))%20%23%20140707460170952%5Cn%5Cn%20%20%20%20def%20inner()%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20nonlocal%20num%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20num%20%2B%3D%201%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20print(num)%5Cn%5Cn%20%20%20%20return%20inner%5Cn%5Cnf%20%3D%20outer()%5Cn%5Cnprint(f.__closure__)%20%23%20__closure__%E7%9A%84%E5%80%BC%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%85%83%E7%BB%84%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%83%E7%BB%84%E4%B8%AD%E4%BF%9D%E5%AD%98%E7%9D%80%E8%A2%ABinner%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E6%89%80%E2%80%9C%E6%8C%BD%E6%95%91%E2%80%9D%E4%B8%8B%E6%9D%A5%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%5Cnprint(f.__closure__%5B0%5D.cell_contents)%20%23%2010%5Cnprint(id(f.__closure__%5B0%5D.cell_contents))%20%23%20140707460170952%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22LSl7m%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u7bd85e94" id="u7bd85e94"><span data-lake-id="u43293134" id="u43293134">思考：内层函数</span><code data-lake-id="u85faf87c" id="u85faf87c"><span data-lake-id="u08c2ab1e" id="u08c2ab1e">inner</span></code><span data-lake-id="u0428118f" id="u0428118f">会保存外层函数</span><code data-lake-id="uf65c4790" id="uf65c4790"><span data-lake-id="uf92cbf5e" id="uf92cbf5e">outer</span></code><span data-lake-id="ua27ada38" id="ua27ada38">中所有的数据吗？ 不会，只会保存</span><code data-lake-id="u49a1b97c" id="u49a1b97c"><span data-lake-id="uf39d29c7" id="uf39d29c7">inner</span></code><span data-lake-id="u0d7c9a5d" id="u0d7c9a5d">中所用到的。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22def%20outer()%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20num%20%3D%2010%5Cn%20%20%20%20msg%20%3D%20'%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD%E5%95%8A%EF%BC%81'%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(msg)%5Cn%5Cn%20%20%20%20def%20inner()%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20nonlocal%20num%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20num%20%2B%3D%201%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20print(num)%5Cn%5Cn%20%20%20%20return%20inner%5Cn%5Cnf%20%3D%20outer()%5Cnprint(f.__closure__)%20%23%20%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%B0__closure__%E4%B8%AD%E5%8F%AA%E6%9C%89num%EF%BC%8C%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89msg%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22CYF4J%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h3 data-lake-id="AJgOq" id="AJgOq" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="ufdad0029" id="ufdad0029">注意点  </span></h3><p data-lake-id="u0eadf216" id="u0eadf216"><span data-lake-id="uad382240" id="uad382240"> 1. 每次获得一个新闭包，互不影响（闭包之间是互相独立的）。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22def%20outer()%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20num%20%3D%2010%5Cn%5Cn%20%20%20%20def%20inner()%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20nonlocal%20num%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20num%20%2B%3D%201%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20print(num)%5Cn%5Cn%20%20%20%20return%20inner%5Cn%5Cnf1%20%3D%20outer()%5Cnf1()%5Cnf1()%5Cnf1()%5Cnprint('*****************')%5Cnf2%20%3D%20outer()%5Cnf2()%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22hCrzJ%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><ol list="u469df106" start="2"><li fid="ue5ec10ac" data-lake-id="uf2f2b291" id="uf2f2b291"><span data-lake-id="uad2d7089" id="uad2d7089">外层变量为可变对象时仍互不影响。</span></li></ol><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22def%20outer()%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20nums%20%3D%20%5B%5D%5Cn%5Cn%20%20%20%20def%20inner(value)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20nums.append(value)%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20print(nums)%5Cn%5Cn%20%20%20%20return%20inner%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E6%AF%8F%E6%AC%A1%E8%B0%83%E7%94%A8%20outer()%20%E9%83%BD%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E6%96%B0%E7%9A%84%20nums%5Cnf1%20%3D%20outer()%5Cnf1(10)%5Cnf1(20)%5Cnf1(30)%5Cnprint('**********************')%5Cnf2%20%3D%20outer()%5Cnf2(666)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22vJYbi%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h3 data-lake-id="iPyRM" id="iPyRM" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u04d73cd7" id="u04d73cd7">闭包的优点</span></h3><ol list="u3e4bca24"><li fid="ucef84e91" data-lake-id="ue0ff072d" id="ue0ff072d"><span data-lake-id="uf97b4218" id="uf97b4218">可以“记住”状态：不用全局变量，也不用写类，就能在多次调用之间保存数据。</span></li><li fid="ucef84e91" data-lake-id="uade79dc9" id="uade79dc9"><span data-lake-id="u30306806" id="u30306806">可以做“配置过的函数”：先传一部分参数，把环境固定住，得到一个定制版函数。</span></li><li fid="ucef84e91" data-lake-id="ud247dd5d" id="ud247dd5d"><span data-lake-id="u9ab15218" id="u9ab15218">可以实现简单的“数据隐藏”：外层变量对外不可见，只能通过内层函数访问。</span></li><li fid="ucef84e91" data-lake-id="u9eefc5dc" id="u9eefc5dc"><span data-lake-id="u03bd72aa" id="u03bd72aa">是装饰器（decorator）等高级用法的基础。</span></li></ol><p data-lake-id="ud54fb35f" id="ud54fb35f"><span data-lake-id="u4cdcdddd" id="u4cdcdddd">小案例：使用闭包实现对文字的美化效果。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22def%20beauty(char%2C%20n)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20def%20show_msg(msg)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20print(char%20*%20n%20%2B%20msg%20%2B%20char%20*%20n)%5Cn%20%20%20%20return%20show_msg%5Cn%5Cnshow1%20%3D%20beauty('*'%2C%203)%5Cnshow1('%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD%E5%95%8A')%5Cnshow1('%E5%B0%9A%E7%A1%85%E8%B0%B7')%5Cn%5Cnshow2%20%3D%20beauty('%40'%2C%205)%5Cnshow2('%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD%E5%95%8A')%5Cnshow2('%E5%B0%9A%E7%A1%85%E8%B0%B7')%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22lWWbj%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h3 data-lake-id="v3vwj" id="v3vwj" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u16af9fb4" id="u16af9fb4"> 闭包的缺点</span></h3><ol list="u5f0d7e23"><li fid="u1726740d" data-lake-id="ud57ebc11" id="ud57ebc11"><span data-lake-id="ue3f72f04" id="ue3f72f04">理解成本较高：对初学者不太友好，滥用会让代码难读。</span></li><li fid="u1726740d" data-lake-id="u665d9f1c" id="u665d9f1c"><span data-lake-id="u56a616c4" id="u56a616c4">如果闭包里引用了很大的对象，又长期不释放，可能会增加内存占用。</span></li><li fid="u1726740d" data-lake-id="u84ebf07b" id="u84ebf07b"><span data-lake-id="u3ca85bf6" id="u3ca85bf6">很多场景下，其实用【类 + 实例属性】会更清晰，闭包不一定是最优解。</span></li></ol><p data-lake-id="uc32b3c56" id="uc32b3c56"><span data-lake-id="u7425d6f3" id="u7425d6f3">例如将上述的文字美化效果，用类实现：</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22class%20Beauty%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20def%20__init__(self%2C%20char%2C%20n)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20self.char%20%3D%20char%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20self.n%20%3D%20n%5Cn%5Cn%20%20%20%20def%20show_msg(self%2C%20msg)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20print(self.char%20*%20self.n%20%2B%20msg%20%2B%20self.char%20*%20self.n)%5Cn%5Cnb1%20%3D%20Beauty('*'%2C%203)%5Cnb1.show_msg('%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD%E5%95%8A')%5Cnb1.show_msg('%E5%B0%9A%E7%A1%85%E8%B0%B7')%5Cn%5Cnb2%20%3D%20Beauty('%23'%2C%205)%5Cnb2.show_msg('%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD%E5%95%8A')%5Cnb2.show_msg('%E5%B0%9A%E7%A1%85%E8%B0%B7')%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22usfUD%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h2 data-lake-id="iVNR8" id="iVNR8" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="uafcc0ab1" id="uafcc0ab1">装饰器</span></h2><ul list="u6cbe8671"><li fid="u5513289e" data-lake-id="u9dbda0e1" id="u9dbda0e1"><strong><span data-lake-id="uf214497b" id="uf214497b">概述</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u8d972d35" id="u8d972d35">：装饰器是一种在【不修改原函数代码】的前提下，对函数进行【增强】的工具。 它是 Python 中非常强大的语法特性，常用于：日志、校验、计时、缓存、权限控制等。   </span></li><li fid="u5513289e" data-lake-id="u53db3ca6" id="u53db3ca6"><strong><span data-lake-id="ude99d38f" id="ude99d38f">核心语法</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u9197044c" id="u9197044c">： 装饰器是一种可调用对象（通常是函数），接收一个函数作为参数，并返回一个新函数。 </span></li></ul><h3 data-lake-id="W7SrQ" id="W7SrQ" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="uedd35691" id="uedd35691">函数装饰器 </span></h3><p data-lake-id="u36a88036" id="u36a88036"><strong><span data-lake-id="uc2fc4b65" id="uc2fc4b65">需求</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u778e435b" id="u778e435b">：在不修改</span><code data-lake-id="ubda628fc" id="ubda628fc"><span data-lake-id="u320f99bf" id="u320f99bf">add</span></code><span data-lake-id="u7841e8ac" id="u7841e8ac">函数的前提下，给</span><code data-lake-id="u60845127" id="u60845127"><span data-lake-id="uf903819d" id="uf903819d">add</span></code><span data-lake-id="u3ccf0171" id="u3ccf0171">函数增加一些额外的功能，例如：计算前打印一句欢迎语。</span></p><h4 data-lake-id="bwlVN" id="bwlVN"><span data-lake-id="ubd295e1c" id="ubd295e1c">1️⃣</span><span data-lake-id="udda62124" id="udda62124">定义函数装饰器</span></h4><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22def%20say_hello(func)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20def%20wrapper(*args%2C%20**kwargs)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20print('%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%91%E8%A6%81%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E4%BA%86')%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20return%20func(*args%2C%20**kwargs)%5Cn%20%20%20%20return%20wrapper%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22oLyU8%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><blockquote data-lake-id="u4a30eda3" id="u4a30eda3"><p data-lake-id="ue3d4c031" id="ue3d4c031"><span data-lake-id="u1faf4c78" id="u1faf4c78">定义装饰器核心规则：</span></p><ol list="ud12604e0"><li fid="u14e626c7" data-lake-id="ucece13a2" id="ucece13a2"><span data-lake-id="uf30e1c2a" id="uf30e1c2a">接收被装饰的函数、同时返回新函数（wrapper）</span></li><li fid="u14e626c7" data-lake-id="u5ace8149" id="u5ace8149"><span data-lake-id="u4e65adbd" id="u4e65adbd">装饰器“吐出来”的是 wrapper 函数，以后别人调用的也是 wrapper 函数。</span></li><li fid="u14e626c7" data-lake-id="u0ae4774f" id="u0ae4774f"><span data-lake-id="u66415343" id="u66415343">为了保证参数的兼容性，wrapper 函数要通过 *args 和 **kwargs 接收参数。</span></li><li fid="u14e626c7" data-lake-id="ue9f30952" id="ue9f30952"><span data-lake-id="u0c3c1cfe" id="u0c3c1cfe">wrapper 函数中主要做的是：调用原函数（被装饰的函数）、执行其它逻辑，但要记得将原函数的返回值 return 出去。</span></li></ol></blockquote><h4 data-lake-id="aawcN" id="aawcN"><span data-lake-id="u106e762d" id="u106e762d">2️⃣</span><span data-lake-id="ue2738810" id="ue2738810">使用函数装饰器（手动装饰）</span></h4><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22def%20say_hello(func)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20def%20wrapper(*args%2C%20**kwargs)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20print('%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%91%E8%A6%81%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E4%BA%86')%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20return%20func(*args%2C%20**kwargs)%5Cn%20%20%20%20return%20wrapper%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E8%B0%83%E7%94%A8say_hello%E8%A3%85%E9%A5%B0%E5%99%A8%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%B9add%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E8%A3%85%E9%A5%B0%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E5%BE%97%E5%88%B0%E8%A3%85%E9%A5%B0%E5%90%8E%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B0%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%5Cnadd%20%3D%20say_hello(add)%5Cn%5Cnresult%20%3D%20add(10%2C%2020%2C%2030)%5Cnprint(result)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22AdXnL%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h4 data-lake-id="aHjSE" id="aHjSE"><span data-lake-id="u64653546" id="u64653546">3️⃣</span><span data-lake-id="ue2be5c20" id="ue2be5c20">使用函数装饰器（语法糖 @）</span></h4><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22def%20say_hello(func)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20def%20wrapper(*args%2C%20**kwargs)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20print('%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%91%E8%A6%81%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E4%BA%86')%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20return%20func(*args%2C%20**kwargs)%5Cn%20%20%20%20return%20wrapper%5Cn%5Cn%40say_hello%5Cndef%20add(x%2C%20y%2C%20z)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20res%20%3D%20x%20%2B%20y%20%2B%20z%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(f'%7Bx%7D%E5%92%8C%7By%7D%E5%92%8C%7Bz%7D%E7%9B%B8%E5%8A%A0%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C%E6%98%AF%EF%BC%9A%7Bres%7D')%5Cn%20%20%20%20return%20res%5Cn%5Cnresult1%20%3D%20add(10%2C%2020%2C%2030)%5Cnprint(result1)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22BQ2vm%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><blockquote data-lake-id="ucf91c318" id="ucf91c318"><p data-lake-id="u812d7cfc" id="u812d7cfc"><span data-lake-id="u7e07a115" id="u7e07a115">上述代码的执行流程：</span></p><ol list="u9e1e083a"><li fid="u3266066e" data-lake-id="u5bc9e13f" id="u5bc9e13f"><code data-lake-id="u72b83c30" id="u72b83c30"><span data-lake-id="u20a409a9" id="u20a409a9">@say_hello</span></code><span data-lake-id="uf70c6a50" id="uf70c6a50"> 会自动执行： </span><code data-lake-id="u6be7f8f3" id="u6be7f8f3"><span data-lake-id="u515fe926" id="u515fe926">add = say_hello(add)</span></code><span data-lake-id="ua2cb88bd" id="ua2cb88bd">。</span></li><li fid="u3266066e" data-lake-id="u5e715449" id="u5e715449"><span data-lake-id="uce0618af" id="uce0618af">以后调用 </span><code data-lake-id="u5c04bb94" id="u5c04bb94"><span data-lake-id="uc5e05e84" id="uc5e05e84">add()</span></code><span data-lake-id="u9536764d" id="u9536764d">时，真正执行的是</span><code data-lake-id="u9eaee919" id="u9eaee919"><span data-lake-id="u7970d377" id="u7970d377">wrapper()</span></code><span data-lake-id="ufe8f5f4f" id="ufe8f5f4f">。</span></li></ol></blockquote><h4 data-lake-id="VVSgW" id="VVSgW"><span data-lake-id="u5d6fd3f2" id="u5d6fd3f2">4️⃣</span><span data-lake-id="uc71ca520" id="uc71ca520">带参数的函数装饰器（三层嵌套）</span></h4><p data-lake-id="uf4837931" id="uf4837931"><strong><span data-lake-id="u98dccfe0" id="u98dccfe0">需求</span></strong><span data-lake-id="ufb3f387f" id="ufb3f387f">：装饰不同的函数，打印不同的欢迎语。</span></p><p data-lake-id="uceb836b9" id="uceb836b9"><strong><span data-lake-id="u02c64824" id="u02c64824">核心：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u697afbf3" id="u697afbf3">带参数的装饰器最终是三层嵌套结构：外层接收配置、中间层接收函数、内层接收具体参数。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22def%20say_hello(msg)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20def%20outer(func)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20def%20wrapper(*args%2C%20**kwargs)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20print(f'%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%91%E8%A6%81%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%7Bmsg%7D%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E4%BA%86')%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20return%20func(*args%2C%20**kwargs)%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20return%20wrapper%5Cn%20%20%20%20return%20outer%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E8%A3%85%E9%A5%B0%E5%8A%A0%E6%B3%95%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%5Cn%40say_hello('%E5%8A%A0%E6%B3%95')%5Cndef%20add(x%2C%20y%2C%20z)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20res%20%3D%20x%20%2B%20y%20%2B%20z%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(f'%7Bx%7D%E5%92%8C%7By%7D%E5%92%8C%7Bz%7D%E7%9B%B8%E5%8A%A0%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C%E6%98%AF%EF%BC%9A%7Bres%7D')%5Cn%20%20%20%20return%20res%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E8%A3%85%E9%A5%B0%E5%87%8F%E6%B3%95%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%5Cn%40say_hello('%E5%87%8F%E6%B3%95')%5Cndef%20sub(x%2C%20y)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20res%20%3D%20x%20-%20y%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(f'%7Bx%7D%E5%92%8C%7By%7D%E7%9B%B8%E5%87%8F%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C%E6%98%AF%EF%BC%9A%7Bres%7D')%5Cn%20%20%20%20return%20res%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%5Cnresult1%20%3D%20add(10%2C%2020%2C%2030)%5Cnprint(result1)%5Cn%5Cnresult2%20%3D%20sub(20%2C%2010)%5Cnprint(result2)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22S8Qrb%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h4 data-lake-id="ABcBD" id="ABcBD"><span data-lake-id="u4c2fefac" id="u4c2fefac">5️⃣</span><span data-lake-id="u13c6df45" id="u13c6df45">多个函数装饰器一起使用</span></h4><p data-lake-id="uc29ce36e" id="uc29ce36e"><span data-lake-id="u84465cee" id="u84465cee">核心：注意装饰顺序，距离函数最近的装饰器，会先工作。</span></p><p data-lake-id="u3da0fe2d" id="u3da0fe2d"><span data-lake-id="u9f81f35b" id="u9f81f35b">例如下面代码：</span><code data-lake-id="u0223dff9" id="u0223dff9"><span data-lake-id="u78cd5f3c" id="u78cd5f3c">test2</span></code><span data-lake-id="u785237dc" id="u785237dc">先装饰，</span><code data-lake-id="ue6aeba1d" id="ue6aeba1d"><span data-lake-id="u2b1484f5" id="u2b1484f5">test1</span></code><span data-lake-id="u43d0f87c" id="u43d0f87c">再装饰。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22def%20test1(func)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20print('%E6%88%91%E6%98%AFtest1%E8%A3%85%E9%A5%B0%E5%99%A8')%5Cn%20%20%20%20def%20wrapper(*args%2C%20**kwargs)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20res%20%3D%20func(*args%2C%20**kwargs)%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20print('test1%E8%BF%BD%E5%8A%A0%E7%9A%84%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91')%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20return%20res%5Cn%20%20%20%20return%20wrapper%5Cn%5Cndef%20test2(func)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20print('%E6%88%91%E6%98%AFtest2%E8%A3%85%E9%A5%B0%E5%99%A8')%5Cn%20%20%20%20def%20wrapper(*args%2C%20**kwargs)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20res%20%3D%20func(*args%2C%20**kwargs)%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20print('test2%E8%BF%BD%E5%8A%A0%E7%9A%84%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91')%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20return%20res%5Cn%20%20%20%20return%20wrapper%5Cn%5Cn%40test1%5Cn%40test2%5Cndef%20add(x%2C%20y)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20res%20%3D%20x%20%2B%20y%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(f'%7Bx%7D%E5%92%8C%7By%7D%E7%9B%B8%E5%8A%A0%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C%E6%98%AF%7Bres%7D')%5Cn%20%20%20%20return%20res%5Cn%5Cnresult%20%3D%20add(10%2C%2020)%5Cnprint(result)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22mQjla%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h3 data-lake-id="ZKwUQ" id="ZKwUQ" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="uc89d0c76" id="uc89d0c76">类装饰器</span></h3><ol list="ud49c25df"><li fid="uc1652215" data-lake-id="u23a598ac" id="u23a598ac"><span data-lake-id="ub5206963" id="ub5206963">包含</span><code data-lake-id="u05f45a89" id="u05f45a89"><span data-lake-id="u847aac3c" id="u847aac3c">__call__</span></code><span data-lake-id="ua66ac2df" id="ua66ac2df">方法的类，就是类装饰器。</span></li><li fid="uc1652215" data-lake-id="u7db941f7" id="u7db941f7"><span data-lake-id="u95713650" id="u95713650">像调用函数一样，去调用类装饰器的实例对象，就会触发</span><code data-lake-id="u35a9e0d8" id="u35a9e0d8"><span data-lake-id="u835ca77d" id="u835ca77d">__call__</span></code><span data-lake-id="uc959d8a2" id="uc959d8a2">方法的调用。</span></li><li fid="uc1652215" data-lake-id="u7af3b814" id="u7af3b814"><code data-lake-id="u203804fd" id="u203804fd"><span data-lake-id="ub4febcf0" id="ub4febcf0">__call__</span></code><span data-lake-id="u62420fea" id="u62420fea">方法通常接收一个函数作为参数，并且会返回一个新函数。</span></li></ol><h4 data-lake-id="KgVr2" id="KgVr2"><span data-lake-id="ua65ac074" id="ua65ac074">1️⃣</span><span data-lake-id="u4abfe657" id="u4abfe657">定义类装饰器</span></h4><p data-lake-id="u3d92aa4e" id="u3d92aa4e"><span data-lake-id="uc58c7e22" id="uc58c7e22">需求和之前一样，还是给</span><code data-lake-id="u83ebfaaa" id="u83ebfaaa"><span data-lake-id="u27dc1801" id="u27dc1801">add</span></code><span data-lake-id="u8504933c" id="u8504933c">函数增加【打印欢迎语】的功能。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22class%20SayHello%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20def%20__call__(self%2C%20func)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20def%20wrapper(*args%2C%20**kwargs)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20print('%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%91%E8%A6%81%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E4%BA%86')%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20return%20func(*args%2C%20**kwargs)%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20return%20wrapper%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22dOLNS%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h4 data-lake-id="ZLx3t" id="ZLx3t"><span data-lake-id="u15f4f9f0" id="u15f4f9f0">2️⃣</span><span data-lake-id="u99aa766a" id="u99aa766a">使用类装饰器（手动装饰）</span></h4><p data-lake-id="uc1863f25" id="uc1863f25"><span data-lake-id="ub0bc564f" id="ub0bc564f">使用类装饰器的流程：先创建类的实例对象，随后调用实例对象，并传入要装饰的函数</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22class%20SayHello%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20def%20__call__(self%2C%20func)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20def%20wrapper(*args%2C%20**kwargs)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20print('%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%91%E8%A6%81%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E4%BA%86')%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20return%20func(*args%2C%20**kwargs)%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20return%20wrapper%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%5Cn%23%20%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%20SayHello%20%E5%8E%BB%E8%A3%85%E9%A5%B0%20add%20%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%88%E6%89%8B%E5%8A%A8%E8%A3%85%E9%A5%B0%EF%BC%89%5Cnsay%20%3D%20SayHello()%5Cnadd%20%3D%20say(add)%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E8%B0%83%E7%94%A8%E8%A3%85%E9%A5%B0%E5%90%8E%E7%9A%84%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%5Cnresult%20%3D%20add(10%2C%2020)%5Cnprint(result)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22QQBbE%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h4 data-lake-id="gARC4" id="gARC4"><span data-lake-id="udf2fd92e" id="udf2fd92e">3️⃣</span><span data-lake-id="u505305ce" id="u505305ce">使用类装饰器（语法糖 @）</span></h4><p data-lake-id="u590723fc" id="u590723fc"><span data-lake-id="u0ccc6b04" id="u0ccc6b04">通过</span><code data-lake-id="ub9e1e190" id="ub9e1e190"><span data-lake-id="u9c2ed475" id="u9c2ed475">语法糖@</span></code><span data-lake-id="udd29920f" id="udd29920f">使用装饰器时，类名后要加圆括号调用</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22class%20SayHello%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20def%20__call__(self%2C%20func)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20def%20wrapper(*args%2C%20**kwargs)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20print('%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%91%E8%A6%81%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E4%BA%86')%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20return%20func(*args%2C%20**kwargs)%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20return%20wrapper%5Cn%5Cn%40SayHello()%5Cndef%20add(x%2C%20y)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20res%20%3D%20x%20%2B%20y%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(f'%7Bx%7D%E5%92%8C%7By%7D%E7%9B%B8%E5%8A%A0%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C%E6%98%AF%7Bres%7D')%5Cn%20%20%20%20return%20res%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E4%BE%9D%E7%84%B6%E6%8C%89%E7%85%A7%E5%8E%9F%E6%9C%AC%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E8%B0%83%E7%94%A8%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86%E8%B0%83%E7%94%A8%E7%9A%84%E6%98%AF%E8%A2%AB%E8%A3%85%E9%A5%B0%E5%90%8E%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B0%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%5Cnresult%20%3D%20add(10%2C%2020)%5Cnprint(result)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22VH4rg%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h4 data-lake-id="hggtt" id="hggtt"><span data-lake-id="u728920dc" id="u728920dc">4️⃣</span><span data-lake-id="u5fb5aeef" id="u5fb5aeef">带参数的类装饰器</span></h4><p data-lake-id="ub506a26a" id="ub506a26a"><span data-lake-id="ub3adcb12" id="ub3adcb12">带参数的类装饰器写起来，要比带参数的函数装饰器简单，不需要三层嵌套结构</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22class%20SayHello%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20def%20__init__(self%2C%20msg)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20self.msg%20%3D%20msg%5Cn%5Cn%20%20%20%20def%20__call__(self%2C%20func)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20def%20wrapper(*args%2C%20**kwargs)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20print(f'%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%91%E8%A6%81%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%7Bself.msg%7D%E8%AE%A1%E7%AE%97%E4%BA%86')%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20return%20func(*args%2C%20**kwargs)%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20return%20wrapper%5Cn%5Cn%40SayHello('%E5%8A%A0%E6%B3%95')%5Cndef%20add(x%2C%20y)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20res%20%3D%20x%20%2B%20y%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(f'%7Bx%7D%E5%92%8C%7By%7D%E7%9B%B8%E5%8A%A0%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C%E6%98%AF%7Bres%7D')%5Cn%20%20%20%20return%20res%5Cn%5Cnresult%20%3D%20add(10%2C%2020)%5Cnprint(result)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22YgYN7%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h4 data-lake-id="sG80T" id="sG80T"><span data-lake-id="u7c43e634" id="u7c43e634">5️⃣</span><span data-lake-id="u7c6b9013" id="u7c6b9013">多个类装饰器一起使用</span></h4><p data-lake-id="u1a360d8e" id="u1a360d8e"><span data-lake-id="ua84a76ee" id="ua84a76ee">和之前的函数装饰器一样，离函数近的装饰器，先工作。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%AA%E7%B1%BB%E8%A3%85%E9%A5%B0%E5%99%A8%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%5Cnclass%20Test1%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20def%20__call__(self%2C%20func)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20def%20wrapper(*args%2C%20**kwargs)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20print('%E6%88%91%E6%98%AFTest1%E8%BF%BD%E5%8A%A0%E7%9A%84%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91')%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20return%20func(*args%2C%20**kwargs)%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20return%20wrapper%5Cn%5Cnclass%20Test2%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20def%20__call__(self%2C%20func)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20def%20wrapper(*args%2C%20**kwargs)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20print('%E6%88%91%E6%98%AFTest2%E8%BF%BD%E5%8A%A0%E7%9A%84%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91')%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20return%20func(*args%2C%20**kwargs)%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20return%20wrapper%5Cn%5Cn%40Test1()%5Cn%40Test2()%5Cndef%20add(x%2C%20y)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20res%20%3D%20x%20%2B%20y%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(f'%7Bx%7D%E5%92%8C%7By%7D%E7%9B%B8%E5%8A%A0%E7%9A%84%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C%E6%98%AF%7Bres%7D')%5Cn%20%20%20%20return%20res%5Cn%5Cnresult%20%3D%20add(10%2C%2020)%5Cnprint(result)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Ce8ul%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h2 data-lake-id="BMKob" id="BMKob" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u9bf09abf" id="u9bf09abf">类型注解 vs 函数类型注解</span></h2><p data-lake-id="u0fc0b653" id="u0fc0b653"><span data-lake-id="u516f6b19" id="u516f6b19"> 类型注解不会影响程序运行，它只是给人和工具看的，它可以提高代码可读性、让 IDE 智能提示更强 。</span></p><h3 data-lake-id="bbKvz" id="bbKvz" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="uece530ae" id="uece530ae">变量类型注解</span></h3><p data-lake-id="u420949ba" id="u420949ba"><span data-lake-id="uedb8d1cc" id="uedb8d1cc">语法格式：</span><code data-lake-id="ua5a8457d" id="ua5a8457d"><span data-lake-id="u0d040022" id="u0d040022">变量名: 类型 = 值</span></code><span data-lake-id="u97a284ed" id="u97a284ed">。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22num%3A%20int%20%3D%20100%5Cnprcie%3A%20float%20%3D%2012.5%5Cnmessage%3A%20str%20%3D%20'%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD%E5%95%8A'%5Cnis_vip%3A%20bool%20%3D%20True%5Cnresult%3A%20None%20%3D%20None%20%20%23%20%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95%E4%B8%8A%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86%E8%BF%99%E4%B9%88%E5%86%99%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E6%84%8F%E4%B9%89%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22DyuW6%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u327feea1" id="u327feea1"><span data-lake-id="u0ec8122c" id="u0ec8122c">注意：可以先写变量的类型注解，以后再赋值。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22school%3A%20str%5Cnprint('*******'%2C%20school)%5Cnschool%20%3D%20'%E5%B0%9A%E7%A1%85%E8%B0%B7'%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22TB2Db%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><blockquote data-lake-id="ubcf1d8ad" id="ubcf1d8ad"><p data-lake-id="u689d785f" id="u689d785f"><span data-lake-id="uf379631c" id="uf379631c">备注：上述代码中，</span><code data-lake-id="u662d482a" id="u662d482a"><span data-lake-id="uaf4b0620" id="uaf4b0620">school: str</span></code><span data-lake-id="u8072d420" id="u8072d420">并不是在定义变量，只是说明：如果未来有</span><code data-lake-id="u2109834d" id="u2109834d"><span data-lake-id="u78921c26" id="u78921c26">school</span></code><span data-lake-id="u49224b70" id="u49224b70">变量，那应该是</span><code data-lake-id="u5745bb76" id="u5745bb76"><span data-lake-id="ub854b2d9" id="ub854b2d9">str</span></code><span data-lake-id="uf00e0f45" id="uf00e0f45">类型。Python 执行到</span><code data-lake-id="ubcf052d5" id="ubcf052d5"><span data-lake-id="uad290539" id="uad290539">school = '尚硅谷'</span></code><span data-lake-id="ub918d630" id="ub918d630">这句代码时，才会真正的定义</span><code data-lake-id="uec50ecf0" id="uec50ecf0"><span data-lake-id="u0a27965a" id="u0a27965a">school</span></code><span data-lake-id="u4493d112" id="u4493d112">变量。</span></p></blockquote><p data-lake-id="u34ba75a2" id="u34ba75a2"><span data-lake-id="u3a31679a" id="u3a31679a">容器类型的注解：</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20hobby%20%E6%98%AF%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E4%B8%94%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%E5%BF%85%E9%A1%BB%E6%98%AF%20str%20%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%5Cnhobby%3A%20list%5Bstr%5D%20%3D%20%5B'%E6%8A%BD%E7%83%9F'%2C%20'%E5%96%9D%E9%85%92'%2C%20'%E7%83%AB%E5%A4%B4'%5D%5Cn%5Cn%23%20hobby%20%E6%98%AF%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E4%B8%94%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E6%98%AF%EF%BC%9Astr%20%E6%88%96%20int%20%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%5Cnhobby%3A%20list%5Bstr%20%7C%20int%5D%20%3D%20%5B'%E6%8A%BD%E7%83%9F'%2C%20'%E5%96%9D%E9%85%92'%2C%20'%E7%83%AB%E5%A4%B4'%5D%5Cn%23%20%E4%B8%8A%E9%9D%A2%E8%BF%99%E8%A1%8C%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E7%9A%84%E6%97%A7%E5%86%99%E6%B3%95%E5%A6%82%E4%B8%8B%EF%BC%9A%5Cnfrom%20typing%20import%20Union%5Cnhobby%3A%20list%5BUnion%5Bstr%2C%20int%5D%5D%20%3D%20%5B'%E6%8A%BD%E7%83%9F'%2C%20'%E5%96%9D%E9%85%92'%2C%20'%E7%83%AB%E5%A4%B4'%5D%5Cn%5Cn%23%20citys%20%E6%98%AF%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E4%B8%94%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88%E4%B8%AD%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%E5%BF%85%E9%A1%BB%E6%98%AF%20str%20%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%5Cncitys%3A%20set%5Bstr%5D%20%3D%20%7B'%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC'%2C%20'%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7'%2C%20'%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3'%7D%5Cn%5Cn%23%20citys%20%E6%98%AF%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E4%B8%94%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88%E4%B8%AD%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E6%98%AF%EF%BC%9Astr%20%E6%88%96%20float%20%E6%88%96%20bool%20%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%5Cncitys%3A%20set%5Bstr%20%7C%20float%20%7C%20bool%5D%20%3D%20%7B'%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC'%2C%20'%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7'%2C%20'%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3'%7D%5Cn%5Cn%23%20persons%20%E6%98%AF%E5%AD%97%E5%85%B8%EF%BC%8C%E9%94%AE%E6%98%AF%20str%20%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%EF%BC%8C%E5%80%BC%E6%98%AF%20int%20%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%5Cnpersons%3A%20dict%5Bstr%2C%20int%5D%20%3D%20%7B'%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89'%3A%2018%2C%20'%E6%9D%8E%E5%9B%9B'%3A%2019%2C%20'%E7%8E%8B%E4%BA%94'%3A%2020%7D%5Cn%5Cn%23%20persons%20%E6%98%AF%E5%AD%97%E5%85%B8%EF%BC%8C%E9%94%AE%E6%98%AF%20str%20%E6%88%96%20int%20%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%EF%BC%8C%E5%80%BC%E6%98%AF%20int%20%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%5Cnpersons%3A%20dict%5Bstr%20%7C%20int%2C%20int%5D%20%3D%20%7B'%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89'%3A%2018%2C%20'%E6%9D%8E%E5%9B%9B'%3A%2019%2C%20'%E7%8E%8B%E4%BA%94'%3A%2020%7D%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22nTtQQ%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u2aed2e58" id="u2aed2e58"><span data-lake-id="u4f403ecf" id="u4f403ecf">元组的类型注解有些特殊：</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20scores%20%E6%98%AF%E5%85%83%E7%BB%84%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E4%B8%94%E5%85%83%E7%BB%84%E4%B8%AD%E4%BB%85%E5%8C%85%E5%90%AB1%E4%B8%AAint%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%5Cnscores%3A%20tuple%5Bint%5D%20%3D%20(60%2C)%5Cn%5Cn%23%20scores%20%E6%98%AF%E5%85%83%E7%BB%84%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E4%B8%94%E5%85%83%E7%BB%84%E4%B8%AD%E5%8C%85%E5%90%AB3%E4%B8%AAint%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%5Cnscores%3A%20tuple%5Bint%2C%20int%2C%20int%5D%20%3D%20(60%2C%2070%2C%2080)%5Cn%5Cn%23%20scores%20%E6%98%AF%E5%85%83%E7%BB%84%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E4%B8%94%E5%85%83%E7%BB%84%E4%B8%AD%E5%8C%85%E5%90%AB%E4%BB%BB%E6%84%8F%E4%B8%AA%E6%95%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86%E6%AF%8F%E4%B8%AA%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%E7%9A%84%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%E5%BF%85%E9%A1%BB%E6%98%AFint%5Cnscores%3A%20tuple%5Bint%2C%20...%5D%20%3D%20(60%2C%2070%2C%2080%2C%2090%2C%20100)%5Cn%5Cn%23%20scores%20%E6%98%AF%E5%85%83%E7%BB%84%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B6%E4%B8%94%E5%85%83%E7%BB%84%E4%B8%AD%E5%8C%85%E5%90%AB%E4%BB%BB%E6%84%8F%E4%B8%AA%E6%95%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%EF%BC%8C%E6%AF%8F%E4%B8%AA%E5%85%83%E7%B4%A0%E7%9A%84%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E6%98%AF%EF%BC%9Aint%20%E6%88%96%20str%5Cnscores%3A%20tuple%5Bint%20%7C%20str%2C%20...%5D%20%3D%20(60%2C%20'70'%2C%2080%2C%20'90'%2C%20100)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22guw3D%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="ua598700a" id="ua598700a"><span data-lake-id="ub2cf9e4a" id="ub2cf9e4a">Python 中存在类型推导：根据变量初始赋值的实际数据，自动推断变量的类型。</span></p><ol list="u18ddbe2c"><li fid="ua0426e41" data-lake-id="u3b85b010" id="u3b85b010"><span data-lake-id="u9707d980" id="u9707d980">对于非容器变量：后续如果改变类型，不会警告。</span></li><li fid="ua0426e41" data-lake-id="u95a5c8ea" id="u95a5c8ea"><span data-lake-id="u6b87e8d2" id="u6b87e8d2">对于容器变量：要求内部元素类型必须与推导出来的一致，否则就会警告。</span></li></ol><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22x%20%3D%20100%5Cnx%20%3D%20'%E5%B0%9A%E7%A1%85%E8%B0%B7'%5Cn%5Cny%20%3D%20%5B10%2C%2020%2C%2030%5D%5Cny.append('40')%20%20%23%20%E6%AD%A4%E8%A1%8C%E4%BC%9A%E6%9C%89%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22vH82H%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h3 data-lake-id="bwyQv" id="bwyQv" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="uc9f1d89a" id="uc9f1d89a">函数类型注解</span></h3><ol list="ub2922558"><li fid="u642bf47e" data-lake-id="u5918808e" id="u5918808e"><span data-lake-id="u30542bfe" id="u30542bfe">函数类型注解：给函数的【参数】和【返回值】添加类型说明。</span></li><li fid="u642bf47e" data-lake-id="u5fb56aa2" id="u5fb56aa2"><span data-lake-id="ufb25d2a3" id="ufb25d2a3">语法格式：</span><code data-lake-id="u3cdb1ec3" id="u3cdb1ec3"><span data-lake-id="ucd3d1fd3" id="ucd3d1fd3">函数名(参数1: 类型, 参数2: 类型) -&gt; 返回值类型:</span></code></li></ol><p data-lake-id="u7af99d76" id="u7af99d76"><span data-lake-id="ub8c19db2" id="ub8c19db2">1️⃣</span><span data-lake-id="u623e38cd" id="u623e38cd">给参数和返回值加类型注解</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22def%20add(x%3A%20int%2C%20y%3A%20int)%20-%3E%20int%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20return%20x%20%2B%20y%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22brdhV%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u223400c6" id="u223400c6"><span data-lake-id="ubf040cee" id="ubf040cee">2️⃣</span><span data-lake-id="ufec5ccb9" id="ufec5ccb9"> 带默认值的参数，可以不写注解</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22def%20add(x%3D1%2C%20y%3D1)%20-%3E%20int%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20return%20x%20%2B%20y%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22DzABT%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="ua03557ba" id="ua03557ba"><span data-lake-id="ub6921043" id="ub6921043">3️⃣</span><span data-lake-id="u774e0721" id="u774e0721"> 设置多个返回值的类型注解</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22def%20show_nums_info(nums%3A%20list%5Bint%5D)%20-%3E%20tuple%5Bint%2C%20int%2C%20float%5D%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20max_v%20%3D%20max(nums)%5Cn%20%20%20%20min_v%20%3D%20min(nums)%5Cn%20%20%20%20return%20max_v%2C%20min_v%2C%20max_v%20%2F%20min_v%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22cus