collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Ir6vR%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h1 data-lake-id="Uhc3m" id="Uhc3m"><span data-lake-id="ufeac779e" id="ufeac779e">第 9 章 错误与异常</span></h1><h2 data-lake-id="irG93" id="irG93" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u2ad6c850" id="u2ad6c850"> 错误与异常</span></h2><p data-lake-id="u2f1860e6" id="u2f1860e6"><strong><span data-lake-id="u7294bde8" id="u7294bde8">错误</span></strong><span data-lake-id="ucd4fcd6f" id="ucd4fcd6f">：代码本身有语法错误，解释器无法执行代码。———— </span><strong><span data-lake-id="u2cae4e63" id="u2cae4e63" style="color: #DF2A3F">无法</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u638996a5" id="u638996a5">通过异常处理机制解决。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22age%20%3D%2018%5Cnif%20age%20%3E%3D%2018%5Cn%20%20%20%20print('%E6%88%90%E5%B9%B4%E4%BA%BA')%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22__widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ZONcX%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%2C%22widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u16fbcb78" id="u16fbcb78"><strong><span data-lake-id="u7c741898" id="u7c741898">异常：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u7f7c9e61" id="u7f7c9e61">代码在语法上没问题，但执行过程中出现了问题。———— </span><strong><span data-lake-id="u45428023" id="u45428023" style="color: #5C8D07">可以</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u568c42e5" id="u568c42e5">通过异常处理机制解决。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E4%B8%AD%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E7%9A%84%E5%BC%82%E5%B8%B8%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%201.ZeroDivisionError%EF%BC%9A%E5%BD%93%E9%99%A4%E6%95%B0%E4%B8%BA%200%20%E6%97%B6%E8%A7%A6%E5%8F%91%E3%80%82%5Cnnum1%20%3D%20100%5Cnnum2%20%3D%200%5Cnresult%20%3D%20num1%20%2F%20num2%5Cn%5Cn%23%202.TypeError%EF%BC%9A%E5%BD%93%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%E4%B8%8D%E6%AD%A3%E7%A1%AE%E6%88%96%E4%B8%8D%E5%85%BC%E5%AE%B9%E6%97%B6%E8%A7%A6%E5%8F%91%E3%80%82%5Cnresult%20%3D%20'10'%20%2B%205%5Cn%5Cn%23%203.AttributeError%3A%20%E5%BD%93%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E6%8C%87%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%E5%B1%9E%E6%80%A7%E6%88%96%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E6%97%B6%E8%A7%A6%E5%8F%91%E3%80%82%5Cn%23%20%E6%BC%94%E7%A4%BA1%5Cnclass%20Person%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20def%20__init__(self%2C%20name%2C%20age)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20self.name%20%3D%20name%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20self.age%20%3D%20age%5Cn%5Cnp1%20%3D%20Person('%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89'%2C%2018)%5Cnprint(p1.name)%5Cnprint(p1.age)%5Cnprint(p1.gender)%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E6%BC%94%E7%A4%BA2%5Cnnums%20%3D%20%5B10%2C%2020%2C%2030%5D%5Cnnums.add(40)%5Cn%5Cn%23%204.IndexError%EF%BC%9A%E5%BD%93%E7%B4%A2%E5%BC%95%E8%B6%85%E5%87%BA%E8%8C%83%E5%9B%B4%EF%BC%88%E7%B4%A2%E5%BC%95%E8%B6%8A%E7%95%8C%EF%BC%89%E6%97%B6%E8%A7%A6%E5%8F%91%E3%80%82%5Cnnums%20%3D%20%5B10%2C%2020%2C%2030%2C%2040%5D%5Cnprint(nums%5B4%5D)%5Cn%5Cn%23%205.NameError%EF%BC%9A%E5%BD%93%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%8D%E5%AD%98%E5%9C%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%E6%97%B6%E8%A7%A6%E5%8F%91%E3%80%82%5Cnprint(school)%5Cn%5Cn%23%206.KeyError%EF%BC%9A%E5%BD%93%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%E5%AD%97%E5%85%B8%E4%B8%AD%E4%B8%8D%E5%AD%98%E5%9C%A8%E7%9A%84%20key%20%E6%97%B6%E8%A7%A6%E5%8F%91%E3%80%82%5Cnperson%20%3D%20%7B'name'%3A'%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89'%2C%20'age'%3A18%7D%5Cnprint(person%5B'gender'%5D)%5Cn%5Cn%23%207.ValueError%EF%BC%9A%E5%BD%93%E5%80%BC%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%88%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%E6%AD%A3%E7%A1%AE%E6%97%B6%E8%A7%A6%E5%8F%91%E3%80%82%5Cnint('hello')%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Afalse%2C%22name%22%3A%22%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E4%B8%AD%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E7%9A%84%E5%BC%82%E5%B8%B8%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22vXgeN%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u2954602d" id="u2954602d"><span data-lake-id="u25c4900a" id="u25c4900a">Python 中异常类的继承关系（层级关系）如下（了解即可）：</span></p><blockquote data-lake-id="u8cee2b4d" id="u8cee2b4d"><p data-lake-id="u09f7dfe2" id="u09f7dfe2"><span data-lake-id="u243936cf" id="u243936cf">官方地址：</span><a href="https://docs.python.org/zh-cn/3.13/library/exceptions.html#exception-hierarchy" target="_blank" data-lake-id="ua0f3826b" id="ua0f3826b"><span data-lake-id="ub3ff350e" id="ub3ff350e">https://docs.python.org/zh-cn/3.13/library/exceptions.html#exception-hierarchy</span></a></p></blockquote><p data-lake-id="ue6483e19" id="ue6483e19"><span data-lake-id="u5073a22e" id="u5073a22e">其中：</span><code data-lake-id="u05d3167e" id="u05d3167e"><span data-lake-id="u1b4152d1" id="u1b4152d1">BaseException</span></code><span data-lake-id="ued1bdc9f" id="ued1bdc9f">是所有异常类的父类，</span><code data-lake-id="u5031fb05" id="u5031fb05"><span data-lake-id="uab294eb5" id="uab294eb5">Exception</span></code><span data-lake-id="u00c0e3a9" id="u00c0e3a9">中包含的是开发中常见的业务异常。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22plain%22%2C%22