%3A%22bTlLw%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h2 data-lake-id="rufbh" id="rufbh" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u54dffa10" id="u54dffa10">生成器</span></h2><h3 data-lake-id="KEbkX" id="KEbkX"><span data-lake-id="u3cec22a8" id="u3cec22a8">1️⃣</span><span data-lake-id="u2dda9cf9" id="u2dda9cf9">两个概念</span></h3><ol list="u019f5882"><li fid="u6b52b7bb" data-lake-id="u13d3d65a" id="u13d3d65a"><span data-lake-id="uad87a85e" id="uad87a85e">生成器函数：函数体中如果出现了</span><code data-lake-id="u7e2f81b5" id="u7e2f81b5"><span data-lake-id="u19f521a6" id="u19f521a6">yield</span></code><span data-lake-id="u12d13ed4" id="u12d13ed4">关键字，那该函数是『生成器函数』。</span></li><li fid="u6b52b7bb" data-lake-id="u4cc2228b" id="u4cc2228b"><span data-lake-id="u0f0e190b" id="u0f0e190b">生成器对象：调用『生成器函数』时，其函数体不会立刻执行，而是返回一个『生成器对象』。</span></li></ol><blockquote data-lake-id="ub2b146e8" id="ub2b146e8"><p data-lake-id="u3b9799f3" id="u3b9799f3"><span data-lake-id="u9afed611" id="u9afed611">备注：不管能否执行到</span><code data-lake-id="u98b8b724" id="u98b8b724"><span data-lake-id="u1f170389" id="u1f170389">yield</span></code><span data-lake-id="u3973ac26" id="u3973ac26">所在的位置，只要函数中有</span><code data-lake-id="u568a4018" id="u568a4018"><span data-lake-id="uc7310aa7" id="uc7310aa7">yield</span></code><span data-lake-id="u169044ce" id="u169044ce">，那该函数就是『生成器函数』。</span></p></blockquote><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22def%20demo()%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20print('demo%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%86')%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(100)%5Cn%20%20%20%20yield%5Cn%20%20%20%20a%20%3D%20200%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(a)%5Cn%5Cnd%20%3D%20demo()%5Cnprint(d)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22XQhVE%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h3 data-lake-id="DttrE" id="DttrE"><span data-lake-id="ufe96bde5" id="ufe96bde5">2️⃣</span><span data-lake-id="u9635b657" id="u9635b657">几个细节</span></h3><p data-lake-id="u1944a5a7" id="u1944a5a7"><span data-lake-id="udce5de42" id="udce5de42">写在『生成器函数』中的代码，需要通过『生成器对象』来执行：</span></p><blockquote data-lake-id="u05d1d73d" id="u05d1d73d" class="lake-alert lake-alert-info"><ol list="u018b48bb"><li fid="u117ace67" data-lake-id="u93e5902c" id="u93e5902c"><span data-lake-id="u449e8602" id="u449e8602">调用『生成器对象』的</span><code data-lake-id="uf530a2de" id="uf530a2de"><span data-lake-id="u0c7b61c4" id="u0c7b61c4">__next__</span></code><span data-lake-id="u60717b34" id="u60717b34">方法，会让『生成器函数』中的代码开始执行。</span></li><li fid="u117ace67" data-lake-id="u19494034" id="u19494034"><span data-lake-id="uaef91a29" id="uaef91a29">当『生成器函数』中的代码开始执行后，遇到</span><code data-lake-id="u477f9340" id="u477f9340"><span data-lake-id="u66541856" id="u66541856">yield</span></code><span data-lake-id="udc3e4b64" id="udc3e4b64">会“暂停”，并会记录“暂停”的位置。</span></li><li fid="u117ace67" data-lake-id="uf5a92a70" id="uf5a92a70"><span data-lake-id="uf0141967" id="uf0141967">后续调用</span><code data-lake-id="u54751baa" id="u54751baa"><span data-lake-id="u88e467f8" id="u88e467f8">__next__</span></code><span data-lake-id="u92089b7e" id="u92089b7e">方法时，都会从上一次“暂停”的位置，继续运行，直到再次遇到 yield。</span></li><li fid="u117ace67" data-lake-id="ub55efda3" id="ub55efda3"><span data-lake-id="u429b4999" id="u429b4999">遇到</span><code data-lake-id="u91a86d49" id="u91a86d49"><span data-lake-id="ud8a52955" id="ud8a52955">return</span></code><span data-lake-id="ub340dee1" id="ub340dee1">会抛出</span><code data-lake-id="ub0197558" id="ub0197558"><span data-lake-id="ued012ba3" id="ued012ba3">StopIteration</span></code><span data-lake-id="u0a555d8e" id="u0a555d8e">异常，并将</span><code data-lake-id="u177e71a2" id="u177e71a2"><span data-lake-id="ua562ef08" id="ua562ef08">return</span></code><span data-lake-id="ud6a22b56" id="ud6a22b56">后面的表达式，作为异常信息。</span></li><li fid="u117ace67" data-lake-id="u5d22e7ce" id="u5d22e7ce"><code data-lake-id="ub0059da1" id="ub0059da1"><span data-lake-id="u62e94f5d" id="u62e94f5d">yield</span></code><span data-lake-id="udc245c77" id="udc245c77">后面所写的表达式，会作为本次</span><code data-lake-id="u947550b2" id="u947550b2"><span data-lake-id="u246711b0" id="u246711b0">__next__</span></code><span data-lake-id="u401d3490" id="u401d3490">方法的返回值。</span></li></ol></blockquote><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22def%20demo()%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20print('demo%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%86')%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(100)%5Cn%20%20%20%20yield%20'%E6%88%91%E6%98%AF%E7%AC%AC1%E4%B8%AAyield%E6%89%80%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE'%5Cn%20%20%20%20a%20%3D%20200%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(a)%5Cn%20%20%20%20yield%20'%E6%88%91%E6%98%AF%E7%AC%AC2%E4%B8%AAyield%E6%89%80%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE'%5Cn%20%20%20%20b%20%3D%20300%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(b)%5Cn%20%20%20%20return%20'%E5%B0%9A%E7%A1%85%E8%B0%B7'%5Cn%5Cnd%20%3D%20demo()%5Cnr1%20%3D%20next(d)%5Cnprint(r1)%5Cnr2%20%3D%20next(d)%5Cnprint(r2)%5Cntry%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20next(d)%5Cnexcept%20StopIteration%20as%20e%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(e)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ZBRDD%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u0271fd80" id="u0271fd80"><span data-lake-id="udb57a188" id="udb57a188">生成器对象是一种特殊的迭代器（本质是通过</span><code data-lake-id="uc9f717ee" id="uc9f717ee"><span data-lake-id="u6bfbe3d0" id="u6bfbe3d0">yield</span></code><span data-lake-id="u7c04e440" id="u7c04e440">自动实现了迭代器协议）</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22def%20demo()%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20print('demo%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%86')%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(100)%5Cn%20%20%20%20yield%20'%E6%88%91%E6%98%AF%E7%AC%AC1%E4%B8%AAyield%E6%89%80%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE'%5Cn%20%20%20%20a%20%3D%20200%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(a)%5Cn%20%20%20%20yield%20'%E6%88%91%E6%98%AF%E7%AC%AC2%E4%B8%AAyield%E6%89%80%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE'%5Cn%20%20%20%20b%20%3D%20300%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(b)%5Cn%20%20%20%20return%20'%E5%B0%9A%E7%A1%85%E8%B0%B7'%5Cn%5Cnd%20%3D%20demo()%5Cn%23%20%E9%AA%8C%E8%AF%81%EF%BC%9A%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E5%99%A8%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1d%EF%BC%8C%E5%92%8C%E8%BF%AD%E4%BB%A3%E5%99%A8%E4%B8%80%E6%A0%B7%EF%BC%8C%E4%B9%9F%E6%8B%A5%E6%9C%89%EF%BC%9A__iter__%20%20%E5%92%8C%20__next__%20%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%5Cnprint(hasattr(d%2C%20'__iter__'))%5Cnprint(hasattr(d%2C%20'__next__'))%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E9%AA%8C%E8%AF%81%EF%BC%9A%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E5%99%A8%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%E7%9A%84__iter__%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%8C%E5%92%8C%E8%BF%AD%E4%BB%A3%E5%99%A8%E4%B8%80%E6%A0%B7%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E%E7%9A%84%E4%B9%9F%E6%98%AF%E8%87%AA%E8%BA%AB%5Cnresult%20%3D%20iter(d)%5Cnprint(result%20%3D%3D%20d)%5Cn%5Cn%23%20for%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E9%81%8D%E5%8E%86%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E5%99%A8%5Cnfor%20item%20in%20d%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(item)%5Cn%5Cn%23%20for%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E8%83%8C%E5%90%8E%E7%9A%84%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91%5Cngen%20%3D%20iter(d)%5Cnwhile%20True%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20try%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20value%20%3D%20next(gen)%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20print(value)%5Cn%20%20%20%20except%20StopIteration%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20break%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22MQrXu%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u7973cb88" id="u7973cb88"><code data-lake-id="u66eb79a4" id="u66eb79a4"><span data-lake-id="uc56405dd" id="uc56405dd">yield</span></code><span data-lake-id="u8b81c384" id="u8b81c384">也能写在循环里</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22region%5Cndef%20create_car(total)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20for%20index%20in%20range(1%2C%20total%20%2B%201)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20yield%20f'%E6%88%91%E6%98%AF%E7%AC%AC%7Bindex%7D%E5%8F%B0%E8%BD%A6'%5Cn%5Cn%23%20cars%E6%98%AF%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E5%99%A8%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%5Cncars%20%3D%20create_car(5)%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E8%B0%83%E7%94%A8%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1cars%E7%9A%84__next__%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%B1%E4%BC%9A%E5%BE%97%E5%88%B0%E4%B8%80%E5%8F%B0%E8%BD%A6%5Cnc1%20%3D%20next(cars)%5Cnprint(c1)%5Cnc2%20%3D%20next(cars)%5Cnprint(c2)%5Cnc3%20%3D%20next(cars)%5Cnprint(c3)%5Cnc4%20%3D%20next(cars)%5Cnprint(c4)%5Cnc5%20%3D%20next(cars)%5Cnprint(c5)%5Cn%5Cnfor%20car%20in%20cars%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(car)%5Cnendregion%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22f40YO%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="uee280bed" id="uee280bed"><code data-lake-id="uc9c31a20" id="uc9c31a20"><span data-lake-id="u9cf69749" id="u9cf69749">yield from</span></code><span data-lake-id="u604fd3f5" id="u604fd3f5">能把一个『可迭代对象』里的东西依次</span><code data-lake-id="u42252fb3" id="u42252fb3"><span data-lake-id="u07fae715" id="u07fae715">yield</span></code><span data-lake-id="u10aabf5c" id="u10aabf5c">出去。(替代：</span><code data-lake-id="u19e3ff36" id="u19e3ff36"><span data-lake-id="u15747125" id="u15747125">for + yield</span></code><span data-lake-id="u0d196916" id="u0d196916">)</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22def%20demo()%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20nums%20%3D%20%5B10%2C%2020%2C%2030%2C%2040%5D%5Cn%20%20%20%20yield%20from%20nums%5Cn%5Cnd%20%3D%20demo()%5Cnr1%20%3D%20next(d)%5Cnprint(r1)%5Cnr2%20%3D%20next(d)%5Cnprint(r2)%5Cnr3%20%3D%20next(d)%5Cnprint(r3)%5Cnr4%20%3D%20next(d)%5Cnprint(r4)%5Cn%5Cnfor%20item%20in%20d%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(item)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Li9mz%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="ufe2d1717" id="ufe2d1717"><span data-lake-id="ubee219a9" id="ubee219a9">使用：</span><code data-lake-id="u7a0b3d88" id="u7a0b3d88"><span data-lake-id="ue896885c" id="ue896885c">生成器.send(值)</span></code><span data-lake-id="u0fc0b2b9" id="u0fc0b2b9"> 可以让生成器继续执行的同时，给上一次</span><code data-lake-id="u1acb79da" id="u1acb79da"><span data-lake-id="u6e749700" id="u6e749700">yield</span></code><span data-lake-id="u201aac69" id="u201aac69">传值。</span></p><blockquote data-lake-id="ucc9ea6a6" id="ucc9ea6a6"><p data-lake-id="u089eba40" id="u089eba40"><span data-lake-id="u907cd315" id="u907cd315">备注1：</span><code data-lake-id="u745c5ca2" id="u745c5ca2"><span data-lake-id="udc76c8d4" id="udc76c8d4">next</span></code><span data-lake-id="uc1ef2823" id="uc1ef2823">只能取值，</span><code data-lake-id="u606c5ecc" id="u606c5ecc"><span data-lake-id="u7082cd50" id="u7082cd50">send</span></code><span data-lake-id="ud8c91912" id="ud8c91912">既能取值，也能送值。</span></p><p data-lake-id="ubbd87844" id="ubbd87844"><span data-lake-id="u8ba1c47c" id="u8ba1c47c">备注2：第一次启动生成器，不能传值！（或者说只能传 None 值）</span></p></blockquote><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22def%20demo()%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20print('demo%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%86')%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(100)%5Cn%20%20%20%20a%20%3D%20yield%20'%E6%88%91%E6%98%AF%E7%AC%AC1%E4%B8%AAyield%E6%89%80%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE'%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(a)%5Cn%20%20%20%20b%20%3D%20yield%20'%E6%88%91%E6%98%AF%E7%AC%AC2%E4%B8%AAyield%E6%89%80%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE'%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(b)%5Cn%20%20%20%20return%20'%E5%B0%9A%E7%A1%85%E8%B0%B7'%5Cn%5Cnd%20%3D%20demo()%5Cnr1%20%3D%20next(d)%20%23%20%E6%AD%A4%E5%A4%84%E7%AD%89%E4%BB%B7%E4%BA%8E%20d.send(None)%5Cnprint(r1)%5Cnr2%20%3D%20d.send(666)%5Cnprint(r2)%5Cntry%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20d.send(888)%5Cnexcept%20StopIteration%20as%20e%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(e)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22fn6U8%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h3 data-lake-id="si9o9" id="si9o9"><span data-lake-id="ue886d5b6" id="ue886d5b6">3️⃣</span><span data-lake-id="u0572ac94" id="u0572ac94">生成器的应用</span></h3><p data-lake-id="u23859314" id="u23859314"><span data-lake-id="u4cc0a487" id="u4cc0a487">用生成器实现遍历</span><code data-lake-id="u41f48f01" id="u41f48f01"><span data-lake-id="uc39cc6c7" id="uc39cc6c7">Person</span></code><span data-lake-id="u640dac33" id="u640dac33">类的实例对象：</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22class%20Person%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20def%20__init__(self%2C%20name%2C%20age%2C%20gender%2C%20address)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20self.name%20%3D%20name%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20self.age%20%3D%20age%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20self.gender%20%3D%20gender%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20self.address%20%3D%20address%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20self.__attr%20%3D%20%5Bname%2C%20age%2C%20gender%2C%20address%5D%5Cn%5Cn%20%20%20%20def%20__iter__(self)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%23%20yield%20self.name%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%23%20yield%20self.age%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%23%20yield%20self.gender%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%23%20yield%20self.address%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20yield%20from%20self.__attr%5Cn%5Cnp1%20%3D%20Person('%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%89'%2C%2018%2C%20'%E7%94%B7'%2C%20'%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E6%98%8C%E5%B9%B3')%5Cn%23%20%E7%9B%AE%E6%A0%87%EF%BC%9A%5Cnfor%20attr%20in%20p1%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(attr)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22hG6Fb%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="ua951114c" id="ua951114c"><span data-lake-id="u3f722588" id="u3f722588">用生成器实现斐波那契数列：</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22def%20fibo(total)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20pre%20%3D%201%5Cn%20%20%20%20cur%20%3D%201%5Cn%5Cn%20%20%20%20for%20index%20in%20range(total)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20if%20index%20%3C%202%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20yield%201%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20else%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20value%20%3D%20pre%20%2B%20cur%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20pre%20%3D%20cur%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20cur%20%3D%20value%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20yield%20value%5Cn%5Cnf1%20%3D%20fibo(10)%5Cn%5Cnfor%20item%20in%20f1%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(item)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22NWFAF%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u262ede13" id="u262ede13"><span data-lake-id="u366c833c" id="u366c833c">无论是迭代器，还是生成器对象，都可以用</span><code data-lake-id="u8d8611fe" id="u8d8611fe"><span data-lake-id="u99ab7e20" id="u99ab7e20">list</span></code><span data-lake-id="u7c983747" id="u7c983747">、</span><code data-lake-id="u1e74e544" id="u1e74e544"><span data-lake-id="ub3fe2582" id="ub3fe2582">tuple</span></code><span data-lake-id="uc1601567" id="uc1601567">、</span><code data-lake-id="u9760202c" id="u9760202c"><span data-lake-id="ue6e9e051" id="ue6e9e051">set</span></code><span data-lake-id="u37ed3d45" id="u37ed3d45">等直接拿到其里面的所有内容（注意：如果数据量很大，可能会挤爆内存）</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22def%20fibo(total)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20pre%20%3D%201%5Cn%20%20%20%20cur%20%3D%201%5Cn%5Cn%20%20%20%20for%20index%20in%20range(total)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20if%20index%20%3C%202%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20yield%201%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20else%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20value%20%3D%20pre%20%2B%20cur%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20pre%20%3D%20cur%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20cur%20%3D%20value%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20yield%20value%5Cn%5Cnf1%20%3D%20fibo(10)%5Cn%5Cnresult%20%3D%20set(f1)%5Cnprint(result)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22bSBPD%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h3 data-lake-id="Uzwx3" id="Uzwx3"><span data-lake-id="u6b9d42d8" id="u6b9d42d8">4️⃣</span><span data-lake-id="uc5185a45" id="uc5185a45">生成器表达式</span></h3><p data-lake-id="ua21ecc97" id="ua21ecc97"><span data-lake-id="u9405bab8" id="u9405bab8">生成器表达式：一种用类似列表推导式的语法，快速创建生成器对象的方式。</span></p><p data-lake-id="uc267e386" id="uc267e386"><span data-lake-id="ubdc3a913" id="ubdc3a913">语法格式：</span><code data-lake-id="ua7b69905" id="ua7b69905"><span data-lake-id="u216c30a8" id="u216c30a8">(表达式 for 变量 in 可迭代对象)</span></code><span data-lake-id="ub88aaa06" id="ub88aaa06">。</span></p><p data-lake-id="u215c9121" id="u215c9121"><span data-lake-id="u49128339" id="u49128339">什么时候适合用生成器表达式？———— 当“每个结果，只依赖当前这一个元素”时。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22nums%20%3D%20%5B10%2C%2020%2C%2030%2C%2040%5D%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8%E6%8E%A8%E5%AF%BC%E5%BC%8F%5Cnresult1%20%3D%20%5Bn%20*%202%20for%20n%20in%20nums%5D%5Cnprint(result1)%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E5%99%A8%E8%A1%A8%E8%BE%BE%E5%BC%8F%EF%BC%88%E5%92%8C%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8%E6%8E%A8%E5%AF%BC%E5%BC%8F%E5%BE%88%E5%83%8F%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E6%90%9E%E6%B7%B7%EF%BC%89%5Cnresult2%20%3D%20(n%20*%202%20for%20n%20in%20nums)%5Cn%5Cnfor%20item%20in%20result2%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(item)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22wEgSi%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><h1 data-lake-id="m78zI" id="m78zI"><span data-lake-id="ua866f8b8" id="ua866f8b8">第 12 章 文件操作</span></h1><h2 data-lake-id="QwQAx" id="QwQAx" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="ub3e548e5" id="ub3e548e5">文件的分类</span></h2><h3 data-lake-id="mphfQ" id="mphfQ"><span data-lake-id="u614ce7e3" id="u614ce7e3">1️⃣</span><strong><span data-lake-id="uef5a6db6" id="uef5a6db6">纯文本文件</span></strong></h3><blockquote data-lake-id="u3f76639f" id="u3f76639f" class="lake-alert lake-alert-info"><ol list="u22ffb6a5"><li fid="u693f98d5" data-lake-id="u780174c9" id="u780174c9"><span data-lake-id="u1bcacebd" id="u1bcacebd">读取和存储时，要遵循某种『字符编码』规范（如：UTF-8 等）进行编码和解码，最终以『二进制』的形式存储。</span></li><li fid="u693f98d5" data-lake-id="u97cf4707" id="u97cf4707"><span data-lake-id="u051b9f8e" id="u051b9f8e">『纯文本文件』最终会呈现为：可以直接阅读的文本信息。</span></li><li fid="u693f98d5" data-lake-id="u9367c649" id="u9367c649"><span data-lake-id="uc85073b1" id="uc85073b1">常见的『纯文本文件』有：</span><code data-lake-id="u400fa39f" id="u400fa39f"><span data-lake-id="uaa3c9585" id="uaa3c9585">.txt</span></code><span data-lake-id="u36c371d3" id="u36c371d3"> </span><code data-lake-id="uc3637953" id="uc3637953"><span data-lake-id="udf010b36" id="udf010b36">.py</span></code><span data-lake-id="uec7b9d6d" id="uec7b9d6d">  </span><code data-lake-id="ub5ed65f0" id="ub5ed65f0"><span data-lake-id="ub490ba9b" id="ub490ba9b">.md</span></code><span data-lake-id="u3252aa75" id="u3252aa75">  </span><code data-lake-id="u05e55d0d" id="u05e55d0d"><span data-lake-id="uae734f63" id="uae734f63">.html</span></code><span data-lake-id="u746a9e2d" id="u746a9e2d"> 等。</span></li></ol></blockquote><h3 data-lake-id="BJY8H" id="BJY8H"><span data-lake-id="u82d03a61" id="u82d03a61">2️⃣</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u62aedccf" id="u62aedccf">二进制文件</span></strong></h3><blockquote data-lake-id="uec709a20" id="uec709a20" class="lake-alert lake-alert-info"><ol list="u4cdbce4a"><li fid="u71a80160" data-lake-id="u6df41c37" id="u6df41c37"><span data-lake-id="u64475e61" id="u64475e61">读取和存储时，不涉及字符编码，会按照某种『文件格式规范』把内容转为『二进制』进行存储。</span></li><li fid="u71a80160" data-lake-id="u26167019" id="u26167019"><span data-lake-id="ub10fe7be" id="ub10fe7be">二进制文件需要由『能够识别其格式的软件』进行解析，最终的呈现形式多种多样（音频、视频、图像、幻灯片等）。</span></li><li fid="u71a80160" data-lake-id="ue1e67c02" id="ue1e67c02"><span data-lake-id="u51180beb" id="u51180beb">常见的二进制文件有：</span><code data-lake-id="ua86fcde0" id="ua86fcde0"><span data-lake-id="u60b1bd87" id="u60b1bd87">.mp3</span></code><span data-lake-id="u428926e4" id="u428926e4"> </span><code data-lake-id="u78857432" id="u78857432"><span data-lake-id="u9f9c6a52" id="u9f9c6a52">.mp4 </span></code><span data-lake-id="ua6868e0c" id="ua6868e0c"> </span><code data-lake-id="u4696d5e1" id="u4696d5e1"><span data-lake-id="uf2994f65" id="uf2994f65">.doc</span></code><span data-lake-id="ua5e950f9" id="ua5e950f9">  </span><code data-lake-id="ud01d1548" id="ud01d1548"><span data-lake-id="u4b13aba9" id="u4b13aba9">.ppt</span></code><span data-lake-id="u5a85092f" id="u5a85092f"> </span><code data-lake-id="udf43d576" id="udf43d576"><span data-lake-id="uc96f7a49" id="uc96f7a49"> .jpg</span></code><span data-lake-id="u9238c7d3" id="u9238c7d3">  </span><code data-lake-id="ua9b3ddf8" id="ua9b3ddf8"><span data-lake-id="ua827af06" id="ua827af06">.png</span></code><span data-lake-id="ua14fa663" id="ua14fa663"> 等。</span></li></ol></blockquote><h2 data-lake-id="jyIm4" id="jyIm4" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u298f5d0b" id="u298f5d0b">绝对路径 vs 相对路径</span></h2><h3 data-lake-id="RA5Rg" id="RA5Rg"><span data-lake-id="u0b636632" id="u0b636632">1️⃣</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u0f0dc230" id="u0f0dc230">绝对路径：</span></strong></h3><p data-lake-id="ueb51bf82" id="ueb51bf82"><span data-lake-id="udea61353" id="udea61353">从文件系统的『根目录』开始，完整描述文件或目录所在的位置。</span></p><blockquote data-lake-id="ubf449cce" id="ubf449cce" class="lake-alert lake-alert-tips"><p data-lake-id="u93c82818" id="u93c82818"><span data-lake-id="u12e84aaf" id="u12e84aaf">举例：</span><code data-lake-id="u4b25103d" id="u4b25103d"><span data-lake-id="u7b7a46aa" id="u7b7a46aa">D:/demo/test/a.txt</span></code><span data-lake-id="u1f5f6d91" id="u1f5f6d91">​</span></p></blockquote><h3 data-lake-id="N2gX0" id="N2gX0"><strong><span data-lake-id="ueac5cfdc" id="ueac5cfdc">2️⃣</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id="ud64ed866" id="ud64ed866">相对路径：</span></strong></h3><p data-lake-id="ubeab2f48" id="ubeab2f48"><span data-lake-id="u48837cf5" id="u48837cf5">以当前『工作目录』为参照，描述目标文件或目录相对于它的位置。</span></p><blockquote data-lake-id="uc278de9e" id="uc278de9e" class="lake-alert lake-alert-tips"><p data-lake-id="u0c5db9a8" id="u0c5db9a8"><span data-lake-id="uc36c479d" id="uc36c479d">举例：</span><code data-lake-id="ucd66ec07" id="ucd66ec07"><span data-lake-id="u09af6078" id="u09af6078">../../a.txt</span></code><span data-lake-id="udd4745ee" id="udd4745ee">（其中</span><code data-lake-id="u86ee303f" id="u86ee303f"><span data-lake-id="u4cc5cc29" id="u4cc5cc29">..</span></code><span data-lake-id="uc9cb8ec0" id="uc9cb8ec0">表示上一级目录）</span></p></blockquote><h2 data-lake-id="T7TXe" id="T7TXe" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u84599eb5" id="u84599eb5">Python 中操作文件的标准流程</span></h2><p data-lake-id="ubb220590" id="ubb220590"><span data-lake-id="u64ca7737" id="u64ca7737">标准流程成如下：</span></p><blockquote data-lake-id="u5537192d" id="u5537192d" class="lake-alert lake-alert-info"><ol list="u65bc2e0d"><li fid="ucc39dc0f" data-lake-id="u0107e18b" id="u0107e18b"><span data-lake-id="ua4df1f76" id="ua4df1f76">创建『文件对象』</span></li><li fid="ucc39dc0f" data-lake-id="u22c7f4f9" id="u22c7f4f9"><span data-lake-id="uc07bea13" id="uc07bea13">操作文件（读取、写入 等）</span></li><li fid="ucc39dc0f" data-lake-id="ucf108a59" id="ucf108a59"><span data-lake-id="u73a8e737" id="u73a8e737">关闭文件</span></li></ol></blockquote><p data-lake-id="u0aca1fe8" id="u0aca1fe8"><span data-lake-id="u4abb0765" id="u4abb0765">文件操作的核心 —— </span><code data-lake-id="u3853c1a5" id="u3853c1a5"><span data-lake-id="ud34ac251" id="ud34ac251">open</span></code><span data-lake-id="uc204f2dc" id="uc204f2dc">函数</span></p><blockquote data-lake-id="u1733d865" id="u1733d865" class="lake-alert lake-alert-color3"><p data-lake-id="u755ddf8a" id="u755ddf8a"><code data-lake-id="u106c4ddc" id="u106c4ddc"><span data-lake-id="ud64d4099" id="ud64d4099">open</span></code><span data-lake-id="ud28c6934" id="ud28c6934">函数最常用的三个参数如下：</span></p><ol list="u9026a00c"><li fid="u458f71f8" data-lake-id="udb1dc189" id="udb1dc189"><code data-lake-id="u5d38ff9b" id="u5d38ff9b"><span data-lake-id="u7301f0c7" id="u7301f0c7">file</span></code><span data-lake-id="uf0f56bcc" id="uf0f56bcc">：要操作的文件路径</span></li><li fid="u458f71f8" data-lake-id="uffb9b3e8" id="uffb9b3e8"><code data-lake-id="ue5dc02db" id="ue5dc02db"><span data-lake-id="u6d26a3e0" id="u6d26a3e0">mode</span></code><span data-lake-id="uc78e3751" id="uc78e3751">：文件的打开模式</span></li></ol><p data-lake-id="ub729286d" id="ub729286d"><span data-lake-id="u2d0c047c" id="u2d0c047c">      		</span><code data-lake-id="u4eeb80db" id="u4eeb80db"><span data-lake-id="u4f010fab" id="u4f010fab">r</span></code><span data-lake-id="u3bc736f6" id="u3bc736f6"> ：读取（默认值）</span></p><p data-lake-id="ua8ad326b" id="ua8ad326b"><span data-lake-id="u6c3fdf55" id="u6c3fdf55">      		</span><code data-lake-id="uf54ba4cb" id="uf54ba4cb"><span data-lake-id="uc80bcaf5" id="uc80bcaf5">w</span></code><span data-lake-id="u0acd8b9e" id="u0acd8b9e"> ：写入，并先截断文件</span></p><p data-lake-id="u62c13292" id="u62c13292"><span data-lake-id="ue397703f" id="ue397703f">     		</span><code data-lake-id="ucb5fd1a1" id="ucb5fd1a1"><span data-lake-id="uc75dafcf" id="uc75dafcf">x</span></code><span data-lake-id="u79af5095" id="u79af5095"> ：排它性创建，如果文件已存在，则创建失败</span></p><p data-lake-id="ue88a5bd4" id="ue88a5bd4"><span data-lake-id="ueb0143a2" id="ueb0143a2">      		</span><code data-lake-id="u53115e40" id="u53115e40"><span data-lake-id="u2ce6b783" id="u2ce6b783">a</span></code><span data-lake-id="ua752fa19" id="ua752fa19"> ：打开文件用于写入，如果文件存在，则在文件末尾追加内容</span></p><p data-lake-id="ub2a719bc" id="ub2a719bc"><span data-lake-id="u78c140cf" id="u78c140cf">      		</span><code data-lake-id="u5dd2a182" id="u5dd2a182"><span data-lake-id="uf4228d56" id="uf4228d56">b</span></code><span data-lake-id="ud55dc65a" id="ud55dc65a"> ：二进制模式</span></p><p data-lake-id="u83eff09c" id="u83eff09c"><span data-lake-id="u714651bc" id="u714651bc">    		</span><code data-lake-id="u39ee601f" id="u39ee601f"><span data-lake-id="u01e3f6b4" id="u01e3f6b4">t</span></code><span data-lake-id="u3e11c792" id="u3e11c792"> ：文本模式（默认值）</span></p><p data-lake-id="u592ab804" id="u592ab804"><span data-lake-id="uf43fec50" id="uf43fec50">      		</span><code data-lake-id="ud11df542" id="ud11df542"><span data-lake-id="uab26e943" id="uab26e943">+</span></code><span data-lake-id="ucffd2be5" id="ucffd2be5"> ：打开用于更新（读取与写入）</span></p><ol list="uc23f5145" start="3"><li fid="u12111aaf" data-lake-id="u8b4c4aeb" id="u8b4c4aeb"><code data-lake-id="u87936181" id="u87936181"><span data-lake-id="ue05664ba" id="ue05664ba">encoding</span></code><span data-lake-id="uc0eb2348" id="uc0eb2348">：字符编码</span></li></ol></blockquote><h2 data-lake-id="vjhSJ" id="vjhSJ" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="u2b5d6884" id="u2b5d6884">读取文件</span></h2><h3 data-lake-id="ibyzs" id="ibyzs"><span data-lake-id="ue6ec6d63" id="ue6ec6d63">1️⃣</span><code data-lake-id="u265586b3" id="u265586b3"><span data-lake-id="u54d0dd71" id="u54d0dd71">read</span></code><span data-lake-id="u78aae781" id="u78aae781">方法</span></h3><ul list="u870eb833"><li fid="u6f97a732" data-lake-id="ua2829683" id="ua2829683"><strong><span data-lake-id="u31bb4621" id="u31bb4621">概述：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u95437ddb" id="u95437ddb">使用『文件对象』的</span><code data-lake-id="uf5701e4b" id="uf5701e4b"><span data-lake-id="u94c0d92c" id="u94c0d92c">read</span></code><span data-lake-id="u2d1eccb5" id="u2d1eccb5">方法，读取文件中的内容。</span></li><li fid="u6f97a732" data-lake-id="u759e10bf" id="u759e10bf"><strong><span data-lake-id="u0c48ed76" id="u0c48ed76">方法说明：</span></strong></li></ul><blockquote data-lake-id="u632c70cc" id="u632c70cc" hindent="2em" class="lake-alert lake-alert-info"><ol list="uee11e880"><li fid="u73414c7c" data-lake-id="ua02a2074" id="ua02a2074"><code data-lake-id="u137fdc20" id="u137fdc20"><span data-lake-id="u524d165a" id="u524d165a">read(size)</span></code><span data-lake-id="u68fa5d1d" id="u68fa5d1d">中的</span><code data-lake-id="ub100f58c" id="ub100f58c"><span data-lake-id="u93b20304" id="u93b20304">size</span></code><span data-lake-id="u0a2b43e8" id="u0a2b43e8">是可选参数。</span></li></ol><p data-lake-id="ue32f26b2" id="ue32f26b2"><span data-lake-id="u88c50fee" id="u88c50fee">     </span><span data-lake-id="uda86e558" id="uda86e558">🔸</span><span data-lake-id="u44a15f4a" id="u44a15f4a">若不传递</span><code data-lake-id="uc1bf6bb6" id="uc1bf6bb6"><span data-lake-id="u5f366300" id="u5f366300">size</span></code><span data-lake-id="u6e43b5df" id="u6e43b5df">参数，表示：读取文件中所有的内容（注意内存占用！）。</span></p><p data-lake-id="uf45b073a" id="uf45b073a"><span data-lake-id="ub6cdf8f6" id="ub6cdf8f6">     </span><span data-lake-id="uba895bf8" id="uba895bf8">🔸</span><span data-lake-id="u611e23e8" id="u611e23e8">若传递了</span><code data-lake-id="u5af8fe7f" id="u5af8fe7f"><span data-lake-id="ue849686b" id="ue849686b">size</span></code><span data-lake-id="u09849d70" id="u09849d70">参数，表示：读取文件中指定个数的字符，或指定大小的字节。</span></p><ol list="u9bc74ac2" start="2"><li fid="ub129d63a" data-lake-id="u2b2a82d7" id="u2b2a82d7"><code data-lake-id="u4c002dfa" id="u4c002dfa"><span data-lake-id="ubbb55676" id="ubbb55676">read</span></code><span data-lake-id="u8115d400" id="u8115d400">会从上一次</span><code data-lake-id="uafe241ed" id="uafe241ed"><span data-lake-id="u23d29800" id="u23d29800">read</span></code><span data-lake-id="u28352a5e" id="u28352a5e">的位置继续读取，若到达文件末尾后继续读取，将返回空字符串。</span></li></ol></blockquote><ul list="ue83a5fc4"><li fid="ube8f592c" data-lake-id="u9cdbecc4" id="u9cdbecc4"><strong><span data-lake-id="u21056da2" id="u21056da2">示例代码：</span></strong></li></ul><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%EF%BC%9A%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E3%80%8E%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%E3%80%8F%5Cn%23%20%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E5%86%99%E6%B3%95%5Cn%23%20file%20%3D%20open(file%3D'a.txt'%2C%20mode%3D'rt'%2C%20encoding%3D'utf-8')%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E7%AE%80%E5%86%99%5Cnfile%20%3D%20open('a.txt'%2C%20'rt'%2C%20encoding%3D'utf-8')%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E7%BB%9D%E5%AF%B9%E8%B7%AF%E5%BE%84%E8%AF%BB%E5%8F%96%5Cn%23%20file%20%3D%20open('D%3A%2Ftest%2Fatguigu.txt'%2C%20'rt'%2C%20encoding%3D'utf-8')%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E8%AF%BB%E5%8F%96%E4%BA%8C%E8%BF%9B%E5%88%B6%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%5Cn%23%20file%20%3D%20open('D%3A%2Ftest%2Fgirl.jpg'%2C%20'rb')%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E6%AD%A5%EF%BC%9A%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%88%E8%AF%BB%E5%8F%96%EF%BC%89%5Cn%23%20%E5%A4%9A%E6%AC%A1%E8%B0%83%E7%94%A8read%E5%8E%BB%E9%80%90%E6%AD%A5%E8%AF%BB%E5%8F%96%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%5Cnr1%20%3D%20file.read(2)%5Cnr2%20%3D%20file.read(3)%5Cnr3%20%3D%20file.read(4)%5Cnr4%20%3D%20file.read()%5Cnprint(r1%2C%20end%3D'')%5Cnprint(r2%2C%20end%3D'')%5Cnprint(r3%2C%20end%3D'')%5Cnprint(r4%2C%20end%3D'')%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E7%94%A8%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E9%85%8D%E5%90%88%E5%A4%9A%E6%AC%A1read%EF%BC%88%E5%AF%B9%E5%86%85%E5%AD%98%E5%8F%8B%E5%A5%BD%EF%BC%89%5Cnwhile%20True%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20result%20%3D%20file.read(10)%5Cn%20%20%20%20if%20result%20%3D%3D%20''%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20break%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(result%2C%20end%3D'')%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E6%AD%A5%EF%BC%9A%E5%85%B3%E9%97%AD%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%5Cnfile.close()%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22__widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22rDexn%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%2C%22widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%7D" hindent="2em"></card><h3 data-lake-id="jl3JY" id="jl3JY"><span data-lake-id="u4338c9af" id="u4338c9af">2️⃣</span><code data-lake-id="u689b139e" id="u689b139e"><span data-lake-id="u6140fb7f" id="u6140fb7f">readline</span></code><span data-lake-id="ua30fe34a" id="ua30fe34a">方法</span></h3><ul list="u1b431269"><li fid="u70252fb0" data-lake-id="ucf3230c0" id="ucf3230c0"><strong><span data-lake-id="u4ac7aae5" id="u4ac7aae5">概述：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u571aa66f" id="u571aa66f">使用文件对象的</span><code data-lake-id="u45817353" id="u45817353"><span data-lake-id="u6d32e6b5" id="u6d32e6b5">readline</span></code><span data-lake-id="u08e22ffc" id="u08e22ffc">方法，读取文件中的一行。</span></li><li fid="u70252fb0" data-lake-id="u07cfe5d7" id="u07cfe5d7"><strong><span data-lake-id="ud655fa7d" id="ud655fa7d">方法说明：</span></strong></li></ul><blockquote data-lake-id="uff028e4a" id="uff028e4a" hindent="2em" class="lake-alert lake-alert-info"><ol list="u6bacc311"><li fid="ue123e6f3" data-lake-id="ucd1e1cb4" id="ucd1e1cb4"><code data-lake-id="u69289394" id="u69289394"><span data-lake-id="u46c27fb4" id="u46c27fb4">readline(size) </span></code><span data-lake-id="u013852eb" id="u013852eb">中的</span><code data-lake-id="u9ee5ebb9" id="u9ee5ebb9"><span data-lake-id="u5d664e6f" id="u5d664e6f">size</span></code><span data-lake-id="u5335795b" id="u5335795b">是可选参数。</span></li></ol><p data-lake-id="u4892017e" id="u4892017e"><span data-lake-id="udc155e9c" id="udc155e9c">     </span><span data-lake-id="ucdddaa2f" id="ucdddaa2f">🔸</span><span data-lake-id="u6a2a744d" id="u6a2a744d">若不传递</span><code data-lake-id="u651bf9d1" id="u651bf9d1"><span data-lake-id="u82fa8160" id="u82fa8160">size</span></code><span data-lake-id="u0cef800c" id="u0cef800c">参数，表示：读取当前这一行所有的内容。</span></p><p data-lake-id="uca0e335b" id="uca0e335b"><span data-lake-id="ufe451b9b" id="ufe451b9b">     </span><span data-lake-id="u3d5e8a0b" id="u3d5e8a0b">🔸</span><span data-lake-id="u26ca0241" id="u26ca0241">若传递了</span><code data-lake-id="ue8ad65e3" id="ue8ad65e3"><span data-lake-id="u071781c9" id="u071781c9">size</span></code><span data-lake-id="udc283e03" id="udc283e03">参数，表示：表示读取当前行时，最多能读取的字符数，或字节数</span></p><p data-lake-id="u019dbe59" id="u019dbe59"><span data-lake-id="u9f9de9a1" id="u9f9de9a1">     </span><span data-lake-id="uca1951ce" id="uca1951ce">🔸</span><span data-lake-id="uc7335629" id="uc7335629">注意：</span><code data-lake-id="u6718d1d5" id="u6718d1d5"><span data-lake-id="u8bb0b1ef" id="u8bb0b1ef">size</span></code><span data-lake-id="u4a7754e7" id="u4a7754e7">不是行数。</span></p><ol list="ubdef5afe" start="2"><li fid="u8d991057" data-lake-id="u92e2d983" id="u92e2d983"><code data-lake-id="u91e39de2" id="u91e39de2"><span data-lake-id="u842fb943" id="u842fb943">readline</span></code><span data-lake-id="u7cdd745a" id="u7cdd745a">方法，也是从上一次位置继续读取，若到达文件末尾后继续读取，返回空字符串。</span></li></ol></blockquote><ul list="uf71d102e"><li fid="u2e5bcb7f" data-lake-id="ud951effc" id="ud951effc"><strong><span data-lake-id="u0c536d87" id="u0c536d87">示例代码：</span></strong></li></ul><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%EF%BC%9A%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E3%80%8E%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%E3%80%8F%5Cnfile%20%3D%20open('a.txt'%2C%20'rt'%2C%20encoding%3D'utf-8')%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E6%AD%A5%EF%BC%9A%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%88%E8%AF%BB%E5%8F%96%EF%BC%89%5Cn%23%20%E4%BE%9D%E6%AC%A1%E8%B0%83%E7%94%A8readline%E9%80%90%E8%A1%8C%E8%AF%BB%E5%8F%96%5Cnr1%20%3D%20file.readline()%5Cnr2%20%3D%20file.readline()%5Cnr3%20%3D%20file.readline()%5Cnr4%20%3D%20file.readline()%5Cnprint(r1.strip())%5Cnprint(r2.strip())%5Cnprint(r3.strip())%5Cnprint(r4.strip())%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E9%85%8D%E5%90%88readline%E9%80%90%E8%A1%8C%E8%AF%BB%E5%8F%96%5Cnwhile%20True%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20line%20%3D%20file.readline()%5Cn%20%20%20%20if%20line%20%3D%3D%20''%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20break%5Cn%20%20%20%20%23%20print(line.strip())%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(line%2C%20end%3D'')%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E6%AD%A5%EF%BC%9A%E5%85%B3%E9%97%AD%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%5Cnfile.close()%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22__widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22CtlPF%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%2C%22widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%7D" hindent="2em"></card><h3 data-lake-id="N2Sf8" id="N2Sf8"><span data-lake-id="ueef0fc24" id="ueef0fc24">3️⃣</span><span data-lake-id="u46bf071d" id="u46bf071d">for 循环遍历文件对象</span></h3><ul list="u4f2079ed"><li fid="u18cee743" data-lake-id="u9d363930" id="u9d363930"><strong><span data-lake-id="u24b07570" id="u24b07570">概述：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="ub801c927" id="ub801c927">可以使用</span><code data-lake-id="u04060e32" id="u04060e32"><span data-lake-id="u4a7700c3" id="u4a7700c3">for</span></code><span data-lake-id="ufcdd5271" id="ufcdd5271">循环直接遍历文件对象（逐行遍历）。</span></li><li fid="u18cee743" data-lake-id="u5406b3a3" id="u5406b3a3"><strong><span data-lake-id="u8ce01790" id="u8ce01790">示例代码：</span></strong></li></ul><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%EF%BC%9A%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E3%80%8E%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%E3%80%8F%5Cnfile%20%3D%20open('a.txt'%2C%20'rt'%2C%20encoding%3D'utf-8')%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E6%AD%A5%EF%BC%9A%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%88%E8%AF%BB%E5%8F%96%EF%BC%89%5Cnfor%20line%20in%20file%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20print(line%2C%20end%3D'')%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E6%AD%A5%EF%BC%9A%E5%85%B3%E9%97%AD%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%5Cnfile.close()%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22__widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22SRmG4%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%2C%22widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%7D" hindent="2em"></card><h3 data-lake-id="EAe1b" id="EAe1b"><span data-lake-id="u93974727" id="u93974727">4️⃣</span><code data-lake-id="u0818bc08" id="u0818bc08"><span data-lake-id="ua2e1853d" id="ua2e1853d">readlines</span></code><span data-lake-id="u46c25096" id="u46c25096">方法</span></h3><ul list="u0c2d9ce4"><li fid="ud0dd2742" data-lake-id="u259ffaa9" id="u259ffaa9"><strong><span data-lake-id="uc9cc4c30" id="uc9cc4c30">概述：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="ub97dfab3" id="ub97dfab3">使用文件对象的</span><code data-lake-id="uee0a8588" id="uee0a8588"><span data-lake-id="u900b065c" id="u900b065c">readlines</span></code><span data-lake-id="ud2de508d" id="ud2de508d">方法，一次性按“行”读完，返回一个列表。</span></li><li fid="ud0dd2742" data-lake-id="ubbb1264f" id="ubbb1264f"><strong><span data-lake-id="u00f37208" id="u00f37208">方法说明：</span></strong></li></ul><blockquote data-lake-id="ud28d6b50" id="ud28d6b50" hindent="2em" class="lake-alert lake-alert-info"><ol list="u52ebc8cf"><li fid="ueb336d45" data-lake-id="ud2c99bbb" id="ud2c99bbb"><code data-lake-id="u4ff10ae7" id="u4ff10ae7"><span data-lake-id="u5dd34c77" id="u5dd34c77">readlines(hint)</span></code><span data-lake-id="ua688f835" id="ua688f835"> 中的</span><code data-lake-id="u28be63c4" id="u28be63c4"><span data-lake-id="u47a6b4df" id="u47a6b4df">hint</span></code><span data-lake-id="u8c186bad" id="u8c186bad">是可选参数。</span></li></ol><p data-lake-id="uebb1b9f6" id="uebb1b9f6"><span data-lake-id="u686f1945" id="u686f1945">      </span><span data-lake-id="ub3b58478" id="ub3b58478">🔸</span><span data-lake-id="udd406ec5" id="udd406ec5">若不传递</span><code data-lake-id="u47e6d170" id="u47e6d170"><span data-lake-id="ueec57249" id="ueec57249">hint</span></code><span data-lake-id="u5ea09b33" id="u5ea09b33">参数，表示：读取当前文件的所有行。</span></p><p data-lake-id="u27799ffc" id="u27799ffc"><span data-lake-id="u084bf7eb" id="u084bf7eb">      </span><span data-lake-id="u8e2b4ddf" id="u8e2b4ddf">🔸</span><span data-lake-id="u02210d4d" id="u02210d4d">若传递了</span><code data-lake-id="u0cb1f4fd" id="u0cb1f4fd"><span data-lake-id="ub51f7340" id="ub51f7340">hint</span></code><span data-lake-id="uc4c43e05" id="uc4c43e05">参数，表示：期望读取的【字符个数 或 字节数】（</span><code data-lake-id="uc2243eaf" id="uc2243eaf"><span data-lake-id="uae1d4347" id="uae1d4347">hint</span></code><span data-lake-id="ube929aff" id="ube929aff">不是行数）。</span></p><ol list="uab11d1d0" start="2"><li fid="u3b623be1" data-lake-id="u87054fd6" id="u87054fd6"><span data-lake-id="u64f5069a" id="u64f5069a">注意：由于</span><code data-lake-id="u7c336635" id="u7c336635"><span data-lake-id="u3d232067" id="u3d232067">readlines</span></code><span data-lake-id="ucbab7b13" id="ucbab7b13">是一次性读取文件的所有内容，所以不适合读取体积较大的文件。</span></li></ol></blockquote><ul list="u0f535eca"><li fid="uf4105766" data-lake-id="u0e7ca2ec" id="u0e7ca2ec"><strong><span data-lake-id="u42a5dd7c" id="u42a5dd7c">示例代码：</span></strong></li></ul><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%EF%BC%9A%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E3%80%8E%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%E3%80%8F%5Cnfile%20%3D%20open('a.txt'%2C%20'rt'%2C%20encoding%3D'utf-8')%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E6%AD%A5%EF%BC%9A%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%88%E8%AF%BB%E5%8F%96%EF%BC%89%5Cnresult%20%3D%20file.readlines()%5Cnprint(result)%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E6%AD%A5%EF%BC%9A%E5%85%B3%E9%97%AD%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%5Cnfile.close()%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22__widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Im1Q5%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%2C%22widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%7D" hindent="2em"></card><h3 data-lake-id="X285v" id="X285v"><span data-lake-id="u5a110c87" id="u5a110c87">⭐</span><span data-lake-id="ucd20c0b5" id="ucd20c0b5">️最佳实践</span></h3><ul list="ue876f5f9"><li fid="u17238f15" data-lake-id="u5321027b" id="u5321027b"><strong><span data-lake-id="u5c490f00" id="u5c490f00">概述：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="ucaacf269" id="ucaacf269">更推荐使用</span><code data-lake-id="u28a30025" id="u28a30025"><span data-lake-id="u0515ca2a" id="u0515ca2a">with</span></code><span data-lake-id="u5d909acf" id="u5d909acf">上下文管理器，结合</span><code data-lake-id="ud23e257f" id="ud23e257f"><span data-lake-id="uc84e2477" id="uc84e2477">for</span></code><span data-lake-id="u2698ef18" id="u2698ef18">循环遍历，逐行读取文件。</span></li></ul><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22with%20open('a.txt'%2C%20'rt'%2C%20encoding%3D'utf-8')%20as%20file%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20for%20line%20in%20file%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20print(line%2C%20end%3D'')%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22__widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ehbnM%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%2C%22widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%7D" hindent="2em"></card><h2 data-lake-id="sCHie" id="sCHie" data-lake-index-type="2"><span data-lake-id="uca22bac9" id="uca22bac9">关于</span><code data-lake-id="u7817a599" id="u7817a599"><span data-lake-id="ua0b340f5" id="ua0b340f5">with</span></code></h2><ul list="uf7e0c4b0"><li fid="u735ef5ae" data-lake-id="u13003e31" id="u13003e31"><strong><span data-lake-id="uceff437d" id="uceff437d">概述：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u797903c7" id="u797903c7">Python 中的</span><code data-lake-id="u198ec04a" id="u198ec04a"><span data-lake-id="udb6b02ac" id="udb6b02ac">with</span></code><span data-lake-id="ufda7d583" id="ufda7d583">主要用于管理程序中“需要成对出现的操作”，例如：</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id="uaadcbea8" id="uaadcbea8" style="padding-left: 2em"><span data-lake-id="ub44995f4" id="ub44995f4">   </span><span data-lake-id="u7dd7042b" id="u7dd7042b">🔸</span><span data-lake-id="u7225c1bc" id="u7225c1bc">上锁 / 解锁</span></p><p data-lake-id="u6360e468" id="u6360e468" style="padding-left: 2em"><span data-lake-id="uab6d7685" id="uab6d7685">   </span><span data-lake-id="u56105c91" id="u56105c91">🔸</span><span data-lake-id="u8eecdcc2" id="u8eecdcc2">打开 / 关闭</span></p><p data-lake-id="u6e6c39de" id="u6e6c39de" style="padding-left: 2em"><span data-lake-id="u64609360" id="u64609360">   </span><span data-lake-id="u954174fd" id="u954174fd">🔸</span><span data-lake-id="u16a1a8c7" id="u16a1a8c7">借用 / 归还</span></p><ul list="u1108a4f4"><li fid="u8c2686fb" data-lake-id="u3f0db19d" id="u3f0db19d"><strong><span data-lake-id="u88ff046b" id="u88ff046b">使用</span></strong><code data-lake-id="u10481288" id="u10481288"><strong><span data-lake-id="u8108fb9c" id="u8108fb9c">with</span></strong></code><strong><span data-lake-id="ua3bc4ca0" id="ua3bc4ca0">的目标：</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u48ee4ca2" id="u48ee4ca2">编码者只管做具体的事，“进入”和“离开”的事，让 Python 自动处理。</span></li><li fid="u8c2686fb" data-lake-id="u5d8b0dae" id="u5d8b0dae"><strong><span data-lake-id="uddd5d9d1" id="uddd5d9d1">语法格式：</span></strong></li></ul><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22with%20%E8%83%BD%E5%BE%97%E5%88%B0%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E4%B8%8A%E4%B8%8B%E6%96%87%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%99%A8%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%A8%E8%BE%BE%E5%BC%8F%20as%20%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E5%85%B7%E4%BD%93%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%8B1%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E5%85%B7%E4%BD%93%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%8B2%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E5%85%B7%E4%BD%93%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%8B3%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Afalse%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22__widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22F5ObF%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%2C%22widthMode%22%3A%22normal%22%7D" hindent="2em"></card><ul list="u4b0813c6"><li fid="ue443e9e4" data-lake-id="ub103d064" id="ub103d064"><strong><span data-lake-id="u62504f55" id="u62504f55">上下文管理器协议：</span></strong></li></ul><blockquote data-lake-id="uc1588cb3" id="uc1588cb3" hindent="2em" class="lake-alert lake-alert-info"><ol list="u06101a3b"><li fid="uf6e45843" data-lake-id="u1ade3971" id="u1ade3971"><code data-lake-id="u7a14eb9e" id="u7a14eb9e"><span data-lake-id="ub6d3acef" id="ub6d3acef">__enter__</span></code><span data-lake-id="u3da3c305" id="u3da3c305"> 方法：</span><code data-lake-id="u1b16efa1" id="u1b16efa1"><span data-lake-id="u95e52b09" id="u95e52b09">with</span></code><span data-lake-id="u83549a97" id="u83549a97">中的代码执行【之前】调用，其返回值会赋值给</span><code data-lake-id="u0f38c6f4" id="u0f38c6f4"><span data-lake-id="ufd1b13d6" id="ufd1b13d6">as</span></code><span data-lake-id="ue6e924e9" id="ue6e924e9">后的变量。</span></li><li fid="uf6e45843" data-lake-id="u9bc97c75" id="u9bc97c75"><code data-lake-id="udfffdf08" id="udfffdf08"><span data-lake-id="u35c23c3b" id="u35c23c3b">__exit__ </span></code><span data-lake-id="u38ca9c93" id="u38ca9c93"> 方法：</span><code data-lake-id="u0d11af16" id="u0d11af16"><span data-lake-id="u54debebb" id="u54debebb">with</span></code><span data-lake-id="u707a94ea" id="u707a94ea">中的代码执行【结束后】调用（无论是</span><code data-lake-id="u5ca9cccb" id="u5ca9cccb"><span data-lake-id="uf06ead70" id="uf06ead70">with</span></code><span data-lake-id="ud4ab64e3" id="ud4ab64e3">中否出现异常都会调用）。</span></li></ol></blockquote><ul list="ud072399a"><li fid="ua512f48c" data-lake-id="u07cf2e38" id="u07cf2e38"><strong><span data-lake-id="u3dd6d97b" id="u3dd6d97b">测试代码：</span></strong></li></ul><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22python%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%20Person%20%E7%B1%BB%EF%BC%8C%E8%AE%A9%E5%85%B6%E5%AE%9E%E4%BE%8B%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%E9%81%B5%E5%BE%AA%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%8A%E4%B8%8B%E6%96%87%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%99%A8%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE%5Cnclass%20Person%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20def%20__init__(self%2C%20name%2C%20age)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20self.name%20%3D%20name%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20self.age%20%3D%20age%5Cn%5Cn%20%20%20%20def%20speak(self)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20print(f'%E6%88%91%E5%8F%AB%7Bself.name%7D%EF%BC%8C%E5%B9%B4%E9%BE%84%E6%98%AF%7Bself.age%7D')%5Cn%5Cn%20%20%20%20def%20__enter__(self)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20print('-----%E6%88%91%E6%98%AF%E8%BF%9B%E5%85%A5%E7%9A%84%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91-----')%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20return%20self%5Cn%5Cn%20%20%20%20%23%20%E5%BD%93%20with%20%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%8F%91%E7%94%9F%E5%BC%82%E5%B8%B8%E6%97%B6%EF%BC%8C__exit__%20%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E7%9A%84%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E%E5%80%BC%E8%A7%84%E5%88%99%E5%A6%82%E4%B8%8B%EF%BC%9A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%23%20%20%20%F0%9F%94%B8%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E%E2%80%9C%E7%9C%9F%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%9A%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E5%BC%82%E5%B8%B8%E3%80%90%E5%B7%B2%E7%BB%8F%E3%80%91%E8%A2%AB%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%EF%BC%8C%E5%BC%82%E5%B8%B8%E3%80%90%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%9A%E3%80%91%E8%A2%AB%E7%BB%A7%E7%BB%AD%E6%8A%9B%E5%87%BA%E3%80%82%5Cn%20%20%20%20%23%20%20%20%F0%9F%94%B8%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E%E2%80%9C%E5%81%87%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%9A%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E5%BC%82%E5%B8%B8%E3%80%90%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E3%80%91%E8%A2%AB%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%EF%BC%8C%E5%BC%82%E5%B8%B8%E3%80%90%E4%BC%9A%E3%80%91%E8%A2%AB%E7%BB%A7%E7%BB%AD%E6%8A%9B%E5%87%BA%E3%80%82%5Cn%20%20%20%20def%20__exit__(self%2C%20exc_type%2C%20exc_val%2C%20exc_tb)%3A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20print('-----%E6%88%91%E6%98%AF%E7%A6%BB%E5%BC%80%E7%9A%84%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91-----')%5Cn%